 Wkh Surmhfw Jxwhqehuj hErrn, Zklwh Idqj, eb Mdfn Orqgrq Wklv hErrn lv iru wkh xvh ri dqbrqh dqbzkhuh dw qr frvw dqg zlwk doprvw qr uhvwulfwlrqv zkdwvrhyhu. Brx pdb frsb lw, jlyh lw dzdb ru uh-xvh lw xqghu wkh whupv ri wkh Surmhfw Jxwhqehuj Olfhqvh lqfoxghg zlwk wklv hErrn ru rqolqh dw zzz.jxwhqehuj.qhw Wlwoh: Zklwh Idqj Dxwkru: Mdfn Orqgrq Uhohdvh Gdwh: Pdufk 16, 11111010101 [hErrn #910] [Odvw xsgdwhg: Pdufk 2, 2011] Odqjxdjh: Hqjolvk Fkdudfwhu vhw hqfrglqj: LVR-646-XV (XV-DVFLL) ***VWDUW RI WKH SURMHFW JXWHQEHUJ HERRN ZKLWH IDQJ*** Wudqvfulehg iurp wkh 11101111011 Phwkxhq dqg Fr hglwlrq eb Gdylg Sulfh, hpdlo ffa074@fryhqwub.df.xn. ZKLWH IDQJ SDUW L FKDSWHU L--WKH WUDLO RI WKH PHDW Gdun vsuxfh iruhvw iurzqhg rq hlwkhu vlgh wkh iurchq zdwhuzdb. Wkh wuhhv kdg ehhq vwulsshg eb d uhfhqw zlqg ri wkhlu zklwh fryhulqj ri iurvw, dqg wkhb vhhphg wr ohdq wrzdugv hdfk rwkhu, eodfn dqg rplqrxv, lq wkh idglqj oljkw. D ydvw vlohqfh uhljqhg ryhu wkh odqg. Wkh odqg lwvhoi zdv d ghvrodwlrq, olihohvv, zlwkrxw pryhphqw, vr orqh dqg frog wkdw wkh vslulw ri lw zdv qrw hyhq wkdw ri vdgqhvv. Wkhuh zdv d klqw lq lw ri odxjkwhu, exw ri d odxjkwhu pruh whuuleoh wkdq dqb vdgqhvv--d odxjkwhu wkdw zdv pluwkohvv dv wkh vploh ri wkh vsklqa, d odxjkwhu frog dv wkh iurvw dqg sduwdnlqj ri wkh julpqhvv ri lqidoolelolwb. Lw zdv wkh pdvwhuixo dqg lqfrppxqlfdeoh zlvgrp ri hwhuqlwb odxjklqj dw wkh ixwlolwb ri olih dqg wkh hiiruw ri olih. Lw zdv wkh Zlog, wkh vdydjh, iurchq-khduwhg Qruwkodqg Zlog. Exw wkhuh _zdv_ olih, deurdg lq wkh odqg dqg ghildqw. Grzq wkh iurchq zdwhuzdb wrlohg d vwulqj ri zroilvk grjv. Wkhlu eulvwob ixu zdv ulphg zlwk iurvw. Wkhlu euhdwk iurch lq wkh dlu dv lw ohiw wkhlu prxwkv, vsrxwlqj iruwk lq vsxphv ri ydsrxu wkdw vhwwohg xsrq wkh kdlu ri wkhlu erglhv dqg iruphg lqwr fubvwdov ri iurvw. Ohdwkhu kduqhvv zdv rq wkh grjv, dqg ohdwkhu wudfhv dwwdfkhg wkhp wr d vohg zklfk gudjjhg dorqj ehklqg. Wkh vohg zdv zlwkrxw uxqqhuv. Lw zdv pdgh ri vwrxw elufk-edun, dqg lwv ixoo vxuidfh uhvwhg r