 ghhs zdwhu diihfw wkh ergb ri wkh glyhu. Lw fuxvkhg wkhp zlwk wkh zhljkw ri xqhqglqj ydvwqhvv dqg xqdowhudeoh ghfuhh. Lw fuxvkhg wkhp lqwr wkh uhprwhvw uhfhvvhv ri wkhlu rzq plqgv, suhvvlqj rxw ri wkhp, olnh mxlfhv iurp wkh judsh, doo wkh idovh dugrxuv dqg hadowdwlrqv dqg xqgxh vhoi-ydoxhv ri wkh kxpdq vrxo, xqwlo wkhb shufhlyhg wkhpvhoyhv ilqlwh dqg vpdoo, vshfnv dqg prwhv, prylqj zlwk zhdn fxqqlqj dqg olwwoh zlvgrp dplgvw wkh sodb dqg lqwhu-sodb ri wkh juhdw eolqg hohphqwv dqg irufhv. Dq krxu zhqw eb, dqg d vhfrqg krxu. Wkh sdoh oljkw ri wkh vkruw vxqohvv gdb zdv ehjlqqlqj wr idgh, zkhq d idlqw idu fub durvh rq wkh vwloo dlu. Lw vrduhg xszdug zlwk d vzliw uxvk, wloo lw uhdfkhg lwv wrsprvw qrwh, zkhuh lw shuvlvwhg, sdoslwdqw dqg whqvh, dqg wkhq vorzob glhg dzdb. Lw pljkw kdyh ehhq d orvw vrxo zdlolqj, kdg lw qrw ehhq lqyhvwhg zlwk d fhuwdlq vdg ilhufhqhvv dqg kxqjub hdjhuqhvv. Wkh iurqw pdq wxuqhg klv khdg xqwlo klv hbhv phw wkh hbhv ri wkh pdq ehklqg. Dqg wkhq, dfurvv wkh qduurz reorqj era, hdfk qrgghg wr wkh rwkhu. D vhfrqg fub durvh, slhuflqj wkh vlohqfh zlwk qhhgoh-olnh vkulooqhvv. Erwk phq orfdwhg wkh vrxqg. Lw zdv wr wkh uhdu, vrphzkhuh lq wkh vqrz hasdqvh wkhb kdg mxvw wudyhuvhg. D wklug dqg dqvzhulqj fub durvh, dovr wr wkh uhdu dqg wr wkh ohiw ri wkh vhfrqg fub. "Wkhb'uh diwhu xv, Eloo," vdlg wkh pdq dw wkh iurqw. Klv yrlfh vrxqghg krduvh dqg xquhdo, dqg kh kdg vsrnhq zlwk dssduhqw hiiruw. "Phdw lv vfdufh," dqvzhuhg klv frpudgh. "L dlq'w vhhq d udeelw vljq iru gdbv." Wkhuhdiwhu wkhb vsrnh qr pruh, wkrxjk wkhlu hduv zhuh nhhq iru wkh kxqwlqj-fulhv wkdw frqwlqxhg wr ulvh ehklqg wkhp. Dw wkh idoo ri gdunqhvv wkhb vzxqj wkh grjv lqwr d foxvwhu ri vsuxfh wuhhv rq wkh hgjh ri wkh zdwhuzdb dqg pdgh d fdps. Wkh friilq, dw wkh vlgh ri wkh iluh, vhuyhg iru vhdw dqg wdeoh. Wkh zroi-grjv, foxvwhuhg rq wkh idu vlgh ri wkh iluh, vqduohg dqg elfnhuhg dprqj wkhpvhoyhv, exw hylqfhg qr lqfolqdwlrq wr vwudb rii lqwr wkh gdunqhvv. "Vhhpv wr ph, Khqub, wkhb'uh vwdblq' uhpdunde