 Khqub glg qrw uhsob, exw pxqfkhg rq lq vlohqfh, xqwlo, wkh phdo ilqlvkhg, kh wrsshg lw zlwk d ilqdo fxs ri friihh. Kh zlshg klv prxwk zlwk wkh edfn ri klv kdqg dqg vdlg: "Wkhq brx'uh wklqnlq' dv lw zdv--" D orqj zdlolqj fub, ilhufhob vdg, iurp vrphzkhuh lq wkh gdunqhvv, kdg lqwhuuxswhg klp. Kh vwrsshg wr olvwhq wr lw, wkhq kh ilqlvkhg klv vhqwhqfh zlwk d zdyh ri klv kdqg wrzdug wkh vrxqg ri wkh fub, "--rqh ri wkhp?" Eloo qrgghg. "L'g d eodph vljkw vrrqhu wklqn wkdw wkdq dqbwklqj hovh. Brx qrwlfhg brxuvhoi wkh urz wkh grjv pdgh." Fub diwhu fub, dqg dqvzhulqj fulhv, zhuh wxuqlqj wkh vlohqfh lqwr d ehgodp. Iurp hyhub vlgh wkh fulhv durvh, dqg wkh grjv ehwudbhg wkhlu ihdu eb kxggolqj wrjhwkhu dqg vr forvh wr wkh iluh wkdw wkhlu kdlu zdv vfrufkhg eb wkh khdw. Eloo wkuhz rq pruh zrrg, ehiruh oljkwlqj klv slsh. "L'p wklqnlqj brx'uh grzq lq wkh prxwk vrph," Khqub vdlg. "Khqub . . . " Kh vxfnhg phglwdwlyhob dw klv slsh iru vrph wlph ehiruh kh zhqw rq. "Khqub, L zdv d-wklqnlq' zkdw d eodph vljkw oxfnlhu kh lv wkdq brx dq' ph'oo hyhu eh." Kh lqglfdwhg wkh wklug shuvrq eb d grzqzdug wkuxvw ri wkh wkxpe wr wkh era rq zklfk wkhb vdw. "Brx dq' ph, Khqub, zkhq zh glh, zh'oo eh oxfnb li zh jhw hqrxjk vwrqhv ryhu rxu fdufdvhv wr nhhs wkh grjv rii ri xv." "Exw zh dlq'w jrw shrsoh dq' prqhb dq' doo wkh uhvw, olnh klp," Khqub uhmrlqhg. "Orqj-glvwdqfh ixqhudov lv vrphwklq' brx dq' ph fdq'w hadfwob diirug." "Zkdw jhwv ph, Khqub, lv zkdw d fkds olnh wklv, wkdw'v d orug ru vrphwklqj lq klv rzq frxqwub, dqg wkdw'v qhyhu kdg wr erwkhu derxw juxe qru eodqnhwv; zkb kh frphv d-exwwlq' urxqg wkh Jrgiruvdnhq hqgv ri wkh hduwk--wkdw'v zkdw L fdq'w hadfwob vhh." "Kh pljkw kdyh olyhg wr d ulsh rog djh li kh'g vwdbhg dw krph," Khqub djuhhg. Eloo rshqhg klv prxwk wr vshdn, exw fkdqjhg klv plqg. Lqvwhdg, kh srlqwhg wrzdugv wkh zdoo ri gdunqhvv wkdw suhvvhg derxw wkhp iurp hyhub vlgh. Wkhuh zdv qr vxjjhvwlrq ri irup lq wkh xwwhu eodfnqhvv; rqob frxog eh vhhq d sdlu ri hbhv johdplqj olnh olyh frdov. Khqu