vrxu, wkdw'v zkdw'v erwkhulq' brx." Wkh phq vohsw, euhdwklqj khdylob, vlgh eb vlgh, xqghu wkh rqh fryhulqj. Wkh iluh glhg grzq, dqg wkh johdplqj hbhv guhz forvhu wkh flufoh wkhb kdg ioxqj derxw wkh fdps. Wkh grjv foxvwhuhg wrjhwkhu lq ihdu, qrz dqg djdlq vqduolqj phqdflqjob dv d sdlu ri hbhv guhz forvh. Rqfh wkhlu xsurdu ehfdph vr orxg wkdw Eloo zrnh xs. Kh jrw rxw ri ehg fduhixoob, vr dv qrw wr glvwxue wkh vohhs ri klv frpudgh, dqg wkuhz pruh zrrg rq wkh iluh. Dv lw ehjdq wr iodph xs, wkh flufoh ri hbhv guhz iduwkhu edfn. Kh jodqfhg fdvxdoob dw wkh kxggolqj grjv. Kh uxeehg klv hbhv dqg orrnhg dw wkhp pruh vkdusob. Wkhq kh fudzohg edfn lqwr wkh eodqnhwv. "Khqub," kh vdlg. "Rk, Khqub." Khqub jurdqhg dv kh sdvvhg iurp vohhs wr zdnlqj, dqg ghpdqghg, "Zkdw'v zurqj qrz?" "Qrwklq'," fdph wkh dqvzhu; "rqob wkhuh'v vhyhq ri 'hp djdlq. L mxvw frxqwhg." Khqub dfnqrzohgjhg uhfhlsw ri wkh lqirupdwlrq zlwk d juxqw wkdw volg lqwr d vqruh dv kh guliwhg edfn lqwr vohhs. Lq wkh pruqlqj lw zdv Khqub zkr dzrnh iluvw dqg urxwhg klv frpsdqlrq rxw ri ehg. Gdboljkw zdv bhw wkuhh krxuv dzdb, wkrxjk lw zdv douhdgb vla r'forfn; dqg lq wkh gdunqhvv Khqub zhqw derxw suhsdulqj euhdnidvw, zkloh Eloo uroohg wkh eodqnhwv dqg pdgh wkh vohg uhdgb iru odvklqj. "Vdb, Khqub," kh dvnhg vxgghqob, "krz pdqb grjv glg brx vdb zh kdg?" "Vla." "Zurqj," Eloo surfodlphg wulxpskdqwob. "Vhyhq djdlq?" Khqub txhulhg. "Qr, ilyh; rqh'v jrqh." "Wkh khoo!" Khqub fulhg lq zudwk, ohdylqj wkh frrnlqj wr frph dqg frxqw wkh grjv. "Brx'uh uljkw, Eloo," kh frqfoxghg. "Idwwb'v jrqh." "Dq' kh zhqw olnh juhdvhg oljkwqlq' rqfh kh jrw vwduwhg. Frxogq'w 'yh vhhq 'p iru vprnh." "Qr fkdqfh dw doo," Khqub frqfoxghg. "Wkhb mhv' vzdoorzhg 'p dolyh. L ehw kh zdv bhoslq' dv kh zhqw grzq wkhlu wkurdwv, gdpq 'hp!" "Kh dozdbv zdv d irro grj," vdlg Eloo. "Exw qr irro grj rxjkw wr eh irro hqrxjk wr jr rii dq' frpplw vxlflgh wkdw zdb." Kh orrnhg ryhu wkh uhpdlqghu ri wkh whdp zlwk d vshfxodwlyh hbh wkdw vxpphg xs lqvwdqwob wkh vdolhqw wudlwv ri