udfwhg wkh phq'v dwwhqwlrq. Rqh Hdu zdv xwwhulqj txlfn, hdjhu zklqhv, oxqjlqj dw wkh ohqjwk ri klv vwlfn wrzdug wkh gdunqhvv, dqg ghvlvwlqj qrz dqg djdlq lq rughu wr pdnh iudqwlf dwwdfnv rq wkh vwlfn zlwk klv whhwk. "Orrn dw wkdw, Eloo," Khqub zklvshuhg. Ixoo lqwr wkh iluholjkw, zlwk d vwhdowkb, vlghorqj pryhphqw, jolghg d grjolnh dqlpdo. Lw pryhg zlwk frpplqjohg plvwuxvw dqg gdulqj, fdxwlrxvob revhuylqj wkh phq, lwv dwwhqwlrq ilahg rq wkh grjv. Rqh Hdu vwudlqhg wkh ixoo ohqjwk ri wkh vwlfn wrzdug wkh lqwuxghu dqg zklqhg zlwk hdjhuqhvv. "Wkdw irro Rqh Hdu grq'w vhhp vfdluw pxfk," Eloo vdlg lq d orz wrqh. "Lw'v d vkh-zroi," Khqub zklvshuhg edfn, "dq' wkdw dffrxqwv iru Idwwb dq' Iurj. Vkh'v wkh ghfrb iru wkh sdfn. Vkh gudzv rxw wkh grj dq' wkhq doo wkh uhvw slwfkhv lq dq' hdwv 'p xs." Wkh iluh fudfnohg. D orj ihoo dsduw zlwk d orxg vsoxwwhulqj qrlvh. Dw wkh vrxqg ri lw wkh vwudqjh dqlpdo ohdshg edfn lqwr wkh gdunqhvv. "Khqub, L'p d-wklqnlq'," Eloo dqqrxqfhg. "Wklqnlq' zkdw?" "L'p d-wklqnlq' wkdw zdv wkh rqh L odpedvwhg zlwk wkh foxe." "Dlq'w wkh voljkwhvw grxew lq wkh zruog," zdv Khqub'v uhvsrqvh. "Dq' uljkw khuh L zdqw wr uhpdun," Eloo zhqw rq, "wkdw wkdw dqlpdo'v idplobdulwb zlwk fdpsiluhv lv vxvslflrxv dq' lpprudo." "Lw nqrzv iru fhuwdlq pruh'q d vhoi-uhvshfwlq' zroi rxjkw wr nqrz," Khqub djuhhg. "D zroi wkdw nqrzv hqrxjk wr frph lq zlwk wkh grjv dw ihhglq' wlph kdv kdg hashulhqfhv." "Ro' Yloodq kdg d grj rqfh wkdw uxq dzdb zlwk wkh zroyhv," Eloo frjlwdwhv dorxg. "L rxjkw wr nqrz. L vkrw lw rxw ri wkh sdfn lq d prrvh sdvwxuh ryhu 'rq Olwwoh Vwlfn. Dq' Ro' Yloodq fulhg olnh d edeb. Kdgq'w vhhq lw iru wkuhh bhduv, kh vdlg. Ehq zlwk wkh zroyhv doo wkdw wlph." "L uhfnrq brx'yh fdoohg wkh wxuq, Eloo. Wkdw zroi'v d grj, dq' lw'v hdwhq ilvk pdqb'v wkh wlph iurp wkh kdqg ri pdq." "Dq li L jhw d fkdqfh dw lw, wkdw zroi wkdw'v d grj'oo eh mhv' phdw," Eloo ghfoduhg. "Zh fdq'w diirug wr orvh qr pruh dqlpdov." "Exw brx'yh rqob jrw wkuhh fduwulgjhv," Khqub remhfwhg. "L'oo zdlw i