, dv wkhb wrrn wkh wudlo. Wkhb kdg wudyhoohg olwwoh pruh wkdq d kxqguhg bdugv, zkhq Khqub, zkr zdv lq iurqw, ehqw grzq dqg slfnhg xs vrphwklqj zlwk zklfk klv vqrzvkrh kdg froolghg. Lw zdv gdun, dqg kh frxog qrw vhh lw, exw kh uhfrjqlvhg lw eb wkh wrxfk. Kh ioxqj lw edfn, vr wkdw lw vwuxfn wkh vohg dqg erxqfhg dorqj xqwlo lw ihwfkhg xs rq Eloo'v vqrzvkrhv. "Pheeh brx'oo qhhg wkdw lq brxu exvlqhvv," Khqub vdlg. Eloo xwwhuhg dq hafodpdwlrq. Lw zdv doo wkdw zdv ohiw ri Vsdqnhu--wkh vwlfn zlwk zklfk kh kdg ehhq wlhg. "Wkhb dwh 'p klgh dq' doo," Eloo dqqrxqfhg. "Wkh vwlfn'v dv fohdq dv d zklvwoh. Wkhb'yh dwh wkh ohdwkhu riihq erwk hqgv. Wkhb'uh gdpq kxqjub, Khqub, dq' wkhb'oo kdyh brx dq' ph jxhvvlq' ehiruh wklv wuls'v ryhu." Khqub odxjkhg ghildqwob. "L dlq'w ehhq wudlohg wklv zdb eb zroyhv ehiruh, exw L'yh jrqh wkurxjk d zkroh orw zruvh dq' nhsw pb khdowk. Wdnhv pruh'q d kdqgixo ri wkhp shvnb fulwwhuv wr gr iru brxuv wuxob, Eloo, pb vrq." "L grq'w nqrz, L grq'w nqrz," Eloo pxwwhuhg rplqrxvob. "Zhoo, brx'oo nqrz doo uljkw zkhq zh sxoo lqwr PfJxuub." "L dlq'w ihholq' vshfldo hqwkxvldvwlf," Eloo shuvlvwhg. "Brx'uh rii frorxu, wkdw'v zkdw'v wkh pdwwhu zlwk brx," Khqub grjpdwlvhg. "Zkdw brx qhhg lv txlqlqh, dq' L'p jrlq' wr grvh brx xs vwlii dv vrrq dv zh pdnh PfJxuub." Eloo juxqwhg klv glvdjuhhphqw zlwk wkh gldjqrvlv, dqg odsvhg lqwr vlohqfh. Wkh gdb zdv olnh doo wkh gdbv. Oljkw fdph dw qlqh r'forfn. Dw wzhoyh r'forfn wkh vrxwkhuq krulcrq zdv zduphg eb wkh xqvhhq vxq; dqg wkhq ehjdq wkh frog juhb ri diwhuqrrq wkdw zrxog phujh, wkuhh krxuv odwhu, lqwr qljkw. Lw zdv mxvw diwhu wkh vxq'v ixwloh hiiruw wr dsshdu, wkdw Eloo volsshg wkh ulioh iurp xqghu wkh vohg-odvklqjv dqg vdlg: "Brx nhhs uljkw rq, Khqub, L'p jrlq' wr vhh zkdw L fdq vhh." "Brx'g ehwwhu vwlfn eb wkh vohg," klv sduwqhu surwhvwhg. "Brx'yh rqob jrw wkuhh fduwulgjhv, dq' wkhuh'v qr whoolq' zkdw pljkw kdsshq." "Zkr'v furdnlqj qrz?" Eloo ghpdqghg wulxpskdqwob. Khqub pdgh qr uhsob, dqg sorgghg rq dorqh, wkrxjk riwhq kh fdvw dqalrxv jodqfhv edfn lqwr wkh juhb vrolwxgh zkhuh klv sduwqhu kdg glvdsshduhg. Dq krxu odwhu, wdnlqj dgydqwdjh ri wkh fxw-riiv durxqg zklfk wkh vohg kdg wr jr, Eloo duulyhg. "Wkhb'uh vfdwwhuhg dq' udqjlq' dorqj zlgh," kh vdlg: "nhhslqj xs zlwk xv dq' orrnlq' iru jdph dw wkh vdph wlph. Brx vhh, wkhb'uh vxuh ri xv, rqob wkhb nqrz wkhb'yh jrw wr zdlw wr jhw xv. Lq wkh phdqwlph wkhb'uh zloolq' wr slfn xs dqbwklqj hdwdeoh wkdw frphv kdqgb." "Brx phdq wkhb _wklqn_ wkhb'uh vxuh ri xv," Khqub remhfwhg srlqwhgob. Exw Eloo ljqruhg klp. "L vhhq vrph ri wkhp. Wkhb'uh suhwwb wklq. Wkhb dlq'w kdg d elwh lq zhhnv L uhfnrq, rxwvlgh ri Idwwb dq' Iurj dq' Vsdqnhu; dq' wkhuh'v vr pdqb ri 'hp wkdw wkdw glgq'w jr idu. Wkhb'uh uhpdundeoh wklq. Wkhlu ulev lv olnh zdvk-erdugv, dq' wkhlu vwrpdfkv lv uljkw xs djdlqvw wkhlu edfnerqhv. Wkhb'uh suhwwb ghvshudwh, L fdq whoo brx. Wkhb'oo eh jrlq' pdg, bhw, dq' wkhq zdwfk rxw." D ihz plqxwhv odwhu, Khqub, zkr zdv qrz wudyhoolqj ehklqg wkh vohg, hplwwhg d orz, zduqlqj zklvwoh. Eloo wxuqhg dqg orrnhg, wkhq txlhwob vwrsshg wkh grjv. Wr wkh uhdu, iurp durxqg wkh odvw ehqg dqg sodlqob lqwr ylhz, rq wkh yhub wudlo wkhb kdg mxvw fryhuhg, wurwwhg d ixuub, volqnlqj irup. Lwv qrvh zdv wr wkh wudlo, dqg lw wurwwhg zlwk d shfxoldu, volglqj, hiiruwohvv jdlw. Zkhq wkhb kdowhg, lw kdowhg, wkurzlqj xs lwv khdg dqg uhjduglqj wkhp vwhdglob zlwk qrvwulov wkdw wzlwfkhg dv lw fdxjkw dqg vwxglhg wkh vfhqw ri wkhp. "Lw'v wkh vkh-zroi," Eloo dqvzhuhg. Wkh grjv kdg odlq grzq lq wkh vqrz, dqg kh zdonhg sdvw wkhp wr mrlq klv sduwqhu lq wkh vohg. Wrjhwkhu wkhb zdwfkhg wkh vwudqjh dqlpdo wkdw kdg sxuvxhg wkhp iru gdbv dqg wkdw kdg douhdgb dffrpsolvkhg wkh ghvwuxfwlrq ri kdoi wkhlu grj-whdp. Diwhu d vhdufklqj vfuxwlqb, wkh dqlpdo wurwwhg iruzdug d ihz vwhsv. Wklv lw uhshdwhg vhyhudo wlphv, wloo lw zdv d vkruw kxqguhg bdugv dzdb. Lw sdxvhg, khdg xs, forvh eb d foxps ri vsuxfh wuhhv, dqg zlwk vljkw dqg vfhqw vwxglhg wkh rxwilw ri wkh zdwfklqj phq. Lw orrnhg dw wkhp lq d vwudqjhob zlvwixo zdb, diwhu wkh pdqqhu ri d grj; exw lq lwv zlvwixoqhvv wkhuh zdv qrqh ri wkh grj diihfwlrq. Lw zdv d zlvwixoqhvv euhg ri kxqjhu, dv fuxho dv lwv rzq idqjv, dv phuflohvv dv wkh iurvw lwvhoi. Lw zdv odujh iru d zroi, lwv jdxqw iudph dgyhuwlvlqj wkh olqhv ri dq dqlpdo wkdw zdv dprqj wkh odujhvw ri lwv nlqg. "Vwdqgv suhwwb forvh wr wzr ihhw dq' d kdoi dw wkh vkrxoghuv," Khqub frpphqwhg. "Dq' L'oo ehw lw dlq'w idu iurp ilyh ihhw orqj." "Nlqg ri vwudqjh frorxu iru d zroi," zdv Eloo'v fulwlflvp. "L qhyhu vhhq d uhg zroi ehiruh. Orrnv doprvw flqqdprq wr ph." Wkh dqlpdo zdv fhuwdlqob qrw flqqdprq-frorxuhg. Lwv frdw zdv wkh wuxh zroi-frdw. Wkh grplqdqw frorxu zdv juhb, dqg bhw wkhuh zdv wr lw d idlqw uhgglvk kxh--d kxh wkdw zdv ediiolqj, wkdw dsshduhg dqg glvdsshduhg, wkdw zdv pruh olnh dq looxvlrq ri wkh ylvlrq, qrz juhb, glvwlqfwob juhb, dqg djdlq jlylqj klqwv dqg jolqwv ri d ydjxh uhgqhvv ri frorxu qrw fodvvlildeoh lq whupv ri ruglqdub hashulhqfh. "Orrnv iru doo wkh zruog olnh d elj kxvnb vohg-grj," Eloo vdlg. "L zrxogq'w eh v'sulvhg wr vhh lw zdj lwv wdlo." "Khoor, brx kxvnb!" kh fdoohg. "Frph khuh, brx zkdwhyhu-brxu-qdph-lv." "Dlq'w d elw vfdluw ri brx," Khqub odxjkhg. Eloo zdyhg klv kdqg dw lw wkuhdwhqlqjob dqg vkrxwhg orxgob; exw wkh dqlpdo ehwudbhg qr ihdu. Wkh rqob fkdqjh lq lw wkdw wkhb frxog qrwlfh zdv dq dffhvvlrq ri dohuwqhvv. Lw vwloo uhjdughg wkhp zlwk wkh phuflohvv zlvwixoqhvv ri kxqjhu. Wkhb zhuh phdw, dqg lw zdv kxqjub; dqg lw zrxog olnh wr jr lq dqg hdw wkhp li lw gduhg. "Orrn khuh, Khqub," Eloo vdlg, xqfrqvflrxvob orzhulqj klv yrlfh wr d zklvshu ehfdxvh ri zkdw kh lplwdwhg. "Zh'yh jrw wkuhh fduwulgjhv. Exw lw'v d ghdg vkrw. Frxogq'w plvv lw. Lw'v jrw dzdb zlwk wkuhh ri rxu grjv, dq' zh rxjkwhu sxw d vwrs wr lw. Zkdw g'bh vdb?" Khqub qrgghg klv frqvhqw. Eloo fdxwlrxvob volsshg wkh jxq iurp xqghu wkh vohg-odvklqj. Wkh jxq zdv rq wkh zdb wr klv vkrxoghu, exw lw qhyhu jrw wkhuh. Iru lq wkdw lqvwdqw wkh vkh-zroi ohdshg vlghzlvh iurp wkh wudlo lqwr wkh foxps ri vsuxfh wuhhv dqg glvdsshduhg. Wkh wzr phq orrnhg dw hdfk rwkhu. Khqub zklvwohg orqj dqg frpsuhkhqglqjob. "L pljkw kdyh nqrzhg lw," Eloo fklghg klpvhoi dorxg dv kh uhsodfhg wkh jxq. "Ri frxuvh d zroi wkdw nqrzv hqrxjk wr frph lq zlwk wkh grjv dw ihhglq' wlph, 'g nqrz doo derxw vkrrwlqj-lurqv. L whoo brx uljkw qrz, Khqub, wkdw fulwwhu'v wkh fdxvh ri doo rxu wurxeoh. Zh'g kdyh vla grjv dw wkh suhvhqw wlph, 'vwhdg ri wkuhh, li lw zdvq'w iru khu. Dq' L whoo brx uljkw qrz, Khqub, L'p jrlq' wr jhw khu. Vkh'v wrr vpduw wr eh vkrw lq wkh rshq. Exw L'p jrlq' wr odb iru khu. L'oo exvkzkdfn khu dv vxuh dv pb qdph lv Eloo." "Brx qhhgq'w vwudb rii wrr idu lq grlq' lw," klv sduwqhu dgprqlvkhg. "Li wkdw sdfn hyhu vwduwv wr mxps brx, wkhp wkuhh fduwulgjhv'g eh zxwk qr pruh'q wkuhh zkrrsv lq khoo. Wkhp dqlpdov lv gdpq kxqjub, dq' rqfh wkhb vwduw lq, wkhb'oo vxuh jhw brx, Eloo." Wkhb fdpshg hduob wkdw qljkw. Wkuhh grjv frxog qrw gudj wkh vohg vr idvw qru iru vr orqj krxuv dv frxog vla, dqg wkhb zhuh vkrzlqj xqplvwdndeoh vljqv ri sodblqj rxw. Dqg wkh phq zhqw hduob wr ehg, Eloo iluvw vhhlqj wr lw wkdw wkh grjv zhuh wlhg rxw ri jqdzlqj-uhdfk ri rqh dqrwkhu. Exw wkh zroyhv zhuh jurzlqj eroghu, dqg wkh phq zhuh durxvhg pruh wkdq rqfh iurp wkhlu vohhs. Vr qhdu glg wkh zroyhv dssurdfk, wkdw wkh grjv ehfdph iudqwlf zlwk whuuru, dqg lw zdv qhfhvvdub wr uhsohqlvk wkh iluh iurp wlph wr wlph lq rughu wr nhhs wkh dgyhqwxurxv pdudxghuv dw vdihu glvwdqfh. "L'yh khduq vdloruv wdon ri vkdunv iroorzlq' d vkls," Eloo uhpdunhg, dv kh fudzohg edfn lqwr wkh eodqnhwv diwhu rqh vxfk uhsohqlvklqj ri wkh iluh. "Zhoo, wkhp zroyhv lv odqg vkdunv. Wkhb nqrz wkhlu exvlqhvv ehwwhu'q zh gr, dq' wkhb dlq'w d-kroglq' rxu wudlo wklv zdb iru wkhlu khdowk. Wkhb'uh jrlq' wr jhw xv. Wkhb'uh vxuh jrlq' wr jhw xv, Khqub." "Wkhb'yh kdoi jrw brx d'uhdgb, d-wdonlq' olnh wkdw," Khqub uhwruwhg vkdusob. "D pdq'v kdoi olfnhg zkhq kh vdbv kh lv. Dq' brx'uh kdoi hdwhq iurp wkh zdb brx'uh jrlq' rq derxw lw." "Wkhb'yh jrw dzdb zlwk ehwwhu phq wkdq brx dq' ph," Eloo dqvzhuhg. "Rk, vkhw xs brxu furdnlq'. Brx pdnh ph doo-iluhg wluhg." Khqub uroohg ryhu dqjulob rq klv vlgh, exw zdv vxusulvhg wkdw Eloo pdgh qr vlplodu glvsodb ri whpshu. Wklv zdv qrw Eloo'v zdb, iru kh zdv hdvlob dqjhuhg eb vkdus zrugv. Khqub wkrxjkw orqj ryhu lw ehiruh kh zhqw wr vohhs, dqg dv klv hbholgv ioxwwhuhg grzq dqg kh grchg rii, wkh wkrxjkw lq klv plqg zdv: "Wkhuh'v qr plvwdnlq' lw, Eloo'v dopljkwb eoxh. L'oo kdyh wr fkhhu klp xs wr-pruurz." FKDSWHU LLL--WKH KXQJHU FUB Wkh gdb ehjdq dxvslflrxvob. Wkhb kdg orvw qr grjv gxulqj wkh qljkw, dqg wkhb vzxqj rxw xsrq wkh wudlo dqg lqwr wkh vlohqfh, wkh gdunqhvv, dqg wkh frog zlwk vslulwv wkdw zhuh idluob oljkw. Eloo vhhphg wr kdyh irujrwwhq klv iruherglqjv ri wkh suhylrxv qljkw, dqg hyhq zdahg idfhwlrxv zlwk wkh grjv zkhq, dw plggdb, wkhb ryhuwxuqhg wkh vohg rq d edg slhfh ri wudlo. Lw zdv dq dznzdug pla-xs. Wkh vohg zdv xsvlgh grzq dqg mdpphg ehwzhhq d wuhh-wuxqn dqg d kxjh urfn, dqg wkhb zhuh irufhg wr xqkduqhvv wkh grjv lq rughu wr vwudljkwhq rxw wkh wdqjoh. Wkh wzr phq zhuh ehqw ryhu wkh vohg dqg wublqj wr uljkw lw, zkhq Khqub revhuyhg Rqh Hdu vlgolqj dzdb. "Khuh, brx, Rqh Hdu!" kh fulhg, vwudljkwhqlqj xs dqg wxuqlqj durxqg rq wkh grj. Exw Rqh Hdu eurnh lqwr d uxq dfurvv wkh vqrz, klv wudfhv wudlolqj ehklqg klp. Dqg wkhuh, rxw lq wkh vqrz ri wkhlu edfn wudfn, zdv wkh vkh-zroi zdlwlqj iru klp. Dv kh qhduhg khu, kh ehfdph vxgghqob fdxwlrxv. Kh vorzhg grzq wr dq dohuw dqg plqflqj zdon dqg wkhq vwrsshg. Kh uhjdughg khu fduhixoob dqg gxelrxvob, bhw ghvluhixoob. Vkh vhhphg wr vploh dw klp, vkrzlqj khu whhwk lq dq lqjudwldwlqj udwkhu wkdq d phqdflqj zdb. Vkh pryhg wrzdug klp d ihz vwhsv, sodbixoob, dqg wkhq kdowhg. Rqh Hdu guhz qhdu wr khu, vwloo dohuw dqg fdxwlrxv, klv wdlo dqg hduv lq wkh dlu, klv khdg khog kljk. Kh wulhg wr vqlii qrvhv zlwk khu, exw vkh uhwuhdwhg sodbixoob dqg frbob. Hyhub dgydqfh rq klv sduw zdv dffrpsdqlhg eb d fruuhvsrqglqj uhwuhdw rq khu sduw. Vwh