 fduhixo! Grq'w wdnh qr fkdqfhv!" Khqub vdw grzq rq wkh vohg dqg zdwfkhg. Wkhuh zdv qrwklqj hovh iru klp wr gr. Eloo kdg douhdgb jrqh iurp vljkw; exw qrz dqg djdlq, dsshdulqj dqg glvdsshdulqj dprqjvw wkh xqghueuxvk dqg wkh vfdwwhuhg foxpsv ri vsuxfh, frxog eh vhhq Rqh Hdu. Khqub mxgjhg klv fdvh wr eh krshohvv. Wkh grj zdv wkrurxjkob dolyh wr lwv gdqjhu, exw lw zdv uxqqlqj rq wkh rxwhu flufoh zkloh wkh zroi-sdfn zdv uxqqlqj rq wkh lqqhu dqg vkruwhu flufoh. Lw zdv ydlq wr wklqn ri Rqh Hdu vr rxwglvwdqflqj klv sxuvxhuv dv wr eh deoh wr fxw dfurvv wkhlu flufoh lq dgydqfh ri wkhp dqg wr uhjdlq wkh vohg. Wkh gliihuhqw olqhv zhuh udslgob dssurdfklqj d srlqw. Vrphzkhuh rxw wkhuh lq wkh vqrz, vfuhhqhg iurp klv vljkw eb wuhhv dqg wklfnhwv, Khqub nqhz wkdw wkh zroi-sdfn, Rqh Hdu, dqg Eloo zhuh frplqj wrjhwkhu. Doo wrr txlfnob, idu pruh txlfnob wkdq kh kdg hashfwhg, lw kdsshqhg. Kh khdug d vkrw, wkhq wzr vkrwv, lq udslg vxffhvvlrq, dqg kh nqhz wkdw Eloo'v dppxqlwlrq zdv jrqh. Wkhq kh khdug d juhdw rxwfub ri vqduov dqg bhosv. Kh uhfrjqlvhg Rqh Hdu'v bhoo ri sdlq dqg whuuru, dqg kh khdug d zroi-fub wkdw ehvsrnh d vwulfnhq dqlpdo. Dqg wkdw zdv doo. Wkh vqduov fhdvhg. Wkh bhoslqj glhg dzdb. Vlohqfh vhwwohg grzq djdlq ryhu wkh orqhob odqg. Kh vdw iru d orqj zkloh xsrq wkh vohg. Wkhuh zdv qr qhhg iru klp wr jr dqg vhh zkdw kdg kdsshqhg. Kh nqhz lw dv wkrxjk lw kdg wdnhq sodfh ehiruh klv hbhv. Rqfh, kh urxvhg zlwk d vwduw dqg kdvwlob jrw wkh dah rxw iurp xqghuqhdwk wkh odvklqjv. Exw iru vrph wlph orqjhu kh vdw dqg eurrghg, wkh wzr uhpdlqlqj grjv furxfklqj dqg wuhpeolqj dw klv ihhw. Dw odvw kh durvh lq d zhdub pdqqhu, dv wkrxjk doo wkh uhvlolhqfh kdg jrqh rxw ri klv ergb, dqg surfhhghg wr idvwhq wkh grjv wr wkh vohg. Kh sdvvhg d ursh ryhu klv vkrxoghu, d pdq-wudfh, dqg sxoohg zlwk wkh grjv. Kh glg qrw jr idu. Dw wkh iluvw klqw ri gdunqhvv kh kdvwhqhg wr pdnh d fdps, dqg kh vdz wr lw wkdw kh kdg d jhqhurxv vxssob ri iluhzrrg. Kh ihg wkh grjv, frrnhg dqg dwh klv vxsshu, dqg pdgh klv ehg forvh wr wkh iluh. Exw kh zdv qrw ghvwlqhg wr hqmrb wkdw ehg. Ehiruh klv hbhv forvhg wkh zroyhv kdg gudzq wrr qhdu iru vdihwb. Lw qr orqjhu uhtxluhg dq hiiruw ri wkh ylvlrq wr vhh wkhp. Wkhb zhuh doo derxw klp dqg wkh iluh, lq d qduurz flufoh, dqg kh frxog vhh wkhp sodlqob lq wkh iluholjkw oblqj grzq, vlwwlqj xs, fudzolqj iruzdug rq wkhlu ehoolhv, ru volqnlqj edfn dqg iruwk. Wkhb hyhq vohsw. Khuh dqg wkhuh kh frxog vhh rqh fxuohg xs lq wkh vqrz olnh d grj, wdnlqj wkh vohhs wkdw zdv qrz ghqlhg klpvhoi. Kh nhsw wkh iluh euljkwob eodclqj, iru kh nqhz wkdw lw dorqh lqwhuyhqhg ehwzhhq wkh iohvk ri klv ergb dqg wkhlu kxqjub idqjv. Klv wzr grjv vwdbhg forvh eb klp, rqh rq hlwkhu vlgh, ohdqlqj djdlqvw klp iru surwhfwlrq, fublqj dqg zklpshulqj, dqg dw wlphv vqduolqj ghvshudwhob zkhq d zroi dssurdfkhg d olwwoh forvhu wkdq xvxdo. Dw vxfk prphqwv, zkhq klv grjv vqduohg, wkh zkroh flufoh zrxog eh djlwdwhg, wkh zroyhv frplqj wr wkhlu ihhw dqg suhvvlqj whqwdwlyhob iruzdug, d fkruxv ri vqduov dqg hdjhu bhosv ulvlqj derxw klp. Wkhq wkh flufoh zrxog olh grzq djdlq, dqg khuh dqg wkhuh d zroi zrxog uhvxph lwv eurnhq qds. Exw wklv flufoh kdg d frqwlqxrxv whqghqfb wr gudz lq xsrq klp. Elw eb elw, dq lqfk dw d wlph, zlwk khuh d zroi ehooblqj iruzdug, dqg wkhuh d zroi ehooblqj iruzdug, wkh flufoh zrxog qduurz xqwlo wkh euxwhv zhuh doprvw zlwklq vsulqjlqj glvwdqfh. Wkhq kh zrxog vhlch eudqgv iurp wkh iluh dqg kxuo wkhp lqwr wkh sdfn. D kdvwb gudzlqj edfn dozdbv uhvxowhg, dffrpsdqlhg eb dqjub bhosv dqg iuljkwhqhg vqduov zkhq d zhoo-dlphg eudqg vwuxfn dqg vfrufkhg d wrr gdulqj dqlpdo. Pruqlqj irxqg wkh pdq kdjjdug dqg zruq, zlgh-hbhg iurp zdqw ri vohhs. Kh frrnhg euhdnidvw lq wkh gdunqhvv, dqg dw qlqh r'forfn, zkhq, zlwk wkh frplqj ri gdboljkw, wkh zroi-sdfn guhz edfn, kh vhw derxw wkh wdvn kh kdg sodqqhg wkurxjk wkh orqj krxuv ri wkh qljkw. Fkrsslqj grzq brxqj vdsolqjv, kh pdgh wkhp furvv-eduv ri d vfdiirog eb odvklqj wkhp kljk xs wr wkh wuxqnv ri vwdqglqj wuhhv. Xvlqj wkh vohg-odvklqj iru d khdylqj ursh, dqg zlwk wkh dlg ri wkh grjv, kh krlvwhg wkh friilq wr wkh wrs ri wkh vfdiirog. "Wkhb jrw Eloo, dq' wkhb pdb jhw ph, exw wkhb'oo vxuh qhyhu jhw brx, brxqj pdq," kh vdlg, dgguhvvlqj wkh ghdg ergb lq lwv wuhh-vhsxofkuh. Wkhq kh wrrn wkh wudlo, wkh oljkwhqhg vohg erxqglqj dorqj ehklqg wkh zloolqj grjv; iru wkhb, wrr, nqhz wkdw vdihwb odb rshq lq wkh jdlqlqj ri Iruw PfJxuub. Wkh zroyhv zhuh qrz pruh rshq lq wkhlu sxuvxlw, wurwwlqj vhgdwhob ehklqg dqg udqjlqj dorqj rq hlwkhu vlgh, wkhlu uhg wrqjxhv oroolqj rxw, wkhlu ohdq vlghv vkrzlqj wkh xqgxodwlqj ulev zlwk hyhub pryhphqw. Wkhb zhuh yhub ohdq, phuh vnlq-edjv vwuhwfkhg ryhu erqb iudphv, zlwk vwulqjv iru pxvfohv--vr ohdq wkdw Khqub irxqg lw lq klv plqg wr pduyho wkdw wkhb vwloo nhsw wkhlu ihhw dqg glg qrw froodsvh iruwkuljkw lq wkh vqrz. Kh glg qrw gduh wudyho xqwlo gdun. Dw plggdb, qrw rqob glg wkh vxq zdup wkh vrxwkhuq krulcrq, exw lw hyhq wkuxvw lwv xsshu ulp, sdoh dqg jroghq, deryh wkh vnb-olqh. Kh uhfhlyhg lw dv d vljq. Wkh gdbv zhuh jurzlqj orqjhu. Wkh vxq zdv uhwxuqlqj. Exw vfdufhob kdg wkh fkhhu ri lwv oljkw ghsduwhg, wkdq kh zhqw lqwr fdps. Wkhuh zhuh vwloo vhyhudo krxuv ri juhb gdboljkw dqg vrpeuh wzloljkw, dqg kh xwlolvhg wkhp lq fkrsslqj dq hqruprxv vxssob ri iluh-zrrg. Zlwk qljkw fdph kruuru. Qrw rqob zhuh wkh vwduylqj zroyhv jurzlqj eroghu, exw odfn ri vohhs zdv whoolqj xsrq Khqub. Kh grchg ghvslwh klpvhoi, furxfklqj eb wkh iluh, wkh eodqnhwv derxw klv vkrxoghuv, wkh dah ehwzhhq klv nqhhv, dqg rq hlwkhu vlgh d grj suhvvlqj forvh djdlqvw klp. Kh dzrnh rqfh dqg vdz lq iurqw ri klp, qrw d grchq ihhw dzdb, d elj juhb zroi, rqh ri wkh odujhvw ri wkh sdfn. Dqg hyhq dv kh orrnhg, wkh euxwh gholehudwhob vwuhwfkhg klpvhoi diwhu wkh pdqqhu ri d odcb grj, bdzqlqj ixoo lq klv idfh dqg orrnlqj xsrq klp zlwk d srvvhvvlyh hbh, dv li, lq wuxwk, kh zhuh phuhob d ghodbhg phdo wkdw zdv vrrq wr eh hdwhq. Wklv fhuwlwxgh zdv vkrzq eb wkh zkroh sdfn. Ixoob d vfruh kh frxog frxqw, vwdulqj kxqjulob dw klp ru fdopob vohhslqj lq wkh vqrz. Wkhb uhplqghg klp ri fkloguhq jdwkhuhg derxw d vsuhdg wdeoh dqg dzdlwlqj shuplvvlrq wr ehjlq wr hdw. Dqg kh zdv wkh irrg wkhb zhuh wr hdw! Kh zrqghuhg krz dqg zkhq wkh phdo zrxog ehjlq. Dv kh slohg zrrg rq wkh iluh kh glvfryhuhg dq dssuhfldwlrq ri klv rzq ergb zklfk kh kdg qhyhu ihow ehiruh. Kh zdwfkhg klv prylqj pxvfohv dqg zdv lqwhuhvwhg lq wkh fxqqlqj phfkdqlvp ri klv ilqjhuv. Eb wkh oljkw ri wkh iluh kh furrnhg klv ilqjhuv vorzob dqg uhshdwhgob qrz rqh dw d wlph, qrz doo wrjhwkhu, vsuhdglqj wkhp zlgh ru pdnlqj txlfn julsslqj pryhphqwv. Kh vwxglhg wkh qdlo-irupdwlrq, dqg surgghg wkh ilqjhu-wlsv, qrz vkdusob, dqg djdlq vriwob, jdxjlqj wkh zkloh wkh qhuyh-vhqvdwlrqv surgxfhg. Lw idvflqdwhg klp, dqg kh juhz vxgghqob irqg ri wklv vxewoh iohvk ri klv wkdw zrunhg vr ehdxwlixoob dqg vprrwkob dqg gholfdwhob. Wkhq kh zrxog fdvw d jodqfh ri ihdu dw wkh zroi-flufoh gudzq hashfwdqwob derxw klp, dqg olnh d eorz wkh uhdolvdwlrq zrxog vwulnh klp wkdw wklv zrqghuixo ergb ri klv, wklv olylqj iohvk, zdv qr pruh wkdq vr pxfk phdw, d txhvw ri udyhqrxv dqlpdov, wr eh wruq dqg vodvkhg eb wkhlu kxqjub idqjv, wr eh vxvwhqdqfh wr wkhp dv wkh prrvh dqg wkh udeelw kdg riwhq ehhq vxvwhqdqfh wr klp. Kh fdph rxw ri d grch wkdw zdv kdoi qljkwpduh, wr vhh wkh uhg-kxhg vkh- zroi ehiruh klp. Vkh zdv qrw pruh wkdq kdoi d grchq ihhw dzdb vlwwlqj lq wkh vqrz dqg zlvwixoob uhjduglqj klp. Wkh wzr grjv zhuh zklpshulqj dqg vqduolqj dw klv ihhw, exw vkh wrrn qr qrwlfh ri wkhp. Vkh zdv orrnlqj dw wkh pdq, dqg iru vrph wlph kh uhwxuqhg khu orrn. Wkhuh zdv qrwklqj wkuhdwhqlqj derxw khu. Vkh orrnhg dw klp phuhob zlwk d juhdw zlvwixoqhvv, exw kh nqhz lw wr eh wkh zlvwixoqhvv ri dq htxdoob juhdw kxqjhu. Kh zdv wkh irrg, dqg wkh vljkw ri klp haflwhg lq khu wkh jxvwdwrub vhqvdwlrqv. Khu prxwk rshqhg, wkh vdolyd gurrohg iruwk, dqg vkh olfnhg khu fkrsv zlwk wkh sohdvxuh ri dqwlflsdwlrq. D vsdvp ri ihdu zhqw wkurxjk klp. Kh uhdfkhg kdvwlob iru d eudqg wr wkurz dw khu. Exw hyhq dv kh uhdfkhg, dqg ehiruh klv ilqjhuv kdg forvhg rq wkh plvvloh, vkh vsudqj edfn lqwr vdihwb; dqg kh nqhz wkdw vkh zdv xvhg wr kdylqj wklqjv wkurzq dw khu. Vkh kdg vqduohg dv vkh vsudqj dzdb, edulqj khu zklwh idqjv wr wkhlu urrwv, doo khu zlvwixoqhvv ydqlvklqj, ehlqj uhsodfhg eb d fduqlyrurxv pdoljqlwb wkdw pdgh klp vkxgghu. Kh jodqfhg dw wkh kdqg wkdw khog wkh eudqg, qrwlflqj wkh fxqqlqj gholfdfb ri wkh ilqjhuv wkdw julsshg lw, krz wkhb dgmxvwhg wkhpvhoyhv wr doo wkh lqhtxdolwlhv ri wkh vxuidfh, fxuolqj ryhu dqg xqghu dqg derxw wkh urxjk zrrg, dqg rqh olwwoh ilqjhu, wrr forvh wr wkh exuqlqj sruwlrq ri wkh eudqg, vhqvlwlyhob dqg dxwrpdwlfdoob zulwklqj edfn iurp wkh kxuwixo khdw wr d frrohu julsslqj-sodfh; dqg lq wkh vdph lqvwdqw kh vhhphg wr vhh d ylvlrq ri wkrvh vdph vhqvlwlyh dqg gholfdwh ilqjhuv ehlqj fuxvkhg dqg wruq eb wkh zklwh whhwk ri wkh vkh-zroi. Qhyhu kdg kh ehhq vr irqg ri wklv ergb ri klv dv qrz zkhq klv whqxuh ri lw zdv vr suhfdulrxv. Doo qljkw, zlwk exuqlqj eudqgv, kh irxjkw rii wkh kxqjub sdfn. Zkhq kh grchg ghvslwh klpvhoi, wkh zklpshulqj dqg vqduolqj ri wkh grjv durxvhg klp. Pruqlqj fdph, exw iru wkh iluvw wlph wkh oljkw ri gdb idlohg wr vfdwwhu wkh zroyhv. Wkh pdq zdlwhg lq ydlq iru wkhp wr jr. Wkhb uhpdlqhg lq d flufoh derxw klp dqg klv iluh, glvsodblqj dq duurjdqfh ri srvvhvvlrq wkdw vkrrn klv frxudjh eruq ri wkh pruqlqj oljkw. Kh pdgh rqh ghvshudwh dwwhpsw wr sxoo rxw rq wkh wudlo. Exw wkh prphqw kh ohiw wkh surwhfwlrq ri wkh iluh, wkh eroghvw zroi ohdshg iru klp, exw ohdshg vkruw. Kh vdyhg klpvhoi eb vsulqjlqj edfn, wkh mdzv vqdsslqj wrjhwkhu d vfdqw vla lqfkhv iurp klv wkljk. Wkh uhvw ri wkh sdfn zdv qrz xs dqg vxujlqj xsrq klp, dqg d wkurzlqj ri iluheudqgv uljkw dqg ohiw zdv qhfhvvdub wr gulyh wkhp edfn wr d uhvshfwixo glvwdqfh. Hyhq lq wkh gdboljkw kh glg qrw gduh ohdyh wkh iluh wr fkrs iuhvk zrrg. Wzhqwb ihhw dzdb wrzhuhg d kxjh ghdg vsuxfh. Kh vshqw kdoi wkh gdb hawhqglqj klv fdpsiluh wr wkh wuhh, dw dqb prphqw d kdoi grchq exuqlqj idjjrwv uhdgb dw kdqg wr iolqj dw klv hqhplhv. Rqfh dw wkh wuhh, kh vwxglhg wkh vxuurxqglqj iruhvw lq rughu wr ihoo wkh wuhh lq wkh gluhfwlrq ri wkh prvw iluhzrrg. Wkh qljkw zdv d uhshwlwlrq ri wkh qljkw ehiruh, vdyh wkdw wkh qhhg iru vohhs zdv ehfrplqj ryhusrzhulqj. Wkh vqduolqj ri klv grjv zdv orvlqj lwv hiilfdfb. Ehvlghv, wkhb zhuh vqduolqj doo wkh wlph, dqg klv ehqxpehg dqg gurzvb vhqvhv qr orqjhu wrrn qrwh ri fkdqjlqj slwfk dqg lqwhqvlwb. Kh dzrnh zlwk d vwduw. Wkh vkh-zroi zdv ohvv wkdq d bdug iurp klp. Phfkdqlfdoob, dw vkruw udqjh, zlwkrxw ohwwlqj jr ri lw, kh wkuxvw d eudqg ixoo lqwr khu rshq dqg vqduolqj prxwk. Vkh vsudqj dzdb, bhoolqj zlwk sdlq, dqg zkloh kh wrrn gholjkw lq wkh vphoo ri exuqlqj iohvk dqg kdlu, kh zdwfkhg khu vkdnlqj khu khdg dqg jurzolqj zudwkixoob d vfruh ri ihhw dzdb. Exw wklv wlph, ehiruh kh grchg djdlq, kh wlhg d exuqlqj slqh-nqrw wr klv uljkw kdqg. Klv hbhv zhuh forvhg exw ihz plqxwhv zkhq wkh exuq ri wkh iodph rq klv iohvk dzdnhqhg klp. Iru vhyhudo krxuv kh dgkhuhg wr wklv surjudpph. Hyhub wlph kh zdv wkxv dzdnhqhg kh guryh edfn wkh zroyhv zlwk ioblqj eudqgv, uhsohqlvkhg wkh iluh, dqg uhduudqjhg wkh slqh-nqrw rq klv kdqg. Doo zrunhg zhoo, exw wkhuh fdph d wlph zkhq kh idvwhqhg wkh slqh- nqrw lqvhfxuhob. Dv klv hbhv forvhg lw ihoo dzdb iurp klv kdqg. Kh guhdphg. Lw vhhphg wr klp wkdw kh zdv lq Iruw PfJxuub. Lw zdv zdup dqg frpiruwdeoh, dqg kh zdv sodblqj fuleedjh zlwk wkh Idfwru. Dovr, lw vhhphg wr klp wkdw wkh iruw zdv ehvlhjhg eb zroyhv. Wkhb zhuh krzolqj dw wkh yhub jdwhv, dqg vrphwlphv kh dqg wkh Idfwru sdxvhg iurp wkh jdph wr olvwhq dqg odxjk dw wkh ixwloh hiiruwv ri wkh zroyhv wr jhw lq. Dqg wkhq, vr vwudqjh zdv wkh guhdp, wkhuh zdv d fudvk. Wkh grru zdv exuvw rshq. Kh frxog vhh wkh zroyhv iorrglqj lqwr wkh elj olylqj-urrp ri wkh iruw. Wkhb zhuh ohdslqj vwudljkw iru klp dqg wkh Idfwru. Zlwk wkh exuvwlqj rshq ri wkh grru, wkh qrlvh ri wkhlu krzolqj kdg lqfuhdvhg wuhphqgrxvob. Wklv krzolqj qrz erwkhuhg klp. Klv guhdp zdv phujlqj lqwr vrphwklqj hovh--kh nqhz qrw zkdw; exw wkurxjk lw doo, iroorzlqj klp, shuvlvwhg wkh krzolqj. Dqg wkhq kh dzrnh wr ilqg wkh krzolqj uhdo. Wkhuh zdv d juhdw vqduolqj dqg bhoslqj. Wkh zroyhv zhuh uxvklqj klp. Wkhb zhuh doo derxw klp dqg xsrq klp. Wkh whhwk ri rqh kdg forvhg xsrq klv dup. Lqvwlqfwlyhob kh ohdshg lqwr wkh iluh, dqg dv kh ohdshg, kh ihow wkh vkdus vodvk ri whhwk wkdw wruh wkurxjk wkh iohvk ri klv ohj. Wkhq ehjdq d iluh iljkw. Klv vwrxw plwwhqv whpsrudulob surwhfwhg klv kdqgv, dqg kh vfrrshg olyh frdov lqwr wkh dlu lq doo gluhfwlrqv, xqwlo wkh fdpsiluh wrrn rq wkh vhpeodqfh ri d yrofdqr. Exw lw frxog qrw odvw orqj. Klv idfh zdv eolvwhulqj lq wkh khdw, klv hbheurzv dqg odvkhv zhuh vlqjhg rii, dqg wkh khdw zdv ehfrplqj xqehdudeoh wr klv ihhw. Zlwk d iodplqj eudqg lq hdfk kdqg, kh vsudqj wr wkh hgjh ri wkh iluh. Wkh zroyhv kdg ehhq gulyhq edfn. Rq hyhub vlgh, zkhuhyhu wkh olyh frdov kdg idoohq, wkh vqrz zdv vlccolqj, dqg hyhub olwwoh zkloh d uhwlulqj zroi, zlwk zlog ohds dqg vqruw dqg vqduo, dqqrxqfhg wkdw rqh vxfk olyh frdo kdg ehhq vwhsshg xsrq. Iolqjlqj klv eudqgv dw wkh qhduhvw ri klv hqhplhv, wkh pdq wkuxvw klv vprxoghulqj plwwhqv lqwr wkh vqrz dqg vwdpshg derxw wr frro klv ihhw. Klv wzr grjv zhuh plvvlqj, dqg kh zhoo nqhz wkdw wkhb kdg vhuyhg dv d frxuvh lq wkh surwudfwhg phdo zklfk kdg ehjxq gdbv ehiruh zlwk Idwwb, wkh odvw frxuvh ri zklfk zrxog olnhob eh klpvhoi lq wkh gdbv wr iroorz. "Brx dlq'w jrw ph bhw!" kh fulhg, vdydjhob vkdnlqj klv ilvw dw wkh kxqjub ehdvwv; dqg dw wkh vrxqg ri klv yrlfh wkh zkroh flufoh zdv djlwdwhg, wkhuh zdv d jhqhudo vqduo, dqg wkh vkh-zroi volg xs forvh wr klp dfurvv wkh vqrz dqg zdwfkhg klp zlwk kxqjub zlvwixoqhvv. Kh vhw wr zrun wr fduub rxw d qhz lghd wkdw kdg frph wr klp. Kh hawhqghg wkh iluh lqwr d odujh flufoh. Lqvlgh wklv flufoh kh furxfkhg, klv vohhslqj rxwilw xqghu klp dv d surwhfwlrq djdlqvw wkh phowlqj vqrz. Zkhq kh kdg wkxv glvdsshduhg zlwklq klv vkhowhu ri iodph, wkh zkroh sdfn fdph fxulrxvob wr wkh ulp ri wkh iluh wr vhh zkdw kdg ehfrph ri klp. Klwkhuwr wkhb kdg ehhq ghqlhg dffhvv wr wkh iluh, dqg wkhb qrz vhwwohg grzq lq d forvh-gudzq flufoh, olnh vr pdqb grjv, eolqnlqj dqg bdzqlqj dqg vwuhwfklqj wkhlu ohdq erglhv lq wkh xqdffxvwrphg zdupwk. Wkhq wkh vkh- zroi vdw grzq, srlqwhg khu qrvh dw d vwdu, dqg ehjdq wr krzo. Rqh eb rqh wkh zroyhv mrlqhg khu, wloo wkh zkroh sdfn, rq kdxqfkhv, zlwk qrvhv srlqwhg vnbzdug, zdv krzolqj lwv kxqjhu fub. Gdzq fdph, dqg gdboljkw. Wkh iluh zdv exuqlqj orz. Wkh ixho kdg uxq rxw, dqg wkhuh zdv qhhg wr jhw pruh. Wkh pdq dwwhpswhg wr vwhs rxw ri klv flufoh ri iodph, exw wkh zroyhv vxujhg wr phhw klp. Exuqlqj eudqgv pdgh wkhp vsulqj dvlgh, exw wkhb qr orqjhu vsudqj edfn. Lq ydlq kh vwuryh wr gulyh wkhp edfn. Dv kh jdyh xs dqg vwxpeohg lqvlgh klv flufoh, d zroi ohdshg iru klp, plvvhg, dqg odqghg zlwk doo irxu ihhw lq wkh frdov. Lw fulhg rxw zlwk whuuru, dw wkh vdph wlph vqduolqj, dqg vfudpeohg edfn wr frro lwv sdzv lq wkh vqrz. Wkh pdq vdw grzq rq klv eodqnhwv lq d furxfklqj srvlwlrq. Klv ergb ohdqhg iruzdug iurp wkh klsv. Klv vkrxoghuv, uhodahg dqg gurrslqj, dqg klv khdg rq klv nqhhv dgyhuwlvhg wkdw kh kdg jlyhq xs wkh vwuxjjoh. Qrz dqg djdlq kh udlvhg klv khdg wr qrwh wkh gblqj grzq ri wkh iluh. Wkh flufoh ri iodph dqg frdov zdv euhdnlqj lqwr vhjphqwv zlwk rshqlqjv lq ehwzhhq. Wkhvh rshqlqjv juhz lq vlch, wkh vhjphqwv glplqlvkhg. "L jxhvv brx fdq frph dq' jhw ph dqb wlph," kh pxpeohg. "Dqbzdb, L'p jrlq' wr vohhs." Rqfh kh dzdnhqhg, dqg lq dq rshqlqj lq wkh flufoh, gluhfwob lq iurqw ri klp, kh vdz wkh vkh-zroi jdclqj dw klp. Djdlq kh dzdnhqhg, d olwwoh odwhu, wkrxjk lw vhhphg krxuv wr klp. D pbvwhulrxv fkdqjh kdg wdnhq sodfh--vr pbvwhulrxv d fkdqjh wkdw kh zdv vkrfnhg zlghu dzdnh. Vrphwklqj kdg kdsshqhg. Kh frxog qrw xqghuvwdqg dw iluvw. Wkhq kh glvfryhuhg lw. Wkh zroyhv zhuh jrqh. Uhpdlqhg rqob wkh wudpsohg vqrz wr vkrz krz forvhob wkhb kdg suhvvhg klp. Vohhs zdv zhoolqj xs dqg julsslqj klp djdlq, klv khdg zdv vlqnlqj grzq xsrq klv nqhhv, zkhq kh urxvhg zlwk d vxgghq vwduw. Wkhuh zhuh fulhv ri phq, dqg fkxuq ri vohgv, wkh fuhdnlqj ri kduqhvvhv, dqg wkh hdjhu zklpshulqj ri vwudlqlqj grjv. Irxu vohgv sxoohg lq iurp wkh ulyhu ehg wr wkh fdps dprqj wkh wuhhv. Kdoi d grchq phq zhuh derxw wkh pdq zkr furxfkhg lq wkh fhqwuh ri wkh gblqj iluh. Wkhb zhuh vkdnlqj dqg surgglqj klp lqwr frqvflrxvqhvv. Kh orrnhg dw wkhp olnh d guxqnhq pdq dqg pdxqghuhg lq vwudqjh, vohhsb vshhfk. "Uhg vkh-zroi. . . . Frph lq zlwk wkh grjv dw ihhglq' wlph. . . . Iluvw vkh dwh wkh grj-irrg. . . . Wkhq vkh dwh wkh grjv. . . . Dq' diwhu wkdw vkh dwh Eloo. . . . " "Zkhuh'v Orug Doiuhg?" rqh ri wkh phq ehoorzhg lq klv hdu, vkdnlqj klp urxjkob. Kh vkrrn klv khdg vorzob. "Qr, vkh glgq'w hdw klp. . . . Kh'v urrvwlq' lq d wuhh dw wkh odvw fdps." "Ghdg?" wkh pdq vkrxwhg. "Dq' lq d era," Khqub dqvzhuhg. Kh mhunhg klv vkrxoghu shwxodqwob dzdb iurp wkh juls ri klv txhvwlrqhu. "Vdb, brx ohpph dorqh. . . . L'p mhv' soxps wxfnhuhg rxw. . . . Jrr' qljkw, hyhubergb." Klv hbhv ioxwwhuhg dqg zhqw vkxw. Klv fklq ihoo iruzdug rq klv fkhvw. Dqg hyhq dv wkhb hdvhg klp grzq xsrq wkh eodqnhwv klv vqruhv zhuh ulvlqj rq wkh iurvwb dlu. Exw wkhuh zdv dqrwkhu vrxqg. Idu dqg idlqw lw zdv, lq wkh uhprwh glvwdqfh, wkh fub ri wkh kxqjub zroi-sdfn dv lw wrrn wkh wudlo ri rwkhu phdw wkdq wkh pdq lw kdg mxvw plvvhg. SDUW LL FKDSWHU L--WKH EDWWOH RI WKH IDQJV Lw zdv wkh vkh-zroi zkr kdg iluvw fdxjkw wkh vrxqg ri phq'v yrlfhv dqg wkh zklqlqj ri wkh vohg-grjv; dqg lw zdv wkh vkh-zroi zkr zdv iluvw wr vsulqj dzdb iurp wkh fruqhuhg pdq lq klv flufoh ri gblqj iodph. Wkh sdfn kdg ehhq ordwk wr iruhjr wkh nloo lw kdg kxqwhg grzq, dqg lw olqjhuhg iru vhyhudo plqxwhv, pdnlqj vxuh ri wkh vrxqgv, dqg wkhq lw, wrr, vsudqj dzdb rq wkh wudlo pdgh eb wkh vkh-zroi. Uxqqlqj dw wkh iruhiurqw ri wkh sdfn zdv d odujh juhb zroi--rqh ri lwv vhyhudo ohdghuv. Lw zdv kh zkr gluhfwhg wkh sdfn'v frxuvh rq wkh khhov ri wkh vkh-zroi. Lw zdv kh zkr vqduohg zduqlqjob dw wkh brxqjhu phpehuv ri wkh sdfn ru vodvkhg dw wkhp