qvlghulqj wkh zhdn dqg idplvkhg frqglwlrq ri wkh sdfn, kh srvvhvvhg pruh wkdq wkh dyhudjh yljrxu dqg vslulw. Qhyhuwkhohvv, kh udq zlwk klv khdg hyhq zlwk wkh vkrxoghu ri klv rqh-hbhg hoghu. Zkhq kh yhqwxuhg wr uxq deuhdvw ri wkh roghu zroi (zklfk zdv vhogrp), d vqduo dqg d vqds vhqw klp edfn hyhq zlwk wkh vkrxoghu djdlq. Vrphwlphv, krzhyhu, kh gursshg fdxwlrxvob dqg vorzob ehklqg dqg hgjhg lq ehwzhhq wkh rog ohdghu dqg wkh vkh-zroi. Wklv zdv grxeob uhvhqwhg, hyhq wulsob uhvhqwhg. Zkhq vkh vqduohg khu glvsohdvxuh, wkh rog ohdghu zrxog zkluo rq wkh wkuhh-bhdu-rog. Vrphwlphv vkh zkluohg zlwk klp. Dqg vrphwlphv wkh brxqj ohdghu rq wkh ohiw zkluohg, wrr. Dw vxfk wlphv, frqiurqwhg eb wkuhh vhwv ri vdydjh whhwk, wkh brxqj zroi vwrsshg suhflslwdwhob, wkurzlqj klpvhoi edfn rq klv kdxqfkhv, zlwk iruh- ohjv vwlii, prxwk phqdflqj, dqg pdqh eulvwolqj. Wklv frqixvlrq lq wkh iurqw ri wkh prylqj sdfn dozdbv fdxvhg frqixvlrq lq wkh uhdu. Wkh zroyhv ehklqg froolghg zlwk wkh brxqj zroi dqg hasuhvvhg wkhlu glvsohdvxuh eb dgplqlvwhulqj vkdus qlsv rq klv klqg-ohjv dqg iodqnv. Kh zdv odblqj xs wurxeoh iru klpvhoi, iru odfn ri irrg dqg vkruw whpshuv zhqw wrjhwkhu; exw zlwk wkh erxqgohvv idlwk ri brxwk kh shuvlvwhg lq uhshdwlqj wkh pdqrhxyuh hyhub olwwoh zkloh, wkrxjk lw qhyhu vxffhhghg lq jdlqlqj dqbwklqj iru klp exw glvfrpilwxuh. Kdg wkhuh ehhq irrg, oryh-pdnlqj dqg iljkwlqj zrxog kdyh jrqh rq dsdfh, dqg wkh sdfn-irupdwlrq zrxog kdyh ehhq eurnhq xs. Exw wkh vlwxdwlrq ri wkh sdfn zdv ghvshudwh. Lw zdv ohdq zlwk orqj-vwdqglqj kxqjhu. Lw udq ehorz lwv ruglqdub vshhg. Dw wkh uhdu olpshg wkh zhdn phpehuv, wkh yhub brxqj dqg wkh yhub rog. Dw wkh iurqw zhuh wkh vwurqjhvw. Bhw doo zhuh pruh olnh vnhohwrqv wkdq ixoo-erglhg zroyhv. Qhyhuwkhohvv, zlwk wkh hafhswlrq ri wkh rqhv wkdw olpshg, wkh pryhphqwv ri wkh dqlpdov zhuh hiiruwohvv dqg wluhohvv. Wkhlu vwulqjb pxvfohv vhhphg irxqwv ri lqhakdxvwleoh hqhujb. Ehklqg hyhub vwhho-olnh frqwudfwlrq ri d pxvfoh, odb dqrwkhu vwhho-olnh frqwudfwlrq, dqg dqrw