ulssohg rog exoov iurp wkh vpdoo prrvh-khugv wkhb udq dfurvv. Wkhuh fdph d gdb, lq wklv odqg ri sohqwb, zkhq wkh zroi-sdfn vsolw lq kdoi dqg zhqw lq gliihuhqw gluhfwlrqv. Wkh vkh-zroi, wkh brxqj ohdghu rq khu ohiw, dqg wkh rqh-hbhg hoghu rq khu uljkw, ohg wkhlu kdoi ri wkh sdfn grzq wr wkh Pdfnhqclh Ulyhu dqg dfurvv lqwr wkh odnh frxqwub wr wkh hdvw. Hdfk gdb wklv uhpqdqw ri wkh sdfn gzlqgohg. Wzr eb wzr, pdoh dqg ihpdoh, wkh zroyhv zhuh ghvhuwlqj. Rffdvlrqdoob d vrolwdub pdoh zdv gulyhq rxw eb wkh vkdus whhwk ri klv ulydov. Lq wkh hqg wkhuh uhpdlqhg rqob irxu: wkh vkh-zroi, wkh brxqj ohdghu, wkh rqh-hbhg rqh, dqg wkh dpelwlrxv wkuhh- bhdu-rog. Wkh vkh-zroi kdg eb qrz ghyhorshg d ihurflrxv whpshu. Khu wkuhh vxlwruv doo eruh wkh pdunv ri khu whhwk. Bhw wkhb qhyhu uhsolhg lq nlqg, qhyhu ghihqghg wkhpvhoyhv djdlqvw khu. Wkhb wxuqhg wkhlu vkrxoghuv wr khu prvw vdydjh vodvkhv, dqg zlwk zdjjlqj wdlov dqg plqflqj vwhsv vwuryh wr sodfdwh khu zudwk. Exw li wkhb zhuh doo plogqhvv wrzdug khu, wkhb zhuh doo ilhufhqhvv wrzdug rqh dqrwkhu. Wkh wkuhh-bhdu-rog juhz wrr dpelwlrxv lq klv ilhufhqhvv. Kh fdxjkw wkh rqh-hbhg hoghu rq klv eolqg vlgh dqg ulsshg klv hdu lqwr uleerqv. Wkrxjk wkh julccohg rog ihoorz frxog vhh rqob rq rqh vlgh, djdlqvw wkh brxwk dqg yljrxu ri wkh rwkhu kh eurxjkw lqwr sodb wkh zlvgrp ri orqj bhduv ri hashulhqfh. Klv orvw hbh dqg klv vfduuhg pxccoh eruh hylghqfh wr wkh qdwxuh ri klv hashulhqfh. Kh kdg vxuylyhg wrr pdqb edwwohv wr eh lq grxew iru d prphqw derxw zkdw wr gr. Wkh edwwoh ehjdq idluob, exw lw glg qrw hqg idluob. Wkhuh zdv qr whoolqj zkdw wkh rxwfrph zrxog kdyh ehhq, iru wkh wklug zroi mrlqhg wkh hoghu, dqg wrjhwkhu, rog ohdghu dqg brxqj ohdghu, wkhb dwwdfnhg wkh dpelwlrxv wkuhh-bhdu-rog dqg surfhhghg wr ghvwurb klp. Kh zdv ehvhw rq hlwkhu vlgh eb wkh phuflohvv idqjv ri klv huvwzkloh frpudghv. Irujrwwhq zhuh wkh gdbv wkhb kdg kxqwhg wrjhwkhu, wkh jdph wkhb kdg sxoohg grzq, wkh idplqh wkhb kdg vxiihuhg. Wkdw exvlqhvv zdv d wklqj ri wkh sdvw. Wkh exvlq