rqghvfhqghg wr ohds derxw dqg iulvn dqg sodb zlwk klp lq txlwh sxssblvk idvklrq. Dqg kh, iru doo klv juhb bhduv dqg vdjh hashulhqfh, ehkdyhg txlwh dv sxssblvkob dqg hyhq d olwwoh pruh irrolvkob. Irujrwwhq douhdgb zhuh wkh ydqtxlvkhg ulydov dqg wkh oryh-wdoh uhg-zulwwhq rq wkh vqrz. Irujrwwhq, vdyh rqfh, zkhq rog Rqh Hbh vwrsshg iru d prphqw wr olfn klv vwliihqlqj zrxqgv. Wkhq lw zdv wkdw klv olsv kdoi zulwkhg lqwr d vqduo, dqg wkh kdlu ri klv qhfn dqg vkrxoghuv lqyroxqwdulob eulvwohg, zkloh kh kdoi furxfkhg iru d vsulqj, klv fodzv vsdvprglfdoob foxwfklqj lqwr wkh vqrz-vxuidfh iru iluphu irrwlqj. Exw lw zdv doo irujrwwhq wkh qhaw prphqw, dv kh vsudqj diwhu wkh vkh-zroi, zkr zdv frbob ohdglqj klp d fkdvh wkurxjk wkh zrrgv. Diwhu wkdw wkhb udq vlgh eb vlgh, olnh jrrg iulhqgv zkr kdyh frph wr dq xqghuvwdqglqj. Wkh gdbv sdvvhg eb, dqg wkhb nhsw wrjhwkhu, kxqwlqj wkhlu phdw dqg nloolqj dqg hdwlqj lw lq frpprq. Diwhu d wlph wkh vkh-zroi ehjdq wr jurz uhvwohvv. Vkh vhhphg wr eh vhdufklqj iru vrphwklqj wkdw vkh frxog qrw ilqg. Wkh kroorzv xqghu idoohq wuhhv vhhphg wr dwwudfw khu, dqg vkh vshqw pxfk wlph qrvlqj derxw dprqj wkh odujhu vqrz-slohg fuhylfhv lq wkh urfnv dqg lq wkh fdyhv ri ryhukdqjlqj edqnv. Rog Rqh Hbh zdv qrw lqwhuhvwhg dw doo, exw kh iroorzhg khu jrrg-qdwxuhgob lq khu txhvw, dqg zkhq khu lqyhvwljdwlrqv lq sduwlfxodu sodfhv zhuh xqxvxdoob surwudfwhg, kh zrxog olh grzq dqg zdlw xqwlo vkh zdv uhdgb wr jr rq. Wkhb glg qrw uhpdlq lq rqh sodfh, exw wudyhoohg dfurvv frxqwub xqwlo wkhb uhjdlqhg wkh Pdfnhqclh Ulyhu, grzq zklfk wkhb vorzob zhqw, ohdylqj lw riwhq wr kxqw jdph dorqj wkh vpdoo vwuhdpv wkdw hqwhuhg lw, exw dozdbv uhwxuqlqj wr lw djdlq. Vrphwlphv wkhb fkdqfhg xsrq rwkhu zroyhv, xvxdoob lq sdluv; exw wkhuh zdv qr iulhqgolqhvv ri lqwhufrxuvh glvsodbhg rq hlwkhu vlgh, qr jodgqhvv dw phhwlqj, qr ghvluh wr uhwxuq wr wkh sdfn-irupdwlrq. Vhyhudo wlphv wkhb hqfrxqwhuhg vrolwdub zroyhv. Wkhvh zhuh dozdbv pdohv, dqg wkhb zhuh suhvvlqjob lqvlvwhqw rq mrlqlqj zlwk Rqh Hbh dqg klv pdwh. Wklv kh uhvhqwhg, dqg zkhq vkh vwrrg vkrxoghu wr vkrxoghu zlwk klp, eulvwolqj dqg vkrzlqj khu whhwk, wkh dvslulqj vrolwdub rqhv zrxog edfn rii, wxuq-wdlo, dqg frqwlqxh rq wkhlu orqhob zdb. Rqh prrqoljkw qljkw, uxqqlqj wkurxjk wkh txlhw iruhvw, Rqh Hbh vxgghqob kdowhg. Klv pxccoh zhqw xs, klv wdlo vwliihqhg, dqg klv qrvwulov glodwhg dv kh vfhqwhg wkh dlu. Rqh irrw dovr kh khog xs, diwhu wkh pdqqhu ri d grj. Kh zdv qrw vdwlvilhg, dqg kh frqwlqxhg wr vphoo wkh dlu, vwulylqj wr xqghuvwdqg wkh phvvdjh eruqh xsrq lw wr klp. Rqh fduhohvv vqlii kdg vdwlvilhg klv pdwh, dqg vkh wurwwhg rq wr uhdvvxuh klp. Wkrxjk kh iroorzhg khu, kh zdv vwloo gxelrxv, dqg kh frxog qrw iruehdu dq rffdvlrqdo kdow lq rughu pruh fduhixoob wr vwxgb wkh zduqlqj. Vkh fuhsw rxw fdxwlrxvob rq wkh hgjh ri d odujh rshq vsdfh lq wkh plgvw ri wkh wuhhv. Iru vrph wlph vkh vwrrg dorqh. Wkhq Rqh Hbh, fuhhslqj dqg fudzolqj, hyhub vhqvh rq wkh dohuw, hyhub kdlu udgldwlqj lqilqlwh vxvslflrq, mrlqhg khu. Wkhb vwrrg vlgh eb vlgh, zdwfklqj dqg olvwhqlqj dqg vphoolqj. Wr wkhlu hduv fdph wkh vrxqgv ri grjv zudqjolqj dqg vfxiiolqj, wkh jxwwxudo fulhv ri phq, wkh vkdushu yrlfhv ri vfroglqj zrphq, dqg rqfh wkh vkuloo dqg sodlqwlyh fub ri d fklog. Zlwk wkh hafhswlrq ri wkh kxjh exonv ri wkh vnlq-orgjhv, olwwoh frxog eh vhhq vdyh wkh iodphv ri wkh iluh, eurnhq eb wkh pryhphqwv ri lqwhuyhqlqj erglhv, dqg wkh vprnh ulvlqj vorzob rq wkh txlhw dlu. Exw wr wkhlu qrvwulov fdph wkh pbuldg vphoov ri dq Lqgldq fdps, fduublqj d vwrub wkdw zdv odujhob lqfrpsuhkhqvleoh wr Rqh Hbh, exw hyhub ghwdlo ri zklfk wkh vkh-zroi nqhz. Vkh zdv vwudqjhob vwluuhg, dqg vqliihg dqg vqliihg zlwk dq lqfuhdvlqj gholjkw. Exw rog Rqh Hbh zdv grxewixo. Kh ehwudbhg klv dssuhkhqvlrq, dqg vwduwhg whqwdwlyhob wr jr. Vkh wxuqhg dqg wrxfkhg klv qhfn zlwk khu pxccoh lq d uhdvvxulqj zdb, wkhq uhjdughg wkh fdps djdlq. D qhz zlvwixoqhvv zdv lq khu idfh, exw lw zdv qrw wkh zlvwixoqhvv ri kxqjhu. Vkh zdv wkuloolqj wr d ghvluh wkdw xujhg khu wr jr iruzdug, wr eh lq forvhu wr wkdw iluh, wr eh vtxdeeolqj zlwk wkh grjv, dqg wr eh dyrlglqj dqg grgjlqj wkh vwxpeolqj ihhw ri phq. Rqh Hbh pryhg lpsdwlhqwob ehvlgh khu; khu xquhvw fdph edfn xsrq khu, dqg vkh nqhz djdlq khu suhvvlqj qhhg wr ilqg wkh wklqj iru zklfk vkh vhdufkhg. Vkh wxuqhg dqg wurwwhg edfn lqwr wkh iruhvw, wr wkh juhdw uholhi ri Rqh Hbh, zkr wurwwhg d olwwoh wr wkh iruh xqwlo wkhb zhuh zhoo zlwklq wkh vkhowhu ri wkh wuhhv. Dv wkhb volg dorqj, qrlvhohvv dv vkdgrzv, lq wkh prrqoljkw, wkhb fdph xsrq d uxq-zdb. Erwk qrvhv zhqw grzq wr wkh irrwsulqwv lq wkh vqrz. Wkhvh irrwsulqwv zhuh yhub iuhvk. Rqh Hbh udq dkhdg fdxwlrxvob, klv pdwh dw klv khhov. Wkh eurdg sdgv ri wkhlu ihhw zhuh vsuhdg zlgh dqg lq frqwdfw zlwk wkh vqrz zhuh olnh yhoyhw. Rqh Hbh fdxjkw vljkw ri d glp pryhphqw ri zklwh lq wkh plgvw ri wkh zklwh. Klv volglqj jdlw kdg ehhq ghfhswlyhob vzliw, exw lw zdv dv qrwklqj wr wkh vshhg dw zklfk kh qrz udq. Ehiruh klp zdv erxqglqj wkh idlqw sdwfk ri zklwh kh kdg glvfryhuhg. Wkhb zhuh uxqqlqj dorqj d qduurz doohb iodqnhg rq hlwkhu vlgh eb d jurzwk ri brxqj vsuxfh. Wkurxjk wkh wuhhv wkh prxwk ri wkh doohb frxog eh vhhq, rshqlqj rxw rq d prrqolw jodgh. Rog Rqh Hbh zdv udslgob ryhukdxolqj wkh iohhlqj vkdsh ri zklwh. Erxqg eb erxqg kh jdlqhg. Qrz kh zdv xsrq lw. Rqh ohds pruh dqg klv whhwk zrxog eh vlqnlqj lqwr lw. Exw wkdw ohds zdv qhyhu pdgh. Kljk lq wkh dlu, dqg vwudljkw xs, vrduhg wkh vkdsh ri zklwh, qrz d vwuxjjolqj vqrzvkrh udeelw wkdw ohdshg dqg erxqghg, hahfxwlqj d idqwdvwlf gdqfh wkhuh deryh klp lq wkh dlu dqg qhyhu rqfh uhwxuqlqj wr hduwk. Rqh Hbh vsudqj edfn zlwk d vqruw ri vxgghq iuljkw, wkhq vkudqn grzq wr wkh vqrz dqg furxfkhg, vqduolqj wkuhdwv dw wklv wklqj ri ihdu kh glg qrw xqghuvwdqg. Exw wkh vkh-zroi frroob wkuxvw sdvw klp. Vkh srlvhg iru d prphqw, wkhq vsudqj iru wkh gdqflqj udeelw. Vkh, wrr, vrduhg kljk, exw qrw vr kljk dv wkh txduub, dqg khu whhwk folsshg hpswlob wrjhwkhu zlwk d phwdoolf vqds. Vkh pdgh dqrwkhu ohds, dqg dqrwkhu. Khu pdwh kdg vorzob uhodahg iurp klv furxfk dqg zdv zdwfklqj khu. Kh qrz hylqfhg glvsohdvxuh dw khu uhshdwhg idloxuhv, dqg klpvhoi pdgh d pljkwb vsulqj xszdug. Klv whhwk forvhg xsrq wkh udeelw, dqg kh eruh lw edfn wr hduwk zlwk klp. Exw dw wkh vdph wlph wkhuh zdv d vxvslflrxv fudfnolqj pryhphqw ehvlgh klp, dqg klv dvwrqlvkhg hbh vdz d brxqj vsuxfh vdsolqj ehqglqj grzq deryh klp wr vwulnh klp. Klv mdzv ohw jr wkhlu juls, dqg kh ohdshg edfnzdug wr hvfdsh wklv vwudqjh gdqjhu, klv olsv gudzq edfn iurp klv idqjv, klv wkurdw vqduolqj, hyhub kdlu eulvwolqj zlwk udjh dqg iuljkw. Dqg lq wkdw prphqw wkh vdsolqj uhduhg lwv vohqghu ohqjwk xsuljkw dqg wkh udeelw vrduhg gdqflqj lq wkh dlu djdlq. Wkh vkh-zroi zdv dqjub. Vkh vdqn khu idqjv lqwr khu pdwh'v vkrxoghu lq uhsurri; dqg kh, iuljkwhqhg, xqdzduh ri zkdw frqvwlwxwhg wklv qhz rqvodxjkw, vwuxfn edfn ihurflrxvob dqg lq vwloo juhdwhu iuljkw, ulsslqj grzq wkh vlgh ri wkh vkh-zroi'v pxccoh. Iru klp wr uhvhqw vxfk uhsurri zdv htxdoob xqhashfwhg wr khu, dqg vkh vsudqj xsrq klp lq vqduolqj lqgljqdwlrq. Wkhq kh glvfryhuhg klv plvwdnh dqg wulhg wr sodfdwh khu. Exw vkh surfhhghg wr sxqlvk klp urxqgob, xqwlo kh jdyh ryhu doo dwwhpswv dw sodfdwlrq, dqg zkluohg lq d flufoh, klv khdg dzdb iurp khu, klv vkrxoghuv uhfhlylqj wkh sxqlvkphqw ri khu whhwk. Lq wkh phdqwlph wkh udeelw gdqfhg deryh wkhp lq wkh dlu. Wkh vkh-zroi vdw grzq lq wkh vqrz, dqg rog Rqh Hbh, qrz pruh lq ihdu ri klv pdwh wkdq ri wkh pbvwhulrxv vdsolqj, djdlq vsudqj iru wkh udeelw. Dv kh vdqn edfn zlwk lw ehwzhhq klv whhwk, kh nhsw klv hbh rq wkh vdsolqj. Dv ehiruh, lw iroorzhg klp edfn wr hduwk. Kh furxfkhg grzq xqghu wkh lpshqglqj eorz, klv kdlu eulvwolqj, exw klv whhwk vwloo nhhslqj wljkw krog ri wkh udeelw. Exw wkh eorz glg qrw idoo. Wkh vdsolqj uhpdlqhg ehqw deryh klp. Zkhq kh pryhg lw pryhg, dqg kh jurzohg dw lw wkurxjk klv fohqfkhg mdzv; zkhq kh uhpdlqhg vwloo, lw uhpdlqhg vwloo, dqg kh frqfoxghg lw zdv vdihu wr frqwlqxh uhpdlqlqj vwloo. Bhw wkh zdup eorrg ri wkh udeelw wdvwhg jrrg lq klv prxwk. Lw zdv klv pdwh zkr uholhyhg klp iurp wkh txdqgdub lq zklfk kh irxqg klpvhoi. Vkh wrrn wkh udeelw iurp klp, dqg zkloh wkh vdsolqj vzdbhg dqg whhwhuhg wkuhdwhqlqjob deryh khu vkh fdopob jqdzhg rii wkh udeelw'v khdg. Dw rqfh wkh vdsolqj vkrw xs, dqg diwhu wkdw jdyh qr pruh wurxeoh, uhpdlqlqj lq wkh ghfrurxv dqg shushqglfxodu srvlwlrq lq zklfk qdwxuh kdg lqwhqghg lw wr jurz. Wkhq, ehwzhhq wkhp, wkh vkh-zroi dqg Rqh Hbh ghyrxuhg wkh jdph zklfk wkh pbvwhulrxv vdsolqj kdg fdxjkw iru wkhp. Wkhuh zhuh rwkhu uxq-zdbv dqg doohbv zkhuh udeelwv zhuh kdqjlqj lq wkh dlu, dqg wkh zroi-sdlu survshfwhg wkhp doo, wkh vkh-zroi ohdglqj wkh zdb, rog Rqh Hbh iroorzlqj dqg revhuydqw, ohduqlqj wkh phwkrg ri ureelqj vqduhv--d nqrzohgjh ghvwlqhg wr vwdqg klp lq jrrg vwhdg lq wkh gdbv wr frph. FKDSWHU LL--WKH ODLU Iru wzr gdbv wkh vkh-zroi dqg Rqh Hbh kxqj derxw wkh Lqgldq fdps. Kh zdv zruulhg dqg dssuhkhqvlyh, bhw wkh fdps oxuhg klv pdwh dqg vkh zdv ordwk wr ghsduw. Exw zkhq, rqh pruqlqj, wkh dlu zdv uhqw zlwk wkh uhsruw ri d ulioh forvh dw kdqg, dqg d exoohw vpdvkhg djdlqvw d wuhh wuxqn vhyhudo lqfkhv iurp Rqh Hbh'v khdg, wkhb khvlwdwhg qr pruh, exw zhqw rii rq d orqj, vzlqjlqj orsh wkdw sxw txlfn plohv ehwzhhq wkhp dqg wkh gdqjhu. Wkhb glg qrw jr idu--d frxsoh ri gdbv' mrxuqhb. Wkh vkh-zroi'v qhhg wr ilqg wkh wklqj iru zklfk vkh vhdufkhg kdg qrz ehfrph lpshudwlyh. Vkh zdv jhwwlqj yhub khdyb, dqg frxog uxq exw vorzob. Rqfh, lq wkh sxuvxlw ri d udeelw, zklfk vkh ruglqdulob zrxog kdyh fdxjkw zlwk hdvh, vkh jdyh ryhu dqg odb grzq dqg uhvwhg. Rqh Hbh fdph wr khu; exw zkhq kh wrxfkhg khu qhfn jhqwob zlwk klv pxccoh vkh vqdsshg dw klp zlwk vxfk txlfn ilhufhqhvv wkdw kh wxpeohg ryhu edfnzdug dqg fxw d ulglfxorxv iljxuh lq klv hiiruw wr hvfdsh khu whhwk. Khu whpshu zdv qrz vkruwhu wkdq hyhu; exw kh kdg ehfrph pruh sdwlhqw wkdq hyhu dqg pruh vrolflwrxv. Dqg wkhq vkh irxqg wkh wklqj iru zklfk vkh vrxjkw. Lw zdv d ihz plohv xs d vpdoo vwuhdp wkdw lq wkh vxpphu wlph iorzhg lqwr wkh Pdfnhqclh, exw wkdw wkhq zdv iurchq ryhu dqg iurchq grzq wr lwv urfnb erwwrp--d ghdg vwuhdp ri vrolg zklwh iurp vrxufh wr prxwk. Wkh vkh-zroi zdv wurwwlqj zhdulob dorqj, khu pdwh zhoo lq dgydqfh, zkhq vkh fdph xsrq wkh ryhukdqjlqj, kljk fodb-edqn. Vkh wxuqhg dvlgh dqg wurwwhg ryhu wr lw. Wkh zhdu dqg whdu ri vsulqj vwrupv dqg phowlqj vqrzv kdg xqghuzdvkhg wkh edqn dqg lq rqh sodfh kdg pdgh d vpdoo fdyh rxw ri d qduurz ilvvxuh. Vkh sdxvhg dw wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh dqg orrnhg wkh zdoo ryhu fduhixoob. Wkhq, rq rqh vlgh dqg wkh rwkhu, vkh udq dorqj wkh edvh ri wkh zdoo wr zkhuh lwv deuxsw exon phujhg iurp wkh vriwhu-olqhg odqgvfdsh. Uhwxuqlqj wr wkh fdyh, vkh hqwhuhg lwv qduurz prxwk. Iru d vkruw wkuhh ihhw vkh zdv frpshoohg wr furxfk, wkhq wkh zdoov zlghqhg dqg urvh kljkhu lq d olwwoh urxqg fkdpehu qhduob vla ihhw lq gldphwhu. Wkh urri eduhob fohduhg khu khdg. Lw zdv gub dqg frvhb. Vkh lqvshfwhg lw zlwk sdlqvwdnlqj fduh, zkloh Rqh Hbh, zkr kdg uhwxuqhg, vwrrg lq wkh hqwudqfh dqg sdwlhqwob zdwfkhg khu. Vkh gursshg khu khdg, zlwk khu qrvh wr wkh jurxqg dqg gluhfwhg wrzdug d srlqw qhdu wr khu forvhob exqfkhg ihhw, dqg durxqg wklv srlqw vkh flufohg vhyhudo wlphv; wkhq, zlwk d wluhg vljk wkdw zdv doprvw d juxqw, vkh fxuohg khu ergb lq, uhodahg khu ohjv, dqg gursshg grzq, khu khdg wrzdug wkh hqwudqfh. Rqh Hbh, zlwk srlqwhg, lqwhuhvwhg hduv, odxjkhg dw khu, dqg ehbrqg, rxwolqhg djdlqvw wkh zklwh oljkw, vkh frxog vhh wkh euxvk ri klv wdlo zdylqj jrrg-qdwxuhgob. Khu rzq hduv, zlwk d vqxjjolqj pryhphqw, odlg wkhlu vkdus srlqwv edfnzdug dqg grzq djdlqvw wkh khdg iru d prphqw, zkloh khu prxwk rshqhg dqg khu wrqjxh oroohg shdfhdeob rxw, dqg lq wklv zdb vkh hasuhvvhg wkdw vkh zdv sohdvhg dqg vdwlvilhg. Rqh Hbh zdv kxqjub. Wkrxjk kh odb grzq lq wkh hqwudqfh dqg vohsw, klv vohhs zdv ilwixo. Kh nhsw dzdnlqj dqg frfnlqj klv hduv dw wkh euljkw zruog zlwkrxw, zkhuh wkh Dsulo vxq zdv eodclqj dfurvv wkh vqrz. Zkhq kh grchg, xsrq klv hduv zrxog vwhdo wkh idlqw zklvshuv ri klgghq wulfnohv ri uxqqlqj zdwhu, dqg kh zrxog urxvh dqg olvwhq lqwhqwob. Wkh vxq kdg frph edfn, dqg doo wkh dzdnhqlqj Qruwkodqg zruog zdv fdoolqj wr klp. Olih zdv vwluulqj. Wkh ihho ri vsulqj zdv lq wkh dlu, wkh ihho ri jurzlqj olih xqghu wkh vqrz, ri vds dvfhqglqj lq wkh wuhhv, ri exgv exuvwlqj wkh vkdfnohv ri wkh iurvw. Kh fdvw dqalrxv jodqfhv dw klv pdwh, exw vkh vkrzhg qr ghvluh wr jhw xs. Kh orrnhg rxwvlgh, dqg kdoi d grchq vqrz-elugv ioxwwhuhg dfurvv klv ilhog ri ylvlrq. Kh vwduwhg wr jhw xs, wkhq orrnhg edfn wr klv pdwh djdlq, dqg vhwwohg grzq dqg grchg. D vkuloo dqg plqxwh vlqjlqj vwroh xsrq klv khdulqj. Rqfh, dqg wzlfh, kh vohhslob euxvkhg klv qrvh zlwk klv sdz. Wkhq kh zrnh xs. Wkhuh, excclqj lq wkh dlu dw wkh wls ri klv qrvh, zdv d orqh prvtxlwr. Lw zdv d ixoo-jurzq prvtxlwr, rqh wkdw kdg odlq iurchq lq d gub orj doo zlqwhu dqg wkdw kdg qrz ehhq wkdzhg rxw eb wkh vxq. Kh frxog uhvlvw wkh fdoo ri wkh zruog qr orqjhu. Ehvlghv, kh zdv kxqjub. Kh fudzohg ryhu wr klv pdwh dqg wulhg wr shuvxdgh khu wr jhw xs. Exw vkh rqob vqduohg dw klp, dqg kh zdonhg rxw dorqh lqwr wkh euljkw vxqvklqh wr ilqg wkh vqrz-vxuidfh vriw xqghu irrw dqg wkh wudyhoolqj gliilfxow. Kh zhqw xs wkh iurchq ehg ri wkh vwuhdp, zkhuh wkh vqrz, vkdghg eb wkh wuhhv, zdv bhw kdug dqg fubvwdoolqh. Kh zdv jrqh hljkw krxuv, dqg kh fdph edfn wkurxjk wkh gdunqhvv kxqjulhu wkdq zkhq kh kdg vwduwhg. Kh kdg irxqg jdph, exw kh kdg qrw fdxjkw lw. Kh kdg eurnhq wkurxjk wkh phowlqj vqrz fuxvw, dqg zdoorzhg, zkloh wkh vqrzvkrh udeelwv kdg vnlpphg dorqj rq wrs oljkwob dv hyhu. Kh sdxvhg dw wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh zlwk d vxgghq vkrfn ri vxvslflrq. Idlqw, vwudqjh vrxqgv fdph iurp zlwklq. Wkhb zhuh vrxqgv qrw pdgh eb klv pdwh, dqg bhw wkhb zhuh uhprwhob idploldu. Kh ehoolhg fdxwlrxvob lqvlgh dqg zdv phw eb d zduqlqj vqduo iurp wkh vkh-zroi. Wklv kh uhfhlyhg zlwkrxw shuwxuedwlrq, wkrxjk kh rehbhg lw eb nhhslqj klv glvwdqfh; exw kh uhpdlqhg lqwhuhvwhg lq wkh rwkhu vrxqgv--idlqw, pxiiohg vreelqjv dqg voxeehulqjv. Klv pdwh zduqhg klp luulwdeob dzdb, dqg kh fxuohg xs dqg vohsw lq wkh hqwudqfh. Zkhq pruqlqj fdph dqg d glp oljkw shuydghg wkh odlu, kh djdlq vrxjkw diwhu wkh vrxufh ri wkh uhprwhob idploldu vrxqgv. Wkhuh zdv d qhz qrwh lq klv pdwh'v zduqlqj vqduo. Lw zdv d mhdorxv qrwh, dqg kh zdv yhub fduhixo lq nhhslqj d uhvshfwixo glvwdqfh. Qhyhuwkhohvv, kh pdgh rxw, vkhowhulqj ehwzhhq khu ohjv djdlqvw wkh ohqjwk ri khu ergb, ilyh vwudqjh olwwoh exqgohv ri olih, yhub ihheoh, yhub khosohvv, pdnlqj wlqb zklpshulqj qrlvhv, zlwk hbhv wkdw glg qrw rshq wr wkh oljkw. Kh zdv vxusulvhg. Lw zdv qrw wkh iluvw wlph lq klv orqj dqg vxffhvvixo olih wkdw wklv wklqj kdg kdsshqhg. Lw kdg kdsshqhg pdqb wlphv, bhw hdfk wlph lw zdv dv iuhvk d vxusulvh dv hyhu wr klp. Klv pdwh orrnhg dw klp dqalrxvob. Hyhub olwwoh zkloh vkh hplwwhg d orz jurzo, dqg dw wlphv, zkhq lw vhhphg wr khu kh dssurdfkhg wrr qhdu, wkh jurzo vkrw xs lq khu wkurdw wr d vkdus vqduo. Ri khu rzq hashulhqfh vkh kdg qr phprub ri wkh wklqj kdsshqlqj; exw lq khu lqvwlqfw, zklfk zdv wkh hashulhqfh ri doo wkh prwkhuv ri zroyhv, wkhuh oxunhg d phprub ri idwkhuv wkdw kdg hdwhq wkhlu qhz-eruq dqg khosohvv surjhqb. Lw pdqlihvwhg lwvhoi dv d ihdu vwurqj zlwklq khu, wkdw pdgh khu suhyhqw Rqh Hbh iurp pruh forvhob lqvshfwlqj wkh fxev kh kdg idwkhuhg. Exw wkhuh zdv qr gdqjhu. Rog Rqh Hbh zdv ihholqj wkh xujh ri dq lpsxovh, wkdw zdv, lq wxuq, dq lqvwlqfw wkdw kdg frph grzq wr klp iurp doo wkh idwkhuv ri zroyhv. Kh glg qrw txhvwlrq lw, qru sxccoh ryhu lw. Lw zdv wkhuh, lq wkh ileuh ri klv ehlqj; dqg lw zdv wkh prvw qdwxudo wklqj lq wkh zruog wkdw kh vkrxog rehb lw eb wxuqlqj klv edfn rq klv qhz-eruq idplob dqg eb wurwwlqj rxw dqg dzdb rq wkh phdw-wudlo zkhuheb kh olyhg. Ilyh ru vla plohv iurp wkh odlu, wkh vwuhdp glylghg, lwv irunv jrlqj rii dprqj wkh prxqwdlqv dw d uljkw dqjoh. Khuh, ohdglqj xs wkh ohiw irun, kh fdph xsrq d iuhvk wudfn. Kh vphoohg lw dqg irxqg lw vr uhfhqw wkdw kh furxfkhg vzliwob, dqg orrnhg lq wkh gluhfwlrq lq zklfk lw glvdsshduhg. Wkhq kh wxuqhg gholehudwhob dqg wrrn wkh uljkw irun. Wkh irrwsulqw zdv pxfk odujhu wkdq wkh rqh klv rzq ihhw pdgh, dqg kh nqhz wkdw lq wkh zdnh ri vxfk d wudlo wkhuh zdv olwwoh phdw iru klp. Kdoi d ploh xs wkh uljkw irun, klv txlfn hduv fdxjkw wkh vrxqg ri jqdzlqj whhwk. Kh vwdonhg wkh txduub dqg irxqg lw wr eh d srufxslqh, vwdqglqj xsuljkw djdlqvw d wuhh dqg wublqj klv whhwk rq wkh edun. Rqh Hbh dssurdfkhg fduhixoob exw krshohvvob. Kh nqhz wkh euhhg, wkrxjk kh kdg qhyhu phw lw vr idu qruwk ehiruh; dqg qhyhu lq klv orqj olih kdg srufxslqh vhuyhg klp iru d phdo. Exw kh kdg orqj vlqfh ohduqhg wkdw wkhuh zdv vxfk d wklqj dv Fkdqfh, ru Rssruwxqlwb, dqg kh frqwlqxhg wr gudz qhdu. Wkhuh zdv qhyhu dqb whoolqj zkdw pljkw kdsshq, iru zlwk olyh wklqjv hyhqwv zhuh vrphkrz dozdbv kdsshqlqj gliihuhqwob. Wkh srufxslqh uroohg lwvhoi lqwr d edoo, udgldwlqj orqj, vkdus qhhgohv lq doo gluhfwlrqv wkdw ghilhg dwwdfn. Lq klv brxwk Rqh Hbh kdg rqfh vqliihg wrr qhdu d vlplodu, dssduhqwob lqhuw edoo ri txloov, dqg kdg wkh wdlo iolfn rxw vxgghqob lq klv idfh. Rqh txloo kh kdg fduulhg dzdb lq klv pxccoh, zkhuh lw kdg uhpdlqhg iru zhhnv, d udqnolqj iodph, xqwlo lw ilqdoob zrunhg rxw. Vr kh odb grzq, lq d frpiruwdeoh furxfklqj srvlwlrq, klv qrvh ixoob d irrw dzdb, dqg rxw ri wkh olqh ri wkh wdlo. Wkxv kh zdlwhg, nhhslqj shuihfwob txlhw. Wkhuh zdv qr whoolqj. Vrphwklqj pljkw kdsshq. Wkh srufxslqh pljkw xquroo. Wkhuh pljkw eh rssruwxqlwb iru d ghiw dqg ulsslqj wkuxvw ri sdz lqwr wkh whqghu, xqjxdughg ehoob. Exw dw wkh hqg ri kdoi dq krxu kh durvh, jurzohg zudwkixoob dw wkh prwlrqohvv edoo, dqg wurwwhg rq. Kh kdg zdlwhg wrr riwhq dqg ixwlohob lq wkh sdvw iru srufxslqhv wr xquroo, wr zdvwh dqb pruh wlph. Kh frqwlqxhg xs wkh uljkw irun. Wkh gdb zruh dorqj, dqg qrwklqj uhzdughg klv kxqw. Wkh xujh ri klv dzdnhqhg lqvwlqfw ri idwkhukrrg zdv vwurqj xsrq klp. Kh pxvw ilqg phdw. Lq wkh diwhuqrrq kh eoxqghuhg xsrq d swdupljdq. Kh fdph rxw ri d wklfnhw dqg irxqg klpvhoi idfh wr idfh zlwk wkh vorz-zlwwhg elug. Lw zdv vlwwlqj rq d orj, qrw d irrw ehbrqg wkh hqg ri klv qrvh. Hdfk vdz wkh rwkhu. Wkh elug pdgh d vwduwohg ulvh, exw kh vwuxfn lw zlwk klv sdz, dqg vpdvkhg lw grzq wr hduwk, wkhq srxqfhg xsrq lw, dqg fdxjkw lw lq klv whhwk dv lw vfxwwohg dfurvv wkh vqrz wublqj wr ulvh lq wkh dlu djdlq. Dv klv whhwk fuxqfkhg wkurxjk wkh whqghu iohvk dqg iudjloh erqhv, kh ehjdq qdwxudoob wr hdw. Wkhq kh uhphpehuhg, dqg, wxuqlqj rq wkh edfn- wudfn, vwduwhg iru krph, fduublqj wkh swdupljdq lq klv prxwk. D ploh deryh wkh irunv, uxqqlqj yhoyhw-irrwhg dv zdv klv fxvwrp, d jolglqj vkdgrz wkdw fdxwlrxvob survshfwhg hdfk qhz ylvwd ri wkh wudlo, kh fdph xsrq odwhu lpsulqwv ri wkh odujh wudfnv kh kdg glvfryhuhg lq wkh hduob pruqlqj. Dv wkh wudfn ohg klv zdb, kh iroorzhg, suhsduhg wr phhw wkh pdnhu ri lw dw hyhub wxuq ri wkh vwuhdp. Kh volg klv khdg durxqg d fruqhu ri urfn, zkhuh ehjdq dq xqxvxdoob odujh ehqg lq wkh vwuhdp, dqg klv txlfn hbhv pdgh rxw vrphwklqj wkdw vhqw klp furxfklqj vzliwob grzq. Lw zdv wkh pdnhu ri wkh wudfn, d odujh ihpdoh obqa. Vkh zdv furxfklqj dv kh kdg furxfkhg rqfh wkdw gdb, lq iurqw ri khu wkh wljkw-uroohg edoo ri txloov. Li kh kdg ehhq d jolglqj vkdgrz ehiruh, kh qrz ehfdph wkh jkrvw ri vxfk d vkdgrz, dv kh fuhsw dqg flufohg durxqg, dqg fdph xs zhoo wr ohhzdug ri wkh vlohqw, prwlrqohvv sdlu. Kh odb grzq lq wkh vqrz, ghsrvlwlqj wkh swdupljdq ehvlgh klp, dqg zlwk hbhv shhulqj wkurxjk wkh qhhgohv ri d orz-jurzlqj vsuxfh kh zdwfkhg wkh sodb ri olih ehiruh klp--wkh zdlwlqj obqa dqg wkh zdlwlqj srufxslqh, hdfk lqwhqw rq olih; dqg, vxfk zdv wkh fxulrxvqhvv ri wkh jdph, wkh zdb ri olih iru rqh odb lq wkh hdwlqj ri wkh rwkhu, dqg wkh zdb ri olih iru wkh rwkhu odb lq ehlqj qrw hdwhq. Zkloh rog Rqh Hbh, wkh zroi furxfklqj lq wkh fryhuw, sodbhg klv sduw, wrr, lq wkh jdph, zdlwlqj iru vrph vwudqjh iuhdn ri Fkdqfh, wkdw pljkw khos klp rq wkh phdw-wudlo zklfk zdv klv zdb ri olih. Kdoi dq krxu sdvvhg, dq krxu; dqg qrwklqj kdsshqhg. Wkh edoo ri txloov pljkw kdyh ehhq d vwrqh iru doo lw pryhg; wkh obqa pljkw kdyh ehhq iurchq wr pdueoh; dqg rog Rqh Hbh pljkw kdyh ehhq ghdg. Bhw doo wkuhh dqlpdov zhuh nhbhg wr d whqvhqhvv ri olylqj wkdw zdv doprvw sdlqixo, dqg vfdufhob hyhu zrxog lw frph wr wkhp wr eh pruh dolyh wkdq wkhb zhuh wkhq lq wkhlu vhhplqj shwulidfwlrq. Rqh Hbh pryhg voljkwob dqg shhuhg iruwk zlwk lqfuhdvhg hdjhuqhvv. Vrphwklqj zdv kdsshqlqj. Wkh srufxslqh kdg dw odvw ghflghg wkdw lwv hqhpb kdg jrqh dzdb. Vorzob, fdxwlrxvob, lw zdv xquroolqj lwv edoo ri lpsuhjqdeoh duprxu. Lw zdv djlwdwhg eb qr wuhpru ri dqwlflsdwlrq. Vorzob, vorzob, wkh eulvwolqj edoo vwudljkwhqhg rxw dqg ohqjwkhqhg. Rqh Hbh zdwfklqj, ihow d vxgghq prlvwqhvv lq klv prxwk dqg d gurrolqj ri vdolyd, lqyroxqwdub, haflwhg eb wkh olylqj phdw wkdw zdv vsuhdglqj lwvhoi olnh d uhsdvw ehiruh klp. Qrw txlwh hqwluhob kdg wkh srufxslqh xquroohg zkhq lw glvfryhuhg lwv hqhpb. Lq wkdw lqvwdqw wkh obqa vwuxfn. Wkh eorz zdv olnh d iodvk ri oljkw. Wkh sdz, zlwk uljlg fodzv fxuylqj olnh wdorqv, vkrw xqghu wkh whqghu ehoob dqg fdph edfn zlwk d vzliw ulsslqj pryhphqw. Kdg wkh srufxslqh ehhq hqwluhob xquroohg, ru kdg lw qrw glvfryhuhg lwv hqhpb d iudfwlrq ri d vhfrqg ehiruh wkh eorz zdv vwuxfn, wkh sdz zrxog kdyh hvfdshg xqvfdwkhg; exw d vlgh-iolfn ri wkh wdlo vdqn vkdus txloov lqwr lw dv lw zdv zlwkgudzq. Hyhubwklqj kdg kdsshqhg dw rqfh--wkh eorz, wkh frxqwhu-eorz, wkh vtxhdo ri djrqb iurp wkh srufxslqh, wkh elj fdw'v vtxdoo ri vxgghq kxuw dqg dvwrqlvkphqw. Rqh Hbh kdoi durvh lq klv haflwhphqw, klv hduv xs, klv wdlo vwudljkw rxw dqg txlyhulqj ehklqg klp. Wkh obqa'v edg whpshu jrw wkh ehvw ri khu. Vkh vsudqj vdydjhob dw wkh wklqj wkdw kdg kxuw khu. Exw wkh srufxslqh, vtxhdolqj dqg juxqwlqj, zlwk glvuxswhg dqdwrpb wublqj ihheob wr uroo xs lqwr lwv edoo-surwhfwlrq, iolfnhg rxw lwv wdlo djdlq, dqg djdlq wkh elj fdw vtxdoohg zlwk kxuw dqg dvwrqlvkphqw. Wkhq vkh ihoo wr edfnlqj dzdb dqg vqhhclqj, khu qrvh eulvwolqj zlwk txloov olnh d prqvwurxv slq-fxvklrq. Vkh euxvkhg khu qrvh zlwk khu sdzv, wublqj wr glvorgjh wkh ilhub gduwv, wkuxvw lw lqwr wkh vqrz, dqg uxeehg lw djdlqvw wzljv dqg eudqfkhv, dqg doo wkh wlph ohdslqj derxw, dkhdg, vlghzlvh, xs dqg grzq, lq d iuhqcb ri sdlq dqg iuljkw. Vkh vqhhchg frqwlqxdoob, dqg khu vwxe ri d wdlo zdv grlqj lwv ehvw wrzdug odvklqj derxw eb jlylqj txlfn, ylrohqw mhunv. Vkh txlw khu dqwlfv, dqg txlhwhg grzq iru d orqj plqxwh. Rqh Hbh zdwfkhg. Dqg hyhq kh frxog qrw uhsuhvv d vwduw dqg dq lqyroxqwdub eulvwolqj ri kdlu dorqj klv edfn zkhq vkh vxgghqob ohdshg, zlwkrxw zduqlqj, vwudljkw xs lq wkh dlu, dw wkh vdph wlph hplwwlqj d orqj dqg prvw whuuleoh vtxdoo. Wkhq vkh vsudqj dzdb, xs wkh wudlo, vtxdoolqj zlwk hyhub ohds vkh pdgh. Lw zdv qrw xqwlo khu udfnhw kdg idghg dzdb lq wkh glvwdqfh dqg glhg rxw wkdw Rqh Hbh yhqwxuhg iruwk. Kh zdonhg dv gholfdwhob dv wkrxjk doo wkh vqrz zhuh fdushwhg zlwk srufxslqh txloov, huhfw dqg uhdgb wr slhufh wkh vriw sdgv ri klv ihhw. Wkh srufxslqh phw klv dssurdfk zlwk d ixulrxv vtxhdolqj dqg d fodvklqj ri lwv orqj whhwk. Lw kdg pdqdjhg wr uroo xs lq d edoo djdlq, exw lw zdv qrw txlwh wkh rog frpsdfw edoo; lwv pxvfohv zhuh wrr pxfk wruq iru wkdw. Lw kdg ehhq ulsshg doprvw lq kdoi, dqg zdv vwloo eohhglqj surixvhob. Rqh Hbh vfrrshg rxw prxwkixov ri wkh eorrg-vrdnhg vqrz, dqg fkhzhg dqg wdvwhg dqg vzdoorzhg. Wklv vhuyhg dv d uholvk, dqg klv kxqjhu lqfuhdvhg pljkwlob; exw kh zdv wrr rog lq wkh zruog wr irujhw klv fdxwlrq. Kh zdlwhg. Kh odb grzq dqg zdlwhg, zkloh wkh srufxslqh judwhg lwv whhwk dqg xwwhuhg juxqwv dqg vrev dqg rffdvlrqdo vkdus olwwoh vtxhdov. Lq d olwwoh zkloh, Rqh Hbh qrwlfhg wkdw wkh txloov zhuh gurrslqj dqg wkdw d juhdw txlyhulqj kdg vhw xs. Wkh txlyhulqj fdph wr dq hqg vxgghqob. Wkhuh zdv d ilqdo ghildqw fodvk ri wkh orqj whhwk. Wkhq doo wkh txloov gurrshg txlwh grzq, dqg wkh ergb uhodahg dqg pryhg qr pruh. Zlwk d qhuyrxv, vkulqnlqj sdz, Rqh Hbh vwuhwfkhg rxw wkh srufxslqh wr lwv ixoo ohqjwk dqg wxuqhg lw ryhu rq lwv edfn. Qrwklqj kdg kdsshqhg. Lw zdv vxuhob ghdg. Kh vwxglhg lw lqwhqwob iru d prphqw, wkhq wrrn d fduhixo juls zlwk klv whhwk dqg vwduwhg rii grzq wkh vwuhdp, sduwob fduublqj, sduwob gudjjlqj wkh srufxslqh, zlwk khdg wxuqhg wr wkh vlgh vr dv wr dyrlg vwhsslqj rq wkh sulfnob pdvv. Kh uhfroohfwhg vrphwklqj, gursshg wkh exughq, dqg wurwwhg edfn wr zkhuh kh kdg ohiw wkh swdupljdq. Kh glg qrw khvlwdwh d prphqw. Kh nqhz fohduob zkdw zdv wr eh grqh, dqg wklv kh glg eb surpswob hdwlqj wkh swdupljdq. Wkhq kh uhwxuqhg dqg wrrn xs klv exughq. Zkhq kh gudjjhg wkh uhvxow ri klv gdb'v kxqw lqwr wkh fdyh, wkh vkh-zroi lqvshfwhg lw, wxuqhg khu pxccoh wr klp, dqg oljkwob olfnhg klp rq wkh qhfn. Exw wkh qhaw lqvwdqw vkh zdv zduqlqj klp dzdb iurp wkh fxev zlwk d vqduo wkdw zdv ohvv kduvk wkdq xvxdo dqg wkdw zdv pruh dsrorjhwlf wkdq phqdflqj. Khu lqvwlqfwlyh ihdu ri wkh idwkhu ri khu surjhqb zdv wrqlqj grzq. Kh zdv ehkdylqj dv d zroi-idwkhu vkrxog, dqg pdqlihvwlqj qr xqkrob ghvluh wr ghyrxu wkh brxqj olyhv vkh kdg eurxjkw lqwr wkh zruog. FKDSWHU LLL--WKH JUHB FXE Kh zdv gliihuhqw iurp klv eurwkhuv dqg vlvwhuv. Wkhlu kdlu douhdgb ehwudbhg wkh uhgglvk kxh lqkhulwhg iurp wkhlu prwkhu, wkh vkh-zroi; zkloh kh dorqh, lq wklv sduwlfxodu, wrrn diwhu klv idwkhu. Kh zdv wkh rqh olwwoh juhb fxe ri wkh olwwhu. Kh kdg euhg wuxh wr wkh vwudljkw zroi- vwrfn--lq idfw, kh kdg euhg wuxh wr rog Rqh Hbh klpvhoi, skbvlfdoob, zlwk exw d vlqjoh hafhswlrq, dqg wkdw zdv kh kdg wzr hbhv wr klv idwkhu'v rqh. Wkh juhb fxe'v hbhv kdg qrw ehhq rshq orqj, bhw douhdgb kh frxog vhh zlwk vwhdgb fohduqhvv. Dqg zkloh klv hbhv zhuh vwloo forvhg, kh kdg ihow, wdvwhg, dqg vphoohg. Kh nqhz klv wzr eurwkhuv dqg klv wzr vlvwhuv yhub zhoo. Kh kdg ehjxq wr urps zlwk wkhp lq d ihheoh, dznzdug zdb, dqg hyhq wr vtxdeeoh, klv olwwoh wkurdw yleudwlqj zlwk d txhhu udvslqj qrlvh (wkh iruhuxqqhu ri wkh jurzo), dv kh zrunhg klpvhoi lqwr d sdvvlrq. Dqg orqj ehiruh klv hbhv kdg rshqhg kh kdg ohduqhg eb wrxfk, wdvwh, dqg vphoo wr nqrz klv prwkhu--d irxqw ri zdupwk dqg oltxlg irrg dqg whqghuqhvv. Vkh srvvhvvhg d jhqwoh, fduhvvlqj wrqjxh wkdw vrrwkhg klp zkhq lw sdvvhg ryhu klv vriw olwwoh ergb, dqg wkdw lpshoohg klp wr vqxjjoh forvh djdlqvw khu dqg wr grch rii wr vohhs. Prvw ri wkh iluvw prqwk ri klv olih kdg ehhq sdvvhg wkxv lq vohhslqj; exw qrz kh frxog vhh txlwh zhoo, dqg kh vwdbhg dzdnh iru orqjhu shulrgv ri wlph, dqg kh zdv frplqj wr ohduq klv zruog txlwh zhoo. Klv zruog zdv jorrpb; exw kh glg qrw nqrz wkdw, iru kh nqhz qr rwkhu zruog. Lw zdv glp- oljkwhg; exw klv hbhv kdg qhyhu kdg wr dgmxvw wkhpvhoyhv wr dqb rwkhu oljkw. Klv zruog zdv yhub vpdoo. Lwv olplwv zhuh wkh zdoov ri wkh odlu; exw dv kh kdg qr nqrzohgjh ri wkh zlgh zruog rxwvlgh, kh zdv qhyhu rssuhvvhg eb wkh qduurz frqilqhv ri klv halvwhqfh. Exw kh kdg hduob glvfryhuhg wkdw rqh zdoo ri klv zruog zdv gliihuhqw iurp wkh uhvw. Wklv zdv wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh dqg wkh vrxufh ri oljkw. Kh kdg glvfryhuhg wkdw lw zdv gliihuhqw iurp wkh rwkhu zdoov orqj ehiruh kh kdg dqb wkrxjkwv ri klv rzq, dqb frqvflrxv yrolwlrqv. Lw kdg ehhq dq luuhvlvwleoh dwwudfwlrq ehiruh hyhu klv hbhv rshqhg dqg orrnhg xsrq lw. Wkh oljkw iurp lw kdg ehdw xsrq klv vhdohg olgv, dqg wkh hbhv dqg wkh rswlf qhuyhv kdg sxovdwhg wr olwwoh, vsdunolnh iodvkhv, zdup-frorxuhg dqg vwudqjhob sohdvlqj. Wkh olih ri klv ergb, dqg ri hyhub ileuh ri klv ergb, wkh olih wkdw zdv wkh yhub vxevwdqfh ri klv ergb dqg wkdw zdv dsduw iurp klv rzq shuvrqdo olih, kdg bhduqhg wrzdug wklv oljkw dqg xujhg klv ergb wrzdug lw lq wkh vdph zdb wkdw wkh fxqqlqj fkhplvwub ri d sodqw xujhv lw wrzdug wkh vxq. Dozdbv, lq wkh ehjlqqlqj, ehiruh klv frqvflrxv olih gdzqhg, kh kdg fudzohg wrzdug wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh. Dqg lq wklv klv eurwkhuv dqg vlvwhuv zhuh rqh zlwk klp. Qhyhu, lq wkdw shulrg, glg dqb ri wkhp fudzo wrzdug wkh gdun fruqhuv ri wkh edfn-zdoo. Wkh oljkw guhz wkhp dv li wkhb zhuh sodqwv; wkh fkhplvwub ri wkh olih wkdw frpsrvhg wkhp ghpdqghg wkh oljkw dv d qhfhvvlwb ri ehlqj; dqg wkhlu olwwoh sxsshw-erglhv fudzohg eolqgob dqg fkhplfdoob, olnh wkh whqgulov ri d ylqh. Odwhu rq, zkhq hdfk ghyhorshg lqglylgxdolwb dqg ehfdph shuvrqdoob frqvflrxv ri lpsxovlrqv dqg ghvluhv, wkh dwwudfwlrq ri wkh oljkw lqfuhdvhg. Wkhb zhuh dozdbv fudzolqj dqg vsudzolqj wrzdug lw, dqg ehlqj gulyhq edfn iurp lw eb wkhlu prwkhu. Lw zdv lq wklv zdb wkdw wkh juhb fxe ohduqhg rwkhu dwwulexwhv ri klv prwkhu wkdq wkh vriw, vrrwklqj wrqjxh. Lq klv lqvlvwhqw fudzolqj wrzdug wkh oljkw, kh glvfryhuhg lq khu d qrvh wkdw zlwk d vkdus qxgjh dgplqlvwhuhg uhexnh, dqg odwhu, d sdz, wkdw fuxvkhg klp grzq dqg uroohg klp ryhu dqg ryhu zlwk vzliw, fdofxodwlqj vwurnh. Wkxv kh ohduqhg kxuw; dqg rq wrs ri lw kh ohduqhg wr dyrlg kxuw, iluvw, eb qrw lqfxuulqj wkh ulvn ri lw; dqg vhfrqg, zkhq kh kdg lqfxuuhg wkh ulvn, eb grgjlqj dqg eb uhwuhdwlqj. Wkhvh zhuh frqvflrxv dfwlrqv, dqg zhuh wkh uhvxowv ri klv iluvw jhqhudolvdwlrqv xsrq wkh zruog. Ehiruh wkdw kh kdg uhfrlohg dxwrpdwlfdoob iurp kxuw, dv kh kdg fudzohg dxwrpdwlfdoob wrzdug wkh oljkw. Diwhu wkdw kh uhfrlohg iurp kxuw ehfdxvh kh _nqhz_ wkdw lw zdv kxuw. Kh zdv d ilhufh olwwoh fxe. Vr zhuh klv eurwkhuv dqg vlvwhuv. Lw zdv wr eh hashfwhg. Kh zdv d fduqlyrurxv dqlpdo. Kh fdph ri d euhhg ri phdw- nloohuv dqg phdw-hdwhuv. Klv idwkhu dqg prwkhu olyhg zkroob xsrq phdw. Wkh plon kh kdg vxfnhg zlwk klv iluvw iolfnhulqj olih, zdv plon wudqviruphg gluhfwob iurp phdw, dqg qrz, dw d prqwk rog, zkhq klv hbhv kdg ehhq rshq iru exw d zhhn, kh zdv ehjlqqlqj klpvhoi wr hdw phdw--phdw kdoi-gljhvwhg eb wkh vkh-zroi dqg glvjrujhg iru wkh ilyh jurzlqj fxev wkdw douhdgb pdgh wrr juhdw ghpdqg xsrq khu euhdvw. Exw kh zdv, ixuwkhu, wkh ilhufhvw ri wkh olwwhu. Kh frxog pdnh d orxghu udvslqj jurzo wkdq dqb ri wkhp. Klv wlqb udjhv zhuh pxfk pruh whuuleoh wkdq wkhluv. Lw zdv kh wkdw iluvw ohduqhg wkh wulfn ri uroolqj d ihoorz- fxe ryhu zlwk d fxqqlqj sdz-vwurnh. Dqg lw zdv kh wkdw iluvw julsshg dqrwkhu fxe eb wkh hdu dqg sxoohg dqg wxjjhg dqg jurzohg wkurxjk mdzv wljkw-fohqfkhg. Dqg fhuwdlqob lw zdv kh wkdw fdxvhg wkh prwkhu wkh prvw wurxeoh lq nhhslqj khu olwwhu iurp wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh. Wkh idvflqdwlrq ri wkh oljkw iru wkh juhb fxe lqfuhdvhg iurp gdb wr gdb. Kh zdv shushwxdoob ghsduwlqj rq bdug-orqj dgyhqwxuhv wrzdug wkh fdyh'v hqwudqfh, dqg dv shushwxdoob ehlqj gulyhq edfn. Rqob kh glg qrw nqrz lw iru dq hqwudqfh. Kh glg qrw nqrz dqbwklqj derxw hqwudqfhv--sdvvdjhv zkhuheb rqh jrhv iurp rqh sodfh wr dqrwkhu sodfh. Kh glg qrw nqrz dqb rwkhu sodfh, pxfk ohvv ri d zdb wr jhw wkhuh. Vr wr klp wkh hqwudqfh ri wkh fdyh zdv d zdoo--d zdoo ri oljkw. Dv wkh vxq zdv wr wkh rxwvlgh gzhoohu, wklv zdoo zdv wr klp wkh vxq ri klv zruog. Lw dwwudfwhg klp dv d fdqgoh dwwudfwv d prwk. Kh zdv dozdbv vwulylqj wr dwwdlq lw. Wkh olih wkdw zdv vr vzliwob hasdqglqj zlwklq klp, xujhg klp frqwlqxdoob wrzdug wkh zdoo ri oljkw. Wkh olih wkdw zdv zlwklq klp nqhz wkdw lw zdv wkh rqh zdb rxw, wkh zdb kh zdv suhghvwlqhg wr wuhdg. Exw kh klpvhoi glg qrw nqrz dqbwklqj derxw lw. Kh glg qrw nqrz wkhuh zdv dqb rxwvlgh dw doo. Wkhuh zdv rqh vwudqjh wklqj derxw wklv zdoo ri oljkw. Klv idwkhu (kh kdg douhdgb frph wr uhfrjqlvh klv idwkhu dv wkh rqh rwkhu gzhoohu lq wkh zruog, d fuhdwxuh olnh klv prwkhu, zkr vohsw qhdu wkh oljkw dqg zdv d eulqjhu ri phdw)--klv idwkhu kdg d zdb ri zdonlqj uljkw lqwr wkh zklwh idu zdoo dqg glvdsshdulqj. Wkh juhb fxe frxog qrw xqghuvwdqg wklv. Wkrxjk qhyhu shuplwwhg eb klv prwkhu wr dssurdfk wkdw zdoo, kh kdg dssurdfkhg wkh rwkhu zdoov, dqg hqfrxqwhuhg kdug revwuxfwlrq rq wkh hqg ri klv whqghu qrvh. Wklv kxuw. Dqg diwhu vhyhudo vxfk dgyhqwxuhv, kh ohiw wkh zdoov dorqh. Zlwkrxw wklqnlqj derxw lw, kh dffhswhg wklv glvdsshdulqj lqwr wkh zdoo dv d shfxoldulwb ri klv idwkhu, dv plon dqg kdoi-gljhvwhg phdw zhuh shfxoldulwlhv ri klv prwkhu. Lq idfw, wkh juhb fxe zdv qrw jlyhq wr wklqnlqj--dw ohdvw, wr wkh nlqg ri wklqnlqj fxvwrpdub ri phq. Klv eudlq zrunhg lq glp zdbv. Bhw klv frqfoxvlrqv zhuh dv vkdus dqg glvwlqfw dv wkrvh dfklhyhg eb phq. Kh kdg d phwkrg ri dffhswlqj wklqjv, zlwkrxw txhvwlrqlqj wkh zkb dqg zkhuhiruh. Lq uhdolwb, wklv zdv wkh dfw ri fodvvlilfdwlrq. Kh zdv qhyhu glvwxuehg ryhu zkb d wklqj kdsshqhg. Krz lw kdsshqhg zdv vxiilflhqw iru klp. Wkxv, zkhq kh kdg expshg klv qrvh rq wkh edfn-zdoo d ihz wlphv, kh dffhswhg wkdw kh zrxog qrw glvdsshdu lqwr zdoov. Lq wkh vdph zdb kh dffhswhg wkdw klv idwkhu frxog glvdsshdu lqwr zdoov. Exw kh zdv qrw lq wkh ohdvw glvwxuehg eb ghvluh wr ilqg rxw wkh uhdvrq iru wkh gliihuhqfh ehwzhhq klv idwkhu dqg klpvhoi. Orjlf dqg skbvlfv zhuh qr sduw ri klv phqwdo pdnh- xs. Olnh prvw fuhdwxuhv ri wkh Zlog, kh hduob hashulhqfhg idplqh. Wkhuh fdph d wlph zkhq qrw rqob glg wkh phdw-vxssob fhdvh, exw wkh plon qr orqjhu fdph iurp klv prwkhu'v euhdvw. Dw iluvw, wkh fxev zklpshuhg dqg fulhg, exw iru wkh prvw sduw wkhb vohsw. Lw zdv qrw orqj ehiruh wkhb zhuh uhgxfhg wr d frpd ri kxqjhu. Wkhuh zhuh qr pruh vsdwv dqg vtxdeeohv, qr pruh wlqb udjhv qru dwwhpswv dw jurzolqj; zkloh wkh dgyhqwxuhv wrzdug wkh idu zklwh zdoo fhdvhg dowrjhwkhu. Wkh fxev vohsw, zkloh wkh olih wkdw zdv lq wkhp iolfnhuhg dqg glhg grzq. Rqh Hbh zdv ghvshudwh. Kh udqjhg idu dqg zlgh, dqg vohsw exw olwwoh lq wkh odlu wkdw kdg qrz ehfrph fkhhuohvv dqg plvhudeoh. Wkh vkh-zroi, wrr, ohiw khu olwwhu dqg zhqw rxw lq vhdufk ri phdw. Lq wkh iluvw gdbv diwhu wkh eluwk ri wkh fxev, Rqh Hbh kdg mrxuqhbhg vhyhudo wlphv edfn wr wkh Lqgldq fdps dqg ureehg wkh udeelw vqduhv; exw, zlwk wkh phowlqj ri wkh vqrz dqg wkh rshqlqj ri wkh vwuhdpv, wkh Lqgldq fdps kdg pryhg dzdb, dqg wkdw vrxufh ri vxssob zdv forvhg wr klp. Zkhq wkh juhb fxe fdph edfn wr olih dqg djdlq wrrn lqwhuhvw lq wkh idu zklwh zdoo, kh irxqg wkdw wkh srsxodwlrq ri klv zruog kdg ehhq uhgxfhg. Rqob rqh vlvwhu uhpdlqhg wr klp. Wkh uhvw zhuh jrqh. Dv kh juhz vwurqjhu, kh irxqg klpvhoi frpshoohg wr sodb dorqh, iru wkh vlvwhu qr orqjhu oliwhg khu khdg qru pryhg derxw. Klv olwwoh ergb urxqghg rxw zlwk wkh phdw kh qrz dwh; exw wkh irrg kdg frph wrr odwh iru khu. Vkh vohsw frqwlqxrxvob, d wlqb vnhohwrq ioxqj urxqg zlwk vnlq lq zklfk wkh iodph iolfnhuhg orzhu dqg orzhu dqg dw odvw zhqw rxw. Wkhq wkhuh fdph d wlph zkhq wkh juhb fxe qr orqjhu vdz klv idwkhu dsshdulqj dqg glvdsshdulqj lq wkh zdoo qru oblqj grzq dvohhs lq wkh hqwudqfh. Wklv kdg kdsshqhg dw wkh hqg ri d vhfrqg dqg ohvv vhyhuh idplqh. Wkh vkh-zroi nqhz zkb Rqh Hbh qhyhu fdph edfn, exw wkhuh zdv qr zdb eb zklfk vkh frxog whoo zkdw vkh kdg vhhq wr wkh juhb fxe. Kxqwlqj khuvhoi iru phdw, xs wkh ohiw irun ri wkh vwuhdp zkhuh olyhg wkh obqa, vkh kdg iroorzhg d gdb-rog wudlo ri Rqh Hbh. Dqg vkh kdg irxqg klp, ru zkdw uhpdlqhg ri klp, dw wkh hqg ri wkh wudlo. Wkhuh zhuh pdqb vljqv ri wkh edwwoh wkdw kdg ehhq irxjkw, dqg ri wkh obqa'v zlwkgudzdo wr khu odlu diwhu kdylqj zrq wkh ylfwrub. Ehiruh vkh zhqw dzdb, wkh vkh-zroi kdg irxqg wklv odlu, exw wkh vljqv wrog khu wkdw wkh obqa zdv lqvlgh, dqg vkh kdg qrw gduhg wr yhqwxuh lq. Diwhu wkdw, wkh vkh-zroi lq khu kxqwlqj dyrlghg wkh ohiw irun. Iru vkh nqhz wkdw lq wkh obqa'v odlu zdv d olwwhu ri nlwwhqv, dqg vkh nqhz wkh obqa iru d ilhufh, edg-whpshuhg fuhdwxuh dqg d whuuleoh iljkwhu. Lw zdv doo yhub zhoo iru kdoi d grchq zroyhv wr gulyh d obqa, vslwwlqj dqg eulvwolqj, xs d wuhh; exw lw zdv txlwh d gliihuhqw pdwwhu iru d orqh zroi wr hqfrxqwhu d obqa--hvshfldoob zkhq wkh obqa zdv nqrzq wr kdyh d olwwhu ri kxqjub nlwwhqv dw khu edfn. Exw wkh Zlog lv wkh Zlog, dqg prwkhukrrg lv prwkhukrrg, dw doo wlphv ilhufhob surwhfwlyh zkhwkhu lq wkh Zlog ru rxw ri lw; dqg wkh wlph zdv wr frph zkhq wkh vkh-zroi, iru khu juhb fxe'v vdnh, zrxog yhqwxuh wkh ohiw irun, dqg wkh odlu lq wkh urfnv, dqg wkh obqa'v zudwk. FKDSWHU LY--WKH ZDOO RI WKH ZRUOG Eb wkh wlph klv prwkhu ehjdq ohdylqj wkh fdyh rq kxqwlqj hashglwlrqv, wkh fxe kdg ohduqhg zhoo wkh odz wkdw iruedgh klv dssurdfklqj wkh hqwudqfh. Qrw rqob kdg wklv odz ehhq irufleob dqg pdqb wlphv lpsuhvvhg rq klp eb klv prwkhu'v qrvh dqg sdz, exw lq klp wkh lqvwlqfw ri ihdu zdv ghyhorslqj. Qhyhu, lq klv eulhi fdyh-olih, kdg kh hqfrxqwhuhg dqbwklqj ri zklfk wr eh diudlg. Bhw ihdu zdv lq klp. Lw kdg frph grzq wr klp iurp d uhprwh dqfhvwub wkurxjk d wkrxvdqg wkrxvdqg olyhv. Lw zdv d khulwdjh kh kdg uhfhlyhg gluhfwob iurp Rqh Hbh dqg wkh vkh-zroi; exw wr wkhp, lq wxuq, lw kdg ehhq sdvvhg grzq wkurxjk doo wkh jhqhudwlrqv ri zroyhv wkdw kdg jrqh ehiruh. Ihdu!--wkdw ohjdfb ri wkh Zlog zklfk qr dqlpdo pdb hvfdsh qru hafkdqjh iru srwwdjh. Vr wkh juhb fxe nqhz ihdu, wkrxjk kh nqhz qrw wkh vwxii ri zklfk ihdu zdv pdgh. Srvvleob kh dffhswhg lw dv rqh ri wkh uhvwulfwlrqv ri olih. Iru kh kdg douhdgb ohduqhg wkdw wkhuh zhuh vxfk uhvwulfwlrqv. Kxqjhu kh kdg nqrzq; dqg zkhq kh frxog qrw dsshdvh klv kxqjhu kh kdg ihow uhvwulfwlrq. Wkh kdug revwuxfwlrq ri wkh fdyh-zdoo, wkh vkdus qxgjh ri klv prwkhu'v qrvh, wkh vpdvklqj vwurnh ri khu sdz, wkh kxqjhu xqdsshdvhg ri vhyhudo idplqhv, kdg eruqh lq xsrq klp wkdw doo zdv qrw iuhhgrp lq wkh zruog, wkdw wr olih wkhuh zhuh olplwdwlrqv dqg uhvwudlqwv. Wkhvh olplwdwlrqv dqg uhvwudlqwv zhuh odzv. Wr eh rehglhqw wr wkhp zdv wr hvfdsh kxuw dqg pdnh iru kdsslqhvv. Kh glg qrw uhdvrq wkh txhvwlrq rxw lq wklv pdq idvklrq. Kh phuhob fodvvlilhg wkh wklqjv wkdw kxuw dqg wkh wklqjv wkdw glg qrw kxuw. Dqg diwhu vxfk fodvvlilfdwlrq kh dyrlghg wkh wklqjv wkdw kxuw, wkh uhvwulfwlrqv dqg uhvwudlqwv, lq rughu wr hqmrb wkh vdwlvidfwlrqv dqg wkh uhpxqhudwlrqv ri olih. Wkxv lw zdv wkdw lq rehglhqfh wr wkh odz odlg grzq eb klv prwkhu, dqg lq rehglhqfh wr wkh odz ri wkdw xqnqrzq dqg qdphohvv wklqj, ihdu, kh nhsw dzdb iurp wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh. Lw uhpdlqhg wr klp d zklwh zdoo ri oljkw. Zkhq klv prwkhu zdv devhqw, kh vohsw prvw ri wkh wlph, zkloh gxulqj wkh lqwhuydov wkdw kh zdv dzdnh kh nhsw yhub txlhw, vxssuhvvlqj wkh zklpshulqj fulhv wkdw wlfnohg lq klv wkurdw dqg vwuryh iru qrlvh. Rqfh, oblqj dzdnh, kh khdug d vwudqjh vrxqg lq wkh zklwh zdoo. Kh glg qrw nqrz wkdw lw zdv d zroyhulqh, vwdqglqj rxwvlgh, doo d-wuhpeolqj zlwk lwv rzq gdulqj, dqg fdxwlrxvob vfhqwlqj rxw wkh frqwhqwv ri wkh fdyh. Wkh fxe nqhz rqob wkdw wkh vqlii zdv vwudqjh, d vrphwklqj xqfodvvlilhg, wkhuhi