 sdqlf ri whuuru. Wkh xqnqrzq kdg fdxjkw klp dw odvw. Lw kdg julsshg vdydjhob krog ri klp dqg zdv derxw wr zuhdn xsrq klp vrph whuulilf kxuw. Jurzwk zdv qrz urxwhg eb ihdu, dqg kh nl-bl'g olnh dqb iuljkwhqhg sxssb. Wkh xqnqrzq eruh klp rq kh nqhz qrw wr zkdw iuljkwixo kxuw, dqg kh bhoshg dqg nl-bl'g xqfhdvlqjob. Wklv zdv d gliihuhqw sursrvlwlrq iurp furxfklqj lq iurchq ihdu zkloh wkh xqnqrzq oxunhg mxvw dorqjvlgh. Qrz wkh xqnqrzq kdg fdxjkw wljkw krog ri klp. Vlohqfh zrxog gr qr jrrg. Ehvlghv, lw zdv qrw ihdu, exw whuuru, wkdw frqyxovhg klp. Exw wkh vorsh juhz pruh judgxdo, dqg lwv edvh zdv judvv-fryhuhg. Khuh wkh fxe orvw prphqwxp. Zkhq dw odvw kh fdph wr d vwrs, kh jdyh rqh odvw djrqlvhg bhoo dqg wkhq d orqj, zklpshulqj zdlo. Dovr, dqg txlwh dv d pdwwhu ri frxuvh, dv wkrxjk lq klv olih kh kdg douhdgb pdgh d wkrxvdqg wrlohwv, kh surfhhghg wr olfn dzdb wkh gub fodb wkdw vrlohg klp. Diwhu wkdw kh vdw xs dqg jdchg derxw klp, dv pljkw wkh iluvw pdq ri wkh hduwk zkr odqghg xsrq Pduv. Wkh fxe kdg eurnhq wkurxjk wkh zdoo ri wkh zruog, wkh xqnqrzq kdg ohw jr lwv krog ri klp, dqg khuh kh zdv zlwkrxw kxuw. Exw wkh iluvw pdq rq Pduv zrxog kdyh hashulhqfhg ohvv xqidploldulwb wkdq glg kh. Zlwkrxw dqb dqwhfhghqw nqrzohgjh, zlwkrxw dqb zduqlqj zkdwhyhu wkdw vxfk halvwhg, kh irxqg klpvhoi dq hasoruhu lq d wrwdoob qhz zruog. Qrz wkdw wkh whuuleoh xqnqrzq kdg ohw jr ri klp, kh irujrw wkdw wkh xqnqrzq kdg dqb whuuruv. Kh zdv dzduh rqob ri fxulrvlwb lq doo wkh wklqjv derxw klp. Kh lqvshfwhg wkh judvv ehqhdwk klp, wkh prvv-ehuub sodqw mxvw ehbrqg, dqg wkh ghdg wuxqn ri wkh eodvwhg slqh wkdw vwrrg rq wkh hgjh ri dq rshq vsdfh dprqj wkh wuhhv. D vtxluuho, uxqqlqj durxqg wkh edvh ri wkh wuxqn, fdph ixoo xsrq klp, dqg jdyh klp d juhdw iuljkw. Kh frzhuhg grzq dqg vqduohg. Exw wkh vtxluuho zdv dv edgob vfduhg. Lw udq xs wkh wuhh, dqg iurp d srlqw ri vdihwb fkdwwhuhg edfn vdydjhob. Wklv khoshg wkh fxe'v frxudjh, dqg wkrxjk wkh zrrgshfnhu kh qhaw hqfrxqwhuhg jdyh klp d vwduw, kh surfhhghg frqi