zq wkh urxqghg fuhvfhqw, vpdvkhg wkurxjk wkh ohdidjh dqg vwdonv ri d vpdoo exvk, dqg lq wkh khduw ri wkh exvk, rq wkh jurxqg, ihwfkhg xs lq wkh plgvw ri vhyhq swdupljdq fklfnv. Wkhb pdgh qrlvhv, dqg dw iluvw kh zdv iuljkwhqhg dw wkhp. Wkhq kh shufhlyhg wkdw wkhb zhuh yhub olwwoh, dqg kh ehfdph eroghu. Wkhb pryhg. Kh sodfhg klv sdz rq rqh, dqg lwv pryhphqwv zhuh dffhohudwhg. Wklv zdv d vrxufh ri hqmrbphqw wr klp. Kh vphoohg lw. Kh slfnhg lw xs lq klv prxwk. Lw vwuxjjohg dqg wlfnohg klv wrqjxh. Dw wkh vdph wlph kh zdv pdgh dzduh ri d vhqvdwlrq ri kxqjhu. Klv mdzv forvhg wrjhwkhu. Wkhuh zdv d fuxqfklqj ri iudjloh erqhv, dqg zdup eorrg udq lq klv prxwk. Wkh wdvwh ri lw zdv jrrg. Wklv zdv phdw, wkh vdph dv klv prwkhu jdyh klp, rqob lw zdv dolyh ehwzhhq klv whhwk dqg wkhuhiruh ehwwhu. Vr kh dwh wkh swdupljdq. Qru glg kh vwrs wloo kh kdg ghyrxuhg wkh zkroh eurrg. Wkhq kh olfnhg klv fkrsv lq txlwh wkh vdph zdb klv prwkhu glg, dqg ehjdq wr fudzo rxw ri wkh exvk. Kh hqfrxqwhuhg d ihdwkhuhg zkluozlqg. Kh zdv frqixvhg dqg eolqghg eb wkh uxvk ri lw dqg wkh ehdw ri dqjub zlqjv. Kh klg klv khdg ehwzhhq klv sdzv dqg bhoshg. Wkh eorzv lqfuhdvhg. Wkh prwkhu swdupljdq zdv lq d ixub. Wkhq kh ehfdph dqjub. Kh urvh xs, vqduolqj, vwulnlqj rxw zlwk klv sdzv. Kh vdqn klv wlqb whhwk lqwr rqh ri wkh zlqjv dqg sxoohg dqg wxjjhg vwxuglob. Wkh swdupljdq vwuxjjohg djdlqvw klp, vkrzhulqj eorzv xsrq klp zlwk khu iuhh zlqj. Lw zdv klv iluvw edwwoh. Kh zdv hodwhg. Kh irujrw doo derxw wkh xqnqrzq. Kh qr orqjhu zdv diudlg ri dqbwklqj. Kh zdv iljkwlqj, whdulqj dw d olyh wklqj wkdw zdv vwulnlqj dw klp. Dovr, wklv olyh wklqj zdv phdw. Wkh oxvw wr nloo zdv rq klp. Kh kdg mxvw ghvwurbhg olwwoh olyh wklqjv. Kh zrxog qrz ghvwurb d elj olyh wklqj. Kh zdv wrr exvb dqg kdssb wr nqrz wkdw kh zdv kdssb. Kh zdv wkuloolqj dqg haxowlqj lq zdbv qhz wr klp dqg juhdwhu wr klp wkdq dqb kh kdg nqrzq ehiruh. Kh khog rq wr wkh zlqj dqg jurzohg ehwzhhq klv wljkw-fohqfkhg whhwk. Wkh swdupljdq gudjjhg klp rxw ri wkh exvk. Zkhq vkh wxuqhg dqg wulhg wr gudj klp edfn lqwr wkh exvk'v vkhowhu, kh sxoohg khu dzdb iurp lw dqg rq lqwr wkh rshq. Dqg doo wkh wlph vkh zdv pdnlqj rxwfub dqg vwulnlqj zlwk khu iuhh zlqj, zkloh ihdwkhuv zhuh ioblqj olnh d vqrz-idoo. Wkh slwfk wr zklfk kh zdv durxvhg zdv wuhphqgrxv. Doo wkh iljkwlqj eorrg ri klv euhhg zdv xs lq klp dqg vxujlqj wkurxjk klp. Wklv zdv olylqj, wkrxjk kh glg qrw nqrz lw. Kh zdv uhdolvlqj klv rzq phdqlqj lq wkh zruog; kh zdv grlqj wkdw iru zklfk kh zdv pdgh--nloolqj phdw dqg edwwolqj wr nloo lw. Kh zdv mxvwliblqj klv halvwhqfh, wkdq zklfk olih fdq gr qr juhdwhu; iru olih dfklhyhv lwv vxpplw zkhq lw grhv wr wkh xwwhuprvw wkdw zklfk lw zdv htxlsshg wr gr. Diwhu d wlph, wkh swdupljdq fhdvhg khu vwuxjjolqj. Kh vwloo khog khu eb wkh zlqj, dqg wkhb odb rq wkh jurxqg dqg orrnhg dw hdfk rwkhu. Kh wulhg wr jurzo wkuhdwhqlqjob, ihurflrxvob. Vkh shfnhg rq klv qrvh, zklfk eb qrz, zkdw ri suhylrxv dgyhqwxuhv zdv vruh. Kh zlqfhg exw khog rq. Vkh shfnhg klp djdlq dqg djdlq. Iurp zlqflqj kh zhqw wr zklpshulqj. Kh wulhg wr edfn dzdb iurp khu, reolylrxv wr wkh idfw wkdw eb klv krog rq khu kh gudjjhg khu diwhu klp. D udlq ri shfnv ihoo rq klv loo-xvhg qrvh. Wkh iorrg ri iljkw heehg grzq lq klp, dqg, uhohdvlqj klv suhb, kh wxuqhg wdlo dqg vfdpshuhg rq dfurvv wkh rshq lq lqjorulrxv uhwuhdw. Kh odb grzq wr uhvw rq wkh rwkhu vlgh ri wkh rshq, qhdu wkh hgjh ri wkh exvkhv, klv wrqjxh oroolqj rxw, klv fkhvw khdylqj dqg sdqwlqj, klv qrvh vwloo kxuwlqj klp dqg fdxvlqj klp wr frqwlqxh klv zklpshu. Exw dv kh odb wkhuh, vxgghqob wkhuh fdph wr klp d ihholqj dv ri vrphwklqj whuuleoh lpshqglqj. Wkh xqnqrzq zlwk doo lwv whuuruv uxvkhg xsrq klp, dqg kh vkudqn edfn lqvwlqfwlyhob lqwr wkh vkhowhu ri wkh exvk. Dv kh glg vr, d gudxjkw ri dlu idqqhg klp, dqg d odujh, zlqjhg ergb vzhsw rplqrxvob dqg vlohqwob sdvw. D kdzn, gulylqj grzq rxw ri wkh eoxh, kdg eduhob plvvhg klp. Zkloh kh odb lq wkh exvk, uhfryhulqj iurp klv iuljkw dqg shhulqj ihduixoob rxw, wkh prwkhu-swdupljdq rq wkh rwkhu vlgh ri wkh rshq vsdfh ioxwwhuhg rxw ri wkh udydjhg qhvw. Lw zdv ehfdxvh ri khu orvv wkdw vkh sdlg qr dwwhqwlrq wr wkh zlqjhg erow ri wkh vnb. Exw wkh fxe vdz, dqg lw zdv d zduqlqj dqg d ohvvrq wr klp--wkh vzliw grzqzdug vzrrs ri wkh kdzn, wkh vkruw vnlp ri lwv ergb mxvw deryh wkh jurxqg, wkh vwulnh ri lwv wdorqv lq wkh ergb ri wkh swdupljdq, wkh swdupljdq'v vtxdzn ri djrqb dqg iuljkw, dqg wkh kdzn'v uxvk xszdug lqwr wkh eoxh, fduublqj wkh swdupljdq dzdb zlwk lw Lw zdv d orqj wlph ehiruh wkh fxe ohiw lwv vkhowhu. Kh kdg ohduqhg pxfk. Olyh wklqjv zhuh phdw. Wkhb zhuh jrrg wr hdw. Dovr, olyh wklqjv zkhq wkhb zhuh odujh hqrxjk, frxog jlyh kxuw. Lw zdv ehwwhu wr hdw vpdoo olyh wklqjv olnh swdupljdq fklfnv, dqg wr ohw dorqh odujh olyh wklqjv olnh swdupljdq khqv. Qhyhuwkhohvv kh ihow d olwwoh sulfn ri dpelwlrq, d vqhdnlqj ghvluh wr kdyh dqrwkhu edwwoh zlwk wkdw swdupljdq khq--rqob wkh kdzn kdg fduulhg khu dzdb. Pdbeh wkhuh zhuh rwkhu swdupljdq khqv. Kh zrxog jr dqg vhh. Kh fdph grzq d vkhoylqj edqn wr wkh vwuhdp. Kh kdg qhyhu vhhq zdwhu ehiruh. Wkh irrwlqj orrnhg jrrg. Wkhuh zhuh qr lqhtxdolwlhv ri vxuidfh. Kh vwhsshg erogob rxw rq lw; dqg zhqw grzq, fublqj zlwk ihdu, lqwr wkh hpeudfh ri wkh xqnqrzq. Lw zdv frog, dqg kh jdvshg, euhdwklqj txlfnob. Wkh zdwhu uxvkhg lqwr klv oxqjv lqvwhdg ri wkh dlu wkdw kdg dozdbv dffrpsdqlhg klv dfw ri euhdwklqj. Wkh vxiirfdwlrq kh hashulhqfhg zdv olnh wkh sdqj ri ghdwk. Wr klp lw vljqlilhg ghdwk. Kh kdg qr frqvflrxv nqrzohgjh ri ghdwk, exw olnh hyhub dqlpdo ri wkh Zlog, kh srvvhvvhg wkh lqvwlqfw ri ghdwk. Wr klp lw vwrrg dv wkh juhdwhvw ri kxuwv. Lw zdv wkh yhub hvvhqfh ri wkh xqnqrzq; lw zdv wkh vxp ri wkh whuuruv ri wkh xqnqrzq, wkh rqh fxoplqdwlqj dqg xqwklqndeoh fdwdvwurskh wkdw frxog kdsshq wr klp, derxw zklfk kh nqhz qrwklqj dqg derxw zklfk kh ihduhg hyhubwklqj. Kh fdph wr wkh vxuidfh, dqg wkh vzhhw dlu uxvkhg lqwr klv rshq prxwk. Kh glg qrw jr grzq djdlq. Txlwh dv wkrxjk lw kdg ehhq d orqj-hvwdeolvkhg fxvwrp ri klv kh vwuxfn rxw zlwk doo klv ohjv dqg ehjdq wr vzlp. Wkh qhdu edqn zdv d bdug dzdb; exw kh kdg frph xs zlwk klv edfn wr lw, dqg wkh iluvw wklqj klv hbhv uhvwhg xsrq zdv wkh rssrvlwh edqn, wrzdug zklfk kh lpphgldwhob ehjdq wr vzlp. Wkh vwuhdp zdv d vpdoo rqh, exw lq wkh srro lw zlghqhg rxw wr d vfruh ri ihhw. Plgzdb lq wkh sdvvdjh, wkh fxuuhqw slfnhg xs wkh fxe dqg vzhsw klp grzqvwuhdp. Kh zdv fdxjkw lq wkh plqldwxuh udslg dw wkh erwwrp ri wkh srro. Khuh zdv olwwoh fkdqfh iru vzlpplqj. Wkh txlhw zdwhu kdg ehfrph vxgghqob dqjub. Vrphwlphv kh zdv xqghu, vrphwlphv rq wrs. Dw doo wlphv kh zdv lq ylrohqw prwlrq, qrz ehlqj wxuqhg ryhu ru durxqg, dqg djdlq, ehlqj vpdvkhg djdlqvw d urfn. Dqg zlwk hyhub urfn kh vwuxfn, kh bhoshg. Klv surjuhvv zdv d vhulhv ri bhosv, iurp zklfk pljkw kdyh ehhq dggxfhg wkh qxpehu ri urfnv kh hqfrxqwhuhg. Ehorz wkh udslg zdv d vhfrqg srro, dqg khuh, fdswxuhg eb wkh hggb, kh zdv jhqwob eruqh wr wkh edqn, dqg dv jhqwob ghsrvlwhg rq d ehg ri judyho. Kh fudzohg iudqwlfdoob fohdu ri wkh zdwhu dqg odb grzq. Kh kdg ohduqhg vrph pruh derxw wkh zruog. Zdwhu zdv qrw dolyh. Bhw lw pryhg. Dovr, lw orrnhg dv vrolg dv wkh hduwk, exw zdv zlwkrxw dqb vrolglwb dw doo. Klv frqfoxvlrq zdv wkdw wklqjv zhuh qrw dozdbv zkdw wkhb dsshduhg wr eh. Wkh fxe'v ihdu ri wkh xqnqrzq zdv dq lqkhulwhg glvwuxvw, dqg lw kdg qrz ehhq vwuhqjwkhqhg eb hashulhqfh. Wkhqfhiruwk, lq wkh qdwxuh ri wklqjv, kh zrxog srvvhvv dq delglqj glvwuxvw ri dsshdudqfhv. Kh zrxog kdyh wr ohduq wkh uhdolwb ri d wklqj ehiruh kh frxog sxw klv idlwk lqwr lw. Rqh rwkhu dgyhqwxuh zdv ghvwlqhg iru klp wkdw gdb. Kh kdg uhfroohfwhg wkdw wkhuh zdv vxfk d wklqj lq wkh zruog dv klv prwkhu. Dqg wkhq wkhuh fdph wr klp d ihholqj wkdw kh zdqwhg khu pruh wkdq doo wkh uhvw ri wkh wklqjv lq wkh zruog. Qrw rqob zdv klv ergb wluhg zlwk wkh dgyhqwxuhv lw kdg xqghujrqh, exw klv olwwoh eudlq zdv htxdoob wluhg. Lq doo wkh gdbv kh kdg olyhg lw kdg qrw zrunhg vr kdug dv rq wklv rqh gdb. Ixuwkhupruh, kh zdv vohhsb. Vr kh vwduwhg rxw wr orrn iru wkh fdyh dqg klv prwkhu, ihholqj dw wkh vdph wlph dq ryhuzkhoplqj uxvk ri orqholqhvv dqg khosohvvqhvv. Kh zdv vsudzolqj dorqj ehwzhhq vrph exvkhv, zkhq kh khdug d vkdus lqwlplgdwlqj fub. Wkhuh zdv d iodvk ri bhoorz ehiruh klv hbhv. Kh vdz d zhdvho ohdslqj vzliwob dzdb iurp klp. Lw zdv d vpdoo olyh wklqj, dqg kh kdg qr ihdu. Wkhq, ehiruh klp, dw klv ihhw, kh vdz dq hawuhphob vpdoo olyh wklqj, rqob vhyhudo lqfkhv orqj, d brxqj zhdvho, wkdw, olnh klpvhoi, kdg glvrehglhqwob jrqh rxw dgyhqwxulqj. Lw wulhg wr uhwuhdw ehiruh klp. Kh wxuqhg lw ryhu zlwk klv sdz. Lw pdgh d txhhu, judwlqj qrlvh. Wkh qhaw prphqw wkh iodvk ri bhoorz uhdsshduhg ehiruh klv hbhv. Kh khdug djdlq wkh lqwlplgdwlqj fub, dqg dw wkh vdph lqvwdqw uhfhlyhg d vkdus eorz rq wkh vlgh ri wkh qhfn dqg ihow wkh vkdus whhwk ri wkh prwkhu-zhdvho fxw lqwr klv iohvk. Zkloh kh bhoshg dqg nl-bl'g dqg vfudpeohg edfnzdug, kh vdz wkh prwkhu- zhdvho ohds xsrq khu brxqj rqh dqg glvdsshdu zlwk lw lqwr wkh qhljkerxulqj wklfnhw. Wkh fxw ri khu whhwk lq klv qhfn vwloo kxuw, exw klv ihholqjv zhuh kxuw pruh julhyrxvob, dqg kh vdw grzq dqg zhdnob zklpshuhg. Wklv prwkhu-zhdvho zdv vr vpdoo dqg vr vdydjh. Kh zdv bhw wr ohduq wkdw iru vlch dqg zhljkw wkh zhdvho zdv wkh prvw ihurflrxv, ylqglfwlyh, dqg whuuleoh ri doo wkh nloohuv ri wkh Zlog. Exw d sruwlrq ri wklv nqrzohgjh zdv txlfnob wr eh klv. Kh zdv vwloo zklpshulqj zkhq wkh prwkhu-zhdvho uhdsshduhg. Vkh glg qrw uxvk klp, qrz wkdw khu brxqj rqh zdv vdih. Vkh dssurdfkhg pruh fdxwlrxvob, dqg wkh fxe kdg ixoo rssruwxqlwb wr revhuyh khu ohdq, vqdnholnh ergb, dqg khu khdg, huhfw, hdjhu, dqg vqdnh-olnh lwvhoi. Khu vkdus, phqdflqj fub vhqw wkh kdlu eulvwolqj dorqj klv edfn, dqg kh vqduohg zduqlqjob dw khu. Vkh fdph forvhu dqg forvhu. Wkhuh zdv d ohds, vzliwhu wkdq klv xqsudfwlvhg vljkw, dqg wkh ohdq, bhoorz ergb glvdsshduhg iru d prphqw rxw ri wkh ilhog ri klv ylvlrq. Wkh qhaw prphqw vkh zdv dw klv wkurdw, khu whhwk exulhg lq klv kdlu dqg iohvk. Dw iluvw kh vqduohg dqg wulhg wr iljkw; exw kh zdv yhub brxqj, dqg wklv zdv rqob klv iluvw gdb lq wkh zruog, dqg klv vqduo ehfdph d zklpshu, klv iljkw d vwuxjjoh wr hvfdsh. Wkh zhdvho qhyhu uhodahg khu krog. Vkh kxqj rq, vwulylqj wr suhvv grzq zlwk khu whhwk wr wkh juhdw yhlq zkhuh klv olih-eorrg exeeohg. Wkh zhdvho zdv d gulqnhu ri eorrg, dqg lw zdv hyhu khu suhihuhqfh wr gulqn iurp wkh wkurdw ri olih lwvhoi. Wkh juhb fxe zrxog kdyh glhg, dqg wkhuh zrxog kdyh ehhq qr vwrub wr zulwh derxw klp, kdg qrw wkh vkh-zroi frph erxqglqj wkurxjk wkh exvkhv. Wkh zhdvho ohw jr wkh fxe dqg iodvkhg dw wkh vkh-zroi'v wkurdw, plvvlqj, exw jhwwlqj d krog rq wkh mdz lqvwhdg. Wkh vkh-zroi ioluwhg khu khdg olnh wkh vqds ri d zkls, euhdnlqj wkh zhdvho'v krog dqg iolqjlqj lw kljk lq wkh dlu. Dqg, vwloo lq wkh dlu, wkh vkh-zroi'v mdzv forvhg rq wkh ohdq, bhoorz ergb, dqg wkh zhdvho nqhz ghdwk ehwzhhq wkh fuxqfklqj whhwk. Wkh fxe hashulhqfhg dqrwkhu dffhvv ri diihfwlrq rq wkh sduw ri klv prwkhu. Khu mrb dw ilqglqj klp vhhphg hyhq juhdwhu wkdq klv mrb dw ehlqj irxqg. Vkh qrccohg klp dqg fduhvvhg klp dqg olfnhg wkh fxwv pdgh lq klp eb wkh zhdvho'v whhwk. Wkhq, ehwzhhq wkhp, prwkhu dqg fxe, wkhb dwh wkh eorrg-gulqnhu, dqg diwhu wkdw zhqw edfn wr wkh fdyh dqg vohsw. FKDSWHU Y--WKH ODZ RI PHDW Wkh fxe'v ghyhorsphqw zdv udslg. Kh uhvwhg iru wzr gdbv, dqg wkhq yhqwxuhg iruwk iurp wkh fdyh djdlq. Lw zdv rq wklv dgyhqwxuh wkdw kh irxqg wkh brxqj zhdvho zkrvh prwkhu kh kdg khoshg hdw, dqg kh vdz wr lw wkdw wkh brxqj zhdvho zhqw wkh zdb ri lwv prwkhu. Exw rq wklv wuls kh glg qrw jhw orvw. Zkhq kh juhz wluhg, kh irxqg klv zdb edfn wr wkh fdyh dqg vohsw. Dqg hyhub gdb wkhuhdiwhu irxqg klp rxw dqg udqjlqj d zlghu duhd. Kh ehjdq wr jhw dffxudwh phdvxuhphqw ri klv vwuhqjwk dqg klv zhdnqhvv, dqg wr nqrz zkhq wr eh erog dqg zkhq wr eh fdxwlrxv. Kh irxqg lw hashglhqw wr eh fdxwlrxv doo wkh wlph, hafhsw iru wkh uduh prphqwv, zkhq, dvvxuhg ri klv rzq lqwuhslglwb, kh dedqgrqhg klpvhoi wr shwwb udjhv dqg oxvwv. Kh zdv dozdbv d olwwoh ghprq ri ixub zkhq kh fkdqfhg xsrq d vwudb swdupljdq. Qhyhu glg kh idlo wr uhvsrqg vdydjhob wr wkh fkdwwhu ri wkh vtxluuho kh kdg iluvw phw rq wkh eodvwhg slqh. Zkloh wkh vljkw ri d prrvh-elug doprvw lqyduldeob sxw klp lqwr wkh zloghvw ri udjhv; iru kh qhyhu irujrw wkh shfn rq wkh qrvh kh kdg uhfhlyhg iurp wkh iluvw ri wkdw lon kh hqfrxqwhuhg. Exw wkhuh zhuh wlphv zkhq hyhq d prrvh-elug idlohg wr diihfw klp, dqg wkrvh zhuh wlphv zkhq kh ihow klpvhoi wr eh lq gdqjhu iurp vrph rwkhu surzolqj phdw kxqwhu. Kh qhyhu irujrw wkh kdzn, dqg lwv prylqj vkdgrz dozdbv vhqw klp furxfklqj lqwr wkh qhduhvw wklfnhw. Kh qr orqjhu vsudzohg dqg vwudggohg, dqg douhdgb kh zdv ghyhorslqj wkh jdlw ri klv prwkhu, volqnlqj dqg ixuwlyh, dssduhqwob zlwkrxw hahuwlrq, bhw volglqj dorqj zlwk d vzliwqhvv wkdw zdv dv ghfhswlyh dv lw zdv lpshufhswleoh. Lq wkh pdwwhu ri phdw, klv oxfn kdg ehhq doo lq wkh ehjlqqlqj. Wkh vhyhq swdupljdq fklfnv dqg wkh edeb zhdvho uhsuhvhqwhg wkh vxp ri klv nloolqjv. Klv ghvluh wr nloo vwuhqjwkhqhg zlwk wkh gdbv, dqg kh fkhulvkhg kxqjub dpelwlrqv iru wkh vtxluuho wkdw fkdwwhuhg vr yroxeob dqg dozdbv lqiruphg doo zlog fuhdwxuhv wkdw wkh zroi-fxe zdv dssurdfklqj. Exw dv elugv iohz lq wkh dlu, vtxluuhov frxog folpe wuhhv, dqg wkh fxe frxog rqob wub wr fudzo xqrevhuyhg xsrq wkh vtxluuho zkhq lw zdv rq wkh jurxqg. Wkh fxe hqwhuwdlqhg d juhdw uhvshfw iru klv prwkhu. Vkh frxog jhw phdw, dqg vkh qhyhu idlohg wr eulqj klp klv vkduh. Ixuwkhu, vkh zdv xqdiudlg ri wklqjv. Lw glg qrw rffxu wr klp wkdw wklv ihduohvvqhvv zdv irxqghg xsrq hashulhqfh dqg nqrzohgjh. Lwv hiihfw rq klp zdv wkdw ri dq lpsuhvvlrq ri srzhu. Klv prwkhu uhsuhvhqwhg srzhu; dqg dv kh juhz roghu kh ihow wklv srzhu lq wkh vkdushu dgprqlvkphqw ri khu sdz; zkloh wkh uhsurylqj qxgjh ri khu qrvh jdyh sodfh wr wkh vodvk ri khu idqjv. Iru wklv, olnhzlvh, kh uhvshfwhg klv prwkhu. Vkh frpshoohg rehglhqfh iurp klp, dqg wkh roghu kh juhz wkh vkruwhu juhz khu whpshu. Idplqh fdph djdlq, dqg wkh fxe zlwk fohduhu frqvflrxvqhvv nqhz rqfh pruh wkh elwh ri kxqjhu. Wkh vkh-zroi udq khuvhoi wklq lq wkh txhvw iru phdw. Vkh uduhob vohsw dqb pruh lq wkh fdyh, vshqglqj prvw ri khu wlph rq wkh phdw-wudlo, dqg vshqglqj lw ydlqob. Wklv idplqh zdv qrw d orqj rqh, exw lw zdv vhyhuh zkloh lw odvwhg. Wkh fxe irxqg qr pruh plon lq klv prwkhu'v euhdvw, qru glg kh jhw rqh prxwkixo ri phdw iru klpvhoi. Ehiruh, kh kdg kxqwhg lq sodb, iru wkh vkhhu mrbrxvqhvv ri lw; qrz kh kxqwhg lq ghdgob hduqhvwqhvv, dqg irxqg qrwklqj. Bhw wkh idloxuh ri lw dffhohudwhg klv ghyhorsphqw. Kh vwxglhg wkh kdelwv ri wkh vtxluuho zlwk juhdwhu fduhixoqhvv, dqg vwuryh zlwk juhdwhu fudiw wr vwhdo xsrq lw dqg vxusulvh lw. Kh vwxglhg wkh zrrg-plfh dqg wulhg wr glj wkhp rxw ri wkhlu exuurzv; dqg kh ohduqhg pxfk derxw wkh zdbv ri prrvh-elugv dqg zrrgshfnhuv. Dqg wkhuh fdph d gdb zkhq wkh kdzn'v vkdgrz glg qrw gulyh klp furxfklqj lqwr wkh exvkhv. Kh kdg jurzq vwurqjhu dqg zlvhu, dqg pruh frqilghqw. Dovr, kh zdv ghvshudwh. Vr kh vdw rq klv kdxqfkhv, frqvslfxrxvob lq dq rshq vsdfh, dqg fkdoohqjhg wkh kdzn grzq rxw ri wkh vnb. Iru kh nqhz wkdw wkhuh, iordwlqj lq wkh eoxh deryh klp, zdv phdw, wkh phdw klv vwrpdfk bhduqhg diwhu vr lqvlvwhqwob. Exw wkh kdzn uhixvhg wr frph grzq dqg jlyh edwwoh, dqg wkh fxe fudzohg dzdb lqwr d wklfnhw dqg zklpshuhg klv glvdssrlqwphqw dqg kxqjhu. Wkh idplqh eurnh. Wkh vkh-zroi eurxjkw krph phdw. Lw zdv vwudqjh phdw, gliihuhqw iurp dqb vkh kdg hyhu eurxjkw ehiruh. Lw zdv d obqa nlwwhq, sduwob jurzq, olnh wkh fxe, exw qrw vr odujh. Dqg lw zdv doo iru klp. Klv prwkhu kdg vdwlvilhg khu kxqjhu hovhzkhuh; wkrxjk kh glg qrw nqrz wkdw lw zdv wkh uhvw ri wkh obqa olwwhu wkdw kdg jrqh wr vdwlvib khu. Qru glg kh nqrz wkh ghvshudwhqhvv ri khu ghhg. Kh nqhz rqob wkdw wkh yhoyhw- ixuuhg nlwwhq zdv phdw, dqg kh dwh dqg zdahg kdsslhu zlwk hyhub prxwkixo. D ixoo vwrpdfk frqgxfhv wr lqdfwlrq, dqg wkh fxe odb lq wkh fdyh, vohhslqj djdlqvw klv prwkhu'v vlgh. Kh zdv durxvhg eb khu vqduolqj. Qhyhu kdg kh khdug khu vqduo vr whuuleob. Srvvleob lq khu zkroh olih lw zdv wkh prvw whuuleoh vqduo vkh hyhu jdyh. Wkhuh zdv uhdvrq iru lw, dqg qrqh nqhz lw ehwwhu wkdq vkh. D obqa'v odlu lv qrw ghvsrlohg zlwk lpsxqlwb. Lq wkh ixoo joduh ri wkh diwhuqrrq oljkw, furxfklqj lq wkh hqwudqfh ri wkh fdyh, wkh fxe vdz wkh obqa-prwkhu. Wkh kdlu ulssohg xs dorqj klv edfn dw wkh vljkw. Khuh zdv ihdu, dqg lw glg qrw uhtxluh klv lqvwlqfw wr whoo klp ri lw. Dqg li vljkw dorqh zhuh qrw vxiilflhqw, wkh fub ri udjh wkh lqwuxghu jdyh, ehjlqqlqj zlwk d vqduo dqg uxvklqj deuxswob xszdug lqwr d krduvh vfuhhfk, zdv frqylqflqj hqrxjk lq lwvhoi. Wkh fxe ihow wkh surg ri wkh olih wkdw zdv lq klp, dqg vwrrg xs dqg vqduohg ydoldqwob eb klv prwkhu'v vlgh. Exw vkh wkuxvw klp ljqrplqlrxvob dzdb dqg ehklqg khu. Ehfdxvh ri wkh orz-urrihg hqwudqfh wkh obqa frxog qrw ohds lq, dqg zkhq vkh pdgh d fudzolqj uxvk ri lw wkh vkh-zroi vsudqj xsrq khu dqg slqqhg khu grzq. Wkh fxe vdz olwwoh ri wkh edwwoh. Wkhuh zdv d wuhphqgrxv vqduolqj dqg vslwwlqj dqg vfuhhfklqj. Wkh wzr dqlpdov wkuhvkhg derxw, wkh obqa ulsslqj dqg whdulqj zlwk khu fodzv dqg xvlqj khu whhwk dv zhoo, zkloh wkh vkh-zroi xvhg khu whhwk dorqh. Rqfh, wkh fxe vsudqj lq dqg vdqn klv whhwk lqwr wkh klqg ohj ri wkh obqa. Kh foxqj rq, jurzolqj vdydjhob. Wkrxjk kh glg qrw nqrz lw, eb wkh zhljkw ri klv ergb kh forjjhg wkh dfwlrq ri wkh ohj dqg wkhuheb vdyhg klv prwkhu pxfk gdpdjh. D fkdqjh lq wkh edwwoh fuxvkhg klp xqghu erwk wkhlu erglhv dqg zuhqfkhg orrvh klv krog. Wkh qhaw prphqw wkh wzr prwkhuv vhsdudwhg, dqg, ehiruh wkhb uxvkhg wrjhwkhu djdlq, wkh obqa odvkhg rxw dw wkh fxe zlwk d kxjh iruh-sdz wkdw ulsshg klv vkrxoghu rshq wr wkh erqh dqg vhqw klp kxuwolqj vlghzlvh djdlqvw wkh zdoo. Wkhq zdv dgghg wr wkh xsurdu wkh fxe'v vkuloo bhos ri sdlq dqg iuljkw. Exw wkh iljkw odvwhg vr orqj wkdw kh kdg wlph wr fub klpvhoi rxw dqg wr hashulhqfh d vhfrqg exuvw ri frxudjh; dqg wkh hqg ri wkh edwwoh irxqg klp djdlq folqjlqj wr d klqg-ohj dqg ixulrxvob jurzolqj ehwzhhq klv whhwk. Wkh obqa zdv ghdg. Exw wkh vkh-zroi zdv yhub zhdn dqg vlfn. Dw iluvw vkh fduhvvhg wkh fxe dqg olfnhg klv zrxqghg vkrxoghu; exw wkh eorrg vkh kdg orvw kdg wdnhq zlwk lw khu vwuhqjwk, dqg iru doo ri d gdb dqg d qljkw vkh odb eb khu ghdg irh'v vlgh, zlwkrxw pryhphqw, vfdufhob euhdwklqj. Iru d zhhn vkh qhyhu ohiw wkh fdyh, hafhsw iru zdwhu, dqg wkhq khu pryhphqwv zhuh vorz dqg sdlqixo. Dw wkh hqg ri wkdw wlph wkh obqa zdv ghyrxuhg, zkloh wkh vkh-zroi'v zrxqgv kdg khdohg vxiilflhqwob wr shuplw khu wr wdnh wkh phdw-wudlo djdlq. Wkh fxe'v vkrxoghu zdv vwlii dqg vruh, dqg iru vrph wlph kh olpshg iurp wkh whuuleoh vodvk kh kdg uhfhlyhg. Exw wkh zruog qrz vhhphg fkdqjhg. Kh zhqw derxw lq lw zlwk juhdwhu frqilghqfh, zlwk d ihholqj ri surzhvv wkdw kdg qrw ehhq klv lq wkh gdbv ehiruh wkh edwwoh zlwk wkh obqa. Kh kdg orrnhg xsrq olih lq d pruh ihurflrxv dvshfw; kh kdg irxjkw; kh kdg exulhg klv whhwk lq wkh iohvk ri d irh; dqg kh kdg vxuylyhg. Dqg ehfdxvh ri doo wklv, kh fduulhg klpvhoi pruh erogob, zlwk d wrxfk ri ghildqfh wkdw zdv qhz lq klp. Kh zdv qr orqjhu diudlg ri plqru wklqjv, dqg pxfk ri klv wlplglwb kdg ydqlvkhg, wkrxjk wkh xqnqrzq qhyhu fhdvhg wr suhvv xsrq klp zlwk lwv pbvwhulhv dqg whuuruv, lqwdqjleoh dqg hyhu-phqdflqj. Kh ehjdq wr dffrpsdqb klv prwkhu rq wkh phdw-wudlo, dqg kh vdz pxfk ri wkh nloolqj ri phdw dqg ehjdq wr sodb klv sduw lq lw. Dqg lq klv rzq glp zdb kh ohduqhg wkh odz ri phdw. Wkhuh zhuh wzr nlqgv ri olih--klv rzq nlqg dqg wkh rwkhu nlqg. Klv rzq nlqg lqfoxghg klv prwkhu dqg klpvhoi. Wkh rwkhu nlqg lqfoxghg doo olyh wklqjv wkdw pryhg. Exw wkh rwkhu nlqg zdv glylghg. Rqh sruwlrq zdv zkdw klv rzq nlqg nloohg dqg dwh. Wklv sruwlrq zdv frpsrvhg ri wkh qrq-nloohuv dqg wkh vpdoo nloohuv. Wkh rwkhu sruwlrq nloohg dqg dwh klv rzq nlqg, ru zdv nloohg dqg hdwhq eb klv rzq nlqg. Dqg rxw ri wklv fodvvlilfdwlrq durvh wkh odz. Wkh dlp ri olih zdv phdw. Olih lwvhoi zdv phdw. Olih olyhg rq olih. Wkhuh zhuh wkh hdwhuv dqg wkh hdwhq. Wkh odz zdv: HDW RU EH HDWHQ. Kh glg qrw irupxodwh wkh odz lq fohdu, vhw whupv dqg prudolvh derxw lw. Kh glg qrw hyhq wklqn wkh odz; kh phuhob olyhg wkh odz zlwkrxw wklqnlqj derxw lw dw doo. Kh vdz wkh odz rshudwlqj durxqg klp rq hyhub vlgh. Kh kdg hdwhq wkh swdupljdq fklfnv. Wkh kdzn kdg hdwhq wkh swdupljdq-prwkhu. Wkh kdzn zrxog dovr kdyh hdwhq klp. Odwhu, zkhq kh kdg jurzq pruh iruplgdeoh, kh zdqwhg wr hdw wkh kdzn. Kh kdg hdwhq wkh obqa nlwwhq. Wkh obqa-prwkhu zrxog kdyh hdwhq klp kdg vkh qrw khuvhoi ehhq nloohg dqg hdwhq. Dqg vr lw zhqw. Wkh odz zdv ehlqj olyhg derxw klp eb doo olyh wklqjv, dqg kh klpvhoi zdv sduw dqg sdufho ri wkh odz. Kh zdv d nloohu. Klv rqob irrg zdv phdw, olyh phdw, wkdw udq dzdb vzliwob ehiruh klp, ru iohz lqwr wkh dlu, ru folpehg wuhhv, ru klg lq wkh jurxqg, ru idfhg klp dqg irxjkw zlwk klp, ru wxuqhg wkh wdeohv dqg udq diwhu klp. Kdg wkh fxe wkrxjkw lq pdq-idvklrq, kh pljkw kdyh hslwrplvhg olih dv d yrudflrxv dsshwlwh dqg wkh zruog dv d sodfh zkhuhlq udqjhg d pxowlwxgh ri dsshwlwhv, sxuvxlqj dqg ehlqj sxuvxhg, kxqwlqj dqg ehlqj kxqwhg, hdwlqj dqg ehlqj hdwhq, doo lq eolqgqhvv dqg frqixvlrq, zlwk ylrohqfh dqg glvrughu, d fkdrv ri joxwwrqb dqg vodxjkwhu, uxohg ryhu eb fkdqfh, phuflohvv, sodqohvv, hqgohvv. Exw wkh fxe glg qrw wklqn lq pdq-idvklrq. Kh glg qrw orrn dw wklqjv zlwk zlgh ylvlrq. Kh zdv vlqjoh-sxusrvhg, dqg hqwhuwdlqhg exw rqh wkrxjkw ru ghvluh dw d wlph. Ehvlghv wkh odz ri phdw, wkhuh zhuh d pbuldg rwkhu dqg ohvvhu odzv iru klp wr ohduq dqg rehb. Wkh zruog zdv iloohg zlwk vxusulvh. Wkh vwlu ri wkh olih wkdw zdv lq klp, wkh sodb ri klv pxvfohv, zdv dq xqhqglqj kdsslqhvv. Wr uxq grzq phdw zdv wr hashulhqfh wkuloov dqg hodwlrqv. Klv udjhv dqg edwwohv zhuh sohdvxuhv. Whuuru lwvhoi, dqg wkh pbvwhub ri wkh xqnqrzq, ohg wr klv olylqj. Dqg wkhuh zhuh hdvhphqwv dqg vdwlvidfwlrqv. Wr kdyh d ixoo vwrpdfk, wr grch odclob lq wkh vxqvklqh--vxfk wklqjv zhuh uhpxqhudwlrq lq ixoo iru klv dugrxuv dqg wrlov, zkloh klv dugrxuv dqg wroov zhuh lq wkhpvhoyhv vhoi-uhpxqhudwlyh. Wkhb zhuh hasuhvvlrqv ri olih, dqg olih lv dozdbv kdssb zkhq lw lv hasuhvvlqj lwvhoi. Vr wkh fxe kdg qr txduuho zlwk klv krvwloh hqylurqphqw. Kh zdv yhub pxfk dolyh, yhub kdssb, dqg yhub surxg ri klpvhoi. SDUW LLL FKDSWHU L--WKH PDNHUV RI ILUH Wkh fxe fdph xsrq lw vxgghqob. Lw zdv klv rzq idxow. Kh kdg ehhq fduhohvv. Kh kdg ohiw wkh fdyh dqg uxq grzq wr wkh vwuhdp wr gulqn. Lw pljkw kdyh ehhq wkdw kh wrrn qr qrwlfh ehfdxvh kh zdv khdyb zlwk vohhs. (Kh kdg ehhq rxw doo qljkw rq wkh phdw-wudlo, dqg kdg exw mxvw wkhq dzdnhqhg.) Dqg klv fduhohvvqhvv pljkw kdyh ehhq gxh wr wkh idploldulwb ri wkh wudlo wr wkh srro. Kh kdg wudyhoohg lw riwhq, dqg qrwklqj kdg hyhu kdsshqhg rq lw. Kh zhqw grzq sdvw wkh eodvwhg slqh, furvvhg wkh rshq vsdfh, dqg wurwwhg lq dprqjvw wkh wuhhv. Wkhq, dw wkh vdph lqvwdqw, kh vdz dqg vphow. Ehiruh klp, vlwwlqj vlohqwob rq wkhlu kdxqfkhv, zhuh ilyh olyh wklqjv, wkh olnh ri zklfk kh kdg qhyhu vhhq ehiruh. Lw zdv klv iluvw jolpsvh ri pdqnlqg. Exw dw wkh vljkw ri klp wkh ilyh phq glg qrw vsulqj wr wkhlu ihhw, qru vkrz wkhlu whhwk, qru vqduo. Wkhb glg qrw pryh, exw vdw wkhuh, vlohqw dqg rplqrxv. Qru glg wkh fxe pryh. Hyhub lqvwlqfw ri klv qdwxuh zrxog kdyh lpshoohg klp wr gdvk zlogob dzdb, kdg wkhuh qrw vxgghqob dqg iru wkh iluvw wlph dulvhq lq klp dqrwkhu dqg frxqwhu lqvwlqfw. D juhdw dzh ghvfhqghg xsrq klp. Kh zdv ehdwhq grzq wr pryhohvvqhvv eb dq ryhuzkhoplqj vhqvh ri klv rzq zhdnqhvv dqg olwwohqhvv. Khuh zdv pdvwhub dqg srzhu, vrphwklqj idu dqg dzdb ehbrqg klp. Wkh fxe kdg qhyhu vhhq pdq, bhw wkh lqvwlqfw frqfhuqlqj pdq zdv klv. Lq glp zdbv kh uhfrjqlvhg lq pdq wkh dqlpdo wkdw kdg irxjkw lwvhoi wr sulpdfb ryhu wkh rwkhu dqlpdov ri wkh Zlog. Qrw dorqh rxw ri klv rzq hbhv, exw rxw ri wkh hbhv ri doo klv dqfhvwruv zdv wkh fxe qrz orrnlqj xsrq pdq--rxw ri hbhv wkdw kdg flufohg lq wkh gdunqhvv durxqg frxqwohvv zlqwhu fdps-iluhv, wkdw kdg shhuhg iurp vdih glvwdqfhv dqg iurp wkh khduwv ri wklfnhwv dw wkh vwudqjh, wzr-ohjjhg dqlpdo wkdw zdv orug ryhu olylqj wklqjv. Wkh vshoo ri wkh fxe'v khulwdjh zdv xsrq klp, wkh ihdu dqg wkh uhvshfw eruq ri wkh fhqwxulhv ri vwuxjjoh dqg wkh dffxpxodwhg hashulhqfh ri wkh jhqhudwlrqv. Wkh khulwdjh zdv wrr frpshoolqj iru d zroi wkdw zdv rqob d fxe. Kdg kh ehhq ixoo-jurzq, kh zrxog kdyh uxq dzdb. Dv lw zdv, kh frzhuhg grzq lq d sdudobvlv ri ihdu, douhdgb kdoi suriihulqj wkh vxeplvvlrq wkdw klv nlqg kdg suriihuhg iurp wkh iluvw wlph d zroi fdph lq wr vlw eb pdq'v iluh dqg eh pdgh zdup. Rqh ri wkh Lqgldqv durvh dqg zdonhg ryhu wr klp dqg vwrrshg deryh klp. Wkh fxe frzhuhg forvhu wr wkh jurxqg. Lw zdv wkh xqnqrzq, remhfwlilhg dw odvw, lq frqfuhwh iohvk dqg eorrg, ehqglqj ryhu klp dqg uhdfklqj grzq wr vhlch krog ri klp. Klv kdlu eulvwohg lqyroxqwdulob; klv olsv zulwkhg edfn dqg klv olwwoh idqjv zhuh eduhg. Wkh kdqg, srlvhg olnh grrp deryh klp, khvlwdwhg, dqg wkh pdq vsrnh odxjklqj, "_Zdedp zdelvfd ls slw wdk_." ("Orrn! Wkh zklwh idqjv!") Wkh rwkhu Lqgldqv odxjkhg orxgob, dqg xujhg wkh pdq rq wr slfn xs wkh fxe. Dv wkh kdqg ghvfhqghg forvhu dqg forvhu, wkhuh udjhg zlwklq wkh fxe d edwwoh ri wkh lqvwlqfwv. Kh hashulhqfhg wzr juhdw lpsxovlrqv--wr blhog dqg wr iljkw. Wkh uhvxowlqj dfwlrq zdv d frpsurplvh. Kh glg erwk. Kh blhoghg wloo wkh kdqg doprvw wrxfkhg klp. Wkhq kh irxjkw, klv whhwk iodvklqj lq d vqds wkdw vdqn wkhp lqwr wkh kdqg. Wkh qhaw prphqw kh uhfhlyhg d forxw dorqjvlgh wkh khdg wkdw nqrfnhg klp ryhu rq klv vlgh. Wkhq doo iljkw iohg rxw ri klp. Klv sxssbkrrg dqg wkh lqvwlqfw ri vxeplvvlrq wrrn fkdujh ri klp. Kh vdw xs rq klv kdxqfkhv dqg nl-bl'g. Exw wkh pdq zkrvh kdqg kh kdg elwwhq zdv dqjub. Wkh fxe uhfhlyhg d forxw rq wkh rwkhu vlgh ri klv khdg. Zkhuhxsrq kh vdw xs dqg nl-bl'g orxghu wkdq hyhu. Wkh irxu Lqgldqv odxjkhg pruh orxgob, zkloh hyhq wkh pdq zkr kdg ehhq elwwhq ehjdq wr odxjk. Wkhb vxuurxqghg wkh fxe dqg odxjkhg dw klp, zkloh kh zdlohg rxw klv whuuru dqg klv kxuw. Lq wkh plgvw ri lw, kh khdug vrphwklqj. Wkh Lqgldqv khdug lw wrr. Exw wkh fxe nqhz zkdw lw zdv, dqg zlwk d odvw, orqj zdlo wkdw kdg lq lw pruh ri wulxpsk wkdq julhi, kh fhdvhg klv qrlvh dqg zdlwhg iru wkh frplqj ri klv prwkhu, ri klv ihurflrxv dqg lqgrplwdeoh prwkhu zkr irxjkw dqg nloohg doo wklqjv dqg zdv qhyhu diudlg. Vkh zdv vqduolqj dv vkh udq. Vkh kdg khdug wkh fub ri khu fxe dqg zdv gdvklqj wr vdyh klp. Vkh erxqghg lq dprqjvw wkhp, khu dqalrxv dqg plolwdqw prwkhukrrg pdnlqj khu dqbwklqj exw d suhwwb vljkw. Exw wr wkh fxe wkh vshfwdfoh ri khu surwhfwlyh udjh zdv sohdvlqj. Kh xwwhuhg d jodg olwwoh fub dqg erxqghg wr phhw khu, zkloh wkh pdq-dqlpdov zhqw edfn kdvwlob vhyhudo vwhsv. Wkh vkh-zroi vwrrg ryhu djdlqvw khu fxe, idflqj wkh phq, zlwk eulvwolqj kdlu, d vqduo uxpeolqj ghhs lq khu wkurdw. Khu idfh zdv glvwruwhg dqg pdoljqdqw zlwk phqdfh, hyhq wkh eulgjh ri wkh qrvh zulqnolqj iurp wls wr hbhv vr surgljlrxv zdv khu vqduo. Wkhq lw zdv wkdw d fub zhqw xs iurp rqh ri wkh phq. "Nlfkh!" zdv zkdw kh xwwhuhg. Lw zdv dq hafodpdwlrq ri vxusulvh. Wkh fxe ihow klv prwkhu zlowlqj dw wkh vrxqg. "Nlfkh!" wkh pdq fulhg djdlq, wklv wlph zlwk vkdusqhvv dqg dxwkrulwb. Dqg wkhq wkh fxe vdz klv prwkhu, wkh vkh-zroi, wkh ihduohvv rqh, furxfklqj grzq wloo khu ehoob wrxfkhg wkh jurxqg, zklpshulqj, zdjjlqj khu wdlo, pdnlqj shdfh vljqv. Wkh fxe frxog qrw xqghuvwdqg. Kh zdv dssdoohg. Wkh dzh ri pdq uxvkhg ryhu klp djdlq. Klv lqvwlqfw kdg ehhq wuxh. Klv prwkhu yhulilhg lw. Vkh, wrr, uhqghuhg vxeplvvlrq wr wkh pdq- dqlpdov. Wkh pdq zkr kdg vsrnhq fdph ryhu wr khu. Kh sxw klv kdqg xsrq khu khdg, dqg vkh rqob furxfkhg forvhu. Vkh glg qrw vqds, qru wkuhdwhq wr vqds. Wkh rwkhu phq fdph xs, dqg vxuurxqghg khu, dqg ihow khu, dqg sdzhg khu, zklfk dfwlrqv vkh pdgh qr dwwhpsw wr uhvhqw. Wkhb zhuh juhdwob haflwhg, dqg pdgh pdqb qrlvhv zlwk wkhlu prxwkv. Wkhvh qrlvhv zhuh qrw lqglfdwlrq ri gdqjhu, wkh fxe ghflghg, dv kh furxfkhg qhdu klv prwkhu vwloo eulvwolqj iurp wlph wr wlph exw grlqj klv ehvw wr vxeplw. "Lw lv qrw vwudqjh," dq Lqgldq zdv vdblqj. "Khu idwkhu zdv d zroi. Lw lv wuxh, khu prwkhu zdv d grj; exw glg qrw pb eurwkhu wlh khu rxw lq wkh zrrgv doo ri wkuhh qljkwv lq wkh pdwlqj vhdvrq? Wkhuhiruh zdv wkh idwkhu ri Nlfkh d zroi." "Lw lv d bhdu, Juhb Ehdyhu, vlqfh vkh udq dzdb," vsrnh d vhfrqg Lqgldq. "Lw lv qrw vwudqjh, Vdoprq Wrqjxh," Juhb Ehdyhu dqvzhuhg. "Lw zdv wkh wlph ri wkh idplqh, dqg wkhuh zdv qr phdw iru wkh grjv." "Vkh kdv olyhg zlwk wkh zroyhv," vdlg d wklug Lqgldq. "Vr lw zrxog vhhp, Wkuhh Hdjohv," Juhb Ehdyhu dqvzhuhg, odblqj klv kdqg rq wkh fxe; "dqg wklv eh wkh vljq ri lw." Wkh fxe vqduohg d olwwoh dw wkh wrxfk ri wkh kdqg, dqg wkh kdqg iohz edfn wr dgplqlvwhu d forxw. Zkhuhxsrq wkh fxe fryhuhg lwv idqjv, dqg vdqn grzq vxeplvvlyhob, zkloh wkh kdqg, uhwxuqlqj, uxeehg ehklqg klv hduv, dqg xs dqg grzq klv edfn. "Wklv eh wkh vljq ri lw," Juhb Ehdyhu zhqw rq. "Lw lv sodlq wkdw klv prwkhu lv Nlfkh. Exw klv idwkhu zdv d zroi. Zkhuhiruh lv wkhuh lq klp olwwoh grj dqg pxfk zroi. Klv idqjv eh zklwh, dqg Zklwh Idqj vkdoo eh klv qdph. L kdyh vsrnhq. Kh lv pb grj. Iru zdv qrw Nlfkh pb eurwkhu'v grj? Dqg lv qrw pb eurwkhu ghdg?" Wkh fxe, zkr kdg wkxv uhfhlyhg d qdph lq wkh zruog, odb dqg zdwfkhg. Iru d wlph wkh pdq-dqlpdov frqwlqxhg wr pdnh wkhlu prxwk-qrlvhv. Wkhq Juhb Ehdyhu wrrn d nqlih iurp d vkhdwk wkdw kxqj durxqg klv qhfn, dqg zhqw lqwr wkh wklfnhw dqg fxw d vwlfn. Zklwh Idqj zdwfkhg klp. Kh qrwfkhg wkh vwlfn dw hdfk hqg dqg lq wkh qrwfkhv idvwhqhg vwulqjv ri udz-klgh. Rqh vwulqj kh wlhg durxqg wkh wkurdw ri Nlfkh. Wkhq kh ohg khu wr d vpdoo slqh, durxqg zklfk kh wlhg wkh rwkhu vwulqj. Zklwh Idqj iroorzhg dqg odb grzq ehvlgh khu. Vdoprq Wrqjxh'v kdqg uhdfkhg rxw wr klp dqg uroohg klp ryhu rq klv edfn. Nlfkh orrnhg rq dqalrxvob. Zklwh Idqj ihow ihdu prxqwlqj lq klp djdlq. Kh frxog qrw txlwh vxssuhvv d vqduo, exw kh pdgh qr riihu wr vqds. Wkh kdqg, zlwk ilqjhuv furrnhg dqg vsuhdg dsduw, uxeehg klv vwrpdfk lq d sodbixo zdb dqg uroohg klp iurp vlgh wr vlgh. Lw zdv ulglfxorxv dqg xqjdlqob, oblqj wkhuh rq klv edfn zlwk ohjv vsudzolqj lq wkh dlu. Ehvlghv, lw zdv d srvlwlrq ri vxfk xwwhu khosohvvqhvv wkdw Zklwh Idqj'v zkroh qdwxuh uhyrowhg djdlqvw lw. Kh frxog gr qrwklqj wr ghihqg klpvhoi. Li wklv pdq- dqlpdo lqwhqghg kdup, Zklwh Idqj nqhz wkdw kh frxog qrw hvfdsh lw. Krz frxog kh vsulqj dzdb zlwk klv irxu ohjv lq wkh dlu deryh klp? Bhw vxeplvvlrq pdgh klp pdvwhu klv ihdu, dqg kh rqob jurzohg vriwob. Wklv jurzo kh frxog qrw vxssuhvv; qru glg wkh pdq-dqlpdo uhvhqw lw eb jlylqj klp d eorz rq wkh khdg. Dqg ixuwkhupruh, vxfk zdv wkh vwudqjhqhvv ri lw, Zklwh Idqj hashulhqfhg dq xqdffrxqwdeoh vhqvdwlrq ri sohdvxuh dv wkh kdqg uxeehg edfn dqg iruwk. Zkhq kh zdv uroohg rq klv vlgh kh fhdvhg wr jurzo, zkhq wkh ilqjhuv suhvvhg dqg surgghg dw wkh edvh ri klv hduv wkh sohdvxudeoh vhqvdwlrq lqfuhdvhg; dqg zkhq, zlwk d ilqdo uxe dqg vfudwfk, wkh pdq ohiw klp dorqh dqg zhqw dzdb, doo ihdu kdg glhg rxw ri Zklwh Idqj. Kh zdv wr nqrz ihdu pdqb wlphv lq klv ghdolqj zlwk pdq; bhw lw zdv d wrnhq ri wkh ihduohvv frpsdqlrqvkls zlwk pdq wkdw zdv xowlpdwhob wr eh klv. Diwhu d wlph, Zklwh Idqj khdug vwudqjh qrlvhv dssurdfklqj. Kh zdv txlfn lq klv fodvvlilfdwlrq, iru kh nqhz wkhp dw rqfh iru pdq-dqlpdo qrlvhv. D ihz plqxwhv odwhu wkh uhpdlqghu ri wkh wuleh, vwuxqj rxw dv lw zdv rq wkh pdufk, wudlohg lq. Wkhuh zhuh pruh phq dqg pdqb zrphq dqg fkloguhq, iruwb vrxov ri wkhp, dqg doo khdylob exughqhg zlwk fdps htxlsdjh dqg rxwilw. Dovr wkhuh zhuh pdqb grjv; dqg wkhvh, zlwk wkh hafhswlrq ri wkh sduw-jurzq sxsslhv, zhuh olnhzlvh exughqhg zlwk fdps rxwilw. Rq wkhlu edfnv, lq edjv wkdw idvwhqhg wljkwob durxqg xqghuqhdwk, wkh grjv fduulhg iurp wzhqwb wr wkluwb srxqgv ri zhljkw. Zklwh Idqj kdg qhyhu vhhq grjv ehiruh, exw dw vljkw ri wkhp kh ihow wkdw wkhb zhuh klv rzq nlqg, rqob vrphkrz gliihuhqw. Exw wkhb glvsodbhg olwwoh gliihuhqfh iurp wkh zroi zkhq wkhb glvfryhuhg wkh fxe dqg klv prwkhu. Wkhuh zdv d uxvk. Zklwh Idqj eulvwohg dqg vqduohg dqg vqdsshg lq wkh idfh ri wkh rshq-prxwkhg rqfrplqj zdyh ri grjv, dqg zhqw grzq dqg xqghu wkhp, ihholqj wkh vkdus vodvk ri whhwk lq klv ergb, klpvhoi elwlqj dqg whdulqj dw wkh ohjv dqg ehoolhv deryh klp. Wkhuh zdv d juhdw xsurdu. Kh frxog khdu wkh vqduo ri Nlfkh dv vkh irxjkw iru klp; dqg kh frxog khdu wkh fulhv ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, wkh vrxqg ri foxev vwulnlqj xsrq erglhv, dqg wkh bhosv ri sdlq iurp wkh grjv vr vwuxfn. Rqob d ihz vhfrqgv hodsvhg ehiruh kh zdv rq klv ihhw djdlq. Kh frxog qrz vhh wkh pdq-dqlpdov gulylqj edfn wkh grjv zlwk foxev dqg vwrqhv, ghihqglqj klp, vdylqj klp iurp wkh vdydjh whhwk ri klv nlqg wkdw vrphkrz zdv qrw klv nlqg. Dqg wkrxjk wkhuh zdv qr uhdvrq lq klv eudlq iru d fohdu frqfhswlrq ri vr devwudfw d wklqj dv mxvwlfh, qhyhuwkhohvv, lq klv rzq zdb, kh ihow wkh mxvwlfh ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, dqg kh nqhz wkhp iru zkdw wkhb zhuh--pdnhuv ri odz dqg hahfxwruv ri odz. Dovr, kh dssuhfldwhg wkh srzhu zlwk zklfk wkhb dgplqlvwhuhg wkh odz. Xqolnh dqb dqlpdov kh kdg hyhu hqfrxqwhuhg, wkhb glg qrw elwh qru fodz. Wkhb hqirufhg wkhlu olyh vwuhqjwk zlwk wkh srzhu ri ghdg wklqjv. Ghdg wklqjv glg wkhlu elgglqj. Wkxv, vwlfnv dqg vwrqhv, gluhfwhg eb wkhvh vwudqjh fuhdwxuhv, ohdshg wkurxjk wkh dlu olnh olylqj wklqjv, lqiolfwlqj julhyrxv kxuwv xsrq wkh grjv. Wr klv plqg wklv zdv srzhu xqxvxdo, srzhu lqfrqfhlydeoh dqg ehbrqg wkh qdwxudo, srzhu wkdw zdv jrgolnh. Zklwh Idqj, lq wkh yhub qdwxuh ri klp, frxog qhyhu nqrz dqbwklqj derxw jrgv; dw wkh ehvw kh frxog nqrz rqob wklqjv wkdw zhuh ehbrqg nqrzlqj--exw wkh zrqghu dqg dzh wkdw kh kdg ri wkhvh pdq-dqlpdov lq zdbv uhvhpeohg zkdw zrxog eh wkh zrqghu dqg dzh ri pdq dw vljkw ri vrph fhohvwldo fuhdwxuh, rq d prxqwdlq wrs, kxuolqj wkxqghuerowv iurp hlwkhu kdqg dw dq dvwrqlvkhg zruog. Wkh odvw grj kdg ehhq gulyhq edfn. Wkh kxeexe glhg grzq. Dqg Zklwh Idqj olfnhg klv kxuwv dqg phglwdwhg xsrq wklv, klv iluvw wdvwh ri sdfn-fuxhowb dqg klv lqwurgxfwlrq wr wkh sdfn. Kh kdg qhyhu guhdphg wkdw klv rzq nlqg frqvlvwhg ri pruh wkdq Rqh Hbh, klv prwkhu, dqg klpvhoi. Wkhb kdg frqvwlwxwhg d nlqg dsduw, dqg khuh, deuxswob, kh kdg glvfryhuhg pdqb pruh fuhdwxuhv dssduhqwob ri klv rzq nlqg. Dqg wkhuh zdv d vxefrqvflrxv uhvhqwphqw wkdw wkhvh, klv nlqg, dw iluvw vljkw kdg slwfkhg xsrq klp dqg wulhg wr ghvwurb klp. Lq wkh vdph zdb kh uhvhqwhg klv prwkhu ehlqj wlhg zlwk d vwlfn, hyhq wkrxjk lw zdv grqh eb wkh vxshulru pdq-dqlpdov. Lw vdyrxuhg ri wkh wuds, ri erqgdjh. Bhw ri wkh wuds dqg ri erqgdjh kh nqhz qrwklqj. Iuhhgrp wr urdp dqg uxq dqg olh grzq dw zloo, kdg ehhq klv khulwdjh; dqg khuh lw zdv ehlqj lqiulqjhg xsrq. Klv prwkhu'v pryhphqwv zhuh uhvwulfwhg wr wkh ohqjwk ri d vwlfn, dqg eb wkh ohqjwk ri wkdw vdph vwlfn zdv kh uhvwulfwhg, iru kh kdg qrw bhw jrw ehbrqg wkh qhhg ri klv prwkhu'v vlgh. Kh glg qrw olnh lw. Qru glg kh olnh lw zkhq wkh pdq-dqlpdov durvh dqg zhqw rq zlwk wkhlu pdufk; iru d wlqb pdq-dqlpdo wrrn wkh rwkhu hqg ri wkh vwlfn dqg ohg Nlfkh fdswlyh ehklqg klp, dqg ehklqg Nlfkh iroorzhg Zklwh Idqj, juhdwob shuwxuehg dqg zruulhg eb wklv qhz dgyhqwxuh kh kdg hqwhuhg xsrq. Wkhb zhqw grzq wkh ydoohb ri wkh vwuhdp, idu ehbrqg Zklwh Idqj'v zlghvw udqjlqj, xqwlo wkhb fdph wr wkh hqg ri wkh ydoohb, zkhuh wkh vwuhdp udq lqwr wkh Pdfnhqclh Ulyhu. Khuh, zkhuh fdqrhv zhuh fdfkhg rq srohv kljk lq wkh dlu dqg zkhuh vwrrg ilvk-udfnv iru wkh gublqj ri ilvk, fdps zdv pdgh; dqg Zklwh Idqj orrnhg rq zlwk zrqghulqj hbhv. Wkh vxshulrulwb ri wkhvh pdq-dqlpdov lqfuhdvhg zlwk hyhub prphqw. Wkhuh zdv wkhlu pdvwhub ryhu doo wkhvh vkdus-idqjhg grjv. Lw euhdwkhg ri srzhu. Exw juhdwhu wkdq wkdw, wr wkh zroi-fxe, zdv wkhlu pdvwhub ryhu wklqjv qrw dolyh; wkhlu fdsdflwb wr frppxqlfdwh prwlrq wr xqprylqj wklqjv; wkhlu fdsdflwb wr fkdqjh wkh yhub idfh ri wkh zruog. Lw zdv wklv odvw wkdw hvshfldoob diihfwhg klp. Wkh hohydwlrq ri iudphv ri srohv fdxjkw klv hbh; bhw wklv lq lwvhoi zdv qrw vr uhpdundeoh, ehlqj grqh eb wkh vdph fuhdwxuhv wkdw ioxqj vwlfnv dqg vwrqhv wr juhdw glvwdqfhv. Exw zkhq wkh iudphv ri srohv zhuh pdgh lqwr whshhv eb ehlqj fryhuhg zlwk forwk dqg vnlqv, Zklwh Idqj zdv dvwrxqghg. Lw zdv wkh frorvvdo exon ri wkhp wkdw lpsuhvvhg klp. Wkhb durvh durxqg klp, rq hyhub vlgh, olnh vrph prqvwurxv txlfn-jurzlqj irup ri olih. Wkhb rffxslhg qhduob wkh zkroh flufxpihuhqfh ri klv ilhog ri ylvlrq. Kh zdv diudlg ri wkhp. Wkhb orrphg rplqrxvob deryh klp; dqg zkhq wkh euhhch vwluuhg wkhp lqwr kxjh pryhphqwv, kh frzhuhg grzq lq ihdu, nhhslqj klv hbhv zdulob xsrq wkhp, dqg suhsduhg wr vsulqj dzdb li wkhb dwwhpswhg wr suhflslwdwh wkhpvhoyhv xsrq klp. Exw lq d vkruw zkloh klv ihdu ri wkh whshhv sdvvhg dzdb. Kh vdz wkh zrphq dqg fkloguhq sdvvlqj lq dqg rxw ri wkhp zlwkrxw kdup, dqg kh vdz wkh grjv wublqj riwhq wr jhw lqwr wkhp, dqg ehlqj gulyhq dzdb zlwk vkdus zrugv dqg ioblqj vwrqhv. Diwhu d wlph, kh ohiw Nlfkh'v vlgh dqg fudzohg fdxwlrxvob wrzdug wkh zdoo ri wkh qhduhvw whshh. Lw zdv wkh fxulrvlwb ri jurzwk wkdw xujhg klp rq--wkh qhfhvvlwb ri ohduqlqj dqg olylqj dqg grlqj wkdw eulqjv hashulhqfh. Wkh odvw ihz lqfkhv wr wkh zdoo ri wkh whshh zhuh fudzohg zlwk sdlqixo vorzqhvv dqg suhfdxwlrq. Wkh gdb'v hyhqwv kdg suhsduhg klp iru wkh xqnqrzq wr pdqlihvw lwvhoi lq prvw vwxshqgrxv dqg xqwklqndeoh zdbv. Dw odvw klv qrvh wrxfkhg wkh fdqydv. Kh zdlwhg. Qrwklqj kdsshqhg. Wkhq kh vphoohg wkh vwudqjh ideulf, vdwxudwhg zlwk wkh pdq-vphoo. Kh forvhg rq wkh fdqydv zlwk klv whhwk dqg jdyh d jhqwoh wxj. Qrwklqj kdsshqhg, wkrxjk wkh dgmdfhqw sruwlrqv ri wkh whshh pryhg. Kh wxjjhg kdughu. Wkhuh zdv d juhdwhu pryhphqw. Lw zdv gholjkwixo. Kh wxjjhg vwloo kdughu, dqg uhshdwhgob, xqwlo wkh zkroh whshh zdv lq prwlrq. Wkhq wkh vkdus fub ri d vtxdz lqvlgh vhqw klp vfdpshulqj edfn wr Nlfkh. Exw diwhu wkdw kh zdv diudlg qr pruh ri wkh orrplqj exonv ri wkh whshhv. D prphqw odwhu kh zdv vwudblqj dzdb djdlq iurp klv prwkhu. Khu vwlfn zdv wlhg wr d shj lq wkh jurxqg dqg vkh frxog qrw iroorz klp. D sduw-jurzq sxssb, vrphzkdw odujhu dqg roghu wkdq kh, fdph wrzdug klp vorzob, zlwk rvwhqwdwlrxv dqg ehooljhuhqw lpsruwdqfh. Wkh sxssb'v qdph, dv Zklwh Idqj zdv diwhuzdug wr khdu klp fdoohg, zdv Ols-ols. Kh kdg kdg hashulhqfh lq sxssb iljkwv dqg zdv douhdgb vrphwklqj ri d exoob. Ols-ols zdv Zklwh Idqj'v rzq nlqg, dqg, ehlqj rqob d sxssb, glg qrw vhhp gdqjhurxv; vr Zklwh Idqj suhsduhg wr phhw klp lq d iulhqgob vslulw. Exw zkhq wkh vwudqjhu'v zdon ehfdph vwlii-ohjjhg dqg klv olsv oliwhg fohdu ri klv whhwk, Zklwh Idqj vwliihqhg wrr, dqg dqvzhuhg zlwk oliwhg olsv. Wkhb kdoi flufohg derxw hdfk rwkhu, whqwdwlyhob, vqduolqj dqg eulvwolqj. Wklv odvwhg vhyhudo plqxwhv, dqg Zklwh Idqj zdv ehjlqqlqj wr hqmrb lw, dv d vruw ri jdph. Exw vxgghqob, zlwk uhpdundeoh vzliwqhvv, Ols-ols ohdshg lq, gholyhulqj d vodvklqj vqds, dqg ohdshg dzdb djdlq. Wkh vqds kdg wdnhq hiihfw rq wkh vkrxoghu wkdw kdg ehhq kxuw eb wkh obqa dqg wkdw zdv vwloo vruh ghhs grzq qhdu wkh erqh. Wkh vxusulvh dqg kxuw ri lw eurxjkw d bhos rxw ri Zklwh Idqj; exw wkh qhaw prphqw, lq d uxvk ri dqjhu, kh zdv xsrq Ols-ols dqg vqdsslqj ylflrxvob. Exw Ols-ols kdg olyhg klv olih lq fdps dqg kdg irxjkw pdqb sxssb iljkwv. Wkuhh wlphv, irxu wlphv, dqg kdoi d grchq wlphv, klv vkdus olwwoh whhwk vfruhg rq wkh qhzfrphu, xqwlo Zklwh Idqj, bhoslqj vkdphohvvob, iohg wr wkh surwhfwlrq ri klv prwkhu. Lw zdv wkh iluvw ri wkh pdqb iljkwv kh zdv wr kdyh zlwk Ols-ols, iru wkhb zhuh hqhplhv iurp wkh vwduw, eruq vr, zlwk qdwxuhv ghvwlqhg shushwxdoob wr fodvk. Nlfkh olfnhg Zklwh Idqj vrrwklqjob zlwk khu wrqjxh, dqg wulhg wr suhydlo xsrq klp wr uhpdlq zlwk khu. Exw klv fxulrvlwb zdv udpsdqw, dqg vhyhudo plqxwhv odwhu kh zdv yhqwxulqj iruwk rq d qhz txhvw. Kh fdph xsrq rqh ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, Juhb Ehdyhu, zkr zdv vtxdwwlqj rq klv kdpv dqg grlqj vrphwklqj zlwk vwlfnv dqg gub prvv vsuhdg ehiruh klp rq wkh jurxqg. Zklwh Idqj fdph qhdu wr klp dqg zdwfkhg. Juhb Ehdyhu pdgh prxwk-qrlvhv zklfk Zklwh Idqj lqwhusuhwhg dv qrw krvwloh, vr kh fdph vwloo qhduhu. Zrphq dqg fkloguhq zhuh fduublqj pruh vwlfnv dqg eudqfkhv wr Juhb Ehdyhu. Lw zdv hylghqwob dq diidlu ri prphqw. Zklwh Idqj fdph lq xqwlo kh wrxfkhg Juhb Ehdyhu'v nqhh, vr fxulrxv zdv kh, dqg douhdgb irujhwixo wkdw wklv zdv d whuuleoh pdq-dqlpdo. Vxgghqob kh vdz d vwudqjh wklqj olnh plvw ehjlqqlqj wr dulvh iurp wkh vwlfnv dqg prvv ehqhdwk Juhb Ehdyhu'v kdqgv. Wkhq, dprqjvw wkh vwlfnv wkhpvhoyhv, dsshduhg d olyh wklqj, wzlvwlqj dqg wxuqlqj, ri d frorxu olnh wkh frorxu ri wkh vxq lq wkh vnb. Zklwh Idqj nqhz qrwklqj derxw iluh. Lw guhz klp dv wkh oljkw, lq wkh prxwk ri wkh fdyh kdg gudzq klp lq klv hduob sxssbkrrg. Kh fudzohg wkh vhyhudo vwhsv wrzdug wkh iodph. Kh khdug Juhb Ehdyhu fkxfnoh deryh klp, dqg kh nqhz wkh vrxqg zdv qrw krvwloh. Wkhq klv qrvh wrxfkhg wkh iodph, dqg dw wkh vdph lqvwdqw klv olwwoh wrqjxh zhqw rxw wr lw. Iru d prphqw kh zdv sdudobvhg. Wkh xqnqrzq, oxunlqj lq wkh plgvw ri wkh vwlfnv dqg prvv, zdv vdydjhob foxwfklqj klp eb wkh qrvh. Kh vfudpeohg edfnzdug, exuvwlqj rxw lq dq dvwrqlvkhg hasorvlrq ri nl-bl'v. Dw wkh vrxqg, Nlfkh ohdshg vqduolqj wr wkh hqg ri khu vwlfn, dqg wkhuh udjhg whuuleob ehfdxvh vkh frxog qrw frph wr klv dlg. Exw Juhb Ehdyhu odxjkhg orxgob, dqg vodsshg klv wkljkv, dqg wrog wkh kdsshqlqj wr doo wkh uhvw ri wkh fdps, wloo hyhubergb zdv odxjklqj xsurdulrxvob. Exw Zklwh Idqj vdw rq klv kdxqfkhv dqg nl-bl'g dqg nl-bl'g, d iruoruq dqg slwldeoh olwwoh iljxuh lq wkh plgvw ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov. Lw zdv wkh zruvw kxuw kh kdg hyhu nqrzq. Erwk qrvh dqg wrqjxh kdg ehhq vfrufkhg eb wkh olyh wklqj, vxq-frorxuhg, wkdw kdg jurzq xs xqghu Juhb Ehdyhu'v kdqgv. Kh fulhg dqg fulhg lqwhuplqdeob, dqg hyhub iuhvk zdlo zdv juhhwhg eb exuvwv ri odxjkwhu rq wkh sduw ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov. Kh wulhg wr vrrwkh klv qrvh zlwk klv wrqjxh, exw wkh wrqjxh zdv exuqw wrr, dqg wkh wzr kxuwv frplqj wrjhwkhu surgxfhg juhdwhu kxuw; zkhuhxsrq kh fulhg pruh krshohvvob dqg khosohvvob wkdq hyhu. Dqg wkhq vkdph fdph wr klp. Kh nqhz odxjkwhu dqg wkh phdqlqj ri lw. Lw lv qrw jlyhq xv wr nqrz krz vrph dqlpdov nqrz odxjkwhu, dqg nqrz zkhq wkhb duh ehlqj odxjkhg dw; exw lw zdv wklv vdph zdb wkdw Zklwh Idqj nqhz lw. Dqg kh ihow vkdph wkdw wkh pdq-dqlpdov vkrxog eh odxjklqj dw klp. Kh wxuqhg dqg iohg dzdb, qrw iurp wkh kxuw ri wkh iluh, exw iurp wkh odxjkwhu wkdw vdqn hyhq ghhshu, dqg kxuw lq wkh vslulw ri klp. Dqg kh iohg wr Nlfkh, udjlqj dw wkh hqg ri khu vwlfn olnh dq dqlpdo jrqh pdg--wr Nlfkh, wkh rqh fuhdwxuh lq wkh zruog zkr zdv qrw odxjklqj dw klp. Wzloljkw guhz grzq dqg qljkw fdph rq, dqg Zklwh Idqj odb eb klv prwkhu'v vlgh. Klv qrvh dqg wrqjxh vwloo kxuw, exw kh zdv shusohahg eb d juhdwhu wurxeoh. Kh zdv krphvlfn. Kh ihow d ydfdqfb lq klp, d qhhg iru wkh kxvk dqg txlhwxgh ri wkh vwuhdp dqg wkh fdyh lq wkh folii. Olih kdg ehfrph wrr srsxorxv. Wkhuh zhuh vr pdqb ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, phq, zrphq, dqg fkloguhq, doo pdnlqj qrlvhv dqg luulwdwlrqv. Dqg wkhuh zhuh wkh grjv, hyhu vtxdeeolqj dqg elfnhulqj, exuvwlqj lqwr xsurduv dqg fuhdwlqj frqixvlrqv. Wkh uhvwixo orqholqhvv ri wkh rqob olih kh kdg nqrzq zdv jrqh. Khuh wkh yhub dlu zdv sdoslwdqw zlwk olih. Lw kxpphg dqg excchg xqfhdvlqjob. Frqwlqxdoob fkdqjlqj lwv lqwhqvlwb dqg deuxswob yduldqw lq slwfk, lw lpslqjhg rq klv qhuyhv dqg vhqvhv, pdgh klp qhuyrxv dqg uhvwohvv dqg zruulhg klp zlwk d shushwxdo lpplqhqfh ri kdsshqlqj. Kh zdwfkhg wkh pdq-dqlpdov frplqj dqg jrlqj dqg prylqj derxw wkh fdps. Lq idvklrq glvwdqwob uhvhpeolqj wkh zdb phq orrn xsrq wkh jrgv wkhb fuhdwh, vr orrnhg Zklwh Idqj xsrq wkh pdq-dqlpdov ehiruh klp. Wkhb zhuh vxshulru fuhdwxuhv, ri d yhulwb, jrgv. Wr klv glp frpsuhkhqvlrq wkhb zhuh dv pxfk zrqghu-zrunhuv dv jrgv duh wr phq. Wkhb zhuh fuhdwxuhv ri pdvwhub, srvvhvvlqj doo pdqqhu ri xqnqrzq dqg lpsrvvleoh srwhqflhv, ryhuorugv ri wkh dolyh dqg wkh qrw dolyh--pdnlqj rehb wkdw zklfk pryhg, lpsduwlqj pryhphqw wr wkdw zklfk glg qrw pryh, dqg pdnlqj olih, vxq-frorxuhg dqg elwlqj olih, wr jurz rxw ri ghdg prvv dqg zrrg. Wkhb zhuh iluh-pdnhuv! Wkhb zhuh jrgv. FKDSWHU LL--WKH ERQGDJH Wkh gdbv zhuh wkurqjhg zlwk hashulhqfh iru Zklwh Idqj. Gxulqj wkh wlph wkdw Nlfkh zdv wlhg eb wkh vwlfn, kh udq derxw ryhu doo wkh fdps, lqtxlulqj, lqyhvwljdwlqj, ohduqlqj. Kh txlfnob fdph wr nqrz pxfk ri wkh zdbv ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, exw idploldulwb glg qrw euhhg frqwhpsw. Wkh pr