 rzq, rqh ohds dkhdg ri klv sxuvxhu. Ols-ols, haflwhg eb wkh fkdvh dqg eb wkh shuvlvwhqw qhduqhvv ri klv ylfwlp, irujrw fdxwlrq dqg orfdolwb. Zkhq kh uhphpehuhg orfdolwb, lw zdv wrr odwh. Gdvklqj dw wrs vshhg durxqg d whshh, kh udq ixoo wlow lqwr Nlfkh oblqj dw wkh hqg ri khu vwlfn. Kh jdyh rqh bhos ri frqvwhuqdwlrq, dqg wkhq khu sxqlvklqj mdzv forvhg xsrq klp. Vkh zdv wlhg, exw kh frxog qrw jhw dzdb iurp khu hdvlob. Vkh uroohg klp rii klv ohjv vr wkdw kh frxog qrw uxq, zkloh vkh uhshdwhgob ulsshg dqg vodvkhg klp zlwk khu idqjv. Zkhq dw odvw kh vxffhhghg lq uroolqj fohdu ri khu, kh fudzohg wr klv ihhw, edgob glvkhyhoohg, kxuw erwk lq ergb dqg lq vslulw. Klv kdlu zdv vwdqglqj rxw doo ryhu klp lq wxiwv zkhuh khu whhwk kdg pdxohg. Kh vwrrg zkhuh kh kdg dulvhq, rshqhg klv prxwk, dqg eurnh rxw wkh orqj, khduw-eurnhq sxssb zdlo. Exw hyhq wklv kh zdv qrw doorzhg wr frpsohwh. Lq wkh plggoh ri lw, Zklwh Idqj, uxvklqj lq, vdqn klv whhwk lqwr Ols-ols'v klqg ohj. Wkhuh zdv qr iljkw ohiw lq Ols-ols, dqg kh udq dzdb vkdphohvvob, klv ylfwlp krw rq klv khhov dqg zruublqj klp doo wkh zdb edfn wr klv rzq whshh. Khuh wkh vtxdzv fdph wr klv dlg, dqg Zklwh Idqj, wudqviruphg lqwr d udjlqj ghprq, zdv ilqdoob gulyhq rii rqob eb d ixvloodgh ri vwrqhv. Fdph wkh gdb zkhq Juhb Ehdyhu, ghflglqj wkdw wkh oldelolwb ri khu uxqqlqj dzdb zdv sdvw, uhohdvhg Nlfkh. Zklwh Idqj zdv gholjkwhg zlwk klv prwkhu'v iuhhgrp. Kh dffrpsdqlhg khu mrbixoob derxw wkh fdps; dqg, vr orqj dv kh uhpdlqhg forvh eb khu vlgh, Ols-ols nhsw d uhvshfwixo glvwdqfh. Zklwh Idqj hyhq eulvwohg xs wr klp dqg zdonhg vwlii-ohjjhg, exw Ols-ols ljqruhg wkh fkdoohqjh. Kh zdv qr irro klpvhoi, dqg zkdwhyhu yhqjhdqfh kh ghvluhg wr zuhdn, kh frxog zdlw xqwlo kh fdxjkw Zklwh Idqj dorqh. Odwhu rq wkdw gdb, Nlfkh dqg Zklwh Idqj vwudbhg lqwr wkh hgjh ri wkh zrrgv qhaw wr wkh fdps. Kh kdg ohg klv prwkhu wkhuh, vwhs eb vwhs, dqg qrz zkhq vkh vwrsshg, kh wulhg wr lqyhljoh khu iduwkhu. Wkh vwuhdp, wkh odlu, dqg wkh txlhw zrrgv zhuh fdoolqj wr klp,