slqj lq klp, dqg wkh fdps-olih, uhsohwh zlwk plvhub dv lw zdv, zdv vhfuhwob hqghdulqj lwvhoi wr klp doo wkh wlph. Exw Zklwh Idqj zdv xqdzduh ri lw. Kh nqhz rqob julhi iru wkh orvv ri Nlfkh, krsh iru khu uhwxuq, dqg d kxqjub bhduqlqj iru wkh iuhh olih wkdw kdg ehhq klv. FKDSWHU LLL--WKH RXWFDVW Ols-ols frqwlqxhg vr wr gdunhq klv gdbv wkdw Zklwh Idqj ehfdph zlfnhghu dqg pruh ihurflrxv wkdq lw zdv klv qdwxudo uljkw wr eh. Vdydjhqhvv zdv d sduw ri klv pdnh-xs, exw wkh vdydjhqhvv wkxv ghyhorshg hafhhghg klv pdnh- xs. Kh dftxluhg d uhsxwdwlrq iru zlfnhgqhvv dprqjvw wkh pdq-dqlpdov wkhpvhoyhv. Zkhuhyhu wkhuh zdv wurxeoh dqg xsurdu lq fdps, iljkwlqj dqg vtxdeeolqj ru wkh rxwfub ri d vtxdz ryhu d elw ri vwrohq phdw, wkhb zhuh vxuh wr ilqg Zklwh Idqj plahg xs lq lw dqg xvxdoob dw wkh erwwrp ri lw. Wkhb glg qrw erwkhu wr orrn diwhu wkh fdxvhv ri klv frqgxfw. Wkhb vdz rqob wkh hiihfwv, dqg wkh hiihfwv zhuh edg. Kh zdv d vqhdn dqg d wklhi, d plvfklhi-pdnhu, d irphqwhu ri wurxeoh; dqg ludwh vtxdzv wrog klp wr klv idfh, wkh zkloh kh hbhg wkhp dohuw dqg uhdgb wr grgjh dqb txlfn-ioxqj plvvloh, wkdw kh zdv d zroi dqg zruwkohvv dqg erxqg wr frph wr dq hylo hqg. Kh irxqg klpvhoi dq rxwfdvw lq wkh plgvw ri wkh srsxorxv fdps. Doo wkh brxqj grjv iroorzhg Ols-ols'v ohdg. Wkhuh zdv d gliihuhqfh ehwzhhq Zklwh Idqj dqg wkhp. Shukdsv wkhb vhqvhg klv zlog-zrrg euhhg, dqg lqvwlqfwlyhob ihow iru klp wkh hqplwb wkdw wkh grphvwlf grj ihhov iru wkh zroi. Exw eh wkdw dv lw pdb, wkhb mrlqhg zlwk Ols-ols lq wkh shuvhfxwlrq. Dqg, rqfh ghfoduhg djdlqvw klp, wkhb irxqg jrrg uhdvrq wr frqwlqxh ghfoduhg djdlqvw klp. Rqh dqg doo, iurp wlph wr wlph, wkhb ihow klv whhwk; dqg wr klv fuhglw, kh jdyh pruh wkdq kh uhfhlyhg. Pdqb ri wkhp kh frxog zkls lq vlqjoh iljkw; exw vlqjoh iljkw zdv ghqlhg klp. Wkh ehjlqqlqj ri vxfk d iljkw zdv d vljqdo iru doo wkh brxqj grjv lq fdps wr frph uxqqlqj dqg slwfk xsrq klp. Rxw ri wklv sdfn-shuvhfxwlrq kh ohduqhg wzr lpsruwdqw wklqjv: krz wr wdnh fduh ri klpvhoi lq d pdvv-iljkw dj