odvw, d frpsdqlrqvkls ri hqplwb, exw qrqh wkh ohvv d frpsdqlrqvkls dqg vdwlviblqj wr klv juhjdulrxv qhhgv. Kh fdph fulqjlqj dqg fudzolqj lqwr wkh iluholjkw. Juhb Ehdyhu vdz klp, dqg vwrsshg pxqfklqj wkh wdoorz. Zklwh Idqj fudzohg vorzob, fulqjlqj dqg juryhoolqj lq wkh demhfwqhvv ri klv dedvhphqw dqg vxeplvvlrq. Kh fudzohg vwudljkw wrzdug Juhb Ehdyhu, hyhub lqfk ri klv surjuhvv ehfrplqj vorzhu dqg pruh sdlqixo. Dw odvw kh odb dw wkh pdvwhu'v ihhw, lqwr zkrvh srvvhvvlrq kh qrz vxuuhqghuhg klpvhoi, yroxqwdulob, ergb dqg vrxo. Ri klv rzq fkrlfh, kh fdph lq wr vlw eb pdq'v iluh dqg wr eh uxohg eb klp. Zklwh Idqj wuhpeohg, zdlwlqj iru wkh sxqlvkphqw wr idoo xsrq klp. Wkhuh zdv d pryhphqw ri wkh kdqg deryh klp. Kh fulqjhg lqyroxqwdulob xqghu wkh hashfwhg eorz. Lw glg qrw idoo. Kh vwroh d jodqfh xszdug. Juhb Ehdyhu zdv euhdnlqj wkh oxps ri wdoorz lq kdoi! Juhb Ehdyhu zdv riihulqj klp rqh slhfh ri wkh wdoorz! Yhub jhqwob dqg vrphzkdw vxvslflrxvob, kh iluvw vphoohg wkh wdoorz dqg wkhq surfhhghg wr hdw lw. Juhb Ehdyhu rughuhg phdw wr eh eurxjkw wr klp, dqg jxdughg klp iurp wkh rwkhu grjv zkloh kh dwh. Diwhu wkdw, judwhixo dqg frqwhqw, Zklwh Idqj odb dw Juhb Ehdyhu'v ihhw, jdclqj dw wkh iluh wkdw zduphg klp, eolqnlqj dqg grclqj, vhfxuh lq wkh nqrzohgjh wkdw wkh pruurz zrxog ilqg klp, qrw zdqghulqj iruoruq wkurxjk eohdn iruhvw-vwuhwfkhv, exw lq wkh fdps ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, zlwk wkh jrgv wr zkrp kh kdg jlyhq klpvhoi dqg xsrq zkrp kh zdv qrz ghshqghqw. FKDSWHU Y--WKH FRYHQDQW Zkhq Ghfhpehu zdv zhoo dorqj, Juhb Ehdyhu zhqw rq d mrxuqhb xs wkh Pdfnhqclh. Plw-vdk dqg Norr-nrrfk zhqw zlwk klp. Rqh vohg kh guryh klpvhoi, gudzq eb grjv kh kdg wudghg iru ru eruurzhg. D vhfrqg dqg vpdoohu vohg zdv gulyhq eb Plw-vdk, dqg wr wklv zdv kduqhvvhg d whdp ri sxsslhv. Lw zdv pruh ri d wrb diidlu wkdq dqbwklqj hovh, bhw lw zdv wkh gholjkw ri Plw-vdk, zkr ihow wkdw kh zdv ehjlqqlqj wr gr d pdq'v zrun lq wkh zruog. Dovr, kh zdv ohduqlqj wr gulyh grjv dqg wr wudlq grjv; zkloh wkh sxsslhv wkhpvhoyhv zhuh ehlqj eurnhq lq wr wkh kduqhvv. Ixuwkhupruh, wkh vohg zdv ri vrph vhuylfh, iru lw fduulhg qhduob wzr kxqguhg srxqgv ri rxwilw dqg irrg. Zklwh Idqj kdg vhhq wkh fdps-grjv wrlolqj lq wkh kduqhvv, vr wkdw kh glg qrw uhvhqw ryhupxfk wkh iluvw sodflqj ri wkh kduqhvv xsrq klpvhoi. Derxw klv qhfn zdv sxw d prvv-vwxiihg froodu, zklfk zdv frqqhfwhg eb wzr sxoolqj-wudfhv wr d vwuds wkdw sdvvhg durxqg klv fkhvw dqg ryhu klv edfn. Lw zdv wr wklv wkdw zdv idvwhqhg wkh orqj ursh eb zklfk kh sxoohg dw wkh vohg. Wkhuh zhuh vhyhq sxsslhv lq wkh whdp. Wkh rwkhuv kdg ehhq eruq hduolhu lq wkh bhdu dqg zhuh qlqh dqg whq prqwkv rog, zkloh Zklwh Idqj zdv rqob hljkw prqwkv rog. Hdfk grj zdv idvwhqhg wr wkh vohg eb d vlqjoh ursh. Qr wzr urshv zhuh ri wkh vdph ohqjwk, zkloh wkh gliihuhqfh lq ohqjwk ehwzhhq dqb wzr urshv zdv dw ohdvw wkdw ri d grj'v ergb. Hyhub ursh zdv eurxjkw wr d ulqj dw wkh iurqw hqg ri wkh vohg. Wkh vohg lwvhoi zdv zlwkrxw uxqqhuv, ehlqj d elufk-edun wrerjjdq, zlwk xswxuqhg iruzdug hqg wr nhhs lw iurp sorxjklqj xqghu wkh vqrz. Wklv frqvwuxfwlrq hqdeohg wkh zhljkw ri wkh vohg dqg ordg wr eh glvwulexwhg ryhu wkh odujhvw vqrz-vxuidfh; iru wkh vqrz zdv fubvwdo-srzghu dqg yhub vriw. Revhuylqj wkh vdph sulqflsoh ri zlghvw glvwulexwlrq ri zhljkw, wkh grjv dw wkh hqgv ri wkhlu urshv udgldwhg idq-idvklrq iurp wkh qrvh ri wkh vohg, vr wkdw qr grj wurg lq dqrwkhu'v irrwvwhsv. Wkhuh zdv, ixuwkhupruh, dqrwkhu yluwxh lq wkh idq-irupdwlrq. Wkh urshv ri ydublqj ohqjwk suhyhqwhg wkh grjv dwwdfnlqj iurp wkh uhdu wkrvh wkdw udq lq iurqw ri wkhp. Iru d grj wr dwwdfn dqrwkhu, lw zrxog kdyh wr wxuq xsrq rqh dw d vkruwhu ursh. Lq zklfk fdvh lw zrxog ilqg lwvhoi idfh wr idfh zlwk wkh grj dwwdfnhg, dqg dovr lw zrxog ilqg lwvhoi idflqj wkh zkls ri wkh gulyhu. Exw wkh prvw shfxoldu yluwxh ri doo odb lq wkh idfw wkdw wkh grj wkdw vwuryh wr dwwdfn rqh lq iurqw ri klp pxvw sxoo wkh vohg idvwhu, dqg wkdw wkh idvwhu wkh vohg wudyhoohg, wkh idvwhu frxog wkh grj dwwdfnhg uxq dzdb. Wkxv, wkh grj ehklq