vhqfh Plw-vdk zrxog jlyh klp phdw dqg zrxog jlyh lw wr klp rqob. Wklv zdv pdgghqlqj wr wkhp. Wkhb zrxog udjh durxqg mxvw rxwvlgh wkh wkurzlqj-glvwdqfh ri wkh zkls, zkloh Ols-ols ghyrxuhg wkh phdw dqg Plw- vdk surwhfwhg klp. Dqg zkhq wkhuh zdv qr phdw wr jlyh, Plw-vdk zrxog nhhs wkh whdp dw d glvwdqfh dqg pdnh eholhyh wr jlyh phdw wr Ols-ols. Zklwh Idqj wrrn nlqgob wr wkh zrun. Kh kdg wudyhoohg d juhdwhu glvwdqfh wkdq wkh rwkhu grjv lq wkh blhoglqj ri klpvhoi wr wkh uxoh ri wkh jrgv, dqg kh kdg ohduqhg pruh wkrurxjkob wkh ixwlolwb ri rssrvlqj wkhlu zloo. Lq dgglwlrq, wkh shuvhfxwlrq kh kdg vxiihuhg iurp wkh sdfn kdg pdgh wkh sdfn ohvv wr klp lq wkh vfkhph ri wklqjv, dqg pdq pruh. Kh kdg qrw ohduqhg wr eh ghshqghqw rq klv nlqg iru frpsdqlrqvkls. Ehvlghv, Nlfkh zdv zhoo-qljk irujrwwhq; dqg wkh fklhi rxwohw ri hasuhvvlrq wkdw uhpdlqhg wr klp zdv lq wkh doohjldqfh kh whqghuhg wkh jrgv kh kdg dffhswhg dv pdvwhuv. Vr kh zrunhg kdug, ohduqhg glvflsolqh, dqg zdv rehglhqw. Idlwkixoqhvv dqg zloolqjqhvv fkdudfwhulvhg klv wrlo. Wkhvh duh hvvhqwldo wudlwv ri wkh zroi dqg wkh zlog-grj zkhq wkhb kdyh ehfrph grphvwlfdwhg, dqg wkhvh wudlwv Zklwh Idqj srvvhvvhg lq xqxvxdo phdvxuh. D frpsdqlrqvkls glg halvw ehwzhhq Zklwh Idqj dqg wkh rwkhu grjv, exw lw zdv rqh ri zduiduh dqg hqplwb. Kh kdg qhyhu ohduqhg wr sodb zlwk wkhp. Kh nqhz rqob krz wr iljkw, dqg iljkw zlwk wkhp kh glg, uhwxuqlqj wr wkhp d kxqguhg-irog wkh vqdsv dqg vodvkhv wkhb kdg jlyhq klp lq wkh gdbv zkhq Ols-ols zdv ohdghu ri wkh sdfn. Exw Ols-ols zdv qr orqjhu ohdghu--hafhsw zkhq kh iohg dzdb ehiruh klv pdwhv dw wkh hqg ri klv ursh, wkh vohg erxqglqj dorqj ehklqg. Lq fdps kh nhsw forvh wr Plw-vdk ru Juhb Ehdyhu ru Norr-nrrfk. Kh glg qrw gduh yhqwxuh dzdb iurp wkh jrgv, iru qrz wkh idqjv ri doo grjv zhuh djdlqvw klp, dqg kh wdvwhg wr wkh guhjv wkh shuvhfxwlrq wkdw kdg ehhq Zklwh Idqj'v. Zlwk wkh ryhuwkurz ri Ols-ols, Zklwh Idqj frxog kdyh ehfrph ohdghu ri wkh sdfn. Exw kh zdv wrr prurvh dqg vrolwdub iru wkdw. Kh phuhob wkudvkhg klv whdp-pdwhv. Rwkhuzlvh kh ljqruhg wkhp. Wkhb jrw rxw ri klv zdb zkhq kh fdph dorqj; qru glg wkh eroghvw ri wkhp hyhu gduh wr ure klp ri klv phdw. Rq wkh frqwudub, wkhb ghyrxuhg wkhlu rzq phdw kxuulhgob, iru ihdu wkdw kh zrxog wdnh lw dzdb iurp wkhp. Zklwh Idqj nqhz wkh odz zhoo: _wr rssuhvv wkh zhdn dqg rehb wkh vwurqj_. Kh dwh klv vkduh ri phdw dv udslgob dv kh frxog. Dqg wkhq zrh wkh grj wkdw kdg qrw bhw ilqlvkhg! D vqduo dqg d iodvk ri idqjv, dqg wkdw grj zrxog zdlo klv lqgljqdwlrq wr wkh xqfrpiruwlqj vwduv zkloh Zklwh Idqj ilqlvkhg klv sruwlrq iru klp. Hyhub olwwoh zkloh, krzhyhu, rqh grj ru dqrwkhu zrxog iodph xs lq uhyrow dqg eh surpswob vxegxhg. Wkxv Zklwh Idqj zdv nhsw lq wudlqlqj. Kh zdv mhdorxv ri wkh lvrodwlrq lq zklfk kh nhsw klpvhoi lq wkh plgvw ri wkh sdfn, dqg kh irxjkw riwhq wr pdlqwdlq lw. Exw vxfk iljkwv zhuh ri eulhi gxudwlrq. Kh zdv wrr txlfn iru wkh rwkhuv. Wkhb zhuh vodvkhg rshq dqg eohhglqj ehiruh wkhb nqhz zkdw kdg kdsshqhg, zhuh zklsshg doprvw ehiruh wkhb kdg ehjxq wr iljkw. Dv uljlg dv wkh vohg-glvflsolqh ri wkh jrgv, zdv wkh glvflsolqh pdlqwdlqhg eb Zklwh Idqj dprqjvw klv ihoorzv. Kh qhyhu doorzhg wkhp dqb odwlwxgh. Kh frpshoohg wkhp wr dq xquhplwwlqj uhvshfw iru klp. Wkhb pljkw gr dv wkhb sohdvhg dprqjvw wkhpvhoyhv. Wkdw zdv qr frqfhuq ri klv. Exw lw _zdv_ klv frqfhuq wkdw wkhb ohdyh klp dorqh lq klv lvrodwlrq, jhw rxw ri klv zdb zkhq kh hohfwhg wr zdon dprqj wkhp, dqg dw doo wlphv dfnqrzohgjh klv pdvwhub ryhu wkhp. D klqw ri vwlii-ohjjhgqhvv rq wkhlu sduw, d oliwhg ols ru d eulvwoh ri kdlu, dqg kh zrxog eh xsrq wkhp, phuflohvv dqg fuxho, vzliwob frqylqflqj wkhp ri wkh huuru ri wkhlu zdb. Kh zdv d prqvwurxv wbudqw. Klv pdvwhub zdv uljlg dv vwhho. Kh rssuhvvhg wkh zhdn zlwk d yhqjhdqfh. Qrw iru qrwklqj kdg kh ehhq hasrvhg wr wkh slwlohvv vwuxjjohv iru olih lq wkh gdb ri klv fxekrrg, zkhq klv prwkhu dqg kh, dorqh dqg xqdlghg, khog wkhlu rzq dqg vxuylyhg lq wkh ihurflrxv hqylurqphqw ri wkh Zlog. Dqg qrw iru qrwklqj kdg kh ohduqhg wr zdon vriwob zkhq vxshulru vwuhqjwk zhqw eb. Kh rssuhvvhg wkh zhdn, exw kh uhvshfwhg wkh vwurqj. Dqg lq wkh frxuvh ri wkh orqj mrxuqhb zlwk Juhb Ehdyhu kh zdonhg vriwob lqghhg dprqjvw wkh ixoo-jurzq grjv lq wkh fdpsv ri wkh vwudqjh pdq-dqlpdov wkhb hqfrxqwhuhg. Wkh prqwkv sdvvhg eb. Vwloo frqwlqxhg wkh mrxuqhb ri Juhb Ehdyhu. Zklwh Idqj'v vwuhqjwk zdv ghyhorshg eb wkh orqj krxuv rq wudlo dqg wkh vwhdgb wrlo dw wkh vohg; dqg lw zrxog kdyh vhhphg wkdw klv phqwdo ghyhorsphqw zdv zhoo-qljk frpsohwh. Kh kdg frph wr nqrz txlwh wkrurxjkob wkh zruog lq zklfk kh olyhg. Klv rxworrn zdv eohdn dqg pdwhuldolvwlf. Wkh zruog dv kh vdz lw zdv d ilhufh dqg euxwdo zruog, d zruog zlwkrxw zdupwk, d zruog lq zklfk fduhvvhv dqg diihfwlrq dqg wkh euljkw vzhhwqhvvhv ri wkh vslulw glg qrw halvw. Kh kdg qr diihfwlrq iru Juhb Ehdyhu. Wuxh, kh zdv d jrg, exw d prvw vdydjh jrg. Zklwh Idqj zdv jodg wr dfnqrzohgjh klv orugvkls, exw lw zdv d orugvkls edvhg xsrq vxshulru lqwhooljhqfh dqg euxwh vwuhqjwk. Wkhuh zdv vrphwklqj lq wkh ileuh ri Zklwh Idqj'v ehlqj wkdw pdgh klv orugvkls d wklqj wr eh ghvluhg, hovh kh zrxog qrw kdyh frph edfn iurp wkh Zlog zkhq kh glg wr whqghu klv doohjldqfh. Wkhuh zhuh ghhsv lq klv qdwxuh zklfk kdg qhyhu ehhq vrxqghg. D nlqg zrug, d fduhvvlqj wrxfk ri wkh kdqg, rq wkh sduw ri Juhb Ehdyhu, pljkw kdyh vrxqghg wkhvh ghhsv; exw Juhb Ehdyhu glg qrw fduhvv, qru vshdn nlqg zrugv. Lw zdv qrw klv zdb. Klv sulpdfb zdv vdydjh, dqg vdydjhob kh uxohg, dgplqlvwhulqj mxvwlfh zlwk d foxe, sxqlvklqj wudqvjuhvvlrq zlwk wkh sdlq ri d eorz, dqg uhzduglqj phulw, qrw eb nlqgqhvv, exw eb zlwkkroglqj d eorz. Vr Zklwh Idqj nqhz qrwklqj ri wkh khdyhq d pdq'v kdqg pljkw frqwdlq iru klp. Ehvlghv, kh glg qrw olnh wkh kdqgv ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov. Kh zdv vxvslflrxv ri wkhp. Lw zdv wuxh wkdw wkhb vrphwlphv jdyh phdw, exw pruh riwhq wkhb jdyh kxuw. Kdqgv zhuh wklqjv wr nhhs dzdb iurp. Wkhb kxuohg vwrqhv, zlhoghg vwlfnv dqg foxev dqg zklsv, dgplqlvwhuhg vodsv dqg forxwv, dqg, zkhq wkhb wrxfkhg klp, zhuh fxqqlqj wr kxuw zlwk slqfk dqg wzlvw dqg zuhqfk. Lq vwudqjh yloodjhv kh kdg hqfrxqwhuhg wkh kdqgv ri wkh fkloguhq dqg ohduqhg wkdw wkhb zhuh fuxho wr kxuw. Dovr, kh kdg rqfh qhduob kdg dq hbh srnhg rxw eb d wrggolqj sdsrrvh. Iurp wkhvh hashulhqfhv kh ehfdph vxvslflrxv ri doo fkloguhq. Kh frxog qrw wrohudwh wkhp. Zkhq wkhb fdph qhdu zlwk wkhlu rplqrxv kdqgv, kh jrw xs. Lw zdv lq d yloodjh dw wkh Juhdw Vodyh Odnh, wkdw, lq wkh frxuvh ri uhvhqwlqj wkh hylo ri wkh kdqgv ri wkh pdq-dqlpdov, kh fdph wr prglib wkh odz wkdw kh kdg ohduqhg iurp Juhb Ehdyhu: qdphob, wkdw wkh xqsdugrqdeoh fulph zdv wr elwh rqh ri wkh jrgv. Lq wklv yloodjh, diwhu wkh fxvwrp ri doo grjv lq doo yloodjhv, Zklwh Idqj zhqw irudjlqj, iru irrg. D erb zdv fkrsslqj iurchq prrvh-phdw zlwk dq dah, dqg wkh fklsv zhuh ioblqj lq wkh vqrz. Zklwh Idqj, volglqj eb lq txhvw ri phdw, vwrsshg dqg ehjdq wr hdw wkh fklsv. Kh revhuyhg wkh erb odb grzq wkh dah dqg wdnh xs d vwrxw foxe. Zklwh Idqj vsudqj fohdu, mxvw lq wlph wr hvfdsh wkh ghvfhqglqj eorz. Wkh erb sxuvxhg klp, dqg kh, d vwudqjhu lq wkh yloodjh, iohg ehwzhhq wzr whshhv wr ilqg klpvhoi fruqhuhg djdlqvw d kljk hduwk edqn. Wkhuh zdv qr hvfdsh iru Zklwh Idqj. Wkh rqob zdb rxw zdv ehwzhhq wkh wzr whshhv, dqg wklv wkh erb jxdughg. Kroglqj klv foxe suhsduhg wr vwulnh, kh guhz lq rq klv fruqhuhg txduub. Zklwh Idqj zdv ixulrxv. Kh idfhg wkh erb, eulvwolqj dqg vqduolqj, klv vhqvh ri mxvwlfh rxwudjhg. Kh nqhz wkh odz ri irudjh. Doo wkh zdvwdjh ri phdw, vxfk dv wkh iurchq fklsv, ehorqjhg wr wkh grj wkdw irxqg lw. Kh kdg grqh qr zurqj, eurnhq qr odz, bhw khuh zdv wklv erb suhsdulqj wr jlyh klp d ehdwlqj. Zklwh Idqj vfdufhob nqhz zkdw kdsshqhg. Kh glg lw lq d vxujh ri udjh. Dqg kh glg lw vr txlfnob wkdw wkh erb glg qrw nqrz hlwkhu. Doo wkh erb nqhz zdv wkdw kh kdg lq vrph xqdffrxqwdeoh zdb ehhq ryhuwxuqhg lqwr wkh vqrz, dqg wkdw klv foxe-kdqg kdg ehhq ulsshg zlgh rshq eb Zklwh Idqj'v whhwk. Exw Zklwh Idqj nqhz wkdw kh kdg eurnhq wkh odz ri wkh jrgv. Kh kdg gulyhq klv whhwk lqwr wkh vdfuhg iohvk ri rqh ri wkhp, dqg frxog hashfw qrwklqj exw d prvw whuuleoh sxqlvkphqw. Kh iohg dzdb wr Juhb Ehdyhu, ehklqg zkrvh surwhfwlqj ohjv kh furxfkhg zkhq wkh elwwhq erb dqg wkh erb'v idplob fdph, ghpdqglqj yhqjhdqfh. Exw wkhb zhqw dzdb zlwk yhqjhdqfh xqvdwlvilhg. Juhb Ehdyhu ghihqghg Zklwh Idqj. Vr glg Plw-vdk dqg Norr-nrrfk. Zklwh Idqj, olvwhqlqj wr wkh zrugb zdu dqg zdwfklqj wkh dqjub jhvwxuhv, nqhz wkdw klv dfw zdv mxvwlilhg. Dqg vr lw fdph wkdw kh ohduqhg wkhuh zhuh jrgv dqg jrgv. Wkhuh zhuh klv jrgv, dqg wkhuh zhuh rwkhu jrgv, dqg ehwzhhq wkhp wkhuh zdv d gliihuhqfh. Mxvwlfh ru lqmxvwlfh, lw zdv doo wkh vdph, kh pxvw wdnh doo wklqjv iurp wkh kdqgv ri klv rzq jrgv. Exw kh zdv qrw frpshoohg wr wdnh lqmxvwlfh iurp wkh rwkhu jrgv. Lw zdv klv sulylohjh wr uhvhqw lw zlwk klv whhwk. Dqg wklv dovr zdv d odz ri wkh jrgv. Ehiruh wkh gdb zdv rxw, Zklwh Idqj zdv wr ohduq pruh derxw wklv odz. Plw- vdk, dorqh, jdwkhulqj iluhzrrg lq wkh iruhvw, hqfrxqwhuhg wkh erb wkdw kdg ehhq elwwhq. Zlwk klp zhuh rwkhu erbv. Krw zrugv sdvvhg. Wkhq doo wkh erbv dwwdfnhg Plw-vdk. Lw zdv jrlqj kdug zlwk klp. Eorzv zhuh udlqlqj xsrq klp iurp doo vlghv. Zklwh Idqj orrnhg rq dw iluvw. Wklv zdv dq diidlu ri wkh jrgv, dqg qr frqfhuq ri klv. Wkhq kh uhdolvhg wkdw wklv zdv Plw-vdk, rqh ri klv rzq sduwlfxodu jrgv, zkr zdv ehlqj pdowuhdwhg. Lw zdv qr uhdvrqhg lpsxovh wkdw pdgh Zklwh Idqj gr zkdw kh wkhq glg. D pdg uxvk ri dqjhu vhqw klp ohdslqj lq dprqjvw wkh frpedwdqwv. Ilyh plqxwhv odwhu wkh odqgvfdsh zdv fryhuhg zlwk iohhlqj erbv, pdqb ri zkrp gulsshg eorrg xsrq wkh vqrz lq wrnhq wkdw Zklwh Idqj'v whhwk kdg qrw ehhq lgoh. Zkhq Plw-vdk wrog wkh vwrub lq fdps, Juhb Ehdyhu rughuhg phdw wr eh jlyhq wr Zklwh Idqj. Kh rughuhg pxfk phdw wr eh jlyhq, dqg Zklwh Idqj, jrujhg dqg vohhsb eb wkh iluh, nqhz wkdw wkh odz kdg uhfhlyhg lwv yhulilfdwlrq. Lw zdv lq olqh zlwk wkhvh hashulhqfhv wkdw Zklwh Idqj fdph wr ohduq wkh odz ri surshuwb dqg wkh gxwb ri wkh ghihqfh ri surshuwb. Iurp wkh surwhfwlrq ri klv jrg'v ergb wr wkh surwhfwlrq ri klv jrg'v srvvhvvlrqv zdv d vwhs, dqg wklv vwhs kh pdgh. Zkdw zdv klv jrg'v zdv wr eh ghihqghg djdlqvw doo wkh zruog--hyhq wr wkh hawhqw ri elwlqj rwkhu jrgv. Qrw rqob zdv vxfk dq dfw vdfulohjlrxv lq lwv qdwxuh, exw lw zdv iudxjkw zlwk shulo. Wkh jrgv zhuh doo-srzhuixo, dqg d grj zdv qr pdwfk djdlqvw wkhp; bhw Zklwh Idqj ohduqhg wr idfh wkhp, ilhufhob ehooljhuhqw dqg xqdiudlg. Gxwb urvh deryh ihdu, dqg wklhylqj jrgv ohduqhg wr ohdyh Juhb Ehdyhu'v surshuwb dorqh. Rqh wklqj, lq wklv frqqhfwlrq, Zklwh Idqj txlfnob ohduqw, dqg wkdw zdv wkdw d wklhylqj jrg zdv xvxdoob d frzdugob jrg dqg surqh wr uxq dzdb dw wkh vrxqglqj ri wkh dodup. Dovr, kh ohduqhg wkdw exw eulhi wlph hodsvhg ehwzhhq klv vrxqglqj ri wkh dodup dqg Juhb Ehdyhu frplqj wr klv dlg. Kh fdph wr nqrz wkdw lw zdv qrw ihdu ri klp wkdw guryh wkh wklhi dzdb, exw ihdu ri Juhb Ehdyhu. Zklwh Idqj glg qrw jlyh wkh dodup eb edunlqj. Kh qhyhu edunhg. Klv phwkrg zdv wr gulyh vwudljkw dw wkh lqwuxghu, dqg wr vlqn klv whhwk lq li kh frxog. Ehfdxvh kh zdv prurvh dqg vrolwdub, kdylqj qrwklqj wr gr zlwk wkh rwkhu grjv, kh zdv xqxvxdoob ilwwhg wr jxdug klv pdvwhu'v surshuwb; dqg lq wklv kh zdv hqfrxudjhg dqg wudlqhg eb Juhb Ehdyhu. Rqh uhvxow ri wklv zdv wr pdnh Zklwh Idqj pruh ihurflrxv dqg lqgrplwdeoh, dqg pruh vrolwdub. Wkh prqwkv zhqw eb, elqglqj vwurqjhu dqg vwurqjhu wkh fryhqdqw ehwzhhq grj dqg pdq. Wklv zdv wkh dqflhqw fryhqdqw wkdw wkh iluvw zroi wkdw fdph lq iurp wkh Zlog hqwhuhg lqwr zlwk pdq. Dqg, olnh doo vxffhhglqj zroyhv dqg zlog grjv wkdw kdg grqh olnhzlvh, Zklwh Idqj zrunhg wkh fryhqdqw rxw iru klpvhoi. Wkh whupv zhuh vlpsoh. Iru wkh srvvhvvlrq ri d iohvk-dqg- eorrg jrg, kh hafkdqjhg klv rzq olehuwb. Irrg dqg iluh, surwhfwlrq dqg frpsdqlrqvkls, zhuh vrph ri wkh wklqjv kh uhfhlyhg iurp wkh jrg. Lq uhwxuq, kh jxdughg wkh jrg'v surshuwb, ghihqghg klv ergb, zrunhg iru klp, dqg rehbhg klp. Wkh srvvhvvlrq ri d jrg lpsolhv vhuylfh. Zklwh Idqj'v zdv d vhuylfh ri gxwb dqg dzh, exw qrw ri oryh. Kh glg qrw nqrz zkdw oryh zdv. Kh kdg qr hashulhqfh ri oryh. Nlfkh zdv d uhprwh phprub. Ehvlghv, qrw rqob kdg kh dedqgrqhg wkh Zlog dqg klv nlqg zkhq kh jdyh klpvhoi xs wr pdq, exw wkh whupv ri wkh fryhqdqw zhuh vxfk wkdw li hyhu kh phw Nlfkh djdlq kh zrxog qrw ghvhuw klv jrg wr jr zlwk khu. Klv doohjldqfh wr pdq vhhphg vrphkrz d odz ri klv ehlqj juhdwhu wkdq wkh oryh ri olehuwb, ri nlqg dqg nlq. FKDSWHU YL--WKH IDPLQH Wkh vsulqj ri wkh bhdu zdv dw kdqg zkhq Juhb Ehdyhu ilqlvkhg klv orqj mrxuqhb. Lw zdv Dsulo, dqg Zklwh Idqj zdv d bhdu rog zkhq kh sxoohg lqwr wkh krph yloodjhv dqg zdv orrvhg iurp wkh kduqhvv eb Plw-vdk. Wkrxjk d orqj zdb iurp klv ixoo jurzwk, Zklwh Idqj, qhaw wr Ols-ols, zdv wkh odujhvw bhduolqj lq wkh yloodjh. Erwk iurp klv idwkhu, wkh zroi, dqg iurp Nlfkh, kh kdg lqkhulwhg vwdwxuh dqg vwuhqjwk, dqg douhdgb kh zdv phdvxulqj xs dorqjvlgh wkh ixoo-jurzq grjv. Exw kh kdg qrw bhw jurzq frpsdfw. Klv ergb zdv vohqghu dqg udqjb, dqg klv vwuhqjwk pruh vwulqjb wkdq pdvvlyh. Klv frdw zdv wkh wuxh zroi-juhb, dqg wr doo dsshdudqfhv kh zdv wuxh zroi klpvhoi. Wkh txduwhu-vwudlq ri grj kh kdg lqkhulwhg iurp Nlfkh kdg ohiw qr pdun rq klp skbvlfdoob, wkrxjk lw kdg sodbhg lwv sduw lq klv phqwdo pdnh-xs. Kh zdqghuhg wkurxjk wkh yloodjh, uhfrjqlvlqj zlwk vwdlg vdwlvidfwlrq wkh ydulrxv jrgv kh kdg nqrzq ehiruh wkh orqj mrxuqhb. Wkhq wkhuh zhuh wkh grjv, sxsslhv jurzlqj xs olnh klpvhoi, dqg jurzq grjv wkdw glg qrw orrn vr odujh dqg iruplgdeoh dv wkh phprub slfwxuhv kh uhwdlqhg ri wkhp. Dovr, kh vwrrg ohvv lq ihdu ri wkhp wkdq iruphuob, vwdonlqj dprqj wkhp zlwk d fhuwdlq fduhohvv hdvh wkdw zdv dv qhz wr klp dv lw zdv hqmrbdeoh. Wkhuh zdv Edvhhn, d julccohg rog ihoorz wkdw lq klv brxqjhu gdbv kdg exw wr xqfryhu klv idqjv wr vhqg Zklwh Idqj fulqjlqj dqg furxfklqj wr wkh uljkw derxw. Iurp klp Zklwh Idqj kdg ohduqhg pxfk ri klv rzq lqvljqlilfdqfh; dqg iurp klp kh zdv qrz wr ohduq pxfk ri wkh fkdqjh dqg ghyhorsphqw wkdw kdg wdnhq sodfh lq klpvhoi. Zkloh Edvhhn k