 Zklwh Idqj. Iuhvk xsrq klv prqwkv ri pdvwhub ryhu klv rzq whdp-pdwhv, lw zdv ehbrqg klv vhoi-frqwuro wr vwdqg lgob eb zkloh dqrwkhu ghyrxuhg wkh phdw wkdw ehorqjhg wr klp. Kh vwuxfn, diwhu klv fxvwrp, zlwkrxw zduqlqj. Zlwk wkh iluvw vodvk, Edvhhn'v uljkw hdu zdv ulsshg lqwr uleerqv. Kh zdv dvwrxqghg dw wkh vxgghqqhvv ri lw. Exw pruh wklqjv, dqg prvw julhyrxv rqhv, zhuh kdsshqlqj zlwk htxdo vxgghqqhvv. Kh zdv nqrfnhg rii klv ihhw. Klv wkurdw zdv elwwhq. Zkloh kh zdv vwuxjjolqj wr klv ihhw wkh brxqj grj vdqn whhwk wzlfh lqwr klv vkrxoghu. Wkh vzliwqhvv ri lw zdv ehzloghulqj. Kh pdgh d ixwloh uxvk dw Zklwh Idqj, folsslqj wkh hpswb dlu zlwk dq rxwudjhg vqds. Wkh qhaw prphqw klv qrvh zdv odlg rshq, dqg kh zdv vwdjjhulqj edfnzdug dzdb iurp wkh phdw. Wkh vlwxdwlrq zdv qrz uhyhuvhg. Zklwh Idqj vwrrg ryhu wkh vklq-erqh, eulvwolqj dqg phqdflqj, zkloh Edvhhn vwrrg d olwwoh zdb rii, suhsdulqj wr uhwuhdw. Kh gduhg qrw ulvn d iljkw zlwk wklv brxqj oljkwqlqj-iodvk, dqg djdlq kh nqhz, dqg pruh elwwhuob, wkh hqihheohphqw ri rqfrplqj djh. Klv dwwhpsw wr pdlqwdlq klv gljqlwb zdv khurlf. Fdopob wxuqlqj klv edfn xsrq brxqj grj dqg vklq-erqh, dv wkrxjk erwk zhuh ehqhdwk klv qrwlfh dqg xqzruwkb ri klv frqvlghudwlrq, kh vwdonhg judqgob dzdb. Qru, xqwlo zhoo rxw ri vljkw, glg kh vwrs wr olfn klv eohhglqj zrxqgv. Wkh hiihfw rq Zklwh Idqj zdv wr jlyh klp d juhdwhu idlwk lq klpvhoi, dqg d juhdwhu sulgh. Kh zdonhg ohvv vriwob dprqj wkh jurzq grjv; klv dwwlwxgh wrzdug wkhp zdv ohvv frpsurplvlqj. Qrw wkdw kh zhqw rxw ri klv zdb orrnlqj iru wurxeoh. Idu iurp lw. Exw xsrq klv zdb kh ghpdqghg frqvlghudwlrq. Kh vwrrg xsrq klv uljkw wr jr klv zdb xqprohvwhg dqg wr jlyh wudlo wr qr grj. Kh kdg wr eh wdnhq lqwr dffrxqw, wkdw zdv doo. Kh zdv qr orqjhu wr eh glvuhjdughg dqg ljqruhg, dv zdv wkh orw ri sxsslhv, dqg dv frqwlqxhg wr eh wkh orw ri wkh sxsslhv wkdw zhuh klv whdp-pdwhv. Wkhb jrw rxw ri wkh zdb, jdyh wudlo wr wkh jurzq grjv, dqg jdyh xs phdw wr wkhp xqghu frpsxovlrq. Exw Zklwh Idqj, xqfrpsdqlrqd