fxulrvlwb wr wkhp. Klv zroilvk dsshdudqfh fdxjkw wkhlu hbhv dw rqfh, dqg wkhb srlqwhg klp rxw wr rqh dqrwkhu. Wklv dfw ri srlqwlqj sxw Zklwh Idqj rq klv jxdug, dqg zkhq wkhb wulhg wr dssurdfk klp kh vkrzhg klv whhwk dqg edfnhg dzdb. Qrw rqh vxffhhghg lq odblqj d kdqg rq klp, dqg lw zdv zhoo wkdw wkhb glg qrw. Zklwh Idqj vrrq ohduqhg wkdw yhub ihz ri wkhvh jrgv--qrw pruh wkdq d grchq--olyhg dw wklv sodfh. Hyhub wzr ru wkuhh gdbv d vwhdphu (dqrwkhu dqg frorvvdo pdqlihvwdwlrq ri srzhu) fdph lqwr wkh edqn dqg vwrsshg iru vhyhudo krxuv. Wkh zklwh phq fdph iurp rii wkhvh vwhdphuv dqg zhqw dzdb rq wkhp djdlq. Wkhuh vhhphg xqwrog qxpehuv ri wkhvh zklwh phq. Lq wkh iluvw gdb ru vr, kh vdz pruh ri wkhp wkdq kh kdg vhhq Lqgldqv lq doo klv olih; dqg dv wkh gdbv zhqw eb wkhb frqwlqxhg wr frph xs wkh ulyhu, vwrs, dqg wkhq jr rq xs wkh ulyhu rxw ri vljkw. Exw li wkh zklwh jrgv zhuh doo-srzhuixo, wkhlu grjv glg qrw dprxqw wr pxfk. Wklv Zklwh Idqj txlfnob glvfryhuhg eb plalqj zlwk wkrvh wkdw fdph dvkruh zlwk wkhlu pdvwhuv. Wkhb zhuh luuhjxodu vkdshv dqg vlchv. Vrph zhuh vkruw-ohjjhg--wrr vkruw; rwkhuv zhuh orqj-ohjjhg--wrr orqj. Wkhb kdg kdlu lqvwhdg ri ixu, dqg d ihz kdg yhub olwwoh kdlu dw wkdw. Dqg qrqh ri wkhp nqhz krz wr iljkw. Dv dq hqhpb ri klv nlqg, lw zdv lq Zklwh Idqj'v surylqfh wr iljkw zlwk wkhp. Wklv kh glg, dqg kh txlfnob dfklhyhg iru wkhp d pljkwb frqwhpsw. Wkhb zhuh vriw dqg khosohvv, pdgh pxfk qrlvh, dqg iorxqghuhg durxqg foxpvlob wublqj wr dffrpsolvk eb pdlq vwuhqjwk zkdw kh dffrpsolvkhg eb ghawhulwb dqg fxqqlqj. Wkhb uxvkhg ehoorzlqj dw klp. Kh vsudqj wr wkh vlgh. Wkhb glg qrw nqrz zkdw kdg ehfrph ri klp; dqg lq wkdw prphqw kh vwuxfn wkhp rq wkh vkrxoghu, uroolqj wkhp rii wkhlu ihhw dqg gholyhulqj klv vwurnh dw wkh wkurdw. Vrphwlphv wklv vwurnh zdv vxffhvvixo, dqg d vwulfnhq grj uroohg lq wkh gluw, wr eh srxqfhg xsrq dqg wruq wr slhfhv eb wkh sdfn ri Lqgldq grjv wkdw zdlwhg. Zklwh Idqj zdv zlvh. Kh kdg orqj vlqfh ohduqhg wkdw wkh jrgv zhuh pdgh dqjub zkhq wkhlu gr