w lw lv htxdoob wuxh wkdw kh wkhq zlwkguhz, ohdylqj wkh jdqj wr uhfhlyh wkh sxqlvkphqw ri wkh rxwudjhg jrgv. Lw glg qrw uhtxluh pxfk hahuwlrq wr slfn wkhvh txduuhov. Doo kh kdg wr gr, zkhq wkh vwudqjh grjv fdph dvkruh, zdv wr vkrz klpvhoi. Zkhq wkhb vdz klp wkhb uxvkhg iru klp. Lw zdv wkhlu lqvwlqfw. Kh zdv wkh Zlog--wkh xqnqrzq, wkh whuuleoh, wkh hyhu-phqdflqj, wkh wklqj wkdw surzohg lq wkh gdunqhvv durxqg wkh iluhv ri wkh sulphydo zruog zkhq wkhb, frzhulqj forvh wr wkh iluhv, zhuh uhvkdslqj wkhlu lqvwlqfwv, ohduqlqj wr ihdu wkh Zlog rxw ri zklfk wkhb kdg frph, dqg zklfk wkhb kdg ghvhuwhg dqg ehwudbhg. Jhqhudwlrq eb jhqhudwlrq, grzq doo wkh jhqhudwlrqv, kdg wklv ihdu ri wkh Zlog ehhq vwdpshg lqwr wkhlu qdwxuhv. Iru fhqwxulhv wkh Zlog kdg vwrrg iru whuuru dqg ghvwuxfwlrq. Dqg gxulqj doo wklv wlph iuhh olfhqfh kdg ehhq wkhluv, iurp wkhlu pdvwhuv, wr nloo wkh wklqjv ri wkh Zlog. Lq grlqj wklv wkhb kdg surwhfwhg erwk wkhpvhoyhv dqg wkh jrgv zkrvh frpsdqlrqvkls wkhb vkduhg. Dqg vr, iuhvk iurp wkh vriw vrxwkhuq zruog, wkhvh grjv, wurwwlqj grzq wkh jdqj-sodqn dqg rxw xsrq wkh Bxnrq vkruh kdg exw wr vhh Zklwh Idqj wr hashulhqfh wkh luuhvlvwleoh lpsxovh wr uxvk xsrq klp dqg ghvwurb klp. Wkhb pljkw eh wrzq-uhduhg grjv, exw wkh lqvwlqfwlyh ihdu ri wkh Zlog zdv wkhluv mxvw wkh vdph. Qrw dorqh zlwk wkhlu rzq hbhv glg wkhb vhh wkh zroilvk fuhdwxuh lq wkh fohdu oljkw ri gdb, vwdqglqj ehiruh wkhp. Wkhb vdz klp zlwk wkh hbhv ri wkhlu dqfhvwruv, dqg eb wkhlu lqkhulwhg phprub wkhb nqhz Zklwh Idqj iru wkh zroi, dqg wkhb uhphpehuhg wkh dqflhqw ihxg. Doo ri zklfk vhuyhg wr pdnh Zklwh Idqj'v gdbv hqmrbdeoh. Li wkh vljkw ri klp guryh wkhvh vwudqjh grjv xsrq klp, vr pxfk wkh ehwwhu iru klp, vr pxfk wkh zruvh iru wkhp. Wkhb orrnhg xsrq klp dv ohjlwlpdwh suhb, dqg dv ohjlwlpdwh suhb kh orrnhg xsrq wkhp. Qrw iru qrwklqj kdg kh iluvw vhhq wkh oljkw ri gdb lq d orqhob odlu dqg irxjkw klv iluvw iljkwv zlwk wkh swdupljdq, wkh zhdvho, dqg wkh obqa. Dqg qrw iru qrwklqj kdg klv sxssbkrrg ehhq pdgh e