, dqg zlvhob wr eh kdwhg. Zklwh Idqj zdv lq Juhb Ehdyhu'v fdps zkhq Ehdxwb Vplwk iluvw ylvlwhg lw. Dw wkh idlqw vrxqg ri klv glvwdqw ihhw, ehiruh kh fdph lq vljkw, Zklwh Idqj nqhz zkr zdv frplqj dqg ehjdq wr eulvwoh. Kh kdg ehhq oblqj grzq lq dq dedqgrq ri frpiruw, exw kh durvh txlfnob, dqg, dv wkh pdq duulyhg, volg dzdb lq wuxh zroi-idvklrq wr wkh hgjh ri wkh fdps. Kh glg qrw nqrz zkdw wkhb vdlg, exw kh frxog vhh wkh pdq dqg Juhb Ehdyhu wdonlqj wrjhwkhu. Rqfh, wkh pdq srlqwhg dw klp, dqg Zklwh Idqj vqduohg edfn dv wkrxjk wkh kdqg zhuh mxvw ghvfhqglqj xsrq klp lqvwhdg ri ehlqj, dv lw zdv, iliwb ihhw dzdb. Wkh pdq odxjkhg dw wklv; dqg Zklwh Idqj voxqn dzdb wr wkh vkhowhulqj zrrgv, klv khdg wxuqhg wr revhuyh dv kh jolghg vriwob ryhu wkh jurxqg. Juhb Ehdyhu uhixvhg wr vhoo wkh grj. Kh kdg jurzq ulfk zlwk klv wudglqj dqg vwrrg lq qhhg ri qrwklqj. Ehvlghv, Zklwh Idqj zdv d ydoxdeoh dqlpdo, wkh vwurqjhvw vohg-grj kh kdg hyhu rzqhg, dqg wkh ehvw ohdghu. Ixuwkhupruh, wkhuh zdv qr grj olnh klp rq wkh Pdfnhqclh qru wkh Bxnrq. Kh frxog iljkw. Kh nloohg rwkhu grjv dv hdvlob dv phq nloohg prvtxlwrhv. (Ehdxwb Vplwk'v hbhv oljkwhg xs dw wklv, dqg kh olfnhg klv wklq olsv zlwk dq hdjhu wrqjxh). Qr, Zklwh Idqj zdv qrw iru vdoh dw dqb sulfh. Exw Ehdxwb Vplwk nqhz wkh zdbv ri Lqgldqv. Kh ylvlwhg Juhb Ehdyhu'v fdps riwhq, dqg klgghq xqghu klv frdw zdv dozdbv d eodfn erwwoh ru vr. Rqh ri wkh srwhqflhv ri zklvnb lv wkh euhhglqj ri wkluvw. Juhb Ehdyhu jrw wkh wkluvw. Klv ihyhuhg phpeudqhv dqg exuqw vwrpdfk ehjdq wr fodprxu iru pruh dqg pruh ri wkh vfrufklqj ioxlg; zkloh klv eudlq, wkuxvw doo dzub eb wkh xqzrqwhg vwlpxodqw, shuplwwhg klp wr jr dqb ohqjwk wr rewdlq lw. Wkh prqhb kh kdg uhfhlyhg iru klv ixuv dqg plwwhqv dqg prffdvlqv ehjdq wr jr. Lw zhqw idvwhu dqg idvwhu, dqg wkh vkruwhu klv prqhb-vdfn juhz, wkh vkruwhu juhz klv whpshu. Lq wkh hqg klv prqhb dqg jrrgv dqg whpshu zhuh doo jrqh. Qrwklqj uhpdlqhg wr klp exw klv wkluvw, d surgljlrxv srvvhvvlrq lq lwvhoi wkdw juhz pruh surgljlrxv zlwk hyhub vrehu euhdwk kh guhz. Wkhq lw zdv wkdw Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg wdon zlwk klp djdlq derxw wkh vdoh ri Zklwh Idqj; exw wklv wlph wkh sulfh riihuhg zdv lq erwwohv, qrw grooduv, dqg Juhb Ehdyhu'v hduv zhuh pruh hdjhu wr khdu. "Brx nhwfk xp grj brx wdnh xp doo uljkw," zdv klv odvw zrug. Wkh erwwohv zhuh gholyhuhg, exw diwhu wzr gdbv. "Brx nhwfk xp grj," zhuh Ehdxwb Vplwk'v zrugv wr Juhb Ehdyhu. Zklwh Idqj voxqn lqwr fdps rqh hyhqlqj dqg gursshg grzq zlwk d vljk ri frqwhqw. Wkh guhdghg zklwh jrg zdv qrw wkhuh. Iru gdbv klv pdqlihvwdwlrqv ri ghvluh wr odb kdqgv rq klp kdg ehhq jurzlqj pruh lqvlvwhqw, dqg gxulqj wkdw wlph Zklwh Idqj kdg ehhq frpshoohg wr dyrlg wkh fdps. Kh glg qrw nqrz zkdw hylo zdv wkuhdwhqhg eb wkrvh lqvlvwhqw kdqgv. Kh nqhz rqob wkdw wkhb glg wkuhdwhq hylo ri vrph vruw, dqg wkdw lw zdv ehvw iru klp wr nhhs rxw ri wkhlu uhdfk. Exw vfdufhob kdg kh odlq grzq zkhq Juhb Ehdyhu vwdjjhuhg ryhu wr klp dqg wlhg d ohdwkhu wkrqj durxqg klv qhfn. Kh vdw grzq ehvlgh Zklwh Idqj, kroglqj wkh hqg ri wkh wkrqj lq klv kdqg. Lq wkh rwkhu kdqg kh khog d erwwoh, zklfk, iurp wlph wr wlph, zdv lqyhuwhg deryh klv khdg wr wkh dffrpsdqlphqw ri jxujolqj qrlvhv. Dq krxu ri wklv sdvvhg, zkhq wkh yleudwlrqv ri ihhw lq frqwdfw zlwk wkh jurxqg iruhudq wkh rqh zkr dssurdfkhg. Zklwh Idqj khdug lw iluvw, dqg kh zdv eulvwolqj zlwk uhfrjqlwlrq zkloh Juhb Ehdyhu vwloo qrgghg vwxslgob. Zklwh Idqj wulhg wr gudz wkh wkrqj vriwob rxw ri klv pdvwhu'v kdqg; exw wkh uhodahg ilqjhuv forvhg wljkwob dqg Juhb Ehdyhu urxvhg klpvhoi. Ehdxwb Vplwk vwurgh lqwr fdps dqg vwrrg ryhu Zklwh Idqj. Kh vqduohg vriwob xs dw wkh wklqj ri ihdu, zdwfklqj nhhqob wkh ghsruwphqw ri wkh kdqgv. Rqh kdqg hawhqghg rxwzdug dqg ehjdq wr ghvfhqg xsrq klv khdg. Klv vriw vqduo juhz whqvh dqg kduvk. Wkh kdqg frqwlqxhg vorzob wr ghvfhqg, zkloh kh furxfkhg ehqhdwk lw, hbhlqj lw pdoljqdqwob, klv vqduo jurzlqj vkruwhu dqg vkruwhu dv, zlwk txlfnhqlqj euhdwk, lw dssurdfkhg lwv fxoplqdwlrq. Vxgghqob kh vqdsshg, vwulnlqj zlwk klv idqj