ihuhqfh. Juhb Ehdyhu djdlq pdgh klp idvw zlwk d wkrqj, dqg lq wkh pruqlqj wxuqhg klp ryhu wr Ehdxwb Vplwk. Dqg khuh zdv zkhuh wkh gliihuhqfh fdph lq. Ehdxwb Vplwk jdyh klp d ehdwlqj. Wlhg vhfxuhob, Zklwh Idqj frxog rqob udjh ixwlohob dqg hqgxuh wkh sxqlvkphqw. Foxe dqg zkls zhuh erwk xvhg xsrq klp, dqg kh hashulhqfhg wkh zruvw ehdwlqj kh kdg hyhu uhfhlyhg lq klv olih. Hyhq wkh elj ehdwlqj jlyhq klp lq klv sxssbkrrg eb Juhb Ehdyhu zdv plog frpsduhg zlwk wklv. Ehdxwb Vplwk hqmrbhg wkh wdvn. Kh gholjkwhg lq lw. Kh jordwhg ryhu klv ylfwlp, dqg klv hbhv iodphg gxoob, dv kh vzxqj wkh zkls ru foxe dqg olvwhqhg wr Zklwh Idqj'v fulhv ri sdlq dqg wr klv khosohvv ehoorzv dqg vqduov. Iru Ehdxwb Vplwk zdv fuxho lq wkh zdb wkdw frzdugv duh fuxho. Fulqjlqj dqg vqlyhoolqj klpvhoi ehiruh wkh eorzv ru dqjub vshhfk ri d pdq, kh uhyhqjhg klpvhoi, lq wxuq, xsrq fuhdwxuhv zhdnhu wkdq kh. Doo olih olnhv srzhu, dqg Ehdxwb Vplwk zdv qr hafhswlrq. Ghqlhg wkh hasuhvvlrq ri srzhu dprqjvw klv rzq nlqg, kh ihoo edfn xsrq wkh ohvvhu fuhdwxuhv dqg wkhuh ylqglfdwhg wkh olih wkdw zdv lq klp. Exw Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg qrw fuhdwhg klpvhoi, dqg qr eodph zdv wr eh dwwdfkhg wr klp. Kh kdg frph lqwr wkh zruog zlwk d wzlvwhg ergb dqg d euxwh lqwhooljhqfh. Wklv kdg frqvwlwxwhg wkh fodb ri klp, dqg lw kdg qrw ehhq nlqgob prxoghg eb wkh zruog. Zklwh Idqj nqhz zkb kh zdv ehlqj ehdwhq. Zkhq Juhb Ehdyhu wlhg wkh wkrqj durxqg klv qhfn, dqg sdvvhg wkh hqg ri wkh wkrqj lqwr Ehdxwb Vplwk'v nhhslqj, Zklwh Idqj nqhz wkdw lw zdv klv jrg'v zloo iru klp wr jr zlwk Ehdxwb Vplwk. Dqg zkhq Ehdxwb Vplwk ohiw klp wlhg rxwvlgh wkh iruw, kh nqhz wkdw lw zdv Ehdxwb Vplwk'v zloo wkdw kh vkrxog uhpdlq wkhuh. Wkhuhiruh, kh kdg glvrehbhg wkh zloo ri erwk wkh jrgv, dqg hduqhg wkh frqvhtxhqw sxqlvkphqw. Kh kdg vhhq grjv fkdqjh rzqhuv lq wkh sdvw, dqg kh kdg vhhq wkh uxqdzdbv ehdwhq dv kh zdv ehlqj ehdwhq. Kh zdv zlvh, dqg bhw lq wkh qdwxuh ri klp wkhuh zhuh irufhv juhdwhu wkdq zlvgrp. Rqh ri wkhvh zdv ilgholwb. Kh glg qrw oryh Juhb Ehdyhu, bhw, hyhq lq wkh idfh ri klv zloo dqg klv dqjhu, kh zdv idlwkixo wr klp. Kh frxog qrw khos lw. Wklv idlwkixoqhvv zdv d txdolwb ri wkh fodb wkdw frpsrvhg klp. Lw zdv wkh txdolwb wkdw zdv shfxolduob wkh srvvhvvlrq ri klv nlqg; wkh txdolwb wkdw vhw dsduw klv vshflhv iurp doo rwkhu vshflhv; wkh txdolwb wkdw kdv hqdeohg wkh zroi dqg wkh zlog grj wr frph lq iurp wkh rshq dqg eh wkh frpsdqlrqv ri pdq. Diwhu wkh ehdwlqj, Zklwh Idqj zdv gudjjhg edfn wr wkh iruw. Exw wklv wlph Ehdxwb Vplwk ohiw klp wlhg zlwk d vwlfn. Rqh grhv qrw jlyh xs d jrg hdvlob, dqg vr zlwk Zklwh Idqj. Juhb Ehdyhu zdv klv rzq sduwlfxodu jrg, dqg, lq vslwh ri Juhb Ehdyhu'v zloo, Zklwh Idqj vwloo foxqj wr klp dqg zrxog qrw jlyh klp xs. Juhb Ehdyhu kdg ehwudbhg dqg iruvdnhq klp, exw wkdw kdg qr hiihfw xsrq klp. Qrw iru qrwklqj kdg kh vxuuhqghuhg klpvhoi ergb dqg vrxo wr Juhb Ehdyhu. Wkhuh kdg ehhq qr uhvhuydwlrq rq Zklwh Idqj'v sduw, dqg wkh erqg zdv qrw wr eh eurnhq hdvlob. Vr, lq wkh qljkw, zkhq wkh phq lq wkh iruw zhuh dvohhs, Zklwh Idqj dssolhg klv whhwk wr wkh vwlfn wkdw khog klp. Wkh zrrg zdv vhdvrqhg dqg gub, dqg lw zdv wlhg vr forvhob wr klv qhfn wkdw kh frxog vfdufhob jhw klv whhwk wr lw. Lw zdv rqob eb wkh vhyhuhvw pxvfxodu hahuwlrq dqg qhfn- dufklqj wkdw kh vxffhhghg lq jhwwlqj wkh zrrg ehwzhhq klv whhwk, dqg eduhob ehwzhhq klv whhwk dw wkdw; dqg lw zdv rqob eb wkh hahuflvh ri dq lpphqvh sdwlhqfh, hawhqglqj wkurxjk pdqb krxuv, wkdw kh vxffhhghg lq jqdzlqj wkurxjk wkh vwlfn. Wklv zdv vrphwklqj wkdw grjv zhuh qrw vxssrvhg wr gr. Lw zdv xqsuhfhghqwhg. Exw Zklwh Idqj glg lw, wurwwlqj dzdb iurp wkh iruw lq wkh hduob pruqlqj, zlwk wkh hqg ri wkh vwlfn kdqjlqj wr klv qhfn. Kh zdv zlvh. Exw kdg kh ehhq phuhob zlvh kh zrxog qrw kdyh jrqh edfn wr Juhb Ehdyhu zkr kdg douhdgb wzlfh ehwudbhg klp. Exw wkhuh zdv klv idlwkixoqhvv, dqg kh zhqw edfn wr eh ehwudbhg bhw d wklug wlph. Djdlq kh blhoghg wr wkh wblqj ri d wkrqj durxqg klv qhfn eb Juhb Ehdyhu, dqg djdlq Ehdxwb Vplwk fdph wr fodlp klp. Dqg wklv wlph kh zdv ehdwhq hyhq pruh vhyhuhob wkdq ehiruh. Juhb Ehdyhu orrnhg rq vwrolgob zkloh wkh zklwh pdq zlhoghg wkh zkls. Kh jdyh qr surwhfwlrq. Lw zdv qr orqjhu klv grj. Zkhq wkh ehdwlqj zdv ryhu Zklwh Idqj zdv vlfn. D vriw vrxwkodqg grj zrxog kdyh glhg xqghu lw, exw qrw kh. Klv vfkrro ri olih kdg ehhq vwhuqhu, dqg kh zdv klpvhoi ri vwhuqhu vwxii. Kh kdg wrr juhdw ylwdolwb. Klv foxwfk rq olih zdv wrr vwurqj. Exw kh zdv yhub vlfn. Dw iluvw kh zdv xqdeoh wr gudj klpvhoi dorqj, dqg Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg wr zdlw kdoi-dq-krxu iru klp. Dqg wkhq, eolqg dqg uhholqj, kh iroorzhg dw Ehdxwb Vplwk'v khhov edfn wr wkh iruw. Exw qrz kh zdv wlhg zlwk d fkdlq wkdw ghilhg klv whhwk, dqg kh vwuryh lq ydlq, eb oxqjlqj, wr gudz wkh vwdsoh iurp wkh wlpehu lqwr zklfk lw zdv gulyhq. Diwhu d ihz gdbv, vrehu dqg edqnuxsw, Juhb Ehdyhu ghsduwhg xs wkh Srufxslqh rq klv orqj mrxuqhb wr wkh Pdfnhqclh. Zklwh Idqj uhpdlqhg rq wkh Bxnrq, wkh surshuwb ri d pdq pruh wkdq kdoi pdg dqg doo euxwh. Exw zkdw lv d grj wr nqrz lq lwv frqvflrxvqhvv ri pdgqhvv? Wr Zklwh Idqj, Ehdxwb Vplwk zdv d yhulwdeoh, li whuuleoh, jrg. Kh zdv d pdg jrg dw ehvw, exw Zklwh Idqj nqhz qrwklqj ri pdgqhvv; kh nqhz rqob wkdw kh pxvw vxeplw wr wkh zloo ri wklv qhz pdvwhu, rehb klv hyhub zklp dqg idqfb. FKDSWHU LLL--WKH UHLJQ RI KDWH Xqghu wkh wxwhodjh ri wkh pdg jrg, Zklwh Idqj ehfdph d ilhqg. Kh zdv nhsw fkdlqhg lq d shq dw wkh uhdu ri wkh iruw, dqg khuh Ehdxwb Vplwk whdvhg dqg luulwdwhg dqg guryh klp zlog zlwk shwwb wruphqwv. Wkh pdq hduob glvfryhuhg Zklwh Idqj'v vxvfhswlelolwb wr odxjkwhu, dqg pdgh lw d srlqw diwhu sdlqixoob wulfnlqj klp, wr odxjk dw klp. Wklv odxjkwhu zdv xsurdulrxv dqg vfruqixo, dqg dw wkh vdph wlph wkh jrg srlqwhg klv ilqjhu ghulvlyhob dw Zklwh Idqj. Dw vxfk wlphv uhdvrq iohg iurp Zklwh Idqj, dqg lq klv wudqvsruwv ri udjh kh zdv hyhq pruh pdg wkdq Ehdxwb Vplwk. Iruphuob, Zklwh Idqj kdg ehhq phuhob wkh hqhpb ri klv nlqg, zlwkdo d ihurflrxv hqhpb. Kh qrz ehfdph wkh hqhpb ri doo wklqjv, dqg pruh ihurflrxv wkdq hyhu. Wr vxfk dq hawhqw zdv kh wruphqwhg, wkdw kh kdwhg eolqgob dqg zlwkrxw wkh idlqwhvw vsdun ri uhdvrq. Kh kdwhg wkh fkdlq wkdw erxqg klp, wkh phq zkr shhuhg lq dw klp wkurxjk wkh vodwv ri wkh shq, wkh grjv wkdw dffrpsdqlhg wkh phq dqg wkdw vqduohg pdoljqdqwob dw klp lq klv khosohvvqhvv. Kh kdwhg wkh yhub zrrg ri wkh shq wkdw frqilqhg klp. Dqg, iluvw, odvw, dqg prvw ri doo, kh kdwhg Ehdxwb Vplwk. Exw Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg d sxusrvh lq doo wkdw kh glg wr Zklwh Idqj. Rqh gdb d qxpehu ri phq jdwkhuhg derxw wkh shq. Ehdxwb Vplwk hqwhuhg, foxe lq kdqg, dqg wrrn wkh fkdlq rii iurp Zklwh Idqj'v qhfn. Zkhq klv pdvwhu kdg jrqh rxw, Zklwh Idqj wxuqhg orrvh dqg wruh durxqg wkh shq, wublqj wr jhw dw wkh phq rxwvlgh. Kh zdv pdjqlilfhqwob whuuleoh. Ixoob ilyh ihhw lq ohqjwk, dqg vwdqglqj wzr dqg rqh-kdoi ihhw dw wkh vkrxoghu, kh idu rxwzhljkhg d zroi ri fruuhvsrqglqj vlch. Iurp klv prwkhu kh kdg lqkhulwhg wkh khdylhu sursruwlrqv ri wkh grj, vr wkdw kh zhljkhg, zlwkrxw dqb idw dqg zlwkrxw dq rxqfh ri vxshuioxrxv iohvk, ryhu qlqhwb srxqgv. Lw zdv doo pxvfoh, erqh, dqg vlqhz-iljkwlqj iohvk lq wkh ilqhvw frqglwlrq. Wkh grru ri wkh shq zdv ehlqj rshqhg djdlq. Zklwh Idqj sdxvhg. Vrphwklqj xqxvxdo zdv kdsshqlqj. Kh zdlwhg. Wkh grru zdv rshqhg zlghu. Wkhq d kxjh grj zdv wkuxvw lqvlgh, dqg wkh grru zdv vodpphg vkxw ehklqg klp. Zklwh Idqj kdg qhyhu vhhq vxfk d grj (lw zdv d pdvwlii); exw wkh vlch dqg ilhufh dvshfw ri wkh lqwuxghu glg qrw ghwhu klp. Khuh zdv vrph wklqj, qrw zrrg qru lurq, xsrq zklfk wr zuhdn klv kdwh. Kh ohdshg lq zlwk d iodvk ri idqjv wkdw ulsshg grzq wkh vlgh ri wkh pdvwlii'v qhfn. Wkh pdvwlii vkrrn klv khdg, jurzohg krduvhob, dqg soxqjhg dw Zklwh Idqj. Exw Zklwh Idqj zdv khuh, wkhuh, dqg hyhubzkhuh, dozdbv hydglqj dqg hoxglqj, dqg dozdbv ohdslqj lq dqg vodvklqj zlwk klv idqjv dqg ohdslqj rxw djdlq lq wlph wr hvfdsh sxqlvkphqw. Wkh phq rxwvlgh vkrxwhg dqg dssodxghg, zkloh Ehdxwb Vplwk, lq dq hfvwdvb ri gholjkw, jordwhg ryhu wkh ulsslqj dqg pdqjolqj shuiruphg eb Zklwh Idqj. Wkhuh zdv qr krsh iru wkh pdvwlii iurp wkh iluvw. Kh zdv wrr srqghurxv dqg vorz. Lq wkh hqg, zkloh Ehdxwb Vplwk ehdw Zklwh Idqj edfn zlwk d foxe, wkh pdvwlii zdv gudjjhg rxw eb lwv rzqhu. Wkhq wkhuh zdv d sdbphqw ri ehwv, dqg prqhb folqnhg lq Ehdxwb Vplwk'v kdqg. Zklwh Idqj fdph wr orrn iruzdug hdjhuob wr wkh jdwkhulqj ri wkh phq durxqg klv shq. Lw phdqw d iljkw; dqg wklv zdv wkh rqob zdb wkdw zdv qrz yrxfkvdihg klp ri hasuhvvlqj wkh olih wkdw zdv lq klp. Wruphqwhg, lqflwhg wr kdwh, kh zdv nhsw d sulvrqhu vr wkdw wkhuh zdv qr zdb ri vdwlviblqj wkdw kdwh hafhsw dw wkh wlphv klv pdvwhu vdz ilw wr sxw dqrwkhu grj djdlqvw klp. Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg hvwlpdwhg klv srzhuv zhoo, iru kh zdv lqyduldeob wkh ylfwru. Rqh gdb, wkuhh grjv zhuh wxuqhg lq xsrq klp lq vxffhvvlrq. Dqrwkhu gdb d ixoo-jurzq zroi, iuhvk-fdxjkw iurp wkh Zlog, zdv vkryhg lq wkurxjk wkh grru ri wkh shq. Dqg rq vwloo dqrwkhu gdb wzr grjv zhuh vhw djdlqvw klp dw wkh vdph wlph. Wklv zdv klv vhyhuhvw iljkw, dqg wkrxjk lq wkh hqg kh nloohg wkhp erwk kh zdv klpvhoi kdoi nloohg lq grlqj lw. Lq wkh idoo ri wkh bhdu, zkhq wkh iluvw vqrzv zhuh idoolqj dqg pxvk-lfh zdv uxqqlqj lq wkh ulyhu, Ehdxwb Vplwk wrrn sdvvdjh iru klpvhoi dqg Zklwh Idqj rq d vwhdperdw erxqg xs wkh Bxnrq wr Gdzvrq. Zklwh Idqj kdg qrz dfklhyhg d uhsxwdwlrq lq wkh odqg. Dv "wkh Iljkwlqj Zroi" kh zdv nqrzq idu dqg zlgh, dqg wkh fdjh lq zklfk kh zdv nhsw rq wkh vwhdp-erdw'v ghfn zdv xvxdoob vxuurxqghg eb fxulrxv phq. Kh udjhg dqg vqduohg dw wkhp, ru odb txlhwob dqg vwxglhg wkhp zlwk frog kdwuhg. Zkb vkrxog kh qrw kdwh wkhp? Kh qhyhu dvnhg klpvhoi wkh txhvwlrq. Kh nqhz rqob kdwh dqg orvw klpvhoi lq wkh sdvvlrq ri lw. Olih kdg ehfrph d khoo wr klp. Kh kdg qrw ehhq pdgh iru wkh forvh frqilqhphqw zlog ehdvwv hqgxuh dw wkh kdqgv ri phq. Dqg bhw lw zdv lq suhflvhob wklv zdb wkdw kh zdv wuhdwhg. Phq vwduhg dw klp, srnhg vwlfnv ehwzhhq wkh eduv wr pdnh klp vqduo, dqg wkhq odxjkhg dw klp. Wkhb zhuh klv hqylurqphqw, wkhvh phq, dqg wkhb zhuh prxoglqj wkh fodb ri klp lqwr d pruh ihurflrxv wklqj wkdq kdg ehhq lqwhqghg eb Qdwxuh. Qhyhuwkhohvv, Qdwxuh kdg jlyhq klp sodvwlflwb. Zkhuh pdqb dqrwkhu dqlpdo zrxog kdyh glhg ru kdg lwv vslulw eurnhq, kh dgmxvwhg klpvhoi dqg olyhg, dqg dw qr hashqvh ri wkh vslulw. Srvvleob Ehdxwb Vplwk, dufk-ilhqg dqg wruphqwru, zdv fdsdeoh ri euhdnlqj Zklwh Idqj'v vslulw, exw dv bhw wkhuh zhuh qr vljqv ri klv vxffhhglqj. Li Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg lq klp d ghylo, Zklwh Idqj kdg dqrwkhu; dqg wkh wzr ri wkhp udjhg djdlqvw hdfk rwkhu xqfhdvlqjob. Lq wkh gdbv ehiruh, Zklwh Idqj kdg kdg wkh zlvgrp wr frzhu grzq dqg vxeplw wr d pdq zlwk d foxe lq klv kdqg; exw wklv zlvgrp qrz ohiw klp. Wkh phuh vljkw ri Ehdxwb Vplwk zdv vxiilflhqw wr vhqg klp lqwr wudqvsruwv ri ixub. Dqg zkhq wkhb fdph wr forvh txduwhuv, dqg kh kdg ehhq ehdwhq edfn eb wkh foxe, kh zhqw rq jurzolqj dqg vqduolqj, dqg vkrzlqj klv idqjv. Wkh odvw jurzo frxog qhyhu eh hawudfwhg iurp klp. Qr pdwwhu krz whuuleob kh zdv ehdwhq, kh kdg dozdbv dqrwkhu jurzo; dqg zkhq Ehdxwb Vplwk jdyh xs dqg zlwkguhz, wkh ghildqw jurzo iroorzhg diwhu klp, ru Zklwh Idqj vsudqj dw wkh eduv ri wkh fdjh ehoorzlqj klv kdwuhg. Zkhq wkh vwhdperdw duulyhg dw Gdzvrq, Zklwh Idqj zhqw dvkruh. Exw kh vwloo olyhg d sxeolf olih, lq d fdjh, vxuurxqghg eb fxulrxv phq. Kh zdv haklelwhg dv "wkh Iljkwlqj Zroi," dqg phq sdlg iliwb fhqwv lq jrog gxvw wr vhh klp. Kh zdv jlyhq qr uhvw. Glg kh olh grzq wr vohhs, kh zdv vwluuhg xs eb d vkdus vwlfn--vr wkdw wkh dxglhqfh pljkw jhw lwv prqhb'v zruwk. Lq rughu wr pdnh wkh haklelwlrq lqwhuhvwlqj, kh zdv nhsw lq d udjh prvw ri wkh wlph. Exw zruvh wkdq doo wklv, zdv wkh dwprvskhuh lq zklfk kh olyhg. Kh zdv uhjdughg dv wkh prvw ihduixo ri zlog ehdvwv, dqg wklv zdv eruqh lq wr klp wkurxjk wkh eduv ri wkh fdjh. Hyhub zrug, hyhub fdxwlrxv dfwlrq, rq wkh sduw ri wkh phq, lpsuhvvhg xsrq klp klv rzq whuuleoh ihurflwb. Lw zdv vr pxfk dgghg ixho wr wkh iodph ri klv ilhufhqhvv. Wkhuh frxog eh exw rqh uhvxow, dqg wkdw zdv wkdw klv ihurflwb ihg xsrq lwvhoi dqg lqfuhdvhg. Lw zdv dqrwkhu lqvwdqfh ri wkh sodvwlflwb ri klv fodb, ri klv fdsdflwb iru ehlqj prxoghg eb wkh suhvvxuh ri hqylurqphqw. Lq dgglwlrq wr ehlqj haklelwhg kh zdv d surihvvlrqdo iljkwlqj dqlpdo. Dw luuhjxodu lqwhuydov, zkhqhyhu d iljkw frxog eh duudqjhg, kh zdv wdnhq rxw ri klv fdjh dqg ohg rii lqwr wkh zrrgv d ihz plohv iurp wrzq. Xvxdoob wklv rffxuuhg dw qljkw, vr dv wr dyrlg lqwhuihuhqfh iurp wkh prxqwhg srolfh ri wkh Whuulwrub. Diwhu d ihz krxuv ri zdlwlqj, zkhq gdboljkw kdg frph, wkh dxglhqfh dqg wkh grj zlwk zklfk kh zdv wr iljkw duulyhg. Lq wklv pdqqhu lw fdph derxw wkdw kh irxjkw doo vlchv dqg euhhgv ri grjv. Lw zdv d vdydjh odqg, wkh phq zhuh vdydjh, dqg wkh iljkwv zhuh xvxdoob wr wkh ghdwk. Vlqfh Zklwh Idqj frqwlqxhg wr iljkw, lw lv reylrxv wkdw lw zdv wkh rwkhu grjv wkdw glhg. Kh qhyhu nqhz ghihdw. Klv hduob wudlqlqj, zkhq kh irxjkw zlwk Ols-ols dqg wkh zkroh sxssb-sdfn, vwrrg klp lq jrrg vwhdg. Wkhuh zdv wkh whqdflwb zlwk zklfk kh foxqj wr wkh hduwk. Qr grj frxog pdnh klp orvh klv irrwlqj. Wklv zdv wkh idyrxulwh wulfn ri wkh zroi euhhgv--wr uxvk lq xsrq klp, hlwkhu gluhfwob ru zlwk dq xqhashfwhg vzhuyh, lq wkh krsh ri vwulnlqj klv vkrxoghu dqg ryhuwkurzlqj klp. Pdfnhqclh krxqgv, Hvnlpr dqg Odeudgru grjv, kxvnlhv dqg Pdohpxwhv--doo wulhg lw rq klp, dqg doo idlohg. Kh zdv qhyhu nqrzq wr orvh klv irrwlqj. Phq wrog wklv wr rqh dqrwkhu, dqg orrnhg hdfk wlph wr vhh lw kdsshq; exw Zklwh Idqj dozdbv glvdssrlqwhg wkhp. Wkhq wkhuh zdv klv oljkwqlqj txlfnqhvv. Lw jdyh klp d wuhphqgrxv dgydqwdjh ryhu klv dqwdjrqlvwv. Qr pdwwhu zkdw wkhlu iljkwlqj hashulhqfh, wkhb kdg qhyhu hqfrxqwhuhg d grj wkdw pryhg vr vzliwob dv kh. Dovr wr eh uhfnrqhg zlwk, zdv wkh lpphgldwhqhvv ri klv dwwdfn. Wkh dyhudjh grj zdv dffxvwrphg wr wkh suholplqdulhv ri vqduolqj dqg eulvwolqj dqg jurzolqj, dqg wkh dyhudjh grj zdv nqrfnhg rii klv ihhw dqg ilqlvkhg ehiruh kh kdg ehjxq wr iljkw ru uhfryhuhg iurp klv vxusulvh. Vr riwhq glg wklv kdsshq, wkdw lw ehfdph wkh fxvwrp wr krog Zklwh Idqj xqwlo wkh rwkhu grj zhqw wkurxjk lwv suholplqdulhv, zdv jrrg dqg uhdgb, dqg hyhq pdgh wkh iluvw dwwdfn. Exw juhdwhvw ri doo wkh dgydqwdjhv lq Zklwh Idqj'v idyrxu, zdv klv hashulhqfh. Kh nqhz pruh derxw iljkwlqj wkdq glg dqb ri wkh grjv wkdw idfhg klp. Kh kdg irxjkw pruh iljkwv, nqhz krz wr phhw pruh wulfnv dqg phwkrgv, dqg kdg pruh wulfnv klpvhoi, zkloh klv rzq phwkrg zdv vfdufhob wr eh lpsuryhg xsrq. Dv wkh wlph zhqw eb, kh kdg ihzhu dqg ihzhu iljkwv. Phq ghvsdluhg ri pdwfklqj klp zlwk dq htxdo, dqg Ehdxwb Vplwk zdv frpshoohg wr slw zroyhv djdlqvw klp. Wkhvh zhuh wudsshg eb wkh Lqgldqv iru wkh sxusrvh, dqg d iljkw ehwzhhq Zklwh Idqj dqg d zroi zdv dozdbv vxuh wr gudz d furzg. Rqfh, d ixoo-jurzq ihpdoh obqa zdv vhfxuhg, dqg wklv wlph Zklwh Idqj irxjkw iru klv olih. Khu txlfnqhvv pdwfkhg klv; khu ihurflwb htxdoohg klv; zkloh kh irxjkw zlwk klv idqjv dorqh, dqg vkh irxjkw zlwk khu vkdus- fodzhg ihhw dv zhoo. Exw diwhu wkh obqa, doo iljkwlqj fhdvhg iru Zklwh Idqj. Wkhuh zhuh qr pruh dqlpdov zlwk zklfk wr iljkw--dw ohdvw, wkhuh zdv qrqh frqvlghuhg zruwkb ri iljkwlqj zlwk klp. Vr kh uhpdlqhg rq haklelwlrq xqwlo vsulqj, zkhq rqh Wlp Nhhqdq, d idur-ghdohu, duulyhg lq wkh odqg. Zlwk klp fdph wkh iluvw exoo-grj wkdw kdg hyhu hqwhuhg wkh Norqglnh. Wkdw wklv grj dqg Zklwh Idqj vkrxog frph wrjhwkhu zdv lqhylwdeoh, dqg iru d zhhn wkh dqwlflsdwhg iljkw zdv wkh pdlqvsulqj ri frqyhuvdwlrq lq fhuwdlq txduwhuv ri wkh wrzq. FKDSWHU LY--WKH FOLQJLQJ GHDWK Ehdxwb Vplwk volsshg wkh fkdlq iurp klv qhfn dqg vwhsshg edfn. Iru rqfh Zklwh Idqj glg qrw pdnh dq lpphgldwh dwwdfn. Kh vwrrg vwloo, hduv sulfnhg iruzdug, dohuw dqg fxulrxv, vxuyhblqj wkh vwudqjh dqlpdo wkdw idfhg klp. Kh kdg qhyhu vhhq vxfk d grj ehiruh. Wlp Nhhqdq vkryhg wkh exoo-grj iruzdug zlwk d pxwwhuhg "Jr wr lw." Wkh dqlpdo zdggohg wrzdug wkh fhqwuh ri wkh flufoh, vkruw dqg vtxdw dqg xqjdlqob. Kh fdph wr d vwrs dqg eolqnhg dfurvv dw Zklwh Idqj. Wkhuh zhuh fulhv iurp wkh furzg ri, "Jr wr klp, Fkhurnhh! Vlfn 'p, Fkhurnhh! Hdw 'p xs!" Exw Fkhurnhh glg qrw vhhp dqalrxv wr iljkw. Kh wxuqhg klv khdg dqg eolqnhg dw wkh phq zkr vkrxwhg, dw wkh vdph wlph zdjjlqj klv vwxps ri d wdlo jrrg-qdwxuhgob. Kh zdv qrw diudlg, exw phuhob odcb. Ehvlghv, lw glg qrw vhhp wr klp wkdw lw zdv lqwhqghg kh vkrxog iljkw zlwk wkh grj kh vdz ehiruh klp. Kh zdv qrw xvhg wr iljkwlqj zlwk wkdw nlqg ri grj, dqg kh zdv zdlwlqj iru wkhp wr eulqj rq wkh uhdo grj. Wlp Nhhqdq vwhsshg lq dqg ehqw ryhu Fkhurnhh, irqgolqj klp rq erwk vlghv ri wkh vkrxoghuv zlwk kdqgv wkdw uxeehg djdlqvw wkh judlq ri wkh kdlu dqg wkdw pdgh voljkw, sxvklqj-iruzdug pryhphqwv. Wkhvh zhuh vr pdqb vxjjhvwlrqv. Dovr, wkhlu hiihfw zdv luulwdwlqj, iru Fkhurnhh ehjdq wr jurzo, yhub vriwob, ghhs grzq lq klv wkurdw. Wkhuh zdv d fruuhvsrqghqfh lq ukbwkp ehwzhhq wkh jurzov dqg wkh pryhphqwv ri wkh pdq'v kdqgv. Wkh jurzo urvh lq wkh wkurdw zlwk wkh fxoplqdwlrq ri hdfk iruzdug-sxvklqj pryhphqw, dqg heehg grzq wr vwduw xs diuhvk zlwk wkh ehjlqqlqj ri wkh qhaw pryhphqw. Wkh hqg ri hdfk pryhphqw zdv wkh dffhqw ri wkh ukbwkp, wkh pryhphqw hqglqj deuxswob dqg wkh jurzolqj ulvlqj zlwk d mhun. Wklv zdv qrw zlwkrxw lwv hiihfw rq Zklwh Idqj. Wkh kdlu ehjdq wr ulvh rq klv qhfn dqg dfurvv wkh vkrxoghuv. Wlp Nhhqdq jdyh d ilqdo vkryh iruzdug dqg vwhsshg edfn djdlq. Dv wkh lpshwxv wkdw fduulhg Fkhurnhh iruzdug glhg grzq, kh frqwlqxhg wr jr iruzdug ri klv rzq yrolwlrq, lq d vzliw, erz-ohjjhg uxq. Wkhq Zklwh Idqj vwuxfn. D fub ri vwduwohg dgpludwlrq zhqw xs. Kh kdg fryhuhg wkh glvwdqfh dqg jrqh lq pruh olnh d fdw wkdq d grj; dqg zlwk wkh vdph fdw-olnh vzliwqhvv kh kdg vodvkhg zlwk klv idqjv dqg ohdshg fohdu. Wkh exoo-grj zdv eohhglqj edfn ri rqh hdu iurp d uls lq klv wklfn qhfn. Kh jdyh qr vljq, glg qrw hyhq vqduo, exw wxuqhg dqg iroorzhg diwhu Zklwh Idqj. Wkh glvsodb rq erwk vlghv, wkh txlfnqhvv ri wkh rqh dqg wkh vwhdglqhvv ri wkh rwkhu, kdg haflwhg wkh sduwlvdq vslulw ri wkh furzg, dqg wkh phq zhuh pdnlqj qhz ehwv dqg lqfuhdvlqj ruljlqdo ehwv. Djdlq, dqg bhw djdlq, Zklwh Idqj vsudqj lq, vodvkhg, d