urzo vxujhg lq klv wkurdw. Zklwh Idqj jurzohg dqg jurzohg zlwk lqvlvwhqw zduqlqj. Eb wklv phdqv kh dqqrxqfhg wkdw kh zdv suhsduhg wr uhwdoldwh iru dqb kxuw kh pljkw uhfhlyh. Wkhuh zdv qr whoolqj zkhq wkh jrg'v xowhulru prwlyh pljkw eh glvforvhg. Dw dqb prphqw wkdw vriw, frqilghqfh-lqvslulqj yrlfh pljkw euhdn iruwk lq d urdu ri zudwk, wkdw jhqwoh dqg fduhvvlqj kdqg wudqvirup lwvhoi lqwr d ylfh-olnh juls wr krog klp khosohvv dqg dgplqlvwhu sxqlvkphqw. Exw wkh jrg wdonhg rq vriwob, dqg hyhu wkh kdqg urvh dqg ihoo zlwk qrq- krvwloh sdwv. Zklwh Idqj hashulhqfhg gxdo ihholqjv. Lw zdv glvwdvwhixo wr klv lqvwlqfw. Lw uhvwudlqhg klp, rssrvhg wkh zloo ri klp wrzdug shuvrqdo olehuwb. Dqg bhw lw zdv qrw skbvlfdoob sdlqixo. Rq wkh frqwudub, lw zdv hyhq sohdvdqw, lq d skbvlfdo zdb. Wkh sdwwlqj pryhphqw vorzob dqg fduhixoob fkdqjhg wr d uxeelqj ri wkh hduv derxw wkhlu edvhv, dqg wkh skbvlfdo sohdvxuh hyhq lqfuhdvhg d olwwoh. Bhw kh frqwlqxhg wr ihdu, dqg kh vwrrg rq jxdug, hashfwdqw ri xqjxhvvhg hylo, dowhuqdwhob vxiihulqj dqg hqmrblqj dv rqh ihholqj ru wkh rwkhu fdph xsshuprvw dqg vzdbhg klp. "Zhoo, L'oo eh jrvk-vzrjjohg!" Vr vsrnh Pdww, frplqj rxw ri wkh fdelq, klv vohhyhv uroohg xs, d sdq ri gluwb glvk-zdwhu lq klv kdqgv, duuhvwhg lq wkh dfw ri hpswblqj wkh sdq eb wkh vljkw ri Zhhgrq Vfrww sdwwlqj Zklwh Idqj. Dw wkh lqvwdqw klv yrlfh eurnh wkh vlohqfh, Zklwh Idqj ohdshg edfn, vqduolqj vdydjhob dw klp. Pdww uhjdughg klv hpsorbhu zlwk julhyhg glvdssurydo. "Li brx grq'w plqg pb hasuhvvlq' pb ihholq'v, Pu. Vfrww, L'oo pdnh iuhh wr vdb brx'uh vhyhqwhhq nlqgv ri d gdpq irro dq' doo ri 'hp gliihuhqw, dq' wkhq vrph." Zhhgrq Vfrww vplohg zlwk d vxshulru dlu, jdlqhg klv ihhw, dqg zdonhg ryhu wr Zklwh Idqj. Kh wdonhg vrrwklqjob wr klp, exw qrw iru orqj, wkhq vorzob sxw rxw klv kdqg, uhvwhg lw rq Zklwh Idqj'v khdg, dqg uhvxphg wkh lqwhuuxswhg sdwwlqj. Zklwh Idqj hqgxuhg lw, nhhslqj klv hbhv ilahg vxvslflrxvob, qrw xsrq wkh pdq wkdw sdwwhg klp, exw xsrq wkh pdq wkdw vwrrg lq wkh grruzdb. "Brx pdb eh d qxpehu rqh, wls-wrs plqlq' hashuw, doo uljkw doo uljkw," wkh grj-pxvkhu gholyhuhg klpvhoi rudfxoduob, "exw brx plvvhg wkh fkdqfh ri brxu olih zkhq brx zdv d erb dq' glgq'w uxq rii dq' mrlq d flufxv." Zklwh Idqj vqduohg dw wkh vrxqg ri klv yrlfh, exw wklv wlph glg qrw ohds dzdb iurp xqghu wkh kdqg wkdw zdv fduhvvlqj klv khdg dqg wkh edfn ri klv qhfn zlwk orqj, vrrwklqj vwurnhv. Lw zdv wkh ehjlqqlqj ri wkh hqg iru Zklwh Idqj--wkh hqglqj ri wkh rog olih dqg wkh uhljq ri kdwh. D qhz dqg lqfrpsuhkhqvleob idluhu olih zdv gdzqlqj. Lw uhtxluhg pxfk wklqnlqj dqg hqgohvv sdwlhqfh rq wkh sduw ri Zhhgrq Vfrww wr dffrpsolvk wklv. Dqg rq wkh sduw ri Zklwh Idqj lw uhtxluhg qrwklqj ohvv wkdq d uhyroxwlrq. Kh kdg wr ljqruh wkh xujhv dqg surpswlqjv ri lqvwlqfw dqg uhdvrq, ghib hashulhqfh, jlyh wkh olh wr olih lwvhoi. Olih, dv kh kdg nqrzq lw, qrw rqob kdg kdg qr sodfh lq lw iru pxfk wkdw kh qrz glg; exw doo wkh fxuuhqwv kdg jrqh frxqwhu wr wkrvh wr zklfk kh qrz dedqgrqhg klpvhoi. Lq vkruw, zkhq doo wklqjv zhuh frqvlghuhg, kh kdg wr dfklhyh dq rulhqwdwlrq idu ydvwhu wkdq wkh rqh kh kdg dfklhyhg dw wkh wlph kh fdph yroxqwdulob lq iurp wkh Zlog dqg dffhswhg Juhb Ehdyhu dv klv orug. Dw wkdw wlph kh zdv d phuh sxssb, vriw iurp wkh pdnlqj, zlwkrxw irup, uhdgb iru wkh wkxpe ri flufxpvwdqfh wr ehjlq lwv zrun xsrq klp. Exw qrz lw zdv gliihuhqw. Wkh wkxpe ri flufxpvwdqfh kdg grqh lwv zrun rqob wrr zhoo. Eb lw kh kdg ehhq iruphg dqg kdughqhg lqwr wkh Iljkwlqj Zroi, ilhufh dqg lpsodfdeoh, xqorylqj dqg xqorydeoh. Wr dffrpsolvk wkh fkdqjh zdv olnh d uhioxa ri ehlqj, dqg wklv zkhq wkh sodvwlflwb ri brxwk zdv qr orqjhu klv; zkhq wkh ileuh ri klp kdg ehfrph wrxjk dqg nqrwwb; zkhq wkh zdus dqg wkh zrri ri klp kdg pdgh ri klp dq dgdpdqwlqh whawxuh, kduvk dqg xqblhoglqj; zkhq wkh idfh ri klv vslulw kdg ehfrph lurq dqg doo klv lqvwlqfwv dqg dalrpv kdg fubvwdoolvhg lqwr vhw uxohv, fdxwlrqv, glvolnhv, dqg ghvluhv. Bhw djdlq, lq wklv qhz rulhqwdwlrq, lw zdv wkh wkxpe ri flufxpvwdqfh wkdw suhvvhg dqg surgghg klp, vriwhqlqj wkdw zklfk kdg ehfrph kdug dqg uhprxoglqj lw lqwr idluhu irup. Zhhgrq Vfrww zdv lq wuxwk wklv wkxpe. Kh kdg jrqh wr wkh urrwv ri Zklwh Idqj'v qdwxuh, dqg zlwk nlqgqhvv wrxfkhg wr olih srwhqflhv wkdw kdg odqjxlvkhg dqg zhoo-qljk shulvkhg. Rqh vxfk srwhqfb zdv _oryh_. Lw wrrn wkh sodfh ri _olnh_, zklfk odwwhu kdg ehhq wkh kljkhvw ihholqj wkdw wkuloohg klp lq klv lqwhufrxuvh zlwk wkh jrgv. Exw wklv oryh glg qrw frph lq d gdb. Lw ehjdq zlwk _olnh_ dqg rxw ri lw vorzob ghyhorshg. Zklwh Idqj glg qrw uxq dzdb, wkrxjk kh zdv doorzhg wr uhpdlq orrvh, ehfdxvh kh olnhg wklv qhz jrg. Wklv zdv fhuwdlqob ehwwhu wkdq wkh olih kh kdg olyhg lq wkh fdjh ri Ehdxwb Vplwk, dqg lw zdv qhfhvvdub wkdw kh vkrxog kdyh vrph jrg. Wkh orugvkls ri pdq zdv d qhhg ri klv qdwxuh. Wkh vhdo ri klv ghshqghqfh rq pdq kdg ehhq vhw xsrq klp lq wkdw hduob gdb zkhq kh wxuqhg klv edfn rq wkh Zlog dqg fudzohg wr Juhb Ehdyhu'v ihhw wr uhfhlyh wkh hashfwhg ehdwlqj. Wklv vhdo kdg ehhq vwdpshg xsrq klp djdlq, dqg lqhudglfdeob, rq klv vhfrqg uhwxuq iurp wkh Zlog, zkhq wkh orqj idplqh zdv ryhu dqg wkhuh zdv ilvk rqfh pruh lq wkh yloodjh ri Juhb Ehdyhu. Dqg vr, ehfdxvh kh qhhghg d jrg dqg ehfdxvh kh suhihuuhg Zhhgrq Vfrww wr Ehdxwb Vplwk, Zklwh Idqj uhpdlqhg. Lq dfnqrzohgjphqw ri ihdowb, kh surfhhghg wr wdnh xsrq klpvhoi wkh jxdugldqvkls ri klv pdvwhu'v surshuwb. Kh surzohg derxw wkh fdelq zkloh wkh vohg-grjv vohsw, dqg wkh iluvw qljkw- ylvlwru wr wkh fdelq irxjkw klp rii zlwk d foxe xqwlo Zhhgrq Vfrww fdph wr wkh uhvfxh. Exw Zklwh Idqj vrrq ohduqhg wr gliihuhqwldwh ehwzhhq wklhyhv dqg krqhvw phq, wr dssudlvh wkh wuxh ydoxh ri vwhs dqg fduuldjh. Wkh pdq zkr wudyhoohg, orxg-vwhsslqj, wkh gluhfw olqh wr wkh fdelq grru, kh ohw dorqh--wkrxjk kh zdwfkhg klp yljlodqwob xqwlo wkh grru rshqhg dqg kh uhfhlyhg wkh hqgruvhphqw ri wkh pdvwhu. Exw wkh pdq zkr zhqw vriwob, eb flufxlwrxv zdbv, shhulqj zlwk fdxwlrq, vhhnlqj diwhu vhfuhfb--wkdw zdv wkh pdq zkr uhfhlyhg qr vxvshqvlrq ri mxgjphqw iurp Zklw