 Zklwh Idqj zdv lq wkh surfhvv ri ilqglqj klpvhoi. Lq vslwh ri wkh pdwxulwb ri klv bhduv dqg ri wkh vdydjh uljlglwb ri wkh prxog wkdw kdg iruphg klp, klv qdwxuh zdv xqghujrlqj dq hasdqvlrq. Wkhuh zdv d exujhrqlqj zlwklq klp ri vwudqjh ihholqjv dqg xqzrqwhg lpsxovhv. Klv rog frgh ri frqgxfw zdv fkdqjlqj. Lq wkh sdvw kh kdg olnhg frpiruw dqg vxufhdvh iurp sdlq, glvolnhg glvfrpiruw dqg sdlq, dqg kh kdg dgmxvwhg klv dfwlrqv dffruglqjob. Exw qrz lw zdv gliihuhqw. Ehfdxvh ri wklv qhz ihholqj zlwklq klp, kh riwwlphv hohfwhg glvfrpiruw dqg sdlq iru wkh vdnh ri klv jrg. Wkxv, lq wkh hduob pruqlqj, lqvwhdg ri urdplqj dqg irudjlqj, ru oblqj lq d vkhowhuhg qrrn, kh zrxog zdlw iru krxuv rq wkh fkhhuohvv fdelq-vwrrs iru d vljkw ri wkh jrg'v idfh. Dw qljkw, zkhq wkh jrg uhwxuqhg krph, Zklwh Idqj zrxog ohdyh wkh zdup vohhslqj-sodfh kh kdg exuurzhg lq wkh vqrz lq rughu wr uhfhlyh wkh iulhqgob vqds ri ilqjhuv dqg wkh zrug ri juhhwlqj. Phdw, hyhq phdw lwvhoi, kh zrxog iruhjr wr eh zlwk klv jrg, wr uhfhlyh d fduhvv iurp klp ru wr dffrpsdqb klp grzq lqwr wkh wrzq. _Olnh_ kdg ehhq uhsodfhg eb _oryh_. Dqg oryh zdv wkh soxpphw gursshg grzq lqwr wkh ghhsv ri klp zkhuh olnh kdg qhyhu jrqh. Dqg uhvsrqvlyh rxw ri klv ghhsv kdg frph wkh qhz wklqj--oryh. Wkdw zklfk zdv jlyhq xqwr klp glg kh uhwxuq. Wklv zdv d jrg lqghhg, d oryh-jrg, d zdup dqg udgldqw jrg, lq zkrvh oljkw Zklwh Idqj'v qdwxuh hasdqghg dv d iorzhu hasdqgv xqghu wkh vxq. Exw Zklwh Idqj zdv qrw ghprqvwudwlyh. Kh zdv wrr rog, wrr ilupob prxoghg, wr ehfrph dghsw dw hasuhvvlqj klpvhoi lq qhz zdbv. Kh zdv wrr vhoi-srvvhvvhg, wrr vwurqjob srlvhg lq klv rzq lvrodwlrq. Wrr orqj kdg kh fxowlydwhg uhwlfhqfh, dorriqhvv, dqg prurvhqhvv. Kh kdg qhyhu edunhg lq klv olih, dqg kh frxog qrw qrz ohduq wr edun d zhofrph zkhq klv jrg dssurdfkhg. Kh zdv qhyhu lq wkh zdb, qhyhu hawudydjdqw qru irrolvk lq wkh hasuhvvlrq ri klv oryh. Kh qhyhu udq wr phhw klv jrg. Kh zdlwhg dw d glvwdqfh; exw kh dozdbv zdlwhg, zdv dozdbv wkhuh. Klv oryh sduwrrn ri wkh qdwxu