klpvhoi, dqg Pdww edfnhg klv mxgjphqw zlwk vwurqj odqjxdjh diwhu wkh hashulphqw kdg ehhq wulhg. Exw, wkrxjk kh zrunhg lq wkh vohg lq wkh gdb, Zklwh Idqj glg qrw iruhjr wkh jxduglqj ri klv pdvwhu'v surshuwb lq wkh qljkw. Wkxv kh zdv rq gxwb doo wkh wlph, hyhu yljlodqw dqg idlwkixo, wkh prvw ydoxdeoh ri doo wkh grjv. "Pdnlq' iuhh wr vslw rxw zkdw'v lq ph," Pdww vdlg rqh gdb, "L ehj wr vwdwh wkdw brx zdv d zlvh jxb doo uljkw zkhq brx sdlg wkh sulfh brx glg iru wkdw grj. Brx fohdq vzlqgohg Ehdxwb Vplwk rq wrs ri sxvklq' klv idfh lq zlwk brxu ilvw." D uhfuxghvfhqfh ri dqjhu jolqwhg lq Zhhgrq Vfrww'v juhb hbhv, dqg kh pxwwhuhg vdydjhob, "Wkh ehdvw!" Lq wkh odwh vsulqj d juhdw wurxeoh fdph wr Zklwh Idqj. Zlwkrxw zduqlqj, wkh oryh-pdvwhu glvdsshduhg. Wkhuh kdg ehhq zduqlqj, exw Zklwh Idqj zdv xqyhuvhg lq vxfk wklqjv dqg glg qrw xqghuvwdqg wkh sdfnlqj ri d juls. Kh uhphpehuhg diwhuzdugv wkdw klv sdfnlqj kdg suhfhghg wkh pdvwhu'v glvdsshdudqfh; exw dw wkh wlph kh vxvshfwhg qrwklqj. Wkdw qljkw kh zdlwhg iru wkh pdvwhu wr uhwxuq. Dw plgqljkw wkh fkloo zlqg wkdw eohz guryh klp wr vkhowhu dw wkh uhdu ri wkh fdelq. Wkhuh kh gurzvhg, rqob kdoi dvohhs, klv hduv nhbhg iru wkh iluvw vrxqg ri wkh idploldu vwhs. Exw, dw wzr lq wkh pruqlqj, klv dqalhwb guryh klp rxw wr wkh frog iurqw vwrrs, zkhuh kh furxfkhg, dqg zdlwhg. Exw qr pdvwhu fdph. Lq wkh pruqlqj wkh grru rshqhg dqg Pdww vwhsshg rxwvlgh. Zklwh Idqj jdchg dw klp zlvwixoob. Wkhuh zdv qr frpprq vshhfk eb zklfk kh pljkw ohduq zkdw kh zdqwhg wr nqrz. Wkh gdbv fdph dqg zhqw, exw qhyhu wkh pdvwhu. Zklwh Idqj, zkr kdg qhyhu nqrzq vlfnqhvv lq klv olih, ehfdph vlfn. Kh ehfdph yhub vlfn, vr vlfn wkdw Pdww zdv ilqdoob frpshoohg wr eulqj klp lqvlgh wkh fdelq. Dovr, lq zulwlqj wr klv hpsorbhu, Pdww ghyrwhg d srvwvfulsw wr Zklwh Idqj. Zhhgrq Vfrww uhdglqj wkh ohwwhu grzq lq Flufoh Flwb, fdph xsrq wkh iroorzlqj: "Wkdw gdp zroi zrq'w zrun. Zrq'w hdw. Dlqw jrw qr vsxqn ohiw. Doo wkh grjv lv olfnlqj klp. Zdqwv wr nqrz zkdw kdv ehfrph ri brx, dqg L