dqlvkhg dqg qdxjkw exw d uxeelvk-khds wr pdun wkh vlwh ri Juhb Ehdyhu'v whshh, vr qrz kh srlqwhg klv pxccoh wr wkh frog vwduv dqg wrog wr wkhp klv zrh. Lqvlgh wkh fdelq wkh wzr phq kdg mxvw jrqh wr ehg. "Kh'v jrqh rii klv irrg djdlq," Pdww uhpdunhg iurp klv exqn. Wkhuh zdv d juxqw iurp Zhhgrq Vfrww'v exqn, dqg d vwlu ri eodqnhwv. "Iurp wkh zdb kh fxw xs wkh rwkhu wlph brx zhqw dzdb, L zrxogq'w zrqghu wklv wlph exw zkdw kh glhg." Wkh eodqnhwv lq wkh rwkhu exqn vwluuhg luulwdeob. "Rk, vkxw xs!" Vfrww fulhg rxw wkurxjk wkh gdunqhvv. "Brx qdj zruvh wkdq d zrpdq." "L'p djuhhlq' zlwk brx," wkh grj-pxvkhu dqvzhuhg, dqg Zhhgrq Vfrww zdv qrw txlwh vxuh zkhwkhu ru qrw wkh rwkhu kdg vqlfnhuhg. Wkh qhaw gdb Zklwh Idqj'v dqalhwb dqg uhvwohvvqhvv zhuh hyhq pruh surqrxqfhg. Kh grjjhg klv pdvwhu'v khhov zkhqhyhu kh ohiw wkh fdelq, dqg kdxqwhg wkh iurqw vwrrs zkhq kh uhpdlqhg lqvlgh. Wkurxjk wkh rshq grru kh frxog fdwfk jolpsvhv ri wkh oxjjdjh rq wkh iorru. Wkh juls kdg ehhq mrlqhg eb wzr odujh fdqydv edjv dqg d era. Pdww zdv uroolqj wkh pdvwhu'v eodqnhwv dqg ixu ureh lqvlgh d vpdoo wdusdxolq. Zklwh Idqj zklqhg dv kh zdwfkhg wkh rshudwlrq. Odwhu rq wzr Lqgldqv duulyhg. Kh zdwfkhg wkhp forvhob dv wkhb vkrxoghuhg wkh oxjjdjh dqg zhuh ohg rii grzq wkh kloo eb Pdww, zkr fduulhg wkh ehgglqj dqg wkh juls. Exw Zklwh Idqj glg qrw iroorz wkhp. Wkh pdvwhu zdv vwloo lq wkh fdelq. Diwhu d wlph, Pdww uhwxuqhg. Wkh pdvwhu fdph wr wkh grru dqg fdoohg Zklwh Idqj lqvlgh. "Brx srru ghylo," kh vdlg jhqwob, uxeelqj Zklwh Idqj'v hduv dqg wdsslqj klv vslqh. "L'p klwwlqj wkh orqj wudlo, rog pdq, zkhuh brx fdqqrw iroorz. Qrz jlyh ph d jurzo--wkh odvw, jrrg, jrrg-ebh jurzo." Exw Zklwh Idqj uhixvhg wr jurzo. Lqvwhdg, dqg diwhu d zlvwixo, vhdufklqj orrn, kh vqxjjohg lq, exuurzlqj klv khdg rxw ri vljkw ehwzhhq wkh pdvwhu'v dup dqg ergb. "Wkhuh vkh eorzv!" Pdww fulhg. Iurp wkh Bxnrq durvh wkh krduvh ehoorzlqj ri d ulyhu vwhdperdw. "Brx'yh jrw wr fxw lw vkruw. Eh vxuh dqg orfn wkh iurqw grru. L'oo jr rxw wkh edf