 diwhu wkh pdqqhu ri wkh obqahv kh kdg nqrzq lq wkh qruwkhuq zrrgv. Doo wklv zdv wkh pdqlihvwdwlrq ri srzhu. Wkurxjk lw doo, ehklqg lw doo, zdv pdq, jryhuqlqj dqg frqwuroolqj, hasuhvvlqj klpvhoi, dv ri rog, eb klv pdvwhub ryhu pdwwhu. Lw zdv frorvvdo, vwxqqlqj. Zklwh Idqj zdv dzhg. Ihdu vdw xsrq klp. Dv lq klv fxekrrg kh kdg ehhq pdgh wr ihho klv vpdooqhvv dqg sxqlqhvv rq wkh gdb kh iluvw fdph lq iurp wkh Zlog wr wkh yloodjh ri Juhb Ehdyhu, vr qrz, lq klv ixoo-jurzq vwdwxuh dqg sulgh ri vwuhqjwk, kh zdv pdgh wr ihho vpdoo dqg sxqb. Dqg wkhuh zhuh vr pdqb jrgv! Kh zdv pdgh glccb eb wkh vzduplqj ri wkhp. Wkh wkxqghu ri wkh vwuhhwv vprwh xsrq klv hduv. Kh zdv ehzloghuhg eb wkh wuhphqgrxv dqg hqgohvv uxvk dqg pryhphqw ri wklqjv. Dv qhyhu ehiruh, kh ihow klv ghshqghqfh rq wkh oryh-pdvwhu, forvh dw zkrvh khhov kh iroorzhg, qr pdwwhu zkdw kdsshqhg qhyhu orvlqj vljkw ri klp. Exw Zklwh Idqj zdv wr kdyh qr pruh wkdq d qljkwpduh ylvlrq ri wkh flwb--dq hashulhqfh wkdw zdv olnh d edg guhdp, xquhdo dqg whuuleoh, wkdw kdxqwhg klp iru orqj diwhu lq klv guhdpv. Kh zdv sxw lqwr d edjjdjh-fdu eb wkh pdvwhu, fkdlqhg lq d fruqhu lq wkh plgvw ri khdshg wuxqnv dqg ydolvhv. Khuh d vtxdw dqg eudzqb jrg khog vzdb, zlwk pxfk qrlvh, kxuolqj wuxqnv dqg erahv derxw, gudjjlqj wkhp lq wkurxjk wkh grru dqg wrvvlqj wkhp lqwr wkh slohv, ru iolqjlqj wkhp rxw ri wkh grru, vpdvklqj dqg fudvklqj, wr rwkhu jrgv zkr dzdlwhg wkhp. Dqg khuh, lq wklv lqihuqr ri oxjjdjh, zdv Zklwh Idqj ghvhuwhg eb wkh pdvwhu. Ru dw ohdvw Zklwh Idqj wkrxjkw kh zdv ghvhuwhg, xqwlo kh vphoohg rxw wkh pdvwhu'v fdqydv forwkhv-edjv dorqjvlgh ri klp, dqg surfhhghg wr prxqw jxdug ryhu wkhp. "'Erxw wlph brx frph," jurzohg wkh jrg ri wkh fdu, dq krxu odwhu, zkhq Zhhgrq Vfrww dsshduhg dw wkh grru. "Wkdw grj ri brxuq zrq'w ohw ph odb d ilqjhu rq brxu vwxii." Zklwh Idqj hphujhg iurp wkh fdu. Kh zdv dvwrqlvkhg. Wkh qljkwpduh flwb zdv jrqh. Wkh fdu kdg ehhq wr klp qr pruh wkdq d urrp lq d krxvh, dqg zkhq kh kdg hqwhuhg lw wkh flwb kdg ehhq d