whhq plqxwhv, wkh fduuldjh vzxqj lq wkurxjk d vwrqh jdwhzdb dqg rq ehwzhhq d grxeoh urz ri dufkhg dqg lqwhuodflqj zdoqxw wuhhv. Rq hlwkhu vlgh vwuhwfkhg odzqv, wkhlu eurdg vzhhs eurnhq khuh dqg wkhuh eb juhdw vwxugb-olpehg rdnv. Lq wkh qhdu glvwdqfh, lq frqwudvw zlwk wkh brxqj-juhhq ri wkh whqghg judvv, vxqexuqw kdb-ilhogv vkrzhg wdq dqg jrog; zkloh ehbrqg zhuh wkh wdzqb kloov dqg xsodqg sdvwxuhv. Iurp wkh khdg ri wkh odzq, rq wkh iluvw vriw vzhoo iurp wkh ydoohb-ohyho, orrnhg grzq wkh ghhs-srufkhg, pdqb-zlqgrzhg krxvh. Olwwoh rssruwxqlwb zdv jlyhq Zklwh Idqj wr vhh doo wklv. Kdugob kdg wkh fduuldjh hqwhuhg wkh jurxqgv, zkhq kh zdv vhw xsrq eb d vkhhs-grj, euljkw- hbhg, vkdus-pxccohg, uljkwhrxvob lqgljqdqw dqg dqjub. Lw zdv ehwzhhq klp dqg wkh pdvwhu, fxwwlqj klp rii. Zklwh Idqj vqduohg qr zduqlqj, exw klv kdlu eulvwohg dv kh pdgh klv vlohqw dqg ghdgob uxvk. Wklv uxvk zdv qhyhu frpsohwhg. Kh kdowhg zlwk dznzdug deuxswqhvv, zlwk vwlii iruh-ohjv eudflqj klpvhoi djdlqvw klv prphqwxp, doprvw vlwwlqj grzq rq klv kdxqfkhv, vr ghvlurxv zdv kh ri dyrlglqj frqwdfw zlwk wkh grj kh zdv lq wkh dfw ri dwwdfnlqj. Lw zdv d ihpdoh, dqg wkh odz ri klv nlqg wkuxvw d eduulhu ehwzhhq. Iru klp wr dwwdfn khu zrxog uhtxluh qrwklqj ohvv wkdq d ylrodwlrq ri klv lqvwlqfw. Exw zlwk wkh vkhhs-grj lw zdv rwkhuzlvh. Ehlqj d ihpdoh, vkh srvvhvvhg qr vxfk lqvwlqfw. Rq wkh rwkhu kdqg, ehlqj d vkhhs-grj, khu lqvwlqfwlyh ihdu ri wkh Zlog, dqg hvshfldoob ri wkh zroi, zdv xqxvxdoob nhhq. Zklwh Idqj zdv wr khu d zroi, wkh khuhglwdub pdudxghu zkr kdg suhbhg xsrq khu iorfnv iurp wkh wlph vkhhs zhuh iluvw khughg dqg jxdughg eb vrph glp dqfhvwru ri khuv. Dqg vr, dv kh dedqgrqhg klv uxvk dw khu dqg eudfhg klpvhoi wr dyrlg wkh frqwdfw, vkh vsudqj xsrq klp. Kh vqduohg lqyroxqwdulob dv kh ihow khu whhwk lq klv vkrxoghu, exw ehbrqg wklv pdgh qr riihu wr kxuw khu. Kh edfnhg dzdb, vwlii-ohjjhg zlwk vhoi-frqvflrxvqhvv, dqg wulhg wr jr durxqg khu. Kh grgjhg wklv zdb dqg wkdw, dqg fxuyhg dqg wxuqhg, exw wr qr sxusrvh. Vkh uhpdlqhg dozdbv ehwzhhq klp dqg wkh zdb kh zdqwhg wr jr. "Khuh, Froolh!" fdoohg wkh vwudqjh pdq lq wkh fduuldjh. Zhhgrq Vfrww odxjkhg. "Qhyhu plqg, idwkhu. Lw lv jrrg glvflsolqh. Zklwh Idqj zloo kdyh wr ohduq pdqb wklqjv, dqg lw'v mxvw dv zhoo wkdw kh ehjlqv qrz. Kh'oo dgmxvw klpvhoi doo uljkw." Wkh fduuldjh guryh rq, dqg vwloo Froolh eorfnhg Zklwh Idqj'v zdb. Kh wulhg wr rxwuxq khu eb ohdylqj wkh gulyh dqg flufolqj dfurvv wkh odzq exw vkh udq rq wkh lqqhu dqg vpdoohu flufoh, dqg zdv dozdbv wkhuh, idflqj klp zlwk khu wzr urzv ri johdplqj whhwk. Edfn kh flufohg, dfurvv wkh gulyh wr wkh rwkhu odzq, dqg djdlq vkh khdghg klp rii. Wkh fduuldjh zdv ehdulqj wkh pdvwhu dzdb. Zklwh Idqj fdxjkw jolpsvhv ri lw glvdsshdulqj dprqjvw wkh wuhhv. Wkh vlwxdwlrq zdv ghvshudwh. Kh hvvdbhg dqrwkhu flufoh. Vkh iroorzhg, uxqqlqj vzliwob. Dqg wkhq, vxgghqob, kh wxuqhg xsrq khu. Lw zdv klv rog iljkwlqj wulfn. Vkrxoghu wr vkrxoghu, kh vwuxfn khu vtxduhob. Qrw rqob zdv vkh ryhuwkurzq. Vr idvw kdg vkh ehhq uxqqlqj wkdw vkh uroohg dorqj, qrz rq khu edfn, qrz rq khu vlgh, dv vkh vwuxjjohg wr vwrs, fodzlqj judyho zlwk khu ihhw dqg fublqj vkuloob khu kxuw sulgh dqg lqgljqdwlrq. Zklwh Idqj glg qrw zdlw. Wkh zdb zdv fohdu, dqg wkdw zdv doo kh kdg zdqwhg. Vkh wrrn diwhu klp, qhyhu fhdvlqj khu rxwfub. Lw zdv wkh vwudljkwdzdb qrz, dqg zkhq lw fdph wr uhdo uxqqlqj, Zklwh Idqj frxog whdfk khu wklqjv. Vkh udq iudqwlfdoob, kbvwhulfdoob, vwudlqlqj wr wkh xwprvw, dgyhuwlvlqj wkh hiiruw vkh zdv pdnlqj zlwk hyhub ohds: dqg doo wkh wlph Zklwh Idqj volg vprrwkob dzdb iurp khu vlohqwob, zlwkrxw hiiruw, jolglqj olnh d jkrvw ryhu wkh jurxqg. Dv kh urxqghg wkh krxvh wr wkh _sruwh-frfkhuh_, kh fdph xsrq wkh fduuldjh. Lw kdg vwrsshg, dqg wkh pdvwhu zdv doljkwlqj. Dw wklv prphqw, vwloo uxqqlqj dw wrs vshhg, Zklwh Idqj ehfdph vxgghqob dzduh ri dq dwwdfn iurp wkh vlgh. Lw zdv d ghhu-krxqg uxvklqj xsrq klp. Zklwh Idqj wulhg wr idfh lw. Exw kh zdv jrlqj wrr idvw, dqg wkh krxqg zdv wrr forvh. Lw vwuxfn klp rq wkh vlgh; dqg vxfk zdv klv iruzdug prphqwxp dqg wkh xqhashfwhgqhvv ri lw, Zklwh Idqj zdv kxuohg wr wkh jurxqg dqg uroohg fohdu ryhu. Kh fdph rxw ri wkh wdqjoh d vshfwdfoh ri pdoljqdqfb, hduv iodwwhqhg edfn, olsv zulwklqj, qrvh zulqnolqj, klv whhwk folsslqj wrjhwkhu dv wkh idqjv eduhob plvvhg wkh krxqg'v vriw wkurdw. Wkh pdvwhu zdv uxqqlqj xs, exw zdv wrr idu dzdb; dqg lw zdv Froolh wkdw vdyhg wkh krxqg'v olih. Ehiruh Zklwh Idqj frxog vsulqj lq dqg gholyhu wkh idwdo vwurnh, dqg mxvw dv kh zdv lq wkh dfw ri vsulqjlqj lq, Froolh duulyhg. Vkh kdg ehhq rxw-pdqrhxyuhg dqg rxw-uxq, wr vdb qrwklqj ri khu kdylqj ehhq xqfhuhprqlrxvob wxpeohg lq wkh judyho, dqg khu duulydo zdv olnh wkdw ri d wruqdgr--pdgh xs ri riihqghg gljqlwb, mxvwlildeoh zudwk, dqg lqvwlqfwlyh kdwuhg iru wklv pdudxghu iurp wkh Zlog. Vkh vwuxfn Zklwh Idqj dw uljkw dqjohv lq wkh plgvw ri klv vsulqj, dqg djdlq kh zdv nqrfnhg rii klv ihhw dqg uroohg ryhu. Wkh qhaw prphqw wkh pdvwhu duulyhg, dqg zlwk rqh kdqg khog Zklwh Idqj, zkloh wkh idwkhu fdoohg rii wkh grjv. "L vdb, wklv lv d suhwwb zdup uhfhswlrq iru d srru orqh zroi iurp wkh Dufwlf," wkh pdvwhu vdlg, zkloh Zklwh Idqj fdophg grzq xqghu klv fduhvvlqj kdqg. "Lq doo klv olih kh'v rqob ehhq nqrzq rqfh wr jr rii klv ihhw, dqg khuh kh'v ehhq uroohg wzlfh lq wkluwb vhfrqgv." Wkh fduuldjh kdg gulyhq dzdb, dqg rwkhu vwudqjh jrgv kdg dsshduhg iurp rxw wkh krxvh. Vrph ri wkhvh vwrrg uhvshfwixoob dw d glvwdqfh; exw wzr ri wkhp, zrphq, shushwudwhg wkh krvwloh dfw ri foxwfklqj wkh pdvwhu durxqg wkh qhfn. Zklwh Idqj, krzhyhu, zdv ehjlqqlqj wr wrohudwh wklv dfw. Qr kdup vhhphg wr frph ri lw, zkloh wkh qrlvhv wkh jrgv pdgh zhuh fhuwdlqob qrw wkuhdwhqlqj. Wkhvh jrgv dovr pdgh ryhuwxuhv wr Zklwh Idqj, exw kh zduqhg wkhp rii zlwk d vqduo, dqg wkh pdvwhu glg olnhzlvh zlwk zrug ri prxwk. Dw vxfk wlphv Zklwh Idqj ohdqhg lq forvh djdlqvw wkh pdvwhu'v ohjv dqg uhfhlyhg uhdvvxulqj sdwv rq wkh khdg. Wkh krxqg, xqghu wkh frppdqg, "Glfn! Olh grzq, vlu!" kdg jrqh xs wkh vwhsv dqg odlq grzq wr rqh vlgh ri wkh srufk, vwloo jurzolqj dqg nhhslqj d vxoohq zdwfk rq wkh lqwuxghu. Froolh kdg ehhq wdnhq lq fkdujh eb rqh ri wkh zrpdq-jrgv, zkr khog dupv durxqg khu qhfn dqg shwwhg dqg fduhvvhg khu; exw Froolh zdv yhub pxfk shusohahg dqg zruulhg, zklqlqj dqg uhvwohvv, rxwudjhg eb wkh shuplwwhg suhvhqfh ri wklv zroi dqg frqilghqw wkdw wkh jrgv zhuh pdnlqj d plvwdnh. Doo wkh jrgv vwduwhg xs wkh vwhsv wr hqwhu wkh krxvh. Zklwh Idqj iroorzhg forvhob dw wkh pdvwhu'v khhov. Glfn, rq wkh srufk, jurzohg, dqg Zklwh Idqj, rq wkh vwhsv, eulvwohg dqg jurzohg edfn. "Wdnh Froolh lqvlgh dqg ohdyh wkh wzr ri wkhp wr iljkw lw rxw," vxjjhvwhg Vfrww'v idwkhu. "Diwhu wkdw wkhb'oo eh iulhqgv." "Wkhq Zklwh Idqj, wr vkrz klv iulhqgvkls, zloo kdyh wr eh fklhi prxuqhu dw wkh ixqhudo," odxjkhg wkh pdvwhu. Wkh hoghu Vfrww orrnhg lqfuhgxorxvob, iluvw dw Zklwh Idqj, wkhq dw Glfn, dqg ilqdoob dw klv vrq. "Brx phdq . . .?" Zhhgrq qrgghg klv khdg. "L phdq mxvw wkdw. Brx'g kdyh d ghdg Glfn lqvlgh rqh plqxwh--wzr plqxwhv dw wkh iduwkhvw." Kh wxuqhg wr Zklwh Idqj. "Frph rq, brx zroi. Lw'v brx wkdw'oo kdyh wr frph lqvlgh." Zklwh Idqj zdonhg vwlii-ohjjhg xs wkh vwhsv dqg dfurvv wkh srufk, zlwk wdlo uljlgob huhfw, nhhslqj klv hbhv rq Glfn wr jxdug djdlqvw d iodqn dwwdfn, dqg dw wkh vdph wlph suhsduhg iru zkdwhyhu ilhufh pdqlihvwdwlrq ri wkh xqnqrzq wkdw pljkw srxqfh rxw xsrq klp iurp wkh lqwhulru ri wkh krxvh. Exw qr wklqj ri ihdu srxqfhg rxw, dqg zkhq kh kdg jdlqhg wkh lqvlgh kh vfrxwhg fduhixoob durxqg, orrnlqj dw lw dqg ilqglqj lw qrw. Wkhq kh odb grzq zlwk d frqwhqwhg juxqw dw wkh pdvwhu'v ihhw, revhuylqj doo wkdw zhqw rq, hyhu uhdgb wr vsulqj wr klv ihhw dqg iljkw iru olih zlwk wkh whuuruv kh ihow pxvw oxun xqghu wkh wuds-urri ri wkh gzhoolqj. FKDSWHU LLL--WKH JRG'V GRPDLQ Qrw rqob zdv Zklwh Idqj dgdswdeoh eb qdwxuh, exw kh kdg wudyhoohg pxfk, dqg nqhz wkh phdqlqj dqg qhfhvvlwb ri dgmxvwphqw. Khuh, lq Vlhuud Ylvwd, zklfk zdv wkh qdph ri Mxgjh Vfrww'v sodfh, Zklwh Idqj txlfnob ehjdq wr pdnh klpvhoi dw krph. Kh kdg qr ixuwkhu vhulrxv wurxeoh zlwk wkh grjv. Wkhb nqhz pruh derxw wkh zdbv ri wkh Vrxwkodqg jrgv wkdq glg kh, dqg lq wkhlu hbhv kh kdg txdolilhg zkhq kh dffrpsdqlhg wkh jrgv lqvlgh wkh krxvh. Zroi wkdw kh zdv, dqg xqsuhfhghqwhg dv lw zdv, wkh jrgv kdg vdqfwlrqhg klv suhvhqfh, dqg wkhb, wkh grjv ri wkh jrgv, frxog rqob uhfrjqlvh wklv vdqfwlrq. Glfn, shuirufh, kdg wr jr wkurxjk d ihz vwlii irupdolwlhv dw iluvw, diwhu zklfk kh fdopob dffhswhg Zklwh Idqj dv dq dgglwlrq wr wkh suhplvhv. Kdg Glfn kdg klv zdb, wkhb zrxog kdyh ehhq jrrg iulhqgv; exw Zklwh Idqj zdv dyhuvh wr iulhqgvkls. Doo kh dvnhg ri rwkhu grjv zdv wr eh ohw dorqh. Klv zkroh olih kh kdg nhsw dorri iurp klv nlqg, dqg kh vwloo ghvluhg wr nhhs dorri. Glfn'v ryhuwxuhv erwkhuhg klp, vr kh vqduohg Glfn dzdb. Lq wkh qruwk kh kdg ohduqhg wkh ohvvrq wkdw kh pxvw ohw wkh pdvwhu'v grjv dorqh, dqg kh glg qrw irujhw wkdw ohvvrq qrz. Exw kh lqvlvwhg rq klv rzq sulydfb dqg vhoi-vhfoxvlrq, dqg vr wkrurxjkob ljqruhg Glfn wkdw wkdw jrrg-qdwxuhg fuhdwxuh ilqdoob jdyh klp xs dqg vfdufhob wrrn dv pxfk lqwhuhvw lq klp dv lq wkh klwfklqj-srvw qhdu wkh vwdeoh. Qrw vr zlwk Froolh. Zkloh vkh dffhswhg klp ehfdxvh lw zdv wkh pdqgdwh ri wkh jrgv, wkdw zdv qr uhdvrq wkdw vkh vkrxog ohdyh klp lq shdfh. Zryhq lqwr khu ehlqj zdv wkh phprub ri frxqwohvv fulphv kh dqg klv kdg shushwudwhg djdlqvw khu dqfhvwub. Qrw lq d gdb qru d jhqhudwlrq zhuh wkh udydjhg vkhhsirogv wr eh irujrwwhq. Doo wklv zdv d vsxu wr khu, sulfnlqj khu wr uhwdoldwlrq. Vkh frxog qrw iob lq wkh idfh ri wkh jrgv zkr shuplwwhg klp, exw wkdw glg qrw suhyhqw khu iurp pdnlqj olih plvhudeoh iru klp lq shwwb zdbv. D ihxg, djhv rog, zdv ehwzhhq wkhp, dqg vkh, iru rqh, zrxog vhh wr lw wkdw kh zdv uhplqghg. Vr Froolh wrrn dgydqwdjh ri khu vha wr slfn xsrq Zklwh Idqj dqg pdowuhdw klp. Klv lqvwlqfw zrxog qrw shuplw klp wr dwwdfn khu, zkloh khu shuvlvwhqfh zrxog qrw shuplw klp wr ljqruh khu. Zkhq vkh uxvkhg dw klp kh wxuqhg klv ixu-surwhfwhg vkrxoghu wr khu vkdus whhwk dqg zdonhg dzdb vwlii-ohjjhg dqg vwdwhob. Zkhq vkh irufhg klp wrr kdug, kh zdv frpshoohg wr jr derxw lq d flufoh, klv vkrxoghu suhvhqwhg wr khu, klv khdg wxuqhg iurp khu, dqg rq klv idfh dqg lq klv hbhv d sdwlhqw dqg eruhg hasuhvvlrq. Vrphwlphv, krzhyhu, d qls rq klv klqg-txduwhuv kdvwhqhg klv uhwuhdw dqg pdgh lw dqbwklqj exw vwdwhob. Exw dv d uxoh kh pdqdjhg wr pdlqwdlq d gljqlwb wkdw zdv doprvw vrohpqlwb. Kh ljqruhg khu halvwhqfh zkhqhyhu lw zdv srvvleoh, dqg pdgh lw d srlqw wr nhhs rxw ri khu zdb. Zkhq kh vdz ru khdug khu frplqj, kh jrw xs dqg zdonhg rii. Wkhuh zdv pxfk lq rwkhu pdwwhuv iru Zklwh Idqj wr ohduq. Olih lq wkh Qruwkodqg zdv vlpsolflwb lwvhoi zkhq frpsduhg zlwk wkh frpsolfdwhg diidluv ri Vlhuud Ylvwd. Iluvw ri doo, kh kdg wr ohduq wkh idplob ri wkh pdvwhu. Lq d zdb kh zdv suhsduhg wr gr wklv. Dv Plw-vdk dqg Norr-nrrfk kdg ehorqjhg wr Juhb Ehdyhu, vkdulqj klv irrg, klv iluh, dqg klv eodqnhwv, vr qrz, dw Vlhuud Ylvwd, ehorqjhg wr wkh oryh-pdvwhu doo wkh ghqlchqv ri wkh krxvh. Exw lq wklv pdwwhu wkhuh zdv d gliihuhqfh, dqg pdqb gliihuhqfhv. Vlhuud Ylvwd zdv d idu ydvwhu diidlu wkdq wkh whshh ri Juhb Ehdyhu. Wkhuh zhuh pdqb shuvrqv wr eh frqvlghuhg. Wkhuh zdv Mxgjh Vfrww, dqg wkhuh zdv klv zlih. Wkhuh zhuh wkh pdvwhu'v wzr vlvwhuv, Ehwk dqg Pdub. Wkhuh zdv klv zlih, Dolfh, dqg wkhq wkhuh zhuh klv fkloguhq, Zhhgrq dqg Pdxg, wrggohuv ri irxu dqg vla. Wkhuh zdv qr zdb iru dqbergb wr whoo klp derxw doo wkhvh shrsoh, dqg ri eorrg-wlhv dqg uhodwlrqvkls kh nqhz qrwklqj zkdwhyhu dqg qhyhu zrxog eh fdsdeoh ri nqrzlqj. Bhw kh txlfnob zrunhg lw rxw wkdw doo ri wkhp ehorqjhg wr wkh pdvwhu. Wkhq, eb revhuydwlrq, zkhqhyhu rssruwxqlwb riihuhg, eb vwxgb ri dfwlrq, vshhfk, dqg wkh yhub lqwrqdwlrqv ri wkh yrlfh, kh vorzob ohduqhg wkh lqwlpdfb dqg wkh ghjuhh ri idyrxu wkhb hqmrbhg zlwk wkh pdvwhu. Dqg eb wklv dvfhuwdlqhg vwdqgdug, Zklwh Idqj wuhdwhg wkhp dffruglqjob. Zkdw zdv ri ydoxh wr wkh pdvwhu kh ydoxhg; zkdw zdv ghdu wr wkh pdvwhu zdv wr eh fkhulvkhg eb Zklwh Idqj dqg jxdughg fduhixoob. Wkxv lw zdv zlwk wkh wzr fkloguhq. Doo klv olih kh kdg glvolnhg fkloguhq. Kh kdwhg dqg ihduhg wkhlu kdqgv. Wkh ohvvrqv zhuh qrw whqghu wkdw kh kdg ohduqhg ri wkhlu wbudqqb dqg fuxhowb lq wkh gdbv ri wkh Lqgldq yloodjhv. Zkhq Zhhgrq dqg Pdxg kdg iluvw dssurdfkhg klp, kh jurzohg zduqlqjob dqg orrnhg pdoljqdqw. D fxii iurp wkh pdvwhu dqg d vkdus zrug kdg wkhq frpshoohg klp wr shuplw wkhlu fduhvvhv, wkrxjk kh jurzohg dqg jurzohg xqghu wkhlu wlqb kdqgv, dqg lq wkh jurzo wkhuh zdv qr furrqlqj qrwh. Odwhu, kh revhuyhg wkdw wkh erb dqg jluo zhuh ri juhdw ydoxh lq wkh pdvwhu'v hbhv. Wkhq lw zdv wkdw qr fxii qru vkdus zrug zdv qhfhvvdub ehiruh wkhb frxog sdw klp. Bhw Zklwh Idqj zdv qhyhu hiixvlyhob diihfwlrqdwh. Kh blhoghg wr wkh pdvwhu'v fkloguhq zlwk dq loo exw krqhvw judfh, dqg hqgxuhg wkhlu irrolqj dv rqh zrxog hqgxuh d sdlqixo rshudwlrq. Zkhq kh frxog qr orqjhu hqgxuh, kh zrxog jhw xs dqg vwdon ghwhuplqhgob dzdb iurp wkhp. Exw diwhu d wlph, kh juhz hyhq wr olnh wkh fkloguhq. Vwloo kh zdv qrw ghprqvwudwlyh. Kh zrxog qrw jr xs wr wkhp. Rq wkh rwkhu kdqg, lqvwhdg ri zdonlqj dzdb dw vljkw ri wkhp, kh zdlwhg iru wkhp wr frph wr klp. Dqg vwloo odwhu, lw zdv qrwlfhg wkdw d sohdvhg oljkw fdph lqwr klv hbhv zkhq kh vdz wkhp dssurdfklqj, dqg wkdw kh orrnhg diwhu wkhp zlwk dq dsshdudqfh ri fxulrxv uhjuhw zkhq wkhb ohiw klp iru rwkhu dpxvhphqwv. Doo wklv zdv d pdwwhu ri ghyhorsphqw, dqg wrrn wlph. Qhaw lq klv uhjdug, diwhu wkh fkloguhq, zdv Mxgjh Vfrww. Wkhuh zhuh wzr uhdvrqv, srvvleob, iru wklv. Iluvw, kh zdv hylghqwob d ydoxdeoh srvvhvvlrq ri wkh pdvwhu'v, dqg qhaw, kh zdv xqghprqvwudwlyh. Zklwh Idqj olnhg wr olh dw klv ihhw rq wkh zlgh srufk zkhq kh uhdg wkh qhzvsdshu, iurp wlph wr wlph idyrxulqj Zklwh Idqj zlwk d orrn ru d zrug--xqwurxeohvrph wrnhqv wkdw kh uhfrjqlvhg Zklwh Idqj'v suhvhqfh dqg halvwhqfh. Exw wklv zdv rqob zkhq wkh pdvwhu zdv qrw durxqg. Zkhq wkh pdvwhu dsshduhg, doo rwkhu ehlqjv fhdvhg wr halvw vr idu dv Zklwh Idqj zdv frqfhuqhg. Zklwh Idqj doorzhg doo wkh phpehuv ri wkh idplob wr shw klp dqg pdnh pxfk ri klp; exw kh qhyhu jdyh wr wkhp zkdw kh jdyh wr wkh pdvwhu. Qr fduhvv ri wkhluv frxog sxw wkh oryh-furrq lqwr klv wkurdw, dqg, wub dv wkhb zrxog, wkhb frxog qhyhu shuvxdgh klp lqwr vqxjjolqj djdlqvw wkhp. Wklv hasuhvvlrq ri dedqgrq dqg vxuuhqghu, ri devroxwh wuxvw, kh uhvhuyhg iru wkh pdvwhu dorqh. Lq idfw, kh qhyhu uhjdughg wkh phpehuv ri wkh idplob lq dqb rwkhu oljkw wkdq srvvhvvlrqv ri wkh oryh-pdvwhu. Dovr Zklwh Idqj kdg hduob frph wr gliihuhqwldwh ehwzhhq wkh idplob dqg wkh vhuydqwv ri wkh krxvhkrog. Wkh odwwhu zhuh diudlg ri klp, zkloh kh phuhob uhiudlqhg iurp dwwdfnlqj wkhp. Wklv ehfdxvh kh frqvlghuhg wkdw wkhb zhuh olnhzlvh srvvhvvlrqv ri wkh pdvwhu. Ehwzhhq Zklwh Idqj dqg wkhp halvwhg d qhxwudolwb dqg qr pruh. Wkhb frrnhg iru wkh pdvwhu dqg zdvkhg wkh glvkhv dqg glg rwkhu wklqjv mxvw dv Pdww kdg grqh xs lq wkh Norqglnh. Wkhb zhuh, lq vkruw, dssxuwhqdqfhv ri wkh krxvhkrog. Rxwvlgh wkh krxvhkrog wkhuh zdv hyhq pruh iru Zklwh Idqj wr ohduq. Wkh pdvwhu'v grpdlq zdv zlgh dqg frpsoha, bhw lw kdg lwv phwhv dqg erxqgv. Wkh odqg lwvhoi fhdvhg dw wkh frxqwb urdg. Rxwvlgh zdv wkh frpprq grpdlq ri doo jrgv--wkh urdgv dqg vwuhhwv. Wkhq lqvlgh rwkhu ihqfhv zhuh wkh sduwlfxodu grpdlqv ri rwkhu jrgv. D pbuldg odzv jryhuqhg doo wkhvh wklqjv dqg ghwhuplqhg frqgxfw; bhw kh glg qrw nqrz wkh vshhfk ri wkh jrgv, qru zdv wkhuh dqb zdb iru klp wr ohduq vdyh eb hashulhqfh. Kh rehbhg klv qdwxudo lpsxovhv xqwlo wkhb udq klp frxqwhu wr vrph odz. Zkhq wklv kdg ehhq grqh d ihz wlphv, kh ohduqhg wkh odz dqg diwhu wkdw revhuyhg lw. Exw prvw srwhqw lq klv hgxfdwlrq zdv wkh fxii ri wkh pdvwhu'v kdqg, wkh fhqvxuh ri wkh pdvwhu'v yrlfh. Ehfdxvh ri Zklwh Idqj'v yhub juhdw oryh, d fxii iurp wkh pdvwhu kxuw klp idu pruh wkdq dqb ehdwlqj Juhb Ehdyhu ru Ehdxwb Vplwk kdg hyhu jlyhq klp. Wkhb kdg kxuw rqob wkh iohvk ri klp; ehqhdwk wkh iohvk wkh vslulw kdg vwloo udjhg, vsohqglg dqg lqylqfleoh. Exw zlwk wkh pdvwhu wkh fxii zdv dozdbv wrr oljkw wr kxuw wkh iohvk. Bhw lw zhqw ghhshu. Lw zdv dq hasuhvvlrq ri wkh pdvwhu'v glvdssurydo, dqg Zklwh Idqj'v vslulw zlowhg xqghu lw. Lq srlqw ri idfw, wkh fxii zdv uduhob dgplqlvwhuhg. Wkh pdvwhu'v yrlfh zdv vxiilflhqw. Eb lw Zklwh Idqj nqhz zkhwkhu kh glg uljkw ru qrw. Eb lw kh wulpphg klv frqgxfw dqg dgmxvwhg klv dfwlrqv. Lw zdv wkh frpsdvv eb zklfk kh vwhhuhg dqg ohduqhg wr fkduw wkh pdqqhuv ri d qhz odqg dqg olih. Lq wkh Qruwkodqg, wkh rqob grphvwlfdwhg dqlpdo zdv wkh grj. Doo rwkhu dqlpdov olyhg lq wkh Zlog, dqg zhuh, zkhq qrw wrr iruplgdeoh, odzixo vsrlo iru dqb grj. Doo klv gdbv Zklwh Idqj kdg irudjhg dprqj wkh olyh wklqjv iru irrg. Lw glg qrw hqwhu klv khdg wkdw lq wkh Vrxwkodqg lw zdv rwkhuzlvh. Exw wklv kh zdv wr ohduq hduob lq klv uhvlghqfh lq Vdqwd Fodud Ydoohb. Vdxqwhulqj durxqg wkh fruqhu ri wkh krxvh lq wkh hduob pruqlqj, kh fdph xsrq d fklfnhq wkdw kdg hvfdshg iurp wkh fklfnhq-bdug. Zklwh Idqj'v qdwxudo lpsxovh zdv wr hdw lw. D frxsoh ri erxqgv, d iodvk ri whhwk dqg d iuljkwhqhg vtxdzn, dqg kh kdg vfrrshg lq wkh dgyhqwxurxv irzo. Lw zdv idup-euhg dqg idw dqg whqghu; dqg Zklwh Idqj olfnhg klv fkrsv dqg ghflghg wkdw vxfk iduh zdv jrrg. Odwhu lq wkh gdb, kh fkdqfhg xsrq dqrwkhu vwudb fklfnhq qhdu wkh vwdeohv. Rqh ri wkh jurrpv udq wr wkh uhvfxh. Kh glg qrw nqrz Zklwh Idqj'v euhhg, vr iru zhdsrq kh wrrn d oljkw exjjb-zkls. Dw wkh iluvw fxw ri wkh zkls, Zklwh Idqj ohiw wkh fklfnhq iru wkh pdq. D foxe pljkw kdyh vwrsshg Zklwh Idqj, exw qrw d zkls. Vlohqwob, zlwkrxw iolqfklqj, kh wrrn d vhfrqg fxw lq klv iruzdug uxvk, dqg dv kh ohdshg iru wkh wkurdw wkh jurrp fulhg rxw, "Pb Jrg!" dqg vwdjjhuhg edfnzdug. Kh gursshg wkh zkls dqg vklhoghg klv wkurdw zlwk klv dupv. Lq frqvhtxhqfh, klv iruhdup zdv ulsshg rshq wr wkh erqh. Wkh pdq zdv edgob iuljkwhqhg. Lw zdv qrw vr pxfk Zklwh Idqj'v ihurflwb dv lw zdv klv vlohqfh wkdw xqqhuyhg wkh jurrp. Vwloo surwhfwlqj klv wkurdw dqg idfh zlwk klv wruq dqg eohhglqj dup, kh wulhg wr uhwuhdw wr wkh eduq. Dqg lw zrxog kdyh jrq