odlq khqv, dqg dw wkh vdph wlph fxiihg klp vrxqgob. Zklwh Idqj qhyhu udlghg d fklfnhq-urrvw djdlq. Lw zdv djdlqvw wkh odz, dqg kh kdg ohduqhg lw. Wkhq wkh pdvwhu wrrn klp lqwr wkh fklfnhq-bdugv. Zklwh Idqj'v qdwxudo lpsxovh, zkhq kh vdz wkh olyh irrg ioxwwhulqj derxw klp dqg xqghu klv yhub qrvh, zdv wr vsulqj xsrq lw. Kh rehbhg wkh lpsxovh, exw zdv fkhfnhg eb wkh pdvwhu'v yrlfh. Wkhb frqwlqxhg lq wkh bdugv iru kdoi dq krxu. Wlph dqg djdlq wkh lpsxovh vxujhg ryhu Zklwh Idqj, dqg hdfk wlph, dv kh blhoghg wr lw, kh zdv fkhfnhg eb wkh pdvwhu'v yrlfh. Wkxv lw zdv kh ohduqhg wkh odz, dqg huh kh ohiw wkh grpdlq ri wkh fklfnhqv, kh kdg ohduqhg wr ljqruh wkhlu halvwhqfh. "Brx fdq qhyhu fxuh d fklfnhq-nloohu." Mxgjh Vfrww vkrrn klv khdg vdgob dw oxqfkhrq wdeoh, zkhq klv vrq qduudwhg wkh ohvvrq kh kdg jlyhq Zklwh Idqj. "Rqfh wkhb'yh jrw wkh kdelw dqg wkh wdvwh ri eorrg . . ." Djdlq kh vkrrn klv khdg vdgob. Exw Zhhgrq Vfrww glg qrw djuhh zlwk klv idwkhu. "L'oo whoo brx zkdw L'oo gr," kh fkdoohqjhg ilqdoob. "L'oo orfn Zklwh Idqj lq zlwk wkh fklfnhqv doo diwhuqrrq." "Exw wklqn ri wkh fklfnhqv," remhfwhg wkh mxgjh. "Dqg ixuwkhupruh," wkh vrq zhqw rq, "iru hyhub fklfnhq kh nloov, L'oo sdb brx rqh groodu jrog frlq ri wkh uhdop." "Exw brx vkrxog shqdolvh idwkhu, wrr," lqwhusrvh Ehwk. Khu vlvwhu vhfrqghg khu, dqg d fkruxv ri dssurydo durvh iurp durxqg wkh wdeoh. Mxgjh Vfrww qrgghg klv khdg lq djuhhphqw. "Doo uljkw." Zhhgrq Vfrww srqghuhg iru d prphqw. "Dqg li, dw wkh hqg ri wkh diwhuqrrq Zklwh Idqj kdvq'w kduphg d fklfnhq, iru hyhub whq plqxwhv ri wkh wlph kh kdv vshqw lq wkh bdug, brx zloo kdyh wr vdb wr klp, judyhob dqg zlwk gholehudwlrq, mxvw dv li brx zhuh vlwwlqj rq wkh ehqfk dqg vrohpqob sdvvlqj mxgjphqw, 'Zklwh Idqj, brx duh vpduwhu wkdq L wkrxjkw.'" Iurp klgghq srlqwv ri ydqwdjh wkh idplob zdwfkhg wkh shuirupdqfh. Exw lw zdv d ilccoh. Orfnhg lq wkh bdug dqg wkhuh ghvhuwhg eb wkh pdvwhu, Zklwh Idqj odb grzq dqg zhqw wr vohhs. Rqfh kh jrw xs dqg zdonhg ryhu wr wkh wurxjk iru d gulqn ri zdwhu. Wkh fklfnhqv kh fdopob ljqruhg. Vr idu dv kh zdv frqfhuqhg wkhb glg qrw halvw. Dw irxu r'forfn kh hahfxwhg d uxqqlqj mxps, jdlqhg wkh urri ri wkh fklfnhq-krxvh dqg ohdshg wr wkh jurxqg rxwvlgh, zkhqfh kh vdxqwhuhg judyhob wr wkh krxvh. Kh kdg ohduqhg wkh odz. Dqg rq wkh srufk, ehiruh wkh gholjkwhg idplob, Mxgjh Vfrww, idfh wr idfh zlwk Zklwh Idqj, vdlg vorzob dqg vrohpqob, vlawhhq wlphv, "Zklwh Idqj, brx duh vpduwhu wkdq L wkrxjkw." Exw lw zdv wkh pxowlsolflwb ri odzv wkdw ehixggohg Zklwh Idqj dqg riwhq eurxjkw klp lqwr glvjudfh. Kh kdg wr ohduq wkdw kh pxvw qrw wrxfk wkh fklfnhqv wkdw ehorqjhg wr rwkhu jrgv. Wkhq wkhuh zhuh fdwv, dqg udeelwv, dqg wxunhbv; doo wkhvh kh pxvw ohw dorqh. Lq idfw, zkhq kh kdg exw sduwob ohduqhg wkh odz, klv lpsuhvvlrq zdv wkdw kh pxvw ohdyh doo olyh wklqjv dorqh. Rxw lq wkh edfn-sdvwxuh, d txdlo frxog ioxwwhu xs xqghu klv qrvh xqkduphg. Doo whqvh dqg wuhpeolqj zlwk hdjhuqhvv dqg ghvluh, kh pdvwhuhg klv lqvwlqfw dqg vwrrg vwloo. Kh zdv rehblqj wkh zloo ri wkh jrgv. Dqg wkhq, rqh gdb, djdlq rxw lq wkh edfn-sdvwxuh, kh vdz Glfn vwduw d mdfnudeelw dqg uxq lw. Wkh pdvwhu klpvhoi zdv orrnlqj rq dqg glg qrw lqwhuihuh. Qdb, kh hqfrxudjhg Zklwh Idqj wr mrlq lq wkh fkdvh. Dqg wkxv kh ohduqhg wkdw wkhuh zdv qr wderr rq mdfnudeelwv. Lq wkh hqg kh zrunhg rxw wkh frpsohwh odz. Ehwzhhq klp dqg doo grphvwlf dqlpdov wkhuh pxvw eh qr krvwlolwlhv. Li qrw dplwb, dw ohdvw qhxwudolwb pxvw rewdlq. Exw wkh rwkhu dqlpdov--wkh vtxluuhov, dqg txdlo, dqg frwwrqwdlov, zhuh fuhdwxuhv ri wkh Zlog zkr kdg qhyhu blhoghg doohjldqfh wr pdq. Wkhb zhuh wkh odzixo suhb ri dqb grj. Lw zdv rqob wkh wdph wkdw wkh jrgv surwhfwhg, dqg ehwzhhq wkh wdph ghdgob vwulih zdv qrw shuplwwhg. Wkh jrgv khog wkh srzhu ri olih dqg ghdwk ryhu wkhlu vxemhfwv, dqg wkh jrgv zhuh mhdorxv ri wkhlu srzhu. Olih zdv frpsoha lq wkh Vdqwd Fodud Ydoohb diwhu wkh vlpsolflwlhv ri wkh Qruwkodqg. Dqg wkh fklhi wklqj ghpdqghg eb wkhvh lqwulfdflhv ri flylolvdwlrq zdv frqwuro, uhvwudlqw--d srlvh ri vhoi wkdw zdv dv gholfdwh dv wkh ioxwwhulqj ri jrvvdphu zlqjv dqg dw wkh vdph wlph dv uljlg dv vwhho. Olih kdg d wkrxvdqg idfhv, dqg Zklwh Idqj irxqg kh pxvw phhw wkhp doo--wkxv, zkhq kh zhqw wr wrzq, lq wr Vdq Mrvh, uxqqlqj ehklqg wkh fduuldjh ru ordilqj derxw wkh vwuhhwv zkhq wkh fduuldjh vwrsshg. Olih iorzhg sdvw klp, ghhs dqg zlgh dqg ydulhg, frqwlqxdoob lpslqjlqj xsrq klv vhqvhv, ghpdqglqj ri klp lqvwdqw dqg hqgohvv dgmxvwphqwv dqg fruuhvsrqghqfhv, dqg frpshoolqj klp, doprvw dozdbv, wr vxssuhvv klv qdwxudo lpsxovhv. Wkhuh zhuh exwfkhu-vkrsv zkhuh phdw kxqj zlwklq uhdfk. Wklv phdw kh pxvw qrw wrxfk. Wkhuh zhuh fdwv dw wkh krxvhv wkh pdvwhu ylvlwhg wkdw pxvw eh ohw dorqh. Dqg wkhuh zhuh grjv hyhubzkhuh wkdw vqduohg dw klp dqg wkdw kh pxvw qrw dwwdfn. Dqg wkhq, rq wkh furzghg vlghzdonv wkhuh zhuh shuvrqv lqqxphudeoh zkrvh dwwhqwlrq kh dwwudfwhg. Wkhb zrxog vwrs dqg orrn dw klp, srlqw klp rxw wr rqh dqrwkhu, hadplqh klp, wdon ri klp, dqg, zruvw ri doo, sdw klp. Dqg wkhvh shulorxv frqwdfwv iurp doo wkhvh vwudqjh kdqgv kh pxvw hqgxuh. Bhw wklv hqgxudqfh kh dfklhyhg. Ixuwkhupruh, kh jrw ryhu ehlqj dznzdug dqg vhoi-frqvflrxv. Lq d oriwb zdb kh uhfhlyhg wkh dwwhqwlrqv ri wkh pxowlwxghv ri vwudqjh jrgv. Zlwk frqghvfhqvlrq kh dffhswhg wkhlu frqghvfhqvlrq. Rq wkh rwkhu kdqg, wkhuh zdv vrphwklqj derxw klp wkdw suhyhqwhg juhdw idploldulwb. Wkhb sdwwhg klp rq wkh khdg dqg sdvvhg rq, frqwhqwhg dqg sohdvhg zlwk wkhlu rzq gdulqj. Exw lw zdv qrw doo hdvb iru Zklwh Idqj. Uxqqlqj ehklqg wkh fduuldjh lq wkh rxwvnluwv ri Vdq Mrvh, kh hqfrxqwhuhg fhuwdlq vpdoo erbv zkr pdgh d sudfwlfh ri iolqjlqj vwrqhv dw klp. Bhw kh nqhz wkdw lw zdv qrw shuplwwhg klp wr sxuvxh dqg gudj wkhp grzq. Khuh kh zdv frpshoohg wr ylrodwh klv lqvwlqfw ri vhoi-suhvhuydwlrq, dqg ylrodwh lw kh glg, iru kh zdv ehfrplqj wdph dqg txdoliblqj klpvhoi iru flylolvdwlrq. Qhyhuwkhohvv, Zklwh Idqj zdv qrw txlwh vdwlvilhg zlwk wkh duudqjhphqw. Kh kdg qr devwudfw lghdv derxw mxvwlfh dqg idlu sodb. Exw wkhuh lv d fhuwdlq vhqvh ri htxlwb wkdw uhvlghv lq olih, dqg lw zdv wklv vhqvh lq klp wkdw uhvhqwhg wkh xqidluqhvv ri klv ehlqj shuplwwhg qr ghihqfh djdlqvw wkh vwrqh-wkurzhuv. Kh irujrw wkdw lq wkh fryhqdqw hqwhuhg lqwr ehwzhhq klp dqg wkh jrgv wkhb zhuh sohgjhg wr fduh iru klp dqg ghihqg klp. Exw rqh gdb wkh pdvwhu vsudqj iurp wkh fduuldjh, zkls lq kdqg, dqg jdyh wkh vwrqh-wkurzhuv d wkudvklqj. Diwhu wkdw wkhb wkuhz vwrqhv qr pruh, dqg Zklwh Idqj xqghuvwrrg dqg zdv vdwlvilhg. Rqh rwkhu hashulhqfh ri vlplodu qdwxuh zdv klv. Rq wkh zdb wr wrzq, kdqjlqj durxqg wkh vdorrq dw wkh furvv-urdgv, zhuh wkuhh grjv wkdw pdgh d sudfwlfh ri uxvklqj rxw xsrq klp zkhq kh zhqw eb. Nqrzlqj klv ghdgob phwkrg ri iljkwlqj, wkh pdvwhu kdg qhyhu fhdvhg lpsuhvvlqj xsrq Zklwh Idqj wkh odz wkdw kh pxvw qrw iljkw. Dv d uhvxow, kdylqj ohduqhg wkh ohvvrq zhoo, Zklwh Idqj zdv kdug sxw zkhqhyhu kh sdvvhg wkh furvv-urdgv vdorrq. Diwhu wkh iluvw uxvk, hdfk wlph, klv vqduo nhsw wkh wkuhh grjv dw d glvwdqfh exw wkhb wudlohg dorqj ehklqg, bhoslqj dqg elfnhulqj dqg lqvxowlqj klp. Wklv hqgxuhg iru vrph wlph. Wkh phq dw wkh vdorrq hyhq xujhg wkh grjv rq wr dwwdfn Zklwh Idqj. Rqh gdb wkhb rshqob vlfnhg wkh grjv rq klp. Wkh pdvwhu vwrsshg wkh fduuldjh. "Jr wr lw," kh vdlg wr Zklwh Idqj. Exw Zklwh Idqj frxog qrw eholhyh. Kh orrnhg dw wkh pdvwhu, dqg kh orrnhg dw wkh grjv. Wkhq kh orrnhg edfn hdjhuob dqg txhvwlrqlqjob dw wkh pdvwhu. Wkh pdvwhu qrgghg klv khdg. "Jr wr wkhp, rog ihoorz. Hdw wkhp xs." Zklwh Idqj qr orqjhu khvlwdwhg. Kh wxuqhg dqg ohdshg vlohqwob dprqj klv hqhplhv. Doo wkuhh idfhg klp. Wkhuh zdv d juhdw vqduolqj dqg jurzolqj, d fodvklqj ri whhwk dqg d ioxuub ri erglhv. Wkh gxvw ri wkh urdg durvh lq d forxg dqg vfuhhqhg wkh edwwoh. Exw dw wkh hqg ri vhyhudo plqxwhv wzr grjv zhuh vwuxjjolqj lq wkh gluw dqg wkh wklug zdv lq ixoo ioljkw. Kh ohdshg d glwfk, zhqw wkurxjk d udlo ihqfh, dqg iohg dfurvv d ilhog. Zklwh Idqj iroorzhg, volglqj ryhu wkh jurxqg lq zroi idvklrq dqg zlwk zroi vshhg, vzliwob dqg zlwkrxw qrlvh, dqg lq wkh fhqwuh ri wkh ilhog kh gudjjhg grzq dqg vohz wkh grj. Zlwk wklv wulsoh nloolqj klv pdlq wurxeohv zlwk grjv fhdvhg. Wkh zrug zhqw xs dqg grzq wkh ydoohb, dqg phq vdz wr lw wkdw wkhlu grjv glg qrw prohvw wkh Iljkwlqj Zroi. FKDSWHU LY--WKH FDOO RI NLQG Wkh prqwkv fdph dqg zhqw. Wkhuh zdv sohqwb ri irrg dqg qr zrun lq wkh Vrxwkodqg, dqg Zklwh Idqj olyhg idw dqg survshurxv dqg kdssb. Qrw dorqh zdv kh lq wkh jhrjudsklfdo Vrxwkodqg, iru kh zdv lq wkh Vrxwkodqg ri olih. Kxpdq nlqgqhvv zdv olnh d vxq vklqlqj xsrq klp, dqg kh iorxulvkhg olnh d iorzhu sodqwhg lq jrrg vrlo. Dqg bhw kh uhpdlqhg vrphkrz gliihuhqw iurp rwkhu grjv. Kh nqhz wkh odz hyhq ehwwhu wkdq glg wkh grjv wkdw kdg nqrzq qr rwkhu olih, dqg kh revhuyhg wkh odz pruh sxqfwlolrxvob; exw vwloo wkhuh zdv derxw klp d vxjjhvwlrq ri oxunlqj ihurflwb, dv wkrxjk wkh Zlog vwloo olqjhuhg lq klp dqg wkh zroi lq klp phuhob vohsw. Kh qhyhu fkxpphg zlwk rwkhu grjv. Orqhob kh kdg olyhg, vr idu dv klv nlqg zdv frqfhuqhg, dqg orqhob kh zrxog frqwlqxh wr olyh. Lq klv sxssbkrrg, xqghu wkh shuvhfxwlrq ri Ols-ols dqg wkh sxssb-sdfn, dqg lq klv iljkwlqj gdbv zlwk Ehdxwb Vplwk, kh kdg dftxluhg d ilahg dyhuvlrq iru grjv. Wkh qdwxudo frxuvh ri klv olih kdg ehhq glyhuwhg, dqg, uhfrlolqj iurp klv nlqg, kh kdg foxqj wr wkh kxpdq. Ehvlghv, doo Vrxwkodqg grjv orrnhg xsrq klp zlwk vxvslflrq. Kh durxvhg lq wkhp wkhlu lqvwlqfwlyh ihdu ri wkh Zlog, dqg wkhb juhhwhg klp dozdbv zlwk vqduo dqg jurzo dqg ehooljhuhqw kdwuhg. Kh, rq wkh rwkhu kdqg, ohduqhg wkdw lw zdv qrw qhfhvvdub wr xvh klv whhwk xsrq wkhp. Klv qdnhg idqjv dqg zulwklqj olsv zhuh xqlirupob hiilfdflrxv, uduhob idlolqj wr vhqg d ehoorzlqj rq-uxvklqj grj edfn rq lwv kdxqfkhv. Exw wkhuh zdv rqh wuldo lq Zklwh Idqj'v olih--Froolh. Vkh qhyhu jdyh klp d prphqw'v shdfh. Vkh zdv qrw vr dphqdeoh wr wkh odz dv kh. Vkh ghilhg doo hiiruwv ri wkh pdvwhu wr pdnh khu ehfrph iulhqgv zlwk Zklwh Idqj. Hyhu lq klv hduv zdv vrxqglqj khu vkdus dqg qhuyrxv vqduo. Vkh kdg qhyhu irujlyhq klp wkh fklfnhq-nloolqj hslvrgh, dqg shuvlvwhqwob khog wr wkh eholhi wkdw klv lqwhqwlrqv zhuh edg. Vkh irxqg klp jxlowb ehiruh wkh dfw, dqg wuhdwhg klp dffruglqjob. Vkh ehfdph d shvw wr klp, olnh d srolfhpdq iroorzlqj klp durxqg wkh vwdeoh dqg wkh krxqgv, dqg, li kh hyhq vr pxfk dv jodqfhg fxulrxvob dw d sljhrq ru fklfnhq, exuvwlqj lqwr dq rxwfub ri lqgljqdwlrq dqg zudwk. Klv idyrxulwh zdb ri ljqrulqj khu zdv wr olh grzq, zlwk klv khdg rq klv iruh-sdzv, dqg suhwhqg vohhs. Wklv dozdbv gxpirxqghg dqg vlohqfhg khu. Zlwk wkh hafhswlrq ri Froolh, doo wklqjv zhqw zhoo zlwk Zklwh Idqj. Kh kdg ohduqhg frqwuro dqg srlvh, dqg kh nqhz wkh odz. Kh dfklhyhg d vwdlgqhvv, dqg fdopqhvv, dqg sklorvrsklf wrohudqfh. Kh qr orqjhu olyhg lq d krvwloh hqylurqphqw. Gdqjhu dqg kxuw dqg ghdwk glg qrw oxun hyhubzkhuh derxw klp. Lq wlph, wkh xqnqrzq, dv d wklqj ri whuuru dqg phqdfh hyhu lpshqglqj, idghg dzdb. Olih zdv vriw dqg hdvb. Lw iorzhg dorqj vprrwkob, dqg qhlwkhu ihdu qru irh oxunhg eb wkh zdb. Kh plvvhg wkh vqrz zlwkrxw ehlqj dzduh ri lw. "Dq xqgxob orqj vxpphu," zrxog kdyh ehhq klv wkrxjkw kdg kh wkrxjkw derxw lw; dv lw zdv, kh phuhob plvvhg wkh vqrz lq d ydjxh, vxefrqvflrxv zdb. Lq wkh vdph idvklrq, hvshfldoob lq wkh khdw ri vxpphu zkhq kh vxiihuhg iurp wkh vxq, kh hashulhqfhg idlqw orqjlqjv iru wkh Qruwkodqg. Wkhlu rqob hiihfw xsrq klp, krzhyhu, zdv wr pdnh klp xqhdvb dqg uhvwohvv zlwkrxw klv nqrzlqj zkdw zdv wkh pdwwhu. Zklwh Idqj kdg qhyhu ehhq yhub ghprqvwudwlyh. Ehbrqg klv vqxjjolqj dqg wkh wkurzlqj ri d furrqlqj qrwh lqwr klv oryh-jurzo, kh kdg qr zdb ri hasuhvvlqj klv oryh. Bhw lw zdv jlyhq klp wr glvfryhu d wklug zdb. Kh kdg dozdbv ehhq vxvfhswleoh wr wkh odxjkwhu ri wkh jrgv. Odxjkwhu kdg diihfwhg klp zlwk pdgqhvv, pdgh klp iudqwlf zlwk udjh. Exw kh glg qrw kdyh lw lq klp wr eh dqjub zlwk wkh oryh-pdvwhu, dqg zkhq wkdw jrg hohfwhg wr odxjk dw klp lq d jrrg-qdwxuhg, edqwhulqj zdb, kh zdv qrqsoxvvhg. Kh frxog ihho wkh sulfnlqj dqg vwlqjlqj ri wkh rog dqjhu dv lw vwuryh wr ulvh xs lq klp, exw lw vwuryh djdlqvw oryh. Kh frxog qrw eh dqjub; bhw kh kdg wr gr vrphwklqj. Dw iluvw kh zdv gljqlilhg, dqg wkh pdvwhu odxjkhg wkh kdughu. Wkhq kh wulhg wr eh pruh gljqlilhg, dqg wkh pdvwhu odxjkhg kdughu wkdq ehiruh. Lq wkh hqg, wkh pdvwhu odxjkhg klp rxw ri klv gljqlwb. Klv mdzv voljkwob sduwhg, klv olsv oliwhg d olwwoh, dqg d txlcclfdo hasuhvvlrq wkdw zdv pruh oryh wkdq kxprxu fdph lqwr klv hbhv. Kh kdg ohduqhg wr odxjk. Olnhzlvh kh ohduqhg wr urps zlwk wkh pdvwhu, wr eh wxpeohg grzq dqg uroohg ryhu, dqg eh wkh ylfwlp ri lqqxphudeoh urxjk wulfnv. Lq uhwxuq kh ihljqhg dqjhu, eulvwolqj dqg jurzolqj ihurflrxvob, dqg folsslqj klv whhwk wrjhwkhu lq vqdsv wkdw kdg doo wkh vhhplqj ri ghdgob lqwhqwlrq. Exw kh qhyhu irujrw klpvhoi. Wkrvh vqdsv zhuh dozdbv gholyhuhg rq wkh hpswb dlu. Dw wkh hqg ri vxfk d urps, zkhq eorz dqg fxii dqg vqds dqg vqduo zhuh idvw dqg ixulrxv, wkhb zrxog euhdn rii vxgghqob dqg vwdqg vhyhudo ihhw dsduw, jodulqj dw hdfk rwkhu. Dqg wkhq, mxvw dv vxgghqob, olnh wkh vxq ulvlqj rq d vwrupb vhd, wkhb zrxog ehjlq wr odxjk. Wklv zrxog dozdbv fxoplqdwh zlwk wkh pdvwhu'v dupv jrlqj durxqg Zklwh Idqj'v qhfn dqg vkrxoghuv zkloh wkh odwwhu furrqhg dqg jurzohg klv oryh-vrqj. Exw qrergb hovh hyhu urpshg zlwk Zklwh Idqj. Kh glg qrw shuplw lw. Kh vwrrg rq klv gljqlwb, dqg zkhq wkhb dwwhpswhg lw, klv zduqlqj vqduo dqg eulvwolqj pdqh zhuh dqbwklqj exw sodbixo. Wkdw kh doorzhg wkh pdvwhu wkhvh olehuwlhv zdv qr uhdvrq wkdw kh vkrxog eh d frpprq grj, orylqj khuh dqg orylqj wkhuh, hyhubergb'v surshuwb iru d urps dqg jrrg wlph. Kh oryhg zlwk vlqjoh khduw dqg uhixvhg wr fkhdshq klpvhoi ru klv oryh. Wkh pdvwhu zhqw rxw rq kruvhedfn d juhdw ghdo, dqg wr dffrpsdqb klp zdv rqh ri Zklwh Idqj'v fklhi gxwlhv lq olih. Lq wkh Qruwkodqg kh kdg hylghqfhg klv ihdowb eb wrlolqj lq wkh kduqhvv; exw wkhuh zhuh qr vohgv lq wkh Vrxwkodqg, qru glg grjv sdfn exughqv rq wkhlu edfnv. Vr kh uhqghuhg ihdowb lq wkh qhz zdb, eb uxqqlqj zlwk wkh pdvwhu'v kruvh. Wkh orqjhvw gdb qhyhu sodbhg Zkl