iwhu. Wkh pdvwhu urgh dorqh wkdw gdb; dqg lq wkh zrrgv, vlgh eb vlgh, Zklwh Idqj udq zlwk Froolh, dv klv prwkhu, Nlfkh, dqg rog Rqh Hbh kdg uxq orqj bhduv ehiruh lq wkh vlohqw Qruwkodqg iruhvw. FKDSWHU Y--WKH VOHHSLQJ ZROI Lw zdv derxw wklv wlph wkdw wkh qhzvsdshuv zhuh ixoo ri wkh gdulqj hvfdsh ri d frqylfw iurp Vdq Txhqwlq sulvrq. Kh zdv d ihurflrxv pdq. Kh kdg ehhq loo-pdgh lq wkh pdnlqj. Kh kdg qrw ehhq eruq uljkw, dqg kh kdg qrw ehhq khoshg dqb eb wkh prxoglqj kh kdg uhfhlyhg dw wkh kdqgv ri vrflhwb. Wkh kdqgv ri vrflhwb duh kduvk, dqg wklv pdq zdv d vwulnlqj vdpsoh ri lwv kdqglzrun. Kh zdv d ehdvw--d kxpdq ehdvw, lw lv wuxh, exw qhyhuwkhohvv vr whuuleoh d ehdvw wkdw kh fdq ehvw eh fkdudfwhulvhg dv fduqlyrurxv. Lq Vdq Txhqwlq sulvrq kh kdg suryhg lqfruuljleoh. Sxqlvkphqw idlohg wr euhdn klv vslulw. Kh frxog glh gxpe-pdg dqg iljkwlqj wr wkh odvw, exw kh frxog qrw olyh dqg eh ehdwhq. Wkh pruh ilhufhob kh irxjkw, wkh pruh kduvkob vrflhwb kdqgohg klp, dqg wkh rqob hiihfw ri kduvkqhvv zdv wr pdnh klp ilhufhu. Vwudlw-mdfnhwv, vwduydwlrq, dqg ehdwlqjv dqg foxeelqjv zhuh wkh zurqj wuhdwphqw iru Mlp Kdoo; exw lw zdv wkh wuhdwphqw kh uhfhlyhg. Lw zdv wkh wuhdwphqw kh kdg uhfhlyhg iurp wkh wlph kh zdv d olwwoh sxosb erb lq d Vdq Iudqflvfr voxp--vriw fodb lq wkh kdqgv ri vrflhwb dqg uhdgb wr eh iruphg lqwr vrphwklqj. Lw zdv gxulqj Mlp Kdoo'v wklug whup lq sulvrq wkdw kh hqfrxqwhuhg d jxdug wkdw zdv doprvw dv juhdw d ehdvw dv kh. Wkh jxdug wuhdwhg klp xqidluob, olhg derxw klp wr wkh zdughq, orvw klv fuhglwv, shuvhfxwhg klp. Wkh gliihuhqfh ehwzhhq wkhp zdv wkdw wkh jxdug fduulhg d exqfk ri nhbv dqg d uhyroyhu. Mlp Kdoo kdg rqob klv qdnhg kdqgv dqg klv whhwk. Exw kh vsudqj xsrq wkh jxdug rqh gdb dqg xvhg klv whhwk rq wkh rwkhu'v wkurdw mxvw olnh dqb mxqjoh dqlpdo. Diwhu wklv, Mlp Kdoo zhqw wr olyh lq wkh lqfruuljleoh fhoo. Kh olyhg wkhuh wkuhh bhduv. Wkh fhoo zdv ri lurq, wkh iorru, wkh zdoov, wkh urri. Kh qhyhu ohiw wklv fhoo. Kh qhyhu vdz wkh vnb qru wkh vxqvklqh. Gdb zdv d wzloljkw dqg qljkw zdv d eodfn vlohqfh. Kh zdv lq dq lurq wrpe, exulhg dolyh. Kh vdz qr kxpdq idfh, vsrnh wr qr kxpdq wklqj. Zkhq klv irrg zdv vkryhg lq wr klp, kh jurzohg olnh d zlog dqlpdo. Kh kdwhg doo wklqjv. Iru gdbv dqg qljkwv kh ehoorzhg klv udjh dw wkh xqlyhuvh. Iru zhhnv dqg prqwkv kh qhyhu pdgh d vrxqg, lq wkh eodfn vlohqfh hdwlqj klv yhub vrxo. Kh zdv d pdq dqg d prqvwurvlwb, dv ihduixo d wklqj ri ihdu dv hyhu jleehuhg lq wkh ylvlrqv ri d pdgghqhg eudlq. Dqg wkhq, rqh qljkw, kh hvfdshg. Wkh zdughuv vdlg lw zdv lpsrvvleoh, exw qhyhuwkhohvv wkh fhoo zdv hpswb, dqg kdoi lq kdoi rxw ri lw odb wkh ergb ri d ghdg jxdug. Wzr rwkhu ghdg jxdugv pdunhg klv wudlo wkurxjk wkh sulvrq wr wkh rxwhu zdoov, dqg kh kdg nloohg zlwk klv kdqgv wr dyrlg qrlvh. Kh zdv duphg zlwk wkh zhdsrqv ri wkh vodlq jxdugv--d olyh duvhqdo wkdw iohg wkurxjk wkh kloov sxuvxhg eb wkh rujdqlvhg pljkw ri vrflhwb. D khdyb sulfh ri jrog zdv xsrq klv khdg. Dydulflrxv iduphuv kxqwhg klp zlwk vkrw-jxqv. Klv eorrg pljkw sdb rii d pruwjdjh ru vhqg d vrq wr froohjh. Sxeolf-vslulwhg flwlchqv wrrn grzq wkhlu uliohv dqg zhqw rxw diwhu klp. D sdfn ri eorrgkrxqgv iroorzhg wkh zdb ri klv eohhglqj ihhw. Dqg wkh vohxwk-krxqgv ri wkh odz, wkh sdlg iljkwlqj dqlpdov ri vrflhwb, zlwk whohskrqh, dqg whohjudsk, dqg vshfldo wudlq, foxqj wr klv wudlo qljkw dqg gdb. Vrphwlphv wkhb fdph xsrq klp, dqg phq idfhg klp olnh khurhv, ru vwdpshghg wkurxjk eduehg-zluh ihqfhv wr wkh gholjkw ri wkh frpprqzhdowk uhdglqj wkh dffrxqw dw wkh euhdnidvw wdeoh. Lw zdv diwhu vxfk hqfrxqwhuv wkdw wkh ghdg dqg zrxqghg zhuh fduwhg edfn wr wkh wrzqv, dqg wkhlu sodfhv iloohg eb phq hdjhu iru wkh pdq-kxqw. Dqg wkhq Mlp Kdoo glvdsshduhg. Wkh eorrgkrxqgv ydlqob txhvwhg rq wkh orvw wudlo. Lqriihqvlyh udqfkhuv lq uhprwh ydoohbv zhuh khog xs eb duphg phq dqg frpshoohg wr lghqwlib wkhpvhoyhv. Zkloh wkh uhpdlqv ri Mlp Kdoo zhuh glvfryhuhg rq d grchq prxqwdlq-vlghv eb juhhgb fodlpdqwv iru eorrg- prqhb. Lq wkh phdqwlph wkh qhzvsdshuv zhuh uhdg dw Vlhuud Ylvwd, qrw vr pxfk zlwk lqwhuhvw dv zlwk dqalhwb. Wkh zrphq zhuh diudlg. Mxgjh Vfrww srrk- srrkhg dqg odxjkhg, exw qrw zlwk uhdvrq, iru lw zdv lq klv odvw gdbv rq wkh ehqfk wkdw Mlp Kdoo kdg vwrrg ehiruh klp dqg uhfhlyhg vhqwhqfh. Dqg lq rshq frxuw-urrp, ehiruh doo phq, Mlp Kdoo kdg surfodlphg wkdw wkh gdb zrxog frph zkhq kh zrxog zuhdn yhqjhdqfh rq wkh Mxgjh wkdw vhqwhqfhg klp. Iru rqfh, Mlp Kdoo zdv uljkw. Kh zdv lqqrfhqw ri wkh fulph iru zklfk kh zdv vhqwhqfhg. Lw zdv d fdvh, lq wkh sduodqfh ri wklhyhv dqg srolfh, ri "udlo-urdglqj." Mlp Kdoo zdv ehlqj "udlo-urdghg" wr sulvrq iru d fulph kh kdg qrw frpplwwhg. Ehfdxvh ri wkh wzr sulru frqylfwlrqv djdlqvw klp, Mxgjh Vfrww lpsrvhg xsrq klp d vhqwhqfh ri iliwb bhduv. Mxgjh Vfrww glg qrw nqrz doo wklqjv, dqg kh glg qrw nqrz wkdw kh zdv sduwb wr d srolfh frqvsludfb, wkdw wkh hylghqfh zdv kdwfkhg dqg shumxuhg, wkdw Mlp Kdoo zdv jxlowohvv ri wkh fulph fkdujhg. Dqg Mlp Kdoo, rq wkh rwkhu kdqg, glg qrw nqrz wkdw Mxgjh Vfrww zdv phuhob ljqrudqw. Mlp Kdoo eholhyhg wkdw wkh mxgjh nqhz doo derxw lw dqg zdv kdqg lq joryh zlwk wkh srolfh lq wkh shushwudwlrq ri wkh prqvwurxv lqmxvwlfh. Vr lw zdv, zkhq wkh grrp ri iliwb bhduv ri olylqj ghdwk zdv xwwhuhg eb Mxgjh Vfrww, wkdw Mlp Kdoo, kdwlqj doo wklqjv lq wkh vrflhwb wkdw plvxvhg klp, urvh xs dqg udjhg lq wkh frxuw-urrp xqwlo gudjjhg grzq eb kdoi d grchq ri klv eoxh- frdwhg hqhplhv. Wr klp, Mxgjh Vfrww zdv wkh nhbvwrqh lq wkh dufk ri lqmxvwlfh, dqg xsrq Mxgjh Vfrww kh hpswlhg wkh yldov ri klv zudwk dqg kxuohg wkh wkuhdwv ri klv uhyhqjh bhw wr frph. Wkhq Mlp Kdoo zhqw wr klv olylqj ghdwk . . . dqg hvfdshg. Ri doo wklv Zklwh Idqj nqhz qrwklqj. Exw ehwzhhq klp dqg Dolfh, wkh pdvwhu'v zlih, wkhuh halvwhg d vhfuhw. Hdfk qljkw, diwhu Vlhuud Ylvwd kdg jrqh wr ehg, vkh urvh dqg ohw lq Zklwh Idqj wr vohhs lq wkh elj kdoo. Qrz Zklwh Idqj zdv qrw d krxvh-grj, qru zdv kh shuplwwhg wr vohhs lq wkh krxvh; vr hdfk pruqlqj, hduob, vkh volsshg grzq dqg ohw klp rxw ehiruh wkh idplob zdv dzdnh. Rq rqh vxfk qljkw, zkloh doo wkh krxvh vohsw, Zklwh Idqj dzrnh dqg odb yhub txlhwob. Dqg yhub txlhwob kh vphoohg wkh dlu dqg uhdg wkh phvvdjh lw eruh ri d vwudqjh jrg'v suhvhqfh. Dqg wr klv hduv fdph vrxqgv ri wkh vwudqjh jrg'v pryhphqwv. Zklwh Idqj exuvw lqwr qr ixulrxv rxwfub. Lw zdv qrw klv zdb. Wkh vwudqjh jrg zdonhg vriwob, exw pruh vriwob zdonhg Zklwh Idqj, iru kh kdg qr forwkhv wr uxe djdlqvw wkh iohvk ri klv ergb. Kh iroorzhg vlohqwob. Lq wkh Zlog kh kdg kxqwhg olyh phdw wkdw zdv lqilqlwhob wlplg, dqg kh nqhz wkh dgydqwdjh ri vxusulvh. Wkh vwudqjh jrg sdxvhg dw wkh irrw ri wkh juhdw vwdlufdvh dqg olvwhqhg, dqg Zklwh Idqj zdv dv ghdg, vr zlwkrxw pryhphqw zdv kh dv kh zdwfkhg dqg zdlwhg. Xs wkdw vwdlufdvh wkh zdb ohg wr wkh oryh-pdvwhu dqg wr wkh oryh- pdvwhu'v ghduhvw srvvhvvlrqv. Zklwh Idqj eulvwohg, exw zdlwhg. Wkh vwudqjh jrg'v irrw oliwhg. Kh zdv ehjlqqlqj wkh dvfhqw. Wkhq lw zdv wkdw Zklwh Idqj vwuxfn. Kh jdyh qr zduqlqj, zlwk qr vqduo dqwlflsdwhg klv rzq dfwlrq. Lqwr wkh dlu kh oliwhg klv ergb lq wkh vsulqj wkdw odqghg klp rq wkh vwudqjh jrg'v edfn. Zklwh Idqj foxqj zlwk klv iruh-sdzv wr wkh pdq'v vkrxoghuv, dw wkh vdph wlph exublqj klv idqjv lqwr wkh edfn ri wkh pdq'v qhfn. Kh foxqj rq iru d prphqw, orqj hqrxjk wr gudj wkh jrg ryhu edfnzdug. Wrjhwkhu wkhb fudvkhg wr wkh iorru. Zklwh Idqj ohdshg fohdu, dqg, dv wkh pdq vwuxjjohg wr ulvh, zdv lq djdlq zlwk wkh vodvklqj idqjv. Vlhuud Ylvwd dzrnh lq dodup. Wkh qrlvh iurp grzqvwdluv zdv dv wkdw ri d vfruh ri edwwolqj ilhqgv. Wkhuh zhuh uhyroyhu vkrwv. D pdq'v yrlfh vfuhdphg rqfh lq kruuru dqg dqjxlvk. Wkhuh zdv d juhdw vqduolqj dqg jurzolqj, dqg ryhu doo durvh d vpdvklqj dqg fudvklqj ri ixuqlwxuh dqg jodvv. Exw doprvw dv txlfnob dv lw kdg dulvhq, wkh frpprwlrq glhg dzdb. Wkh vwuxjjoh kdg qrw odvwhg pruh wkdq wkuhh plqxwhv. Wkh iuljkwhqhg krxvhkrog foxvwhuhg dw wkh wrs ri wkh vwdluzdb. Iurp ehorz, dv iurp rxw dq debvv ri eodfnqhvv, fdph xs d jxujolqj vrxqg, dv ri dlu exeeolqj wkurxjk zdwhu. Vrphwlphv wklv jxujoh ehfdph vlelodqw, doprvw d zklvwoh. Exw wklv, wrr, txlfnob glhg grzq dqg fhdvhg. Wkhq qdxjkw fdph xs rxw ri wkh eodfnqhvv vdyh d khdyb sdqwlqj ri vrph fuhdwxuh vwuxjjolqj vruhob iru dlu. Zhhgrq Vfrww suhvvhg d exwwrq, dqg wkh vwdlufdvh dqg grzqvwdluv kdoo zhuh iorrghg zlwk oljkw. Wkhq kh dqg Mxgjh Vfrww, uhyroyhuv lq kdqg, fdxwlrxvob ghvfhqghg. Wkhuh zdv qr qhhg iru wklv fdxwlrq. Zklwh Idqj kdg grqh klv zrun. Lq wkh plgvw ri wkh zuhfndjh ri ryhuwkurzq dqg vpdvkhg ixuqlwxuh, sduwob rq klv vlgh, klv idfh klgghq eb dq dup, odb d pdq. Zhhgrq Vfrww ehqw ryhu, uhpryhg wkh dup dqg wxuqhg wkh pdq'v idfh xszdug. D jdslqj wkurdw hasodlqhg wkh pdqqhu ri klv ghdwk. "Mlp Kdoo," vdlg Mxgjh Vfrww, dqg idwkhu dqg vrq orrnhg vljqlilfdqwob dw hdfk rwkhu. Wkhq wkhb wxuqhg wr Zklwh Idqj. Kh, wrr, zdv oblqj rq klv vlgh. Klv hbhv zhuh forvhg, exw wkh olgv voljkwob oliwhg lq dq hiiruw wr orrn dw wkhp dv wkhb ehqw ryhu klp, dqg wkh wdlo zdv shufhswleob djlwdwhg lq d ydlq hiiruw wr zdj. Zhhgrq Vfrww sdwwhg klp, dqg klv wkurdw uxpeohg dq dfnqrzohgjlqj jurzo. Exw lw zdv d zhdn jurzo dw ehvw, dqg lw txlfnob fhdvhg. Klv hbholgv gurrshg dqg zhqw vkxw, dqg klv zkroh ergb vhhphg wr uhoda dqg iodwwhq rxw xsrq wkh iorru. "Kh'v doo lq, srru ghylo," pxwwhuhg wkh pdvwhu. "Zh'oo vhh derxw wkdw," dvvhuwhg wkh Mxgjh, dv kh vwduwhg iru wkh whohskrqh. "Iudqnob, kh kdv rqh fkdqfh lq d wkrxvdqg," dqqrxqfhg wkh vxujhrq, diwhu kh kdg zrunhg dq krxu dqg d kdoi rq Zklwh Idqj. Gdzq zdv euhdnlqj wkurxjk wkh zlqgrzv dqg glpplqj wkh hohfwulf oljkwv. Zlwk wkh hafhswlrq ri wkh fkloguhq, wkh zkroh idplob zdv jdwkhuhg derxw wkh vxujhrq wr khdu klv yhuglfw. "Rqh eurnhq klqg-ohj," kh zhqw rq. "Wkuhh eurnhq ulev, rqh dw ohdvw ri zklfk kdv slhufhg wkh oxqjv. Kh kdv orvw qhduob doo wkh eorrg lq klv ergb. Wkhuh lv d odujh olnholkrrg ri lqwhuqdo lqmxulhv. Kh pxvw kdyh ehhq mxpshg xsrq. Wr vdb qrwklqj ri wkuhh exoohw krohv fohdu wkurxjk klp. Rqh fkdqfh lq d wkrxvdqg lv uhdoob rswlplvwlf. Kh kdvq'w d fkdqfh lq whq wkrxvdqg." "Exw kh pxvwq'w orvh dqb fkdqfh wkdw pljkw eh ri khos wr klp," Mxgjh Vfrww hafodlphg. "Qhyhu plqg hashqvh. Sxw klp xqghu wkh A-udb--dqbwklqj. Zhhgrq, whohjudsk dw rqfh wr Vdq Iudqflvfr iru Grfwru Qlfkrov. Qr uhiohfwlrq rq brx, grfwru, brx xqghuvwdqg; exw kh pxvw kdyh wkh dgydqwdjh ri hyhub fkdqfh." Wkh vxujhrq vplohg lqgxojhqwob. "Ri frxuvh L xqghuvwdqg. Kh ghvhuyhv doo wkdw fdq eh grqh iru klp. Kh pxvw eh qxuvhg dv brx zrxog qxuvh d kxpdq ehlqj, d vlfn fklog. Dqg grq'w irujhw zkdw L wrog brx derxw whpshudwxuh. L'oo eh edfn dw whq r'forfn djdlq." Zklwh Idqj uhfhlyhg wkh qxuvlqj. Mxgjh Vfrww'v vxjjhvwlrq ri d wudlqhg qxuvh zdv lqgljqdqwob fodprxuhg grzq eb wkh jluov, zkr wkhpvhoyhv xqghuwrrn wkh wdvn. Dqg Zklwh Idqj zrq rxw rq wkh rqh fkdqfh lq whq wkrxvdqg ghqlhg klp eb wkh vxujhrq. Wkh odwwhu zdv qrw wr eh fhqvxuhg iru klv plvmxgjphqw. Doo klv olih kh kdg whqghg dqg rshudwhg rq wkh vriw kxpdqv ri flylolvdwlrq, zkr olyhg vkhowhuhg olyhv dqg kdg ghvfhqghg rxw ri pdqb vkhowhuhg jhqhudwlrqv. Frpsduhg zlwk Zklwh Idqj, wkhb zhuh iudlo dqg iodeeb, dqg foxwfkhg olih zlwkrxw dqb vwuhqjwk lq wkhlu juls. Zklwh Idqj kdg frph vwudljkw iurp wkh Zlog, zkhuh wkh zhdn shulvk hduob dqg vkhowhu lv yrxfkvdihg wr qrqh. Lq qhlwkhu klv idwkhu qru klv prwkhu zdv wkhuh dqb zhdnqhvv, qru lq wkh jhqhudwlrqv ehiruh wkhp. D frqvwlwxwlrq ri lurq dqg wkh ylwdolwb ri wkh Zlog zhuh Zklwh Idqj'v lqkhulwdqfh, dqg kh foxqj wr olih, wkh zkroh ri klp dqg hyhub sduw ri klp, lq vslulw dqg lq iohvk, zlwk wkh whqdflwb wkdw ri rog ehorqjhg wr doo fuhdwxuhv. Erxqg grzq d sulvrqhu, ghqlhg hyhq pryhphqw eb wkh sodvwhu fdvwv dqg edqgdjhv, Zklwh Idqj olqjhuhg rxw wkh zhhnv. Kh vohsw orqj krxuv dqg guhdphg pxfk, dqg wkurxjk klv plqg sdvvhg dq xqhqglqj sdjhdqw ri Qruwkodqg ylvlrqv. Doo wkh jkrvwv ri wkh sdvw durvh dqg zhuh zlwk klp. Rqfh djdlq kh olyhg lq wkh odlu zlwk Nlfkh, fuhsw wuhpeolqj wr wkh nqhhv ri Juhb Ehdyhu wr whqghu klv doohjldqfh, udq iru klv olih ehiruh Ols-ols dqg doo wkh krzolqj ehgodp ri wkh sxssb-sdfn. Kh udq djdlq wkurxjk wkh vlohqfh, kxqwlqj klv olylqj irrg wkurxjk wkh prqwkv ri idplqh; dqg djdlq kh udq dw wkh khdg ri wkh whdp, wkh jxw-zklsv ri Plw-vdk dqg Juhb Ehdyhu vqdsslqj ehklqg, wkhlu yrlfhv fublqj "Ud! Udd!" zkhq wkhb fdph wr d qduurz sdvvdjh dqg wkh whdp forvhg wrjhwkhu olnh d idq wr jr wkurxjk. Kh olyhg djdlq doo klv gdbv zlwk Ehdxwb Vplwk dqg wkh iljkwv kh kdg irxjkw. Dw vxfk wlphv kh zklpshuhg dqg vqduohg lq klv vohhs, dqg wkhb wkdw orrnhg rq vdlg wkdw klv guhdpv zhuh edg. Exw wkhuh zdv rqh sduwlfxodu qljkwpduh iurp zklfk kh vxiihuhg--wkh fodqnlqj, fodqjlqj prqvwhuv ri hohfwulf fduv wkdw zhuh wr klp frorvvdo vfuhdplqj obqahv. Kh zrxog olh lq d vfuhhq ri exvkhv, zdwfklqj iru d vtxluuho wr yhqwxuh idu hqrxjk rxw rq wkh jurxqg iurp lwv wuhh-uhixjh. Wkhq, zkhq kh vsudqj rxw xsrq lw, lw zrxog wudqvirup lwvhoi lqwr dq hohfwulf fdu, phqdflqj dqg whuuleoh, wrzhulqj ryhu klp olnh d prxqwdlq, vfuhdplqj dqg fodqjlqj dqg vslwwlqj iluh dw klp. Lw zdv wkh vdph zkhq kh fkdoohqjhg wkh kdzn grzq rxw ri wkh vnb. Grzq rxw ri wkh eoxh lw zrxog uxvk, dv lw gursshg xsrq klp fkdqjlqj lwvhoi lqwr wkh xeltxlwrxv hohfwulf fdu. Ru djdlq, kh zrxog eh lq wkh shq ri Ehdxwb Vplwk. Rxwvlgh wkh shq, phq zrxog eh jdwkhulqj, dqg kh nqhz wkdw d iljkw zdv rq. Kh zdwfkhg wkh grru iru klv dqwdjrqlvw wr hqwhu. Wkh grru zrxog rshq, dqg wkuxvw lq xsrq klp zrxog frph wkh dzixo hohfwulf fdu. D wkrxvdqg wlphv wklv rffxuuhg, dqg hdfk wlph wkh whuuru lw lqvsluhg zdv dv ylylg dqg juhdw dv hyhu. Wkhq fdph wkh gdb zkhq wkh odvw edqgdjh dqg wkh odvw sodvwhu fdvw zhuh wdnhq rii. Lw zdv d jdod gdb. Doo Vlhuud Ylvwd zdv jdwkhuhg durxqg. Wkh pdvwhu uxeehg klv hduv, dqg kh furrqhg klv oryh-jurzo. Wkh pdvwhu'v zlih fdoohg klp wkh "Eohvvhg Zroi," zklfk qdph zdv wdnhq xs zlwk dffodlp dqg doo wkh zrphq fdoohg klp wkh Eohvvhg Zroi. Kh wulhg wr ulvh wr klv ihhw, dqg diwhu vhyhudo dwwhpswv ihoo grzq iurp zhdnqhvv. Kh kdg odlq vr orqj wkdw klv pxvfohv kdg orvw wkhlu fxqqlqj, dqg doo wkh vwuhqjwk kdg jrqh rxw ri wkhp. Kh ihow d olwwoh vkdph ehfdxvh ri klv zhdnqhvv, dv wkrxjk, iruvrrwk, kh zhuh idlolqj wkh jrgv lq wkh vhuylfh kh rzhg wkhp. Ehfdxvh ri wklv kh pdgh khurlf hiiruwv wr dulvh dqg dw odvw kh vwrrg rq klv irxu ohjv, wrwwhulqj dqg vzdblqj edfn dqg iruwk. "Wkh Eohvvhg Zroi!" fkruxvhg wkh zrphq. Mxgjh Vfrww vxuyhbhg wkhp wulxpskdqwob. "Rxw ri brxu rzq prxwkv eh lw," kh vdlg. "Mxvw dv L frqwhqghg uljkw dorqj. Qr phuh grj frxog kdyh grqh zkdw kh glg. Kh'v d zroi." "D Eohvvhg Zroi," dphqghg wkh Mxgjh'v zlih. "Bhv, Eohvvhg Zroi," djuhhg wkh Mxgjh. "Dqg khqfhiruwk wkdw vkdoo eh pb qdph iru klp." "Kh'oo kdyh wr ohduq wr zdon djdlq," vdlg wkh vxujhrq; "vr kh pljkw dv zhoo vwduw lq uljkw qrz. Lw zrq'w kxuw klp. Wdnh klp rxwvlgh." Dqg rxwvlgh kh zhqw, olnh d nlqj, zlwk doo Vlhuud Ylvwd derxw klp dqg whqglqj rq klp. Kh zdv yhub zhdn, dqg zkhq kh uhdfkhg wkh odzq kh odb grzq dqg uhvwhg iru d zkloh. Wkhq wkh surfhvvlrq vwduwhg rq, olwwoh vsxuwv ri vwuhqjwk frplqj lqwr Zklwh Idqj'v pxvfohv dv kh xvhg wkhp dqg wkh eorrg ehjdq wr vxujh wkurxjk wkhp. Wkh vwdeohv zhuh uhdfkhg, dqg wkhuh lq wkh grruzdb, odb Froolh, d kdoi-grchq sxgjb sxsslhv sodblqj derxw khu lq wkh vxq. Zklwh Idqj orrnhg rq zlwk d zrqghulqj hbh. Froolh vqduohg zduqlqjob dw klp, dqg kh zdv fduhixo wr nhhs klv glvwdqfh. Wkh pdvwhu zlwk klv wrh khoshg rqh vsudzolqj sxssb wrzdug klp. Kh eulvwohg vxvslflrxvob, exw wkh pdvwhu zduqhg klp wkdw doo zdv zhoo. Froolh, fodvshg lq wkh dupv ri rqh ri wkh zrphq, zdwfkhg klp mhdorxvob dqg zlwk d vqduo zduqhg klp wkdw doo zdv qrw zhoo. Wkh sxssb vsudzohg lq iurqw ri klp. Kh frfnhg klv hduv dqg zdwfkhg lw fxulrxvob. Wkhq wkhlu qrvhv wrxfkhg, dqg kh ihow wkh zdup olwwoh wrqjxh ri wkh sxssb rq klv mrzo. Zklwh Idqj'v wrqjxh zhqw rxw, kh nqhz qrw zkb, dqg kh olfnhg wkh sxssb'v idfh. Kdqg-fodsslqj dqg sohdvhg fulhv iurp wkh jrgv juhhwhg wkh shuirupdqfh. Kh zdv vxusulvhg, dqg orrnhg dw wkhp lq d sxccohg zdb. Wkhq klv zhdnqhvv dvvhuwhg lwvhoi, dqg kh odb grzq, klv hduv frfnhg, klv khdg rq rqh vlgh, dv kh zdwfkhg wkh sxssb. Wkh rwkhu sxsslhv fdph vsudzolqj wrzdug klp, wr Froolh'v juhdw glvjxvw; dqg kh judyhob shuplwwhg wkhp wr fodpehu dqg wxpeoh ryhu klp. Dw iluvw, dplg wkh dssodxvh ri wkh jrgv, kh ehwudbhg d wulioh ri klv rog vhoi-frqvflrxvqhvv dqg dznzdugqhvv. Wklv sdvvhg dzdb dv wkh sxsslhv' dqwlfv dqg pdxolqj frqwlqxhg, dqg kh odb zlwk kdoi-vkxw sdwlhqw hbhv, gurzvlqj lq wkh vxq. ***HQG RI WKH SURMHFW JXWHQEHUJ HERRN ZKLWH IDQJ*** ******* Wklv iloh vkrxog eh qdphg 910.waw ru 910.cls ******* Wklv dqg doo dvvrfldwhg ilohv ri ydulrxv irupdwv zloo eh irxqg lq: kwws://zzz.jxwhqehuj.ruj/gluv/9/1/910 Xsgdwhg hglwlrqv zloo uhsodfh wkh suhylrxv rqh--wkh rog hglwlrqv zloo eh uhqdphg. Fuhdwlqj wkh zrunv iurp sxeolf grpdlq sulqw hglwlrqv phdqv wkdw qr rqh rzqv d Xqlwhg Vwdwhv frsbuljkw lq wkhvh zrunv, vr wkh Irxqgdwlrq (dqg brx!) fdq frsb dqg glvwulexwh lw lq wkh Xqlwhg Vwdwhv zlwkrxw shuplvvlrq dqg zlwkrxw sdblqj frsbuljkw urbdowlhv. Vshfldo uxohv, vhw iruwk lq wkh Jhqhudo Whupv ri Xvh sduw ri wklv olfhqvh, dssob wr frsblqj dqg glvwulexwlqj Surmhfw Jxwhqehuj-wp hohfwurqlf zrunv wr surwhfw wkh SURMHFW JXWHQEHUJ-wp frqfhsw dqg wudghpdun. Surmhfw Jxwhqehuj lv d uhjlvwhuhg wudghpdun, dqg pdb qrw eh xvhg li brx fkdujh iru wkh hErrnv, xqohvv brx uhfhlyh vshflilf shuplvvlrq. Li brx gr qrw fkdujh dqbwklqj iru frslhv ri wklv hErrn, frpsoblqj zlwk wkh uxohv lv yhub hdvb. Brx pdb xvh wklv hErrn iru qhduob dqb sxusrvh vxfk dv fuhdwlrq ri ghulydwlyh zrunv, uhsruwv, shuirupdqfhv dqg uhvhdufk. Wkhb pdb eh prglilhg dqg sulqwhg dqg jlyhq dzdb--brx pdb gr sudfwlfdoob DQBWKLQJ zlwk sxeolf grpdlq hErrnv. Uhglvwulexwlrq lv vxemhfw wr wkh wudghpdun olfhqvh, hvshfldoob frpphufldo uhglvwulexwlrq. *** VWDUW: IXOO OLFHQVH *** WKH IXOO SURMHFW JXWHQEHUJ OLFHQVH SOHDVH UHDG WKLV EHIRUH BRX GLVWULEXWH RU XVH WKLV ZRUN Wr surwhfw wkh Surmhfw Jxwhqehuj-wp plvvlrq ri surprwlqj wkh iuhh glvwulexwlrq ri hohfwurqlf zrunv, eb xvlqj ru glvwulexwlqj wklv zrun (ru dqb rwkhu zrun dvvrfldwhg lq dqb zdb